src: 跟朋友聊起最近Meta大跌 26%，市值蒸发 2510 亿美元，扎克伯格回应「面临前所未有的竞争」，原因为何？
mt: Chatting with friends about the recent 26% plunge in Meta, a market valuation likely to fall by $251 billion, Zuckerberg responded that he "faced unprecedented competition". What's the reason?
ref: I talked to my friend about the recent 26% plunge in Meta and its loss of US $251 billion in market value; Zuckerberg responded that he was “facing unprecedented competition”; why?

src: Meta（原 Facebook）实质是一家广告公司，收入主要来自于广告，今时今日赚钱的广告公司，自己是有流量渠道的。
mt: Meta (formerly Facebook) is actually an advertising company, and it generates its income mainly from advertisements. Nowadays, advertising companies that make money have their own traffic channels.
ref: Meta (formerly Facebook) is essentially an advertising company, whose revenue mainly comes from advertising; the advertising company that makes money today has its own channel for traffic.

src: Facebook，Instagram，Whatsapp 等等，无论什么样的功能定位，都是 Meta 的流量渠道。
mt: Facebook, Instagram, Whatsapp, etc., no matter what functional positioning it is, are all traffic channels for Meta.
ref: Regardless of its function positioning, Facebook, Instagram, Whatsapp, etc. are all channels of traffic for Meta.

src: 不仅如此，Meta 还是最大的”广告联盟”,很多 App 外接 Meta 的广告，通过 Meta 的广告平台是实现变现。
mt: Not only that, Meta is also the biggest “advertising network”, and many apps are connected with Meta advertisements and realizing earnings through Meta's advertising platform.
ref: Not only that, Meta is also the biggest “advertisement alliance”; Many apps are externally connected to Meta’s advertising, and they achieve realization through Meta’s advertising platform.

src: 但是，时代变了。
mt: However, times have changed.
ref: But, the time has changed.

src: 第一，因为苹果隐私政策的调整，Meta 很难再拿到用户的数据信息，影响了广告投放的效率。
mt: First, due to adjustments of Apple’s privacy policies, it has become difficult for Meta to obtain information about users, which affects the efficiency of advertising.
ref: First, due to the adjustment of Apple’s privacy policy, it is difficult for Meta to get users’ data information now, which affects the efficiency of advertising.

src: 苹果现在的隐私政策对用户很友好，会很明显的提示用户是否允许 App 获取自己的信息，大多数人的正常反应肯定是不允许。
mt: Apples current privacy policies are very user-friendly and will clearly prompt users whether to allow apps to access their own information. The normal response of most people is definitely to not allow it.
ref: Apple’s current privacy policy is very user-friendly; it will use explicit prompt to ask users whether they allow apps to access their own information; most people’s normal reaction is definitely not to allow it.

src: 接下来如果 Google 再捅一刀，对 Meta 的收入影响还会更大。
mt: Next, if Google revs up again, the impact on Meta’s revenue will be even greater.
ref: If Google stabs again next, it will have a greater impact on Meta’s revenue.

src: 第二，以前 Meta 的收入增长里的中国因素也弱化了（这个因素的比重不确定有多高，但确实存在）。
mt: Second, the China factor in Meta's revenue growth has also weakened (the proportion of this factor is uncertain but it does exist).
ref: Second, the Chinese factor in Meta’s revenue growth has also been weakened (the proportion of this factor is uncertain, but it does exist).

src: 大家平时都知道 Meta 在中国是没有业务的，但是这个理解并不准确。
mt: Everyone usually knows that Meta does not have any business in China, but this understanding is not accurate.
ref: We all know that Meta doesn’t have business in China, but this understanding is not accurate.

src: 每年 Meta 至少10%的收入都来自中国，主要是中国做出海业务的公司贡献的。
mt: At least 10 percent of Meta’s revenue comes from China every year, mainly contributed by companies in China doing overseas business.
ref: At least 10% of Meta’s revenue comes from China every year, mainly contributed by Chinese companies engaged in offshore business.

src: Meta 在香港的办公室大概几百人，在大陆还有几大代理商。
mt: Meta has roughly a few hundred people in its offices in Hong Kong and several major agencies in the mainland.
ref: There are around hundreds of staff at its Hong Kong office and several major agents in the mainland.

src: 中国公司想要拓展海外市场，Meta 都是绕不过的广告渠道，烧的钱大多都给了 Meta。
mt: Meta is an inescapable advertising channel for Chinese companies that want to expand to overseas markets, and most of the money they burn goes to Meta.
ref: When Chinese companies want to expand overseas market, Meta is an advertising channel that cannot be bypassed, and so most of the money is given to Meta.

src: 有意思的是，现在字节的 TT 是 Meta 主要的竞争对手之一，但是前两年 Meta 从字节身上可赚到不少钱。
mt: Interestingly, Byte-based TT is now one of Meta's main competitors, but Meta made a lot of money from Byte in the past two years.
ref: Interestingly, the TT of ByteDance now is one of Meta’s main competitors, but Meta made a lot of money from ByteDance in the past two years.

src: 国内各个代理都在帮字节去 Meta 那里投广告，Meta 大中华区的业绩也很不错。
mt: All domestic agencies are helping Byte to advertise on Meta, and Meta’s performance in Greater China is also very good.
ref: All domestic agents are helping ByteDance to do advertising at Meta, and Meta’s performance in Greater China is also very good.

src: 最近我没有专门去了解，但是肯定不会比之前好。
mt: I have not been specifically looking into this recently, but it’s definitely not going to be any better than before.
ref: I haven’t specifically learned about it recently, but it’s definitely not better than before.

src: 中国公司在海外大规模烧钱的阶段已经过去了。
mt: The phase in which Chinese companies were burning cash overseas on a massive scale has ended.
ref: The stage when Chinese companies were burning money overseas on a large scale has passed.

src: 第三，新的流量渠道拓展不顺利。
mt: Thirdly, the expansion of new traffic channels has not been smooth.
ref: Third, the expansion of new traffic channels is not smooth.

src: Facebook 越来越老了，新的包括 TT 在内的平台，都不在 Meta 手中。
mt: Facebook is getting older and newer platforms, including TT, are not in Meta’s hands.
ref: Facebook is getting older, and new platforms including TT is not in the hands of Meta.

src: 最大的问题不仅仅是收入下滑，而是缺乏增长预期。
mt: The biggest problem is not just a decline in revenue but the lack of growth expectations.
ref: The biggest problem is not the decline of revenue but lack of growth expectation.

src: 资本市场不仅仅看中收入，更重要的是看未来的预期怎么样。
mt: The capital market not only cares about income, more importantly it looks at what the future is expected to look like.
ref: The capital market not only focuses on income; more importantly, it depends on future expectations.

src: 很显然，Meta 的预期是不够的。
mt: It is clear that Meta's expectations were insufficient.
ref: Obviously, the expectation for Meta is not enough.

src: 为了给市场讲出新的故事，扎克伯格讲了 “元宇宙”.
mt: In an attempt to tell new stories to the market, Zuckerberg spoke about the "metaverse."
ref: In order to tell new stories to the market, Zuckerberg told the story about “Meta-universe”.

src: 元宇宙确实应该是未来的方向之一，但是元宇宙的实现周期比较长，这个故事在这两三年应该不足以支撑起 Meta 的市值。
mt: The metaverse should indeed be one of the directions in the future, but the implementation cycle of the metaverse is relatively long, and this story should not be enough to support the market value of Meta within these two years.
ref: Meta-universe indeed should be one of the future directions, but the period of the realization of Meta-universe is long, and this story is not sufficient to support the market value of Meta.

src: 所以未来这两年，应该是 Meta 比较艰难的时期。
mt: So in the next two years, it should be a relatively difficult period for Meta.
ref: Therefore, the next two years should be a difficult time for Meta.

src: 别看脸书现在非常的风光，每年也有1,000亿到2,000亿美元的收入，实际上脸书现在危机感非常强，跟其他的互联网企业和高科技公司相比，没有什么好的安全的护城河。
mt: Despite its popularity, Facebook has revenue of US$100 billion to 200 billion a year, but Facebook has a huge sense of crisis now. Compared with other internet companies and high-tech companies, there is no safe moat.
ref: Although Facebook is very popular now with an annual income of US $100 billion to $200 billion; in fact, Facebook has a strong sense of crisis; compared with other Internet companies and high-tech companies, there is not any good security moat.

src: 虽然他的几款社交软件现在的日活比较高，也是主流的社交软件，比如Facebook，WhatsApp等等，但是面对tiktok的快速发展，脸书也没有什么信心，颠覆之间也就是眨眼的功夫。
mt: Although several of his social apps have relatively high daily activities and are also mainstream social apps, such as Facebook, WhatsApp, etc., Facebook still lacks confidence in the face of the rapid development of Tiktok. Any subversion is a blink of an eye.
ref: Although the DAU of several of his social software is relatively high, and they are mainstream social software such as Facebook, WhatsApp; however, in the face of the rapid development of TikTok, Facebook has little confidence, and subversion could happen in the blink of an eye.

src: 而搞元宇宙这个可望而不可及的概念，短时间之内完全没有成功的希望，因此脸书非常的危险，这也是为什么扎克伯格又是换公司的名字，又是不停的寻找新的赛道的根本原因，但是我觉得他的赛道选择是错的，是一条不归路 以上是我的一些思考，供参考。
mt: The limitless concept of the metaverse has no hopes of success in the short term and therefore Facebook is very dangerous. That is the reason why Zuckerberg has changed his company's name and is constantly searching for new tracks. However, I think his single choice of track is wrong and it is a road of no return. Above are my thoughts for reference.
ref: The unattainable concept of meta universe has no hope of success in a short time, so Facebook is in danger; this is also the fundamental reason why Zuckerberg changed the name of the company and kept looking for new tracks, but I think his choice is wrong and there is no way back; the above is some of my thoughts for reference.

src: 第十七条 国家对注册消防工程师资格实行注册执业管理制度。
mt: Article 17 The state implements the registration and practice management system for the qualifications of certified fire protection engineers.
ref: Article 17 The state implements the registration and practice management system for the qualification of certified Fire Engineers.

src: 取得一级、二级注册消防工程师资格证书的人员，经注册方可以相应级别注册消防工程师名义执业。
mt: Those who have obtained the certificates of qualification as a Class I and Class II certified fire engineer may practice in the name of registered fire engineer at the corresponding level.
ref: People who obtained the Level 1 and Level 2 qualification certificates of registered Fire Engineers can practice in the name of registered Fire Engineers of corresponding level.

src: 第十八条 公安部消防局是一级注册消防工程师资格的注册审批部门。
mt: Article 18 The Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security is the approval agency for registration of first-class certified fire engineer qualifications.
ref: Article 18 The Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security is the registration and approval department of the qualification of Level 1 registered Fire Engineer.

src: 省、自治区、直辖市公安机关消防机构为二级注册消防工程师资格的注册审批部门，并负责一级注册消防工程师资格注册的初步审查工作。
mt: Police agencies of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government are responsible for the registration and examination of qualifications for second-level certified fire-fighting engineers and conduct preliminary examinations for the qualification of first-level certified fire engineers.
ref: The fire departments of the public security organs of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government are the registration and approval departments for the qualification of Level 2 registered Fire Engineers, and are responsible for the preliminary review of the qualification of registration of Level 1 registered Fire Engineers.

src: 第十九条 取得一级、二级注册消防工程师资格证书并申请注册的人员，应当受聘于一个经批准的消防技术服务机构或者消防安全重点单位，并通过聘用单位向本单位所在地(聘用单位属企业的，通过本企业向工商注册所在地)的公安机关消防机构提交注册申请材料。
mt: Article 19 Anyone who has obtained certificate of first- or second-level registered fire engineer qualifications and applies for registration shall be employed by an approved fire-fighting technical service organization or key fire safety unit.
ref: Article 19 A person who has obtained the qualification certificate of Level 1 and Level 2 registered Fire Engineer and applies for registration shall be employed by an approved fire protection technical service institution or key fire safety unit, and the employer shall submit registration application materials to the fire protection institution of the public security organ in the place where the employer is located (if the employer is an enterprise, it shall be submitted to the place where the industrial and commercial registration is located).

src: 第二十条 省、自治区、直辖市公安机关消防机构在收到申请人的注册申请材料后，对申请材料不齐全或者不符合法定形式的，应当当场或者在5个工作日内，一次 性告知申请人需要补正的全部内容，逾期不告知的，自收到申请材料之日起即为受理。
mt: Article 20 When registration application materials of a province, autonomous region or municipality directly under the Central Government are received, if the application materials are not complete nor in legal form, the department will inform the applicant on the spot or within 5 working days of just about all the contents requiring a correction.
ref: Article 20 After receiving the registration application materials of the applicant, the fire protection institutions of the public security organs of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the central government shall inform the applicant of all the contents that need to be supplemented and corrected all at once on the spot or within 5 working days if the application materials are incomplete or do not conform to the legal form; if they fail to inform within the time limit, they will be accepted from the date of receiving the application materials.

src: 对受理或者不予受理的注册申请，均应当出具加盖本级公安机关消防机构专用印章和注明日期的书面凭证。
mt: For registration applications that are accepted or rejected, a written certificate stamped with the special seal of the fire department at the local public security organ and dated shall be provided.
ref: For the registration applications that are accepted or rejected, a written certificate stamped with the special seal of the fire protection institution of the public security organ at the same level and date shall be issued.

src: 第二十一条 省、自治区、直辖市公安机关消防机构自受理注册申请之日起20个工作日内，按规定条件和程序完成一级注册消防工程师资格注册申请材料的初步审查工作和二级注册消防工程师资格的注册审批工作，并将一级注册消防工程师资格注册申请材料和初步审查意见报公安部消防局审批。
mt: Article 21 The fire department according to the required conditions and procedures shall complete the preliminary review of the registration application materials for the qualification of a first-class registered fire engineer and the registration approval of the second-level registered fire engineer qualification, and submit the registration application materials and preliminary examination comments to the fire department of the Ministry of Public Security for approval within 20 working days after receiving the registration application.
ref: Article 21 The fire protection institutions of the public security organs of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the central government shall, within 20 working days after the date of accepting the registration application, complete the preliminary review of the application materials for the registration of the Level 1 registered Fire Engineer qualification and the registration and approval of the Level 2 registered Fire Engineer qualification according to the specified conditions and procedures, and submit the application materials for the registration of the Level 1 registered Fire Engineer qualification and the preliminary review opinions to the Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security for approval.

src: 公安部消防局应当自收到省级公安机关消防机构报送的申请材料和初步审查意见之日起，20个工作日内作出是否批准的决定。
mt: The fire department under the Ministry of Public Security shall make a decision on approval or not within 20 working days upon receipt of the application materials and initial examination opinions submitted by the fire protection agencies of the provincial public security authority.
ref: The Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security shall make a decision on whether to approve or not within 20 working days from the date of receiving the application materials and preliminary review opinions submitted by the Fire Department of the provincial public security organ.

src: 在规定的期限内不能作出批准决定的，应当将延长的期限和理由告知申请人。
mt: If an approval decision cannot be made within the prescribed time limit, the applicant shall be notified of the extended time limit and its reasons.
ref: If the approval decision cannot be made within the prescribed time limit, the applicant shall be informed of the extended time limit and the reason.

src: 对作出不予批准决定的，应当书面说明理由，并告知申请人享有依法申请行政复议或者提起行政诉讼的权利。
mt: If a non-approval decision is made, the reasons shall be explained in writing and the applicant shall be informed of the right to apply for administrative reconsideration or file an administrative lawsuit in accordance with the law.
ref: If the decision of disapproval is made, the reasons shall be explained in writing, and the applicant shall be informed of the right to apply for administrative reconsideration or file an administrative lawsuit according to law.

src: 第二十二条 注册审批部门应当自作出批准决定之日起10个工作日内，颁发、送达相应级别的注册证。
mt: Article 22. Registration approval agencies shall issue and deliver a registration certificate of corresponding level within ten working days after the approval decision is made.
ref: Article 22 The registration review and approval department shall issue and deliver the registration certificate of the corresponding level within 10 working days from the date of making the approval decision.

src: 第二十三条 注册证的每一注册有效期为3年。
mt: Article 23. The period of validity for each registration of the certificate is three years.
ref: Article 23 The period of validity is 3 years for each registration period of the registration certificate.

src: 注册证在有效期内是相应级别注册消防工程师的执业凭证，由注册消防工程师本人保管、使用。
mt: The registration certificate is the certification of practice of a registered fire engineer at the corresponding level during its validity period, and it is kept and used by the registered fire engineer.
ref: The registration certificate is the practicing certificate of the registered Fire Engineer of the corresponding level within the period of validity, which is kept and used by the registered Fire Engineer themselves.

src: 第二十四条 申请初始注册的，应当自取得一级、二级注册消防工程师资格证书之日起1年内提出申请。
mt: Article 24 Those who apply for initial registration shall submit the application within one year from the date when they obtain the qualification certificates of first and second class registered fire safety engineers.
ref: Article 24 Initial registration shall be applied within 1 year from the date of obtaining the qualification certificate of Level 1 and Level 2 registered Fire Engineer.

src: 逾期申请初始注册时，须符合本规定继续教育要求。
mt: Those who apply for initial registration after the deadline must be in compliance with the continuing education requirements of this regulation.
ref: When applying for initial registration beyond the time limit, it must meet the requirements on continuing education in this Regulation.

src: 初始注册、延续注册、变更注册、注销注册和不予注册等注册管理的具体办法，由公安部另行规定。
mt: Specific procedures for registration management such as initial registration, continuation of registration, modification of registration, cancellation of registration and non-registration shall be separately prescribed by the Ministry of Public Security.
ref: The specific measures for registration administration of initial registration, continuation of registration, change of registration, cancellation of registration and not-approved registration shall be separately formulated by the Ministry of Public Security.

src: 第二十五条 继续教育是注册消防工程师延续注册、重新注册和逾期初始注册的必备条件。
mt: Article 25: Continuing education is the necessary condition for the renewal of registration, re-registration and overdue initial registration of certified fire engineers.
ref: Article 25 Continuation of Education is a necessary condition for the continuation of registration, re-registration and overdue initial registration of registered Fire Engineers.

src: 在每个注册有效期内，各级别注册消防工程师应当按照规定完成相应的继续教育。
mt: During the validity period of each registration, certified fire engineers at all levels shall complete corresponding continuing education in accordance with regulations.
ref: Within the period of validity of each registration, registered Fire Engineer of different levels shall complete the corresponding continuation of education according to the regulations.

src: 第二十六条 注册审批部门应当及时向社会公告注册消防工程师注册有关情况，建立注册消防工程师诚信档案，对其执业活动实行信用管理。
mt: Article 26 The registration approval department shall promptly announce to the public the registration information of registered fire engineers, establish integrity files for certified fire engineers, and implement credit management for their practice activities.
ref: Article 26 The registration review and approval department shall timely announce the registration of registered Fire Engineers to the public, establish the integrity archives of registered Fire Engineers, and implement credit management on their practices.

src: 第二十七条 各级注册消防工程师资格的注册管理部门，应当严格执行《中华人民共和国行政许可法》有关规定。
mt: Article 27 The administrative departments for registration of registered fire protection engineers at all levels shall strictly implement relevant provisions of the "Administrative License Law of the People's Republic of China".
ref: Article 27 The registration administration departments for the qualification of registered Fire Engineers at all levels shall strictly implement the relevant provisions of the Administrative License Law of the people’s Republic of China.

src: 今日的考试资讯分享到此为止，希望能给大家一些帮助。
mt: Today's exam information sharing ends here, and I hope it can provide some help to you.
ref: This is the end of the sharing of today’s examination information; I hope this will be helpful to you.

src: 大家一定要努力备考，争取早日通过消防工程师考试！
mt: Everyone must work hard to prepare and try to pass the fire engineer exam as soon as possible!
ref: Everyone, please work hard on this and hopefully you will pass the Fire Engineer examination soon!

src: 实时分享金融/财会/建筑最新考试资讯。
mt: Shares the latest information about exams in finance/accounting/architecture in real time
ref: Real time sharing of the latest examination information of Finance/ Accounting/Architecture.

src: 先说结论，我个人认为《四海》是一部全方位的烂片，从各种意义上来说都是。
mt: First of all, I personally think Four Seas is an all-round bad movie, in all senses.
ref: I will say my conclusion first; I think Only Fools Rush In is utterly a terrible film in any sense.

src: 但你要说这部电影是不是一个亮点也没有，那倒也不是至少配乐选的挺好。
mt: But if the movie doesn't have any highlights, it's not at least a good match.
ref: But it is not without any highlight; at least the music is good.

src: 烂片分很多种，让你能在电影院里酣然入睡的算一种，让你看完后义愤填膺的也算一种，《四海》对观众来说就像是峨眉山上的猴子，它能用无数种方式来点燃你的怒火。
mt: There are many kinds of bad movies, including those that make you sleep soundly in the cinema and those that make you feel indignant after watching. The Four Seas is like a monkey on Mount Emei to the audience, which can ignite your anger in countless ways.
ref: There are many types of terrible films; some make you sleep soundly in the cinema, some make you angry after watching it; Only Fools Rush In is like monkeys on Mount Emei; it can ignite your anger in countless ways.

src: 在侮辱观众这点上，韩寒真的是天赋绝伦。
mt: In insulting the audience, Han Han was really talented.
ref: Han Han is super talented in insulting the audience.

src: 这部片子最让人感到痛苦的就是它仿佛是克系小说里的造物，难以名状，漏洞多的就像是小马哥身上的风衣。
mt: The most painful part of this film is that it seems to be a creation in a novel, hard to name, with many loopholes like a windbreaker suited on brother Ma.
ref: The most painful part of the film is that it is hard to describe like a monster in Cthulhu novels, and has as many loopholes as the holes on the trench coat on Javier Mascherano.

src: 甚至看完后你会怀疑这里面是否有导演暗含的隐喻，但当你仔细思考之后发现它其实就是一坨屎。
mt: You may even wonder if there is any metaphor implied by the director, but when you think about it carefully, it is actually a piece of shit.
ref: After watching it, you may even wonder if there is metaphors the director planted in it; but you will find that it is only a piece of shit after close examination.

src: 先简单的说下我很难理解的一些情节。
mt: Let's start with some of the things that I can't understand.
ref: I’ll first briefly talk about some plots that are hard to understand.

src: 男主居住地应该是偏南方的某个小岛上，和他的奶奶相依为命。
mt: The hero should live on an island in the south and live with his grandmother.
ref: The male leading role lives with his grandma on some island in the south.

src: 她奶奶有个愿望是想看下雪，然后剧情就安排邻里中的一个大爷开着小面包车送她去东北看雪。
mt: Her grandmother had a wish to see the snow, and then the plot arranged an old man in the neighborhood to drive her to the northeast to see the snow.
ref: His grandma has a wish, watching the snow, and the a old male neighbor drove a minibus to take her to watch the snow in the Northeast.

src: 高龄老人坐着面包车从南方到东北看雪？？
mt: The elderly in a van see the snow from south to northeast?
ref: An elderly goes to watch the snow in the northeast from the south in a minibus? ?

src: 他和他爹对此还非常放心。
mt: He and his father were very relieved about it.
ref: He and his father were okay with it.

src: 然后这位老人就没下文了。
mt: And then there was no story about the old man.
ref: And then there is no follow-up on this old lady.

src: 在废弃轮船上开酒店，女主他哥怎么拿到营业执照的？
mt: How did the heroine and her brother get a business license to open a hotel on an abandoned ship?
ref: Opening a hotel on an abandoned ship; how does the brother of the female leading role get the license?

src: 岛上飞车党小混混为什么能轻轻松松就把一段山路做到封路？？
mt: Why can the gangsters on the island easily lockdown a mountain road??
ref: How do the racing bike gang on the island easily block a mountain road? ?

src: 然后路中间送钢筋的卡车就停在路边，四周连卡车司机都找不到。
mt: Then the truck that sent the rebar in the middle of the road stopped at the side of the road, and there was no truck driver around.
ref: Then the truck delivering steel bars in the middle of the road just stopped at the roadside, and the truck driver was nowhere to be found.

src: 这道具感也太明显了吧。
mt: This is so obvious.
ref: They are obviously props.

src: 一个征信不行的且有违法嫌疑的小混混飞车党为什么会成为一名辅警？
mt: Why would a gangster with bad credit and suspicion of illegality become an auxiliary policeman?
ref: Why could a little gangster biker with poor credit and who was suspected of breaking the law become an auxiliary policeman?

src: 面对高利贷为啥不报警，电影里警察还特地问了是否有难处？
mt: Why don't you call the police in the face of usurious loans, and the police in the movie also asked if he got some problems?
ref: Why didn’t he call the police when there was usury involved, and the police specifically asked if there was any problem.

src: 一个成年人懂得用智能手机，却不知道在旅馆如何用房卡开门，然后强行安排找不到旅馆老板，坐在房间门外睡一宿？
mt: An adult knows how to use a smartphone, but he doesn't know how to open the door with a room card in a hotel. Then he was required that he couldn't find the hotel owner and sat outside the room door and slept for a whole night.
ref: An adult who knows how to use smart phone doesn’t know how to use the card to open the door at the hotel, and it was forcefully arranged for him not being able to find the owner of the hotel and so he slept outside the hotel for the night?

src: 这种莫名其妙的情节充斥在整个影片里，由于情节过于离谱以至于我回忆它们时都会令我感到痛苦。
mt: This inexplicable plot fills the film, because the plot is so outrageous that I can recall them in pain.
ref: Such ridiculous plots were everywhere in the film; the plots are so ridiculous that I feel painful when I remember them.

src: 除了情节外，更糟糕的是电影的主旨，或者说这电影根本没有主旨，就是一个面目可憎的缝合怪。
mt: In addition to the plot, what's worse is the theme of the film, or the fact that the film has no theme at all, is an abominable stitch.
ref: In addition to the plots, the theme of the film is even more terrible, or you can say there is no theme in the film; it’s just a horrible monster that is stitched together.

src: 影片开头你会以为他想拍个喜剧片，20多分钟后你猜它也许是个励志片，看一半时你觉得它可能是个想体现小镇青年生存不易的剧情片，看完后你就压根也不知道自己究竟看了个啥，随之而来的是对自己深深的怀疑，大过年的为什么要跑到电影院去欣赏大便。
mt: At the beginning of the film, you will think that he wants to make a comedy. More than 20 minutes later, you guess it may be an inspirational film. When you watch it halfway, you think it may be a feature film that wants to reflect the survival of the young people in the town. After watching it, you don't know what you have seen at all, and then you have deep doubts about yourself. Why do you go to the cinema to enjoy such a piece of shit during the Spring Festival?
ref: In the beginning of the film, you may think he wants to make a comedy; after twenty minutes, you may guess it’s an inspiration film; after a half of it, you may think it’s a drama showcasing the hardship of a small town boy; after you watch all of it, you don’t even know what you have watched; what follows is deep doubt in yourself; why would you go to the cinema to watch a piece of shit during the Spring Festival?

src: 对于大部分人来说其实也都非常熟悉各类电影的套路了，比如你要想拍摩托车手，那就励志＋喜剧然后告诉观众一个有天赋的菜鸟是如何一步步走向成功的。
mt: For most people, they are also very familiar with the routines of various movies. For example, if you want to make a motorcycle rider, you can tell the audience how a talented rookie can succeed step by step.
ref: Most people are familiar with the routines of various films; for example, if you want to make a film about a biker, then make it an inspiration + comedy to tell the audience how a talented rookie achieves success step by step.

src: 如果你想拍爱情片，那你就老老实实讲喜欢骑摩托的小镇青年和服务员妹子之间的恩怨纠葛。
mt: If you want to make a romantic movie, tell the truth about the stories between a young man who like to ride motorcycles and a waitresses .
ref: If you want to make a love film, just tell the story about a small town boy who loves to ride motorcycle and a girl who works as a waitress.

src: 如果你想反映现实，那最起码你的情节不能出现和正常世界相悖的东西。
mt: If you want to reflect reality, then at the very least your plot should not contain things which are contrary to the normal world.
ref: If you want to reflect reality, then the plot should not have anything that is contradictory to the normal world.

src: （比如尹正演的那个新摩托刚被烧了，然后还能唱歌的角色），就不能去开一些连肯尼迪看了都遭不住的脑洞。
mt: (For example, Yin Zhengyan's new motorcycle has just been burned and can still sing), so you can't open some brains that even Kennedy can't bear to see.
ref: (Such as the character played by Yin Zheng who sang after his new motorcycle was just burned ) please don’t think about ideas that are ridiculous.

src: 至于女主明明不是弱智可在某些方面表现的就像个5岁小孩，我真不知道这是演技的原因还是导演的要求。
mt: As for the fact that the heroine is not mentally disabled but acts like a 5-year-old child in some ways, I really don't know whether it is the reason for acting or the director's request.
ref: As for why the female leading role acts like a five-year-old child when she is not retarded at all, I really don’t know if there is problem with her acting or it was demanded by the director.

src: 还有一点我也挺想不明白，韩寒作为一个赛车手为什么这么热衷于在他自己的电影里添加撞车情节？
mt: I wonder why Han Han, as a racing driver, is so keen on adding a crash plot to his own movie.
ref: And one more thing I don’t understand is why Han Han as a racer is so keen on adding the plot of car crash in his films?

src: 这样的电影安排在春节档里，难道是为了给观众添堵吗？
mt: Is such a movie arranged in the Spring Festival to add to the audience?
ref: Is such a film being arranged in the Spring Festival season to humiliate the audience?

src: 感谢今天的支持者，80盒全部送出去了！
mt: Thanks to today's supporters, all 80 boxes have been sent out!
ref: Thank you to all the supporters today; all 80 boxes have been given out!

src: 美容养颜汤的材料：
mt: Materials of beauty soup:
ref: Ingredients of beauty soup:

src: 白木耳的作用：味甘、性平，归肺、胃、肾经；有强精、补肾、润肠、益胃、补气、和血、强心、滋阴、润肺、生津、壮身、补脑、提神、美容、嫩肤、延年益寿之功效；用于治肺热咳嗽、肺燥干咳、妇女月经不调、胃炎、大便秘结等病症；对阴虚火旺不受参茸等温热滋补的病人是一种良好的补品
mt: Functions of white agaric: sweet taste, flat nature, tropism to lung, stomach and kidney meridians; it has the effects of strengthening essence, tonifying kidney, moistening intestine, tonifying stomach, tonifying qi, harmonizing blood, strengthening heart, nourishing Yin, moistening lung, generating fluid, strengthening body, tonifying brain, refreshing mind, cosmetic, rejuvenating skin, prolonging life; it is used to treat lung heat cough, lung dryness dry cough, women's irregular menstruation, gastritis, constipation and other diseases; it is a good tonic for patients with Yin deficiency and excessive fire without warmth and nourishing such as ginseng matsutake.
ref: Functions of tremella: sweet in taste and neutral in nature, belong to channels of lung, stomach and kidney, have the effects of strengthening sperm, tonifying kidney, moistening intestine, nourishing stomach, tonifying vitality and blood, strengthening heart, nourishing yin, moistening lungs, promoting secretion, strengthening body, tonifying brain, refreshing beauty, tendering skin and prolonging life; it is used for treatment of diseases such as lung-heat type cough, dry-lung cough, menstrual irregularity of women, gastritis and constipation; it is a good tonic for patients with excessive heat and yin deficiency but are not suitable for warm tonic such as ginseng and velvet antler.

src: 桃胶的作用：味苦，性平，归大肠，膀胱经。
mt: Functions of peach gum: bitter taste, flat nature, large intestine, bladder channel.
ref: Functions of peach glue: bitter in taste, mild in nature, belong to the large intestine and bladder channels.

src: 功效：和血，通淋，止痢，止痛，也可以补水，润肠，如果有便秘的人，可以多吃桃胶。
mt: Efficacy: Harmonize blood, dredge stranguria, relieve dysentery, relieve pain, also can replenish water, moisten intestines. If someone has constipation, he can eat more peach gum.
ref: Effects: tonify blood, dredge lymph, stop dysentery and pain, replenish water, moisten intestines; people with constipation can eat more peach glue.

src: 枸杞子的作用：性平，味甘，归肝，胃经。
mt: Functions of Fructus Lycii: flat nature, sweet taste, tropism to liver and stomach meridian.
ref: Effect of fruits of Chinese wolfberries: neutral in nature and sweet in taste, belonging to the channels of liver and stomach.

src: 益肝明目，滋补肝肾，美白养颜，补虚生津，延缓衰老。
mt: Tonifying liver and improving eyesight, nourishing liver and kidney, whitening and nourishing skin, tonifying deficiency and promoting fluid production, and delaying aging.
ref: Nourish the liver and the eyes, tonify the liver and the kidney, whiten and nourish the skin, nourish deficiency, produce secretion and delay aging.

src: 红枣的作用：味甘，性平，归脾，胃经，有补脾和胃，益气生津养血安神，如果脾胃虚弱，气血不足失眠者可以多服用红枣。
mt: Functions of red dates: sweet taste, flat nature, tropism to the spleen, stomach meridian, tonifying the spleen and harmonizing the stomach, tonifying qi, generating fluid, nourishing blood and tranquilizing the nerves. If the spleen and stomach are weak and the qi and blood are insufficient, patients with insomnia can take more red dates.
ref: Functions of red dates: sweet in taste, calm in nature, return to the spleen, go through stomach channel, tonify the spleen and stomach, replenish qi, generate fluid, nourish blood and calm nerves; people whose spleen and stomach are weak, whose Qi and blood are insufficient, and who suffer from insomnia can eat more red dates.

src: 龙眼肉的作用：味甘性温，归心,脾经，适用于心脾两虚者。
mt: Function of longan: sweet and warm, tropism to heart, spleen channel, suitable for both heart and spleen deficiency.
ref: Functions of arillus gongan: sweet in taste, warm in nature, return to the heart, spleen channel, suitable for those with deficiency of both heart and spleen.

src: 龙眼肉还能润肤美容，养血安神,,补益心脾，壮阳益气，贫血的人也适合服用，失眠者也适合。
mt: Longan can also moisturize skin and beautify your appearance, nourish blood and tranquilize the mind, tonify the heart and spleen, strengthen yang and replenish qi. Anemia is also suitable for people, and is also suitable for those who have insomnia.
ref: Arillus gongan can also moisturize and beautify the skin, nourish blood and calm the nerves, tonify the heart and spleen, invigorate Yang and Qi, and is also suitable for people with anemia and insomnia.

src: 莲子的作用：味甘涩，性平，归心，脾，肾经。
mt: Function of lotus seeds: sweet taste, flat nature, heart, spleen, kidney channel.
ref: Functions of lotus seeds: sweet and astringent in taste, flat in nature, return to heart, spleen and kidney channels.

src: 养心安神，心悸失眠，胃虚，健忘，心烦口渴，滋养补虚，止遗涩精。
mt: Nourishing the heart and tranquilizing the mind, palpitation and insomnia, stomach deficiency, forgetfulness, upset and thirst, nourishing and tonifying deficiency, stopping astringency.
ref: Nourish the heart and calm the nerves, treat palpitations, insomnia, stomach deficiency, forgetfulness, vexation and thirstiness, nourish and replenish deficiency, and prevent spermatorrhea and premature ejaculation.

src: 因此，这个养颜美容汤不仅是一道甜品，而且还可以养生！
mt: Therefore, this beauty soup is not only a dessert, but also help people keep healthy!
ref: Therefore, this beauty soup is not only a dessert, but also helps you stay healthy!

src: 多吃，能使您心神安康！
mt: Eating more can make you feel well!
ref: Eating more can make you healthy both physically and mentally!

src: 而且又不会像燕窝那么贵，多吃不会使你口袋破大洞！
mt: And not as expensive as bird's nest, eating too much won't let you bankrupt!
ref: Plus, it won't be as expensive as bird’s nest, so eating a lot will not make you spend a lot!

src: 想尝试一下网球，但又怕自己坚持不下去，所以想先找个差不多的价格练手 。
mt: I want to try tennis, but I'm afraid I can't hold on, so I want to find a similar price first.
ref: I wanted to try tennis, but I was afraid I couldn’t stick with it, so I thought I would just find one at a suitable price to practice with.

src: 不友好，事实上，价格往往与友好程度成正比，如果不能分辨，那么贵的正常情况会比便宜的拍子友好，这类“入门拍”其实是工业垃圾。
mt: Unfriendly, in fact, the price is often proportional to the degree of friendliness. If it cannot be distinguished, the expensive normal situation will be more friendly than cheap beats. This kind of "primary racket" is actually industrial waste.
ref: It was not friendly; in fact, the price is usually in proportional to the degree of friendliness; if you are not able to distinguish, then expensive ones usually are more friendly than cheaper ones, and the so called “entry-level” rackets are in fact industrial garbage.

src: 它们强度很低，球打到拍子上面，振动非常大，硬球顶不住，高手都很难驾驭。
mt: They are at a very low-intensity, when the ball hits the racket, the vibration is very large, the hard ball cannot resist, even a master player will find it difficult to control.
ref: They are low in strength, and there will be too much vibration when the ball hits on it; it cannot withstand hard balls, and even professional cannot handle it.

src: 它们存在的逻辑和潜台词是———网球这么难，知道你们学不会，也知道你们不舍得买贵的，搞个便宜货糊弄你们，你们玩儿两次，就不会再打了，这样这个拍子便宜，你也不心疼。
mt: The logic and subtext of their existence is --- Tennis is so hard, knowing that you can't learn it, and knowing that you don't want to buy expensive, you can't play twice, and you won't play again, so this racket is cheap, and you don't care.
ref: The logic and subtext of their existence is that tennis is so difficult, we know you can’t learn to play it, and we know you're not willing to buy expensive ones, so we make a cheap one to fool you; you won't play it again after using it once or twice; since the racket is cheap, you don't feel it's a waste.

src: 等你真的能分辨好坏，说明你进步了，到时候再来我这里买贵的，我赚两次钱。
mt: When you can really tell good from bad, it means that you have improved, and then come to me to buy expensive, I make money twice.
ref: If you can tell the difference, it means you have made improvement; then you can come here to buy the expensive ones and I will make money twice.

src: 建议花相似的价钱，买个二手好一点的球拍，选择prince、或者邓禄普的，这两个品牌足够没名气，所以好球拍也卖不上价钱，新拍500、600就很好了，二手的200块，拥有千元拍的享受不香吗？
mt: It is recommended to buy a second-hand better racket at a similar price, such as prince or Deng Lupu. The two brands are not famous enough, so good rackets cannot be sold at a high price. New rackets of RMB 500 and RMB 600 are good, while second-hand rackets of RMB 200 are not. Isn't it good to have a racket of RMB 1,000?
ref: I recommend you to spend the same amount of money on a better-quality second hand racket such as prince or DUNLOP; these two brands are not famous, and so even if they are good, they are not expensive; you can get a new one with 500 or 600 yuan and a second hand one with 200 yuan; isn’t it nice to have a thousand yuan racket with only so little money?

src: 对新手挺友好，但一过了新手阶段就鸡肋了，但大部分人，特别是女生，过不了新手阶段。
mt: It's friendly to novices, but it's hard to pass the novice stage, but most people, especially girls, can't pass the novice stage.
ref: It’s friendly to newbies, but once you passed that stage, it will become not so useful; but most people, especially girls, cannot pass the newbie stage.

src: 第十八届“世界饮料创新奖”（World Beverage Innovation Awards）是FoodBev Media与德国纽伦堡国际啤酒、酿酒及饮料工业展览会（Brau Beviale）联合举办的奖项。
mt: The 18th World Beverage Innovation Awards is a joint initiative of FoodBev Media and the Brau Beviale in Nuremberg, Germany.
ref: The 18th “World Beverage Innovation Awards” is an award jointly held by FoodBev Media and Brau Beviale.

src: 吸引了来自25个国家、22个不同品类的279个作品参赛。
mt: It attracted 279 works from 25 countries with 22 different categories.
ref: It attracted 279 works from 25 countries and 22 categories to participate in the competition.

src: 10月15日，决赛入围者名单公布，最终获奖者名单将于11月11日（英国夏令时）线上公布。
mt: On October 15, the finalists will be announced online on November 11 (United Kingdom Daylight Time).
ref: On October 15th, the list of the finalists was published, and the final list of winners will be published online on November 11 (BST).

src: 我们看到，元气森林的LP28无糖酸奶入围最佳乳饮料奖，伊利安慕希的“GOGO武汉”营销入围最佳营销活动，百事可乐和人民日报新媒体合作的包装还入围最佳包装设计/标签奖。
mt: We can see that Genki Forest's LP28 sugar-free yogurt was shortlisted for the Best Dairy Drink Award, Illian Mosch's "GOGO Wuhan" marketing was shortlisted for the Best Marketing Activity, and the packaging jointly developed by Pepsi and People's Daily New Media was also shortlisted for the Best Packaging Design/Label Award.
ref: We have seen that Genki Forest’s LP28 sugar-free yoghurt was shortlisted for the Award of Best Milk Drink; the marketing of “GOGO Wuhan” of Yili AMBROSIAL was shortlisted for the Award of Best Marketing Activity; the packaging jointly designed by Pepsi and the new media of People’s Daily was shortlisted for the Award of Best Packaging Design/Label.

src: FoodBev Media高级市场营销总监Laura Nettle表示：我们很高兴与Brau Beviale一起庆祝年度世界饮料创新奖的第18年。
mt: Laura Nettle, Senior Marketing Director at FoodBev Media, said that we are pleased to celebrate the 18th year of the annual World Beverage Innovation Awards with Brau Beviale.
ref: Laura Nettle, senior marketing director of Foodbev Media, said, “we are pleased to celebrate the 18th year of the annual world beverage innovation award with Brau beviale”.

src: 从新口味、新概念和新功能到品牌、包装和制造，随着行业不断以更可持续的方式进行创新，我们看到了饮料行业的趋势。
mt: From new tastes, new concepts and new features to branding, packaging and manufacturing, we see trends in the beverage industry as the industry continues to innovate in a more sustainable way.
ref: From new tastes, new concepts, new functions to brands, packaging and manufacturing, as the industry continues to innovate in a more sustainable way, we have seen the trends of the beverage industry.

src: 世界饮料创新奖表彰了全球饮料行业新老品牌今年最具雄心的新产品和新发展。
mt: The World Beverage Innovation Award recognizes the most ambitious new products and developments of new and old brands in the global beverage industry this year.
ref: The world beverage innovation award recognizes the most ambitious new products and developments of new and old brands in the global beverage industry this year.

src: 以下是每个类别的决赛入围者的完整榜单。
mt: The following is the full list of finalists for each category.
ref: Here is the complete list of all the finalists of each category.

src: Ardagh Group开发的技术，可以将100％的回收玻璃重新熔化成新的瓶子。
mt: The technology developed by Ardagh Group can remelt 100% of the recycled glass into new bottles.
ref: Technology developed by Ardagh Group can melt 100% of recycled glass into new bottles.

src: 箱中袋装水，其包装盒采用100％可回收利用，可减少包装66％，减少碳排放97％。
mt: The packaging box of bagged water in the box is 100% recyclable, which can reduce packaging by 66% and carbon emissions by 97%.
ref: The packaging of the bagged water in the box is 100% recyclable, which can reduce packaging by 66% and carbon emission by 97%.

src: LatCub是100％可生物降解，使用更少的纸，并且不使用对环境有害的胶水或胶带。
mt: LatCub is 100% biodegradable, with less paper usage, and does not use glue or tape that is harmful to the environment.
ref: Latcub is 100% biodegradable; it uses less paper, and does not use glue or tape that is harmful to the environment.

src: Ardagh Group开发的技术，可以将100％的回收玻璃重新熔化制成新的瓶子。
mt: The technology developed by Ardagh Group can remelt 100% of the recycled glass into new bottles.
ref: Technology developed by Ardagh Group can melt 100% of recycled glass and make them into new bottles.

src: 最终获奖名单将于11月11日（英国夏令时）在FoodBev Media的 YouTube频道公布，FBIF将持续为您报道，敬请期待！
mt: The final winners will be announced on FoodBev Media's YouTube channel on November 11 (United Kingdom Daylight Time), and FBIF will continue to report for you. Please stay focused!
ref: The final list of the winners will be published on the YouTube channel of FoodBev Media on November 11 (BTS), and FBIF will continue to report for you, so stay tuned!

src: 2021年什么最火？
mt: What was the hottest in 2021?
ref: What is the hottest thing in 2021?

src: 无疑是东京奥运会。
mt: It's definitely the Tokyo Olympics.
ref: It was none other than the Tokyo Olympics.

src: 您以为只有奥运健儿才能拿奖吗？
mt: Do you think only Olympic athletes can win the prize?
ref: Do you think only Olympic athletes can win awards?

src: 前段时间有篇《快看！项目经理可冲击金牌的奥运项目》文章很火，里面提到项目经理们在很多项目上，绝对是可以一马当先，无人能匹： 搬砖、出差、熬夜是项目经理的日常，救火、背锅、道歉更是不在话下。
mt: Some time ago, there was an article named "Look! "Project Managers Can Attack Gold Medal Olympic Projects" is a very popular article, which mentions that project managers can definitely take the lead in many projects, and no one can compete with them: It is the daily routine of project managers to move bricks, go on business trips and stay up late, and it is even more difficult for them to fight fire, carry on business and apologize.
ref: Recently, there is an article titled Look! An article titled Olympic Disciplines in Which Project Managers Can Win Gold Medals was viral, and it mentioned that project managers can be the foremost and unmatched in many disciplines, such as working arduously, going on business trips, and staying up late, the everyday work of project manager, and handling emergency, taking the blame and apologizing are nothing difficult at all.

src: 看似玩笑调侃的一篇文章，却也道出了项目经理们的日常辛酸，背后代表的是对当前项目管理工作的力不从心。
mt: An article that seems to be joking also shows the daily sorrows of project managers, which means that they are unable to do the current project management work.
ref: A seemingly joking article also tells the bitterness of their daily work, and the hidden message is their insufficient energy to handle the current project management work.

src: 而从事项目管理工作的人员，也渐渐选择通过一些行动来让自己摆脱工作中的困境。
mt: And the personnel engaged in project management gradually choose to take some actions to get themselves out of the dilemma of work.
ref: People engaged in project management also gradually choose to get rid of the predicament in work by taking certain actions.

src: 从每年攀升的PMP（国际认证的项目管理专业人士资格）报名人数来看，越来越多的项目管理从业人员通过学习来提升自己的项目管理能力。
mt: Judging from the annual increase in the number of PMP applicants, more and more project management practitioners improve their project management capabilities through learning.
ref: Judging from the increasing number of PMP (internationally certified project management professional qualification) applicants each year, increasing project management practitioners improve their project management ability through learning.

src: 据《中国项目管理二十年发展报告(1999-2019)》称：截止到2019年9月，全国累计PMP®报考人数近60万人次，通过PMP®认证人数约42万人，有效持证人数约30万人, 占全球PMP®持证总量的31.2%。
mt: According to the Twenty-Year Development Report on Project Management in China (1999-2019), as of September 2019, there were nearly 600,000 PMP® applicants in China, about 420,000 PMP® certified applicants and about 300,000 valid certificate holders, accounting for 31.2% of the total number of PMP® certificates in the world.
ref: According to the 20-year Development Report on China’s Project Management (1999-2019), as of September 2019, the national PMP ® applicants totals 600,000, with 420,000 passed the PMP ® certification, and the number of valid certificate holders are about 300,000, accounting for 31.2% of the total number of certificates of PMP ® in the world.

src: 近10年PMP持证人数逐年递增，这说明越来越多的项目管理者意识到：靠简单照搬以往“老经验”来做事已不可取，瞬息万变的工作环境让我们知道一个要学会，站在科学巨人的肩膀上去探索前行的道路。
mt: In the past 10 years, the number of PMP certificate holders has increased year by year, which shows that more and more project managers have realized that it is no longer advisable to simply take the previous "old experience". The rapidly changing working environment lets us know that we should learn and stand on the shoulders of scientific giants to explore the way forward.
ref: In the past ten years, the number of people holding PMP certificates keeps increasing, which indicates that more and more project managers realize it is no longer advisable to do things by simply copying “past experience”; the rapidly changing working environment tells us that we should learn to stand on the shoulders of scientific giants and explore the way forward.

src: 然而，考了PMP就能保证项目管理工作畅通无阻了吗？
mt: However, can PMP ensure smooth project management?
ref: However, can you ensure the smooth proceeding of project management work after passing the PMP test?

src: 很多项目管理初学者表示，通过学习PMP/IPMP等相关课程，可以系统性地掌握项目管理的十大领域和五大过程组等相关知识点，但真正进行项目管理工作的时候却还是一头雾水。
mt: Many project management beginners said that by learning PMP/IPMP and other related courses, they can systematically master the relevant knowledge points such as ten major fields and five major process groups of project management, but they are still confused when it comes to project management.
ref: Many beginners of project management say that by learning courses of PMP/IPMP, they can systematically master knowledge points such as the ten fields and five major process groups of project management, but they are still confused when they are actually engaged in project management work.

src: 很多项目经理常常反馈以下问题： 项目管理认知不到位，单纯依靠个人经验，空有项目管理理论，不知如何实践； 缺乏系统的项目管理流程制度支撑，工作中无法落地，项目预估不准，把控度灵敏度差，项目一拖再拖； 成员分工不明确、团队中的“老油条”不知如何应对 跨部门协助沟通不顺畅，项目难以推进 ……
mt: Many project managers often give feedback on the following problems: poor cognition of project management, simple reliance on personal experience, lack of project management theory and no idea how to practice; lack of systematic project management process and system support, unable to be implemented in work, inaccurate project estimation, poor control sensitivity, and delay of projects; unclear division of labor among members, unclear "old Youtiao" in the team, unsmooth cross-departmental assistance and communication, and difficulty in promoting projects ...
ref: Many project managers often reflect the following problems: project management awareness is not sufficient, relying solely on personal experience, and there is only project management theories and no ideas about how to practice them; lack of support of systematic project management process and system, unable to actually implement the work, inaccurate project estimation, poor sensitivity of control, and project being delayed again and again; the members’ division of labor is not clear, there’s no way to handle the “sophisticated ones” in the team, communication is not smooth between departments, and it is difficult to push the project forward...

src: 因此，专注产品创新与研发管理领域十余载，已帮助众多优秀的企业培养了大批的产品经理、项目经理等研发关键人才，并获得了 “中国企业研发管理人才培训示范基地”等荣誉称号的中天华夏咨询带着《研发项目经理特训营》线上课程来了。
mt: Therefore, focusing on product innovation and R&D management for more than ten years, it has helped many excellent enterprises cultivate a large number of key R&D talents such as product managers and project managers, and Zhongtian Huaxia Consulting, which has won the honorary titles such as "China Enterprise R&D Management Talent Training Demonstration Base", came with the online course "Special Training Camp for R&D Project Managers".
ref: Therefore, ZTCHINA, which has been focusing on the field of product innovation and R&D of management for more than ten years and helped many excellent enterprises cultivate a large number of key R&D talents such as product managers and project managers, and won the honorary title of “China Enterprise R&D and Management Talents Training Demonstration Base”, presents the online course R&D Project Manager Special Training Camp.

src: 《研发项目经理特训营》线上课程 这是一种线上碎片化学习的方式，结合了众多研发型企业的实战案例、工具和方法，帮助您掌握项目经理必备知识及标准动作，走上自身项目管理的进阶之路。
mt: Online course "Special Training Camp for R&D Project Managers" is an online fragmented learning method, which combines the practical cases, tools and methods of many R&D enterprises to help you master the necessary knowledge and standard actions of project managers and embark on the advanced road of your own project management.
ref: The online course R&D Project Manager Special Training Camp is an online fragmented learning method, which combines the practical cases, tools and methods of many research and development type enterprises to help you master the necessary knowledge and standard actions of project managers, and embark on the advancing journey of project management on your own.

src: 这也是一次让企业用更低的成本和更少的投入，促进项目经理的培养进程，为企业带来高效运作结果的机会。
mt: It is also an opportunity for enterprises to promote the training process of project managers and bring efficient operation results with lower cost and less investment.
ref: This is also an opportunity for enterprises to promote the training process of project managers and bring efficient operation results to enterprises with less cost and investment.

src: 口说无凭，可以先看看其他学员怎么评价这门课程： 这门课程不仅是由中天华夏专家团队（原华为研发管理团队），结合国际先进的项目管理方法论和众多知名企业真实业务场景，对课程内容进行深入浅出的专业讲解。
mt: If there is no evidence, you can first see how other trainees evaluate this course: this course is not only provided by Zhongtian Huaxia expert team (former Huawei R&D management team), but also provides in-depth and simple professional explanation of the course content in combination with the international advanced project management methodology and the real business scenarios of many well-known enterprises.
ref: That’s all my own introduction, and you may see how other students evaluate this course: This course is not only a professional explanation of the course content in simple terms by the ZTCHINA expert team (former Huawei R&D management team), combining international advanced project management methodology and real business scenarios of many well-known enterprises.

src: 更是会提供科学实用的管理工具与方法，丰富的模板表单，帮助学员在课后将学习的内容转化运用于具体工作。
mt: It will also provide scientific and practical management tools and methods and rich template forms to help trainees convert what they have learned into specific work after class.
ref: It also provides scientific and practical management tools and methods as well as rich template forms to help students transform and apply the content into specific work after class.

src: 号称新山区超跑排气声最大！
mt: It is said that the exhaust sound of supercars in Xinshan District is the loudest!
ref: It is said to have the biggest exhaust noises of all supercars in Xinshan District!

src: 这次我们团队为大家带来的这款车，是许多男人的梦想！
mt: This time our team brings you this car that is the dream of many men!
ref: The car that our team brings you now is the dream of many men!

src: 它就是Lamborghini的旗舰超跑，Murcielago的换代车型 — Aventador LP700-4！
mt: It's Lamborghini's flagship supercar, Murcielago's replacement model-Aventador LP700-4!
ref: It is Lamborghini’s flagship supercar and Murcielago’s next generation model, Aventador LP700-4!

src: 要价马币近两百万，一年的路税马币十几千，四轮驱动，为什么叫LP700？
mt: The price is nearly two million rmb, the annual road tax is more than ten thousand rmb, four-wheel drive, why called LP700?
ref: It is priced nearly 2 million MYR and pays a road tax of around a dozen thousand each year; it is a four-wheel drive; why is it called LP700?

src: 因为拥有700匹的马力，你能想象有多快吗？
mt: With 700 horsepower, can you imagine how fast it is?
ref: Because it has 700 horsepower; can you image how fast that is?

src: 那算了小编也不知道，数据说0-100km/h加速只需要2.9秒，大概就是小编的myvi才要到30km/h的时候人家就到100km/h了，嗯。
mt: I don't know. According to the data, it only takes 2.9 seconds to accelerate from 0 to 100km/h, which is probably the case with myvi.
ref: Forget it, I don’t know, either; data says it takes only 2.9s to accelerate from 0 to 100km/h; when my myvi just reaches 30km/h, it is already at 100km/h, hum.

src: 低矮的车身、嚣张的剪刀门、遍布车身四周的巨大进气口以及玻璃下一览无余的6.5 v12引擎，完美的诠释了兰博基尼的风格。
mt: The low body, the arrogant scissors doors, the huge air intakes all around the body, and the 6.5 v12 engine, which offers a panoramic view of the glass, which perfectly illustrate the Lamborghini style.
ref: The low car body, extravagant scissor doors, huge air intakes all around the body and the 6.5 V12 engine transparent under the glass perfectly interpret the style of Lamborghini.

src: 对于车款的说明不需要说太多，自己Google一下就好了，小编整理了一些Google不一定给的到的解说！
mt: You don't need to say too much about the car model. Just google it by yourself. The editor sorted out some comments that google may not give!
ref: The model doesn’t need much introduction; you can Google it yourself; I have prepared something Google won’t necessarily be able to provide!

src: 太过备受瞩目，去到哪里大家都在看，很不自在！(其实有点爽)
mt: Too much attention. Everyone was watching wherever they went. It was uncomfortable! (Actually a little cool)
ref: It is too eye-catching; people look at it everywhere you go; it is uncomfortable! (It is actually sweet.)

src: 1km油钱在RM1左右 (车主根本不care)
mt: The fuel cost per 1 km is about RM1 (the car owner doesn't care at all)
ref: Gas is around RM1 for 1km (the owner wouldn’t even care)

src: 上下车的姿势要练习一下，不然会有点尴尬 (因为会爬不出车舱然后卡住一半)
mt: Practice getting on and off the car, or it will be a little awkward (because you will not be able to climb out of the cabin and get stuck in half)
ref: You need to practice the posture of when you get in and out of the car or it may be a little awkward (because you might get stuck halfway and crawl out).

src: 引擎声太大，下车后会顿时耳聋。(不过还是很爽)
mt: The engine is so loud that you will be deaf immediately after getting off the car. (But it's still cool)
ref: The engine is so loud that you will turn deaf when you get out of the car. (But still, it’s sweet.)

src: 车身太大，停在普通停车位会很窄，很怕被隔壁车开门的时候敲到！
mt: The car body is too large, so parking in an ordinary parking space will be very narrow, afraid of being knocked when the next car door is opened!
ref: The car body is too big; it will be narrow for it to park at a normal parking space; you will worry that the neighboring car might hit it while opening the door!

src: 有点寂寞，因为路上没有对手 (小编自己讲的，跟车主无关，哈哈)
mt: It's a little lonely because there is no opponent on the road(The editor speaks for himself, has nothing to do with the owner of the car, haha).
ref: You may get lonely because there is no rivalry on the road (I made it up; it has nothing to do with the car owners, haha.)

src: 大家不要误会，这视频的超跑并没有要出售，抱歉！
mt: Don't get me wrong. The supercar is not for sale. Sorry!
ref: Don’t get me wrong; the supercar in this video is not for sale, sorry!

src: 想要为你的爱车拍摄视频的朋友，欢迎联系我们！
mt: Friends who want to video your car, please contact us!
ref: Please contact us if you want to take a video for your car!

src: 更多你不知道的汽车资讯，就在 The Car Guide / 人民汽车志
mt: More auto information you don't know is in The Car Guide / People's Auto Guide
ref: Know more about cars, come to The Car Guide.

src: 牽扯到价值千万的车祸！
mt: The accident is worth millions of dollars!
ref: A car crash involving tens of millions!

src: Bugatti Chiron 与 Porsche 911 相信车友们都认识，Chiron 是全球最贵超跑之一，而 Porsche 911 的车价也是百万等级！
mt: Bugatti Chiron and Porsche 911 believe that everyone knows that Chiron is one of the most expensive supercars in the world, and the price of Porsche 911 is also one million!
ref: I believe car fans all know Bugatti Chiron and Porsche 911; Chiron is one of the most expensive supercars in the world, and the price of Porsche 911 is also over a million!

src: 那日前，国外就在短短几分钟内撞掉了百万跑车 911 还有千万超跑 Chiron！
mt: Just a few minutes ago, a foreign country hit a million sports cars 911 and ten million supercars Chiron!
ref: Recently, a car crashed into a million-level sports car 911 and a tens-of-millions level super car Chiron in just a few minutes in a foreign country!

src: 看结果，贵是有道理的！
mt: Look at the results, expensive for a reason!
ref: It seems from the result that there’s a reason why it is so expensive!

src: 在NFT火速出圈之时，加密社区又冒出了一个新概念。
mt: At a time when NFT emerged, a new concept emerged in the encrypted community.
ref: As NFT went viral beyond its own circle, a new concept emerged in the encrypted community.

src: 2021年，一款名为《Axie Infinity》的区块链游戏在东南亚地区产生了巨大影响，一些因疫情失去了工作机会的居民开始在这款游戏中获得稳定收入。
mt: In 2021, a blockchain game called Axie Infinity had a huge impact in Southeast Asia, where some residents who lost their jobs due to the pandemic began to earn stable incomes.
ref: In 2021, a blockchain game called Axie Infinity has exerted a huge impact in Southeast Asia, and some residents who lost their jobs due to the epidemic began to earn stable income in this game.

src: 《Axie Infinity》是一款以区块链技术为底层的宠物养成游戏，集合了NFT在内的多种玩法，是目前交易额最高的NFT项目，截止目前已超过30亿美元。
mt: Axie Infinity is a pet-growing game based on blockchain technology, which integrates various games such as NFT. It is the NFT project with the highest turnover at present, and has exceeded USD 3 billion so far.
ref: Axie Infinity is a pet grooming game based on blockchain technology, which integrates a variety of playing methods including NFT, and it is the NFT project with the highest trading volume now, exceeding US $3 billion so far.

src: TokenTerminal 数据显示，Axie Infinity 日收入超过 820 万美元，直逼《王者荣耀》。
mt: According to data from TokenTerminal, Axie Infinity earns more than $8.2 million a day, which is close to the Honor of Kings.
ref: Data of TokenTerminal shows that the daily income of Axie Infinity exceeds 8.2 million US dollars, approaching that of Honor of Kings.

src: 今年8月6日，Axie Infinity官方称其日活用户已超100万。
mt: On August 6, Axie Infinity officially said that its daily active users have exceeded 1 million.
ref: On August 6 this year, Axie Infinity said their daily active users have surpassed one million.

src: 《Axie Infinity》的火热将一种新的“palytoearn”模式传递给更多人，通过区块链与智能合约的帮助，玩家不再是单一的角色，除了能从游戏里获得乐趣及经济收益以外，还可以参与到游戏生态的治理之中。
mt: The popularity of Axie Infinity conveys a new "palytoearn" model to more people. With the help of blockchain and smart contracts, players can no longer be a single character, but can participate in the governance of the game ecology in addition to gaining fun and economic benefits from the game.
ref: The hotness of Axie Infinity has sent the new “palytoearn” pattern to more people; with the help of blockchain and intelligent contract, players are no longer a single character, and in addition to gaining pleasure and economic revenue from the game, they can also participate in the governance of game ecosystem.

src: 这种主体性并不由游戏制作方授予，而是由区块链技术保证。
mt: This subjectivity is not granted by game producers, but by blockchain technology.
ref: The subjectivity is not granted by the game producer, but guaranteed by blockchain technology.

src: 看到一则关于朋友股价的新闻，我最大的感触是企业在赛道的选择，也就是指投资标的行业的选择，首先要选择成长空间大的行业，至少1000亿以上的市场规模；其次，要选择未来增长性好的行业，考虑在未来3-5年后行业增长性达到最佳状态的行业；最后，要选择有政策扶持的行业。
mt: When I read a piece of news about my friend's stock price, my biggest feeling is that enterprises should first choose industries with large growth potential, at least more than RMB 100bn in market size, and then choose industries with good future growth potential, considering the industries with the best growth potential in the next 3-5 years, and finally choose industries supported by policies.
ref: I read a piece of news about one of my friends’ stock price, and my biggest feeling is the how the enterprise chooses its track, that is, the choice of the investment target industry; first of all, they should choose a industry with a large space for development and a market size of at least 100 billion; secondly, we should choose industries with good growth in the future and consider the industries with the best growth in the next 3-5 years; finally, choose industries with policy support.

src: 赛道有多宽指的是市场规模，赛道有多长指的是行业所处发展阶段，赛道是平坦还是崎岖指的是行业的竞争格局。
mt: The width of the track refers to the market size, the length of the track refers to the development stage of the industry, and whether the track is flat or rugged refers to the competitive landscape of the industry.
ref: The width of the track refers to the scale of market, the length of the track refers to the development stage of the industry, and whether the track is easy or bumpy refers to the competitiveness landscape of the industry.

src: 为对的赛道加油！
mt: Cheer for the right track!
ref: Cheer for the right track!

src: 新的一年，第一件事是总结2021 调整2022战术布局。
mt: In the new year, the first thing is to summarize 2021 and adjust the tactical layout of 2022.
ref: In the new year, the first task is to summarize 2021 and adjust the tactical layout of 2022.

src: 战术在于“do the things right”，也就是把事做对。
mt: The tactic is to "do the things right", that is, do the things right.
ref: The key of the tactics is “do the things right”.

src: 而战略在于“do the right thing”,也就是做正确的事。
mt: And strategy is to "do the right thing," which is to do the right thing.
ref: The key of the strategy is “do the right thing”.

src: 战略在于找方向，战术在于落地，在大多数战术思考之上，都有战略思考的空间。
mt: Strategy lies in finding the direction, tactics lies in landing, and there is room for strategic thinking above most tactical thinking.
ref: Strategy lies in finding direction and tactics lies in implementation; above most tactical thinking, there is room for strategic thinking.

src: 比如如何增加顾客数（战术思维）之上，可以思考是在当前领域持续深化还是横向领域延展（战略思维）；比如提升顾客留存率（战术思维）之上，可以思考如何提升核心顾客和高价值顾客的留存率（战略思维）；在提升活动参与度（战术思维）之上，可以考虑如何设置正确的活动KPI，达到正确的活动目标，比如提升目标顾客参与度、激活高价值沉默客、精准拉新；在提升DAU（战术思维）之上，可以考虑目前的增长是否健康可持续。
mt: For example, on the basis of how to increase the number of customers (tactical thinking), it can be considered whether to continuously deepen the current field or expand the horizontal field (strategic thinking); For example, on the basis of improving customer retention rate (tactical thinking), we can think about how to improve the retention rate of core customers and high-value customers (strategic thinking); On top of improving activity engagement (tactical thinking), consider how to set the right activity KPIs to achieve the right activity goals, such as improving target customer engagement, activating high-value silent customers, and accurately attracting new customers; Based on the improvement of DAU (tactical thinking), it can be considered whether the current growth is healthy and sustainable.
ref: For example, on top of how to increase the number of customers (tactical thinking), we can think about whether to continuously deepen the current field or expand the horizontal field (strategic thinking); for example, on top of improving customer retention rate (tactical thinking), we can think about how to improve the retention of core customers and high-value customers (strategic thinking); on top of improving activity participation (tactical thinking), we can consider how to set the correct activity KPIs to achieve the correct activity goals, such as improving the participation of target customers, activating high-value silent customers, and accurately attracting new customers; on top of improving DAU (tactical thinking), we can consider whether the current growth is healthy and sustainable.

src: 诞生12年，比特币在2021年迎来了几个里程碑事件。
mt: Twelve years after its birth, Bitcoin met several milestones events in 2021.
ref: After coming into being 12 years ago, bitcoins ushered in several milestone events in 2021.

src: 9月7日，中美洲小国萨尔瓦多将比特币定为法定货币，这是比特币第一次成为一个国家或地区的法定货币。
mt: On September 7, El Salvador, a small Central American country, designated Bitcoin as the legal currency, which is the first time that Bitcoin has become the legal currency of a country or region.
ref: On September 7, the small country, El Salvador, in Central America designated bitcoins as a legal tender, and this is the first time that bitcoin has become the legal tender of a country or region.

src: 10月12日，美国证监会八年来首次批准ProShares公司推出比特币ETF，并在纽约证券交易所上市，这标志着第一支合规的比特币期货ETF登陆美国资本市场，加密货币投资敞口的再次扩大。
mt: On October 12, the United States Securities Regulatory Commission approved ProShares to launch a Bitcoin ETF for the first time in eight years and listed it on the New York Stock Exchange, marking another expansion of cryptocurrency investment exposure as the first compliant Bitcoin futures ETF landed on the United States capital market.
ref: On October 12, the Securities and Exchange Commission of the United States approved the launch of bitcoin ETF by ProShares company for the first time in eight years and listed it on the New York Stock Exchange, marking the landing of the first compliant bitcoin futures ETF in the US capital market and the expansion of cryptocurrency investment exposure.

src: 从区块链技术发展角度来说，比特币并不是主角。
mt: From the perspective of blockchain technology development, Bitcoin is not the main character.
ref: From the perspective of blockchain technology, bitcoin is not the leading role.

src: 2021年11月14日比特币进行了一次名为“Taproot”的软分叉升级，该升级提高了比特币网络交易的匿名性，且通过改变区块本身的数据结构来减少交易中的数据负担。
mt: On November 14, 2021, Bitcoin conducted a soft fork upgrade called "Taproot", which improved the anonymity of Bitcoin network transactions and reduced the data burden in transactions by changing the data structure of the block itself.
ref: On November 14, 2021, bitcoin carried out a soft bifurcation upgrade called Taproot, which improved the anonymity of bitcoin network transactions and reduced the data burden in transactions by changing the data structure of the block itself.

src: 一级造价初始注册，继续教育学时问题你遇到了吗?
mt: Do you have any problems with the initial registration of Level I cost and the class hours of continuing education?
ref: In the initial registration of Class 1 cost, have you encountered problems in terms of the class hours of further education?

src: 逾期注册人员未提供继续教育学习证明 逾期注册应提供近一年不少于30学时的继续教育证明 重新注册应提供近4年不少于120学时的继续教育证明 重新注册应提供每满1个年度不少于30学时继续教育学习证明
mt: Overdue registrants fail to provide continuing education and learning certificates Overdue registrants shall provide continuing education and learning certificates of no less than 30 hours in the past year Re-registration shall provide continuing education and learning certificates of not less than 120 hours in the past 4 years Re-registration shall provide continuing education and learning certificates of not less than 30 hours in each full year
ref: Overdue registrants failing to provide certificates of further education; in overdue registration, the certificate of further education of no less than 30 class hours in the past year shall be provided; for re-registration, the certificate of further education of no less than 120 class hours in the last four years shall be provided; for re-registration, the certificate of further education of no less than 30 class hours every year shall be provided.

src: 造价工程师继续教育费用标准
mt: Cost Standard for Continuing Education of Cost Engineer
ref: Expense standard of further education of cost engineer

src: 参加网络继续教育的造价工程师在报名时须向各管理机构交纳学习费用，一般情况标准为:30学时必修课的费用为300元/人年(含继续教育统一教材);
mt: Cost engineers participating in online continuing education must pay study fees to various management organizations when registering. The general standard is RMB 300/person-year for compulsory courses of 30 class hours (including unified teaching materials for continuing education);
ref: Cost engineers enrolling in online further education shall pay tuition to various management institutions when signing up; the standard in general is: the cost of 30 class hours of compulsory courses is 300 yuan/person per year (including unified teaching materials for further education);

src: 30学时选修课的费用为300元/人年。
mt: The cost of 30 hours of elective courses is RMB 300/person/year.
ref: The cost of 30 class hours of elective courses is 300 yuan/person per year.

src: 30学时必修课和30学时选修课的费用为600元/人年(含继续教育统一教材)。
mt: The cost of 30 hours of compulsory courses and 30 hours of optional courses is RMB 600/person-year (including unified textbooks for continuing education).
ref: The cost of 30 class hours of compulsory courses and 30 class hours of elective courses is 600 yuan/person per year (including unified textbooks for further education).

src: (一)参加中价协或各省级和部门管理机构组织的注册造价工程师网络继续教育学习，按在线学习课件记录的时间计算学时;
mt: (I) Participate in the online continuing education of registered cost engineers organized by the China Cost Engineering Association or provincial and departmental management agencies, and calculate the class hours according to the time recorded in the online learning courseware;
ref: 1. Participate in the online further education of registered cost engineers organized by the China Cost Engineering Association or provincial and departmental management institutions, and calculate the class hours according to the time recorded in the online learning courseware;

src: (二)参加中价协或各省级和部门管理机构组织的注册造价工程师集中面授培训及各种类型的培训班、研讨会等，每半天可认定4个学时;
mt: (II) Participate in the centralized face-to-face training of registered cost engineers and various types of training courses and seminars organized by the China Cost Engineering Association or provincial and departmental management agencies, and can recognize 4 class hours every half day;
ref: 2. Participate in the centralized face-to-face training of registered cost engineers and various types of training courses, seminars, etc. organized by China Cost Engineering Association or provincial and departmental management institutions, and 4 class hours can be recognized every half day;

src: (三)参加中价协、各省级和部门造价工程师、造价员继续教育授课，每半天可认定10个学时;
mt: (III) Participate in the continuing education and teaching of cost engineers and cost engineers of China Cost Engineers Association, various provinces and departments, and 10 class hours can be recognized every half day;
ref: 3. Participate in courses of further education for cost engineers and cost personnel organized by China Cost Engineering Association, provinces and departments, and 10 class hours can be recognized every half day;

src: (四)参加中价协和省级课题研究、行业标准编制、教材编写,每项每年认定30学时;
mt: (IV) Participate in the research of China Price Union and provincial projects, the compilation of industry standards and the compilation of textbooks, with 30 credit hours per item per year;
ref: 4. Participate in the research projects of China Cost Engineering Association and provincial projects, and the compilation of industry standards and textbooks; each item is recognized as 30 class hours per year;

src: (六)参加全国造价工程师执业资格考试教材编写以及命题、审题、评卷，每年可认定30学时;
mt: (VI) Participating in the compilation of textbooks for the National Cost Engineer Qualification Examination, as well as the proposition, examination and evaluation of questions, 30 class hours can be recognized every year;
ref: 6. Participate in the compilation of teaching materials, setting questions, reviewing questions and evaluation of national cost engineer qualification examination, and it can be recognized as 30 class hours per year;

src: (七)以个人署名且公开发表(以正式刊号为准)的工程造价相关专业论文、著作。
mt: (VII) Professional papers and works related to project cost signed by individuals and published publicly (subject to the official serial number).
ref: 7. Professional papers and works related to project cost with personal signature and which are published publicly (with official publication number).

src: 出版著作每万字认定12学时;
mt: 12 class hours per 10,000 words of published works;
ref: 12 class hours per 10,000 words of published works;

src: 在国家级刊物上发表论文每千字认定8学时，在省级刊物上发表论文每千字认定5学时，在市级刊物上发表论文每千字认定3学时;
mt: 8 class hours for papers published in national journals, 5 class hours for papers published in provincial journals, and 3 class hours for papers published in municipal journals;
ref: Every thousand words in papers published in national journals is recognized as 8 class hours, every thousand words in papers published in provincial journals is recognized as 5 class hours, and every thousand words in papers published in municipal journals is recognized as 3 class hours;

src: (九)参加经中价协、各省级和部门管理机构、省级造价协会批准或授权的工程造价咨询企业组织的可以面向社会的公开培训(企业一般的管理和技能培训除外)，每半天可认定4个学时，每年最高可认定30学时。
mt: (IX) Participate in the public training that can be organized by the engineering cost consulting enterprises approved or authorized by the China Cost Engineering Association, provincial and departmental management agencies and provincial cost associations (except for the general management and skills training of enterprises), which can be recognized for 4 class hours every half day, with a maximum of 30 class hours per year.
ref: 9. Participate in the public training (excluding the general management and skill training of enterprises) that can be open to the society which is approved by China Cost Engineering Association, provincial and departmental management institutions, and the Provincial Cost Association, or organized by authorized engineering cost consulting enterprise; 4 class hours can be recognized every half day, and at most 30 class hours can be recognized every year.

src: 造价工程师网络继续教育学习流程
mt: Cost Engineer Network Continuing Education Learning Process
ref: Process of cost engineer online further education

src: 在注册机构收到费用后，学员身份随即开通，造价工程师即可凭着用户名和密码进入网络教育课堂学习。
mt: After the registration institution receives the fee, the student identity will be opened immediately, and the cost engineer can enter the online education classroom for learning with the user name and password.
ref: After the registration institution receives the tuition, the student identity will be set up immediately, and cost engineers can enter the online education classroom with the user name and password.

src: 学员通过点播课件、提问答疑、网上讨论等方式进行学习。
mt: Students learn through on-demand courseware, Q&A, online discussion, etc.
ref: Students learn through on-demand courseware, question answering, online discussion, etc.

src: 如果忘记密码，登陆时出现用户名和密码不正确，不能登陆学习时，请学员与所属注册机构联系，注册机构可以协助修改学员的密码(但不能修改用户名)，使用其修改后的密码重新登陆。
mt: If you forget your password and your username and password are incorrect during login, and you cannot log in for study, please contact the registration authority. The registration authority can assist in modifying your password (but you cannot modify your username) and log in again with the modified password.
ref: If you forget your password, and your user name and password are incorrect when logging in; if you can’t log in and study, please contact your registration institution, and they can help you change the password (but you can’t change your user name) and you can use the new password to log in again.

src: 扫二维码下载贴吧客户端
mt: Scan the QR code to download the Tieba client
ref: Scan QR code to download Tieba app

src: 看高清直播、视频！
mt: Watch HD live streaming and videos!
ref: Watch HD live broadcast and videos!

src: 2020年9月，陆先生从房屋中介了解到一处位于浙江余姚丈亭镇的厂房，在多次现场看房后，陆先生决定购买该厂房。
mt: In September 2020, Mr.Lu learned from the housing intermediary that a factory building was located in Zhangting Town, Yuyao, Zhejiang Province. After several on-site visits, Lu Xiansheng decided to purchase the factory building.
ref: In September 2020, Mr. Lu learned about a plant located at Yuyao Zhangting Village in Zhejiang through an estate agent and decided to purchase it after seeing it on-site for a few times.

src: 同年12月，陆先生就购买厂房的细节与房屋所有权人的家属林某进行磋商后，于当天通过银行转账汇款20万元作定金。
mt: In December of the same year, Mr.Lu negotiated with Lin Mou, the owner's family, on the details of the purchase of the plant, and remitted RMB 200,000 as a deposit through bank transfer on the same day.
ref: In December of the same year, Mr. Lu negotiated with Lin, a family member of the house owner, about the details of the purchase of the plant, and remitted 200,000 yuan as a deposit by bank transfer on the same day.

src: 林某在《厂房买卖定金收条》上作为收款人签名，其中载明，“若买方不想买此厂房，此定金归卖家，如卖方不愿意卖此厂房，定金将双倍返还卖方，双方约定一周内签订厂房买卖合同。”
mt: Lin Mou signed the Receipt for Plant Sales Deposit as the payee, which stated: "If the buyer does not want to buy the plant, the deposit shall be paid by the seller. If the seller is not willing to sell the plant, the deposit will be returned to the seller in double, and both parties agree to sign the plant sales contract within one week."
