mt: In recent years, the shipment and sales proportion of laser TVs in the world have been increasing, accounting for more than 60% of the total TV sales of 80 inches and above.
ref: In recent years, the proportion of the global shipments and sales of laser TV keeps increasing, accounting for over 60% of the total TV sales of 80 inches and above.

src: 根据中怡康的预测，2020年，激光电视市场销量增长将超过140%，继续保持高速增长。
mt: According to CEC's forecast, the sales volume of laser TV market will increase by more than 140% in 2020, continuing to maintain high-speed growth.
ref: According to the prediction of CMM, the sales volume of laser TV market in 2020 will increase by over 140% and will continue to maintain a high-speed growth.

src: 之所以在大屏市场有如此好的成绩，主要归功于激光电视在护眼方面的出色表现。
mt: The reason for such good results in the large screen market is mainly due to the excellent performance of laser TV in eye protection.
ref: The reason for such great result in the big screen market is mainly the outstanding performance of laser TVs in eye protection .

src: 基于激光电视漫反射的成像原理，激光光源发出的光线并不直射入眼球，相比液晶电视的背光源发光，成像过程更接近自然条件下物体的成像过程，对眼睛产生的刺激也更小。
mt: Based on the imaging principle of diffuse reflection of laser TV, the light emitted by the laser light source does not directly enter the eyeball. Compared with the backlight of LCD TV, the imaging process is closer to the imaging process of objects under natural conditions, and the stimulation to the eye is less.
ref: Based on the imaging principle of diffuse reflection of laser TV, the light emitted by the laser light source does not go directly into the eyeball; compared with the backlight of LCD TV, its imaging process is closer to that of objects under natural conditions, with less irritation to the eyes.

src: 中国电子技术标准化研究院赛西实验室和北京协和医院眼科专家，通过人群相同条件下观看激光电视和液晶电视的严格对比试验，得出了144组测试数据。
mt: Ophthalmologists from CISI Laboratory of China Electronics Standardization Institute and Peking Union Medical College Hospital obtained 144 sets of test data through a strict comparative test of people watching laser TV and LCD TV under the same conditions.
ref: Ophthalmologists from CES Laboratory, China Electronics Standardization Institute, and Peking Union Medical College Hospital obtained 144 groups of test data through a strict comparative experiment of watching laser TV and LCD TV under the same conditions.

src: 数据证实：激光电视的确具有很强的护眼特性，在特定方面甚至具有一定的改善作用。
mt: The data confirms that laser TVs do have strong eye-protection properties and even improve in certain aspects.
ref: Statistics prove that laser TVs can indeed protect the eyes and may even make improvement in certain aspects.

src: 在视力健康越来越受重视的当下，激光电视不仅凭借护眼优势吸引了越来越多用户，也打开了彩电市场的另一个突破口。
mt: At present, laser TV not only attracts more and more users with the advantage of eye protection, but also opens another breakthrough in the color TV market.
ref: As eye protection is gaining more and more attention, laser TVs not only attracted more and more customers with the feature of eye protection, but also made another breakthrough in the market of color TVs.

src: 第二，激光电视更聚焦高端市场。
mt: Second, laser TV focuses more on the high-end market.
ref: Second, laser TV focuses more on high-end market.

src: 与液晶电视价格不断下探相反，目前市售激光电视的价格大多在万元以上，随着尺寸和光源的升级，价格逐步攀升。
mt: Contrary to the continuous decline in the price of LCD TVs, the current price of laser TVs on the market is mostly above RMB 10,000. With the upgrading of size and light source, the price gradually rises.
ref: Contrary to the downward trend of the price of LCD TVs, price of laser TVs on the market now is over 10,000 yuan, and it went up gradually with the upgrading of size and source of light.

src: 激光电视凭什么卖这么贵呢？
mt: Why is laser TV so expensive?
ref: Why are laser TVs so expensive?

src: 肯定是有道理的。
mt: It must make sense.
ref: There must be a reason.

src: 在光源和技术水平的不断发展下，激光电视有很多液晶电视和投影都无法实现的优势。
mt: With the continuous development of light source and technology level, laser TV has many advantages that cannot be realized by LCD TV and projection.
ref: With the continuous development of light source and technology, laser TVs have advantages that many LCD TVs and projectors don’t.

src: 凭借超短焦距投影技术，激光电视的投影距离相对传统投影设备来说要更短，能够在短距离内实现100英寸大屏体验，所需空间不大，而且主机小巧，占用地方很小。
mt: With the ultra-short focal length projection technology, the projection distance of laser TV is shorter than that of traditional projection equipment, which can realize a 100-inch large screen experience in a short distance. The required space is not large, and the host is small and occupies little space.
ref: With the super short focus projection technology, the projection distance of laser TVs is shorter than that of traditional projection equipment; it can realize the 100 inch large screen experience within a short distance; the space required is not large, and the small host takes up very little space.

src: 在亮度方面，大品牌激光电视可以达到2000以上的流明。
mt: In terms of brightness, big-brand laser TVs can reach more than 2,000 lumens.
ref: In terms of lightness, laser TVs from famous brands can reach over 2,000 lumens.

src: 加之发热量更低，对设备损耗小，电视的使用寿命也更长。
mt: Plus lower heat generation, less wear and tear on equipment, and longer TV life.
ref: Plus, the heat is lower, equipment loss is small, and the service life of TV is longer.

src: 除此之外，很多高端激光电视机型还搭载了真4K超高清画质、人工智能系统、仿生屏等众多前沿技术，能够给用户带来更震撼的视听体验。
mt: In addition, many high-end laser TV models are equipped with many cutting-edge technologies such as real 4K ultra-high definition image quality, artificial intelligence system and bionic screen, which can bring users more shocking audio-visual experience.
ref: In addition, many high-end laser TVs are equipped with real 4K ultra HD image, artificial intelligent systems, bionic screens and other cutting-edge technologies, bringing users a more stunning audio-visual experience.

src: 谈不上伪需求，而是需求细分的产物，论画质和投入产出比，激光电视不是影音玩家的菜，想兼顾大屏和观看环境不足，可以尝试，凡事皆有利弊，权衡过后自己判断即可，就怕听信一面之词。
mt: It is not a pseudo demand, but a product of demand subdivision. In terms of picture quality and input-output ratio, laser TV is not a dish for audio and video players. If they want to take into account the large screen and insufficient viewing environment, they can try. Everything has its advantages and disadvantages. After weighing, they can judge by themselves, afraid of listening to what they say.
ref: It's not so much of a fake demand, but the product of demand segmentation; when it comes to image quality and input-output ratio, laser TVs are not what video and audio enthusiasts are after; if you want to take into account the lack of large screen and viewing environment, you can try it; everything has its pros and cons, and you can make a decision yourself after deliberation; just don’t listen to only one side of the story.

src: 简单说，超广角近焦投影机--激光电视，为了贴近幕布，不得不使用价格昂贵的超广角透镜和反射镜，这不符合光学最佳设计。
mt: Briefly, ultra-wide-angle near-focus projectors, laser TVs, have to use expensive ultra-wide-angle lenses and mirrors to get close to the screen, which is not the best optical design.
ref: Simply put, in order to get close to the screen, ultra wide angle close focus projector, laser TV, has to use expensive ultra wide angle lens and reflector, which is not in line with the best optical design.

src: 为了屏蔽部分环境光，使用微结构的菲涅尔幕布，代价高昂，80寸的价格基本能换个65寸液晶。
mt: In order to shield part of the ambient light, the Fresnel curtain with microstructure is expensive, and the price of 80 inches can basically be changed to 65 inches liquid crystal.
ref: In order to shield part of the ambient light, it uses an expensive microstructure Fresnel screen; the price of an 80-inch laser TV basically can be changed into a 65-inch LCD TV.

src: 还有一点，我特别讨厌投影厂商拿漫反射对眼睛好这种当卖点，拜托，眼睛能够看到的幕布上的光线对于眼睛而言就是直射光，你漫反射到天花板上，眼睛也看不到，非要较真液晶电视也是漫“直射”，打开电视天花板不也被照亮吗？
mt: In addition, I especially hate that projection manufacturers take diffuse reflection as a selling point. Please, the light on the curtain that can be seen by the eyes is direct light for the eyes. If you diffuse reflection on the ceiling, the eyes cannot see it. If you want to be more serious, the LCD TV is also diffuse "direct light". If you open the TV ceiling, it will also be illuminated.
ref: Another point is that I especially hate it when projector manufacturers using “diffuse reflection is good for the eyes” as a selling point; please, eyes can see the light on the screen means that it is direct light to the eyes; when it hit the ceiling, eyes cannot see it; if you want to be serious about it, then LCD TV also uses diffused “direct light”; isn’t the ceiling also illuminated when you turn on the TV?

src: 而且，投影幕布如果不是漫反射，根本成不了像。
mt: Moreover, if the projection screen is not diffusely reflective, it cannot be imaged at all.
ref: Moreover, if the projection screen does not use diffuse reflection, imaging is not possible at all.

src: 恰恰被忽略了高增益幕布的热斑（光斑）效应，某一角度大量光线反射到眼睛，那才是真难受。
mt: Ignoring the hot-spot (spot) effect of the high-gain curtain, it is really uncomfortable that a large amount of light is reflected to the eye at an angle.
ref: The hot spot (light spot) effect of the high gain screen is ignored, and a large amount of light at a certain angle being reflected into the eyes is really uncomfortable.

src: 小雨伞买保险，靠谱吗?
mt: Is it reliable to buy insurance in xiaoyusan.com?
ref: Is it safe to buy insurance on Little Umbrella?

src: 小雨伞是一个互联网的保险经纪平台。
mt: Xiaoyushan is an Internet-based insurance brokerage platform.
ref: Little Umbrella is an insurance brokerage platform on the internet.

src: 从设置条件来看：按照《保险经纪机构监管规定(2015年修订)》提示来看，成为保险经纪公司的，必须满足三个关键词：股东、发起人最近3年无重大违法记录、最低限额为人民币5000万元才可以成立、必须经过中国保监会同意。
mt: From the perspective of setting conditions: according to the Provisions on the Supervision and Administration of Insurance Brokerage Institutions (2015 Amendment) tips,  three keywords must be met  to become an insurance brokerage company:shareholders and sponsors who have no major illegal records in the past three years, the minimum limit of RMB 50 million to be established, and must be agreed by the CIRC.
ref: In terms of setup conditions: according to the "Regulations on the Supervision of Insurance Brokerage Institutions (revised in 2015)", the following three key requirements must be met to become an insurance brokerage company, shareholders and initiator have no major illegal records in the past three years, the minimum limit is 50 million yuan, and it must be approved by the CIRC.

src: 这三条其实就是很苛刻的，总结起来就是要有实力，要经过银保监会（监管全国内的保险公司、银行）的国家权威部门批准、股东要有良好的作风，作为保险经纪公司的小雨伞保险，投保者是不用过多质疑小雨伞保险是正规的与否，毕竟有这3条门槛，不是什么保险公司都能达到的。
mt: The three rules are harsh. To sum up, insurance companies need to be competent, approved by the national authorities of the China Banking and Insurance Regulatory Commission (which supervises insurance companies and banks across the country) and have a good style of work. As insurance brokers, insurance applicants don't need to question whether the umbrella insurance is formal. After all, not all insurance companies can meet the three thresholds.
ref: These three requirements are strict enough; in summary, it needs to have strength, to be approved by the national authoritative departments of the China Banking and Insurance Regulatory Commission (supervising insurance companies and banks across the country), and the shareholders’ conduct is descent; as an insurance brokerage company, Little Umbrella Insurance doesn’t need to be questioned by policyholders about whether it is legal or not; after all, not all insurance companies can meet these three requirements.

src: 在这一点上，还不错，是值得信赖的。
mt: At this point, it's not bad, it's trustworthy.
ref: In this regard, it is not bad and worth trusting.

src: 从保险产品来看：小雨伞保险就是一个保险超市，很多公司的明星重疾险都在这家平台上出售，如最新上架的和泰超级玛丽5号重疾险，理赔方和承保方都是和泰人寿，小雨伞保险只是第三方中介，不用质疑它的靠谱性。
mt: From the perspective of insurance products, Xiaoyusan Insurance is an insurance supermarket, and many companies sell their star critical illness insurance on this platform. For example, the newly launched Hetai Super Mary No.5 critical illness insurance, both the claim settler and the underwriter are Hetai Life Insurance. Xiaoyusan Insurance is only a third-party agency, so there is no need to question its reliability.
ref: In terms of insurance products: Little Umbrella Insurance is an insurance supermarket, with star serious illness insurances of many companies on sale on this platform; for example, for the newly added HTLIC Super Mario 5 serious illness insurance, both the claim adjuster and the insurer are HTLIC, and Little Umbrella Insurance is only the third-party intermediary, whose reliability does not need to be questioned.

src: 从缴费模式来看：互联网平台的产品，因为少了营业网点的经营费用，和业务员工资的成本，所以互联网产品普遍性价比比较高，而且缴费方式灵活，支持月缴，减轻投保人的缴费压力，同时可以最大限度的撬动保险的杠杆。
mt: From the perspective of payment model, the products of the Internet platform are generally cost-effective because they reduce the operating expenses of business outlets and the salary cost of salespersons. Moreover, the payment method is flexible, supporting monthly payment, reducing the payment pressure of insurance applicants and maximizing the leverage of insurance.
ref: In terms of payment method: due to the lack of the operating expenses of the business outlets and the cost of the sales people’s salaries, internet products are generally cost-effective, and the payment method is flexible, which supports monthly payment; it reduces the payment pressure of the policyholder, and can leverage of the insurance lever to the greatest extent in the meantime.

src: 这点还是非常不错的。
mt: That's pretty good.
ref: This is good.

src: 可以考虑。
mt: It can be considered.
ref: It can be considered.

src: 从业务员专业度来看：这点尤为重要，因为保险是一个专业度要求非常强的行业，很多互联网产品客户可以自己投保，这种就会存在很多的误区，在健康告知和职业这块，非保险从业人员往往在投保的时候会添加自己的主观意识，觉得自己健康或者符合，这样容易存在很多理赔隐患，有可能被拒赔的风险。
mt: From the perspective of the professionalism of salesmen, this is particularly important because insurance is an industry with very high professionalism requirements. Many Internet product customers can buy insurance by themselves, which has many misunderstandings. In terms of health notification and occupation, non-insurance practitioners often add their subjective awareness when buying insurance and feel that they are healthy or conform to the requirements, which is easy to have many hidden dangers of claim settlement and may be rejected.
ref: In terms of the professional level of sales personnel: this is especially important as insurance industry has a strict requirement on expertise; for many internet products, customers can apply for insurance by themselves, which will cause many misunderstandings; in terms of health notification and occupation, non-insurance practitioners often add their subjective awareness when applying for insurance, and feel that they are healthy or in line with it; like this, there will be a lot of hidden dangers in claims settlement and the risk of being rejected.

src: 我自己曾在“腾讯微保”（和小雨伞一样，也是互联网保险经纪平台）做过保险电话销售，非常负责任的告诉大家。
mt: I once did insurance telemarketing in "Tencent WeSure" (like Xiaoyuguan, also an online insurance brokerage platform) and told everyone very responsiblely.
ref: I worked as insurance telemarketing personnel in “Tencent Micro-Insurance” (like Little Umbrella, it is also an Internet insurance brokerage platform), and I can tell you.

src: 互联网的保险是真的，也靠谱，不靠谱的是人，互联网渠道没有专业的从业人员，也有很多的销售误导。
mt: Internet insurance is real and reliable, and the unreliable is people. There are no professional practitioners in internet channels, and there are also many sales misleading.
ref: The insurance products on the internet are real and reliable, and it is the people who are not reliable; there are no professional practitioners on the internet, and there is much misleading information in sales.

src: 比如：1元保险保600万，买保险送手机，免费领取6万重疾保额，这些营销策略没有错，可是却避重就轻，不会告诉投保人，首月1元，次月是需要按正常收费的，几十到200不等，很多客户扣费一两年自己买的是个啥不清楚。
mt: For example, RMB 1 for insurance of RMB 6 million, free mobile phones for buying insurance, and free sum insured for critical illness of RMB 60,000. These marketing strategies are correct, but they avoid the serious ones and will not tell the policy holder. The first month is RMB 1, and the next month is charged according to the normal rate, ranging from dozens to RMB 200. Many customers do not know what they buy for one or two years.
ref: For example: there is nothing wrong with sales strategies like 1 yuan insurance covers 6 million yuan, buy insurance and get free mobile phones, and get 60,000 serious illness insurance coverage for free; however, they withhold important information and won't tell the policyholder that the first month is 1 yuan, and the fee next month is charged normally, ranging from a few dozens to 200; many customers don’t know what they bought after they’ve been charged for one or two years.

src: 以为可以花1块钱，保险公司赔600万（天下掉馅饼）。
mt: I thought I could spend $1 and the insurance company would pay 6 million.（pennies from the heaven）
ref: They thought they could spend 1 yuan and get a six million claim settlement from the insurance company (pie in the sky).

src: 免费送手机，是保单尾号比如6666，8888这种特殊保单号段才送的，并且如果中奖短信发出，自己不兑换，也没有人提醒的。
mt: Free mobile phones are given only for special policy numbers such as 6666 and 8888. If a winning short message is sent,  you do not redeem it and no one will remind you.
ref: Getting mobile phone for free means only policy ending with special numbers such as 6666 and 8888 can get a free phone, and no one will remind you again if the text message is sent to you and you don’t redeem it yourself.

src: （这对于投保人来说，就又是一个坑）免费领6万重疾保额，是短期的，如果只靠这个，没有其他商业险，万一真发生重疾，6万能干嘛，解决不了问题，以后的生活开始裸奔。
mt: (This is another pit for insurance applicants.) It is a short-term free sum insured for critical illnesses of 60,000 yuan. If you rely only on this and there is no other commercial insurance, what can you do if you really have a critical illness? If the problem cannot be solved, your future life will start running naked.
ref: (This is yet another trap for the policyholder) It is a short-term activity to claim 60000 serious disease insurance for free; if you only rely on this and there is no other commercial insurance, 60000 yuan will not solve any problem in case of the happening of a serious disease, and you will have nothing in your life later.

src: 目前对于互联网保险销售的误导，国家也在严厉打击。
mt: At present, the state is cracking down on the misleading of online insurance sales.
ref: Our country is also cracking down on misleading Internet insurance sales at present.

src: 所以综合来看，平台是没有问题，产品也没有问题，有问题的是业务员的专业度和职业操守。
mt: On the whole, there is no problem with platforms and products. The problem lies in the professionalism and professional ethics of salespersons.
ref: Therefore, there is no problem with the platform or the products; what matters is the professionalism and professional integrity of the salesperson.

src: 建议题主综合慎重考虑，其实很多线下保险经纪公司的产品更广，客户可以选择的机会和产品更多，有些产品的性价比也优于互联网产品。
mt: It is suggested that the topic should be considered carefully. In fact, many offline insurance brokers have a wider range of products, and customers can choose more opportunities and products. Some products are also more cost-effective than Internet products.
ref: It is suggested that the original post should think about it carefully; in fact, there are many offline insurance brokerage companies with a wider range of products, and customers have more opportunities and products to choose from; some products are better than Internet products in terms of cost performance.

src: 我自己就帮助过59位互联网客户，承保线下产品，保费每个人节约2000-3000元/年。
mt: I have helped 59 Internet customers cover offline products, saving RMB 2,000-3,000/year for each person.
ref: I myself have helped 59 Internet customers to underwrite offline products, helping each person save 2000-3000 yuan of premium per year.

src: 如果大家有什么疑问，欢迎与我沟通和交流。
mt: If you have any questions, please communicate with me.
ref: If you have any question, feel free to communicate with me.

src: 我：明亚保险经纪人，有过3年企业管理培训经验，服务过近千家企业用户，合作超过100家保险公司，在投保前，我会从客户需求出发，为客户量身定制保险产品，投保中，为客户货比三家，尽力为客户争取最好的核保结果，投保后，为客户做保单整理，保单托管，让客户放心无忧。
mt: I: Minya Insurance Broker, with 3 years of experience in enterprise management training, has served nearly 1,000 enterprise users and cooperated with more than 100 insurance companies. Before insurance, I will customize insurance products for customers based on their needs. During insurance, I will shop around for customers and try my best to obtain the best underwriting results for customers. After insurance, I will sort out and trust insurance policies for customers, so that customers can be assured.
ref: I am a Mingya Insurance Broker and have three years of experience in enterprise management training; I have served almost a thousand enterprise users and cooperated with over 100 insurance companies; before insuring, I will analyze the needs of my client and customize products for them; while insuring, I will compare all the insurance companies and help my client achieve the best underwriting result; after insuring, I will organize and hold the insurance policy to make my client feel at ease.

src: 跟每个客户一起终身成长。
mt: Grow with every client for life.
ref: Grow with each client for a lifetime.

src: 希望我的回答能够对题主有所帮助！
mt: I hope my answer will help the thread starter！
ref: Hopefully my answer will help the original post!

src: 根据保险监管部门的定义，互联网保险就是投保人点击投保链接后，可以自主完成所有的投保流程的保险业务。
mt: According to the definition of the insurance regulatory authority, online insurance means that insurance applicants can independently complete all insurance processes after clicking the insurance link.
ref: According to the definition of insurance supervising departments, Internet insurance is an insurance business in which the applicant can complete the entire insurance process independently after clicking the insuring link.

src: 在这个过程中，投保人不需要签字，保险顾问也不需要签字，所有步骤全部都可以由投保人自主完成。
mt: In this process, the policy holder and the insurance consultant do not need to sign, and all steps can be completed by the policy holder itself.
ref: In this process, neither the applicant nor the insurance consultant needs to sign, so all the steps can be fulfilled independently by the applicant.

src: 虽然互联网保险的投保没太有“仪式感”，甚至可能连打印版的纸质合同都没有，但是这丝毫不影响电子版合同的有效性与法律效力。
mt: Although there is no "sense of ceremony" in the application of internet insurance, and there may even be no printed contract, this does not affect the validity and legal effect of the electronic contract.
ref: Although insuring an Internet insurance product has no “sense of ritual”, and even there is no printed copy of contact, it doesn’t affect the validity and legal effect of electronic contract at all.

src: 这种模式，有点类似于“电话销售”一般的流水线作业，但如此购买保险也会有一个致命的问题，那就是——后续的服务可能会跟不上。
mt: This model, somewhat similar to the "telemarketing" general assembly line, but buying insurance like this also has a fatal problem, that is -- subsequent services may not keep up.
ref: This pattern is somewhat similar to assembly line operation of “telemarketing”, but buying insurance this way will also have a fatal problem, that is, the follow-up service may not keep up.

src: 保险通常是一份长达几十年的长期契约，我们在购买保险的时候，是不是应该认真思考一下，我们所选择的这个“中介”，是不是一个可以与我们长期相伴、在很多年后也会给我们提供服务的“保险中介人”呢？
mt: Insurance is usually a long-term contract that lasts for decades. When we buy insurance, should we seriously think about whether the "intermediary" we choose is an "insurance intermediary" that can accompany us for a long time and will provide services to us many years later?
ref: Insurance is usually a long-term contract that lasts for decades; when we buy insurance, shouldn’t we seriously consider whether the “intermediary” we choose is an “insurance intermediary” who can accompany us for a long time and provide services to us many years later?

src: 从以前到现在，我都反对任何形式的污蔑和谩骂，更不能接受这类人身攻击的行为。
mt: From the past to the present, I have opposed any form of slander and abuse, let alone such physical attacks.
ref: I have been against any form of insult or abuse since the beginning, and I will not stand such personal attacks.

src: 在文明社会，我们可以包容一切，但就是要杜绝这种恶棍。
mt: In a civilized society, we can tolerate everything, but we must put an end to this kind of villain.
ref: In this civilized society, we can tolerate everything, but we need to get rid of these bullies.

src: 如果不看政党和派系，要先抵制的，就是这种不文明的作风。
mt: If you don't look at political parties and factions, it's this uncivilized style that you have to resist first.
ref: If you don’t look at political parties and factions, it is this uncivilized actions that should be boycotted first.

src: 从你开始发来脸书加好友请求开始，进而发表具调侃性的帖子，再到你试图把所谓我的家地点和父亲名字发布在社交媒体上，我都已经采取不回应的态度。
mt: I've taken a non-responsive attitude since you started sending Facebook friend requests, then posting funny posts, and then trying to post my home location and father's name on social media.
ref: I never replied to you since you started to send me Facebook friend request, published ridicule posts, and then tried to post the so-called location of my home and my father’s name on social media.

src: 你过后变本加厉地不只按一日六餐的频率持续tag我，更在脸书跟你的所谓朋友们继续肆无忌惮地讨论着关于我一些隐晦、羞辱的言论，样貌、身材、好生养、又什么床上种草莓、要不要插之类的留言，我...也算了。
mt: You're not just going to tag me at the rate of six meals a day, but you're going to talk to your so-called friends on Facebook about my privacy, humiliating remarks about my appearance and figure, holding that I am easy to be pregnant, and talking about love bite in bed, whether to insert or not, and I...ignore.
ref: After that, you made it worse by not only continuing to tag me six times a day, but also continuing to wantonly discuss with your so-called friends on Facebook about some obscure and humiliating remarks about me, my appearance, figure, shape fit for giving birth, getting love bites in bed, whether to penetrate or not, I... forget it.

src: 怎知后来我更收到多位朋友发来有关你的脸书朋友户口上载一张你的照片和具性骚扰成分的言论。
mt: But then I received a number of messages from friends about your Facebook friend account posting a picture of you and comments of sexual harassment.
ref: It was unexpected that more people sent me a photo uploaded to your Facebook friends page and your harassing comments.

src: 抱歉，作为一位女生，我再也无法继续沉默了。
mt: Sorry, as a girl, I can't keep silent anymore.
ref: Sorry, I cannot be silent anymore as a girl.

src: 我报警的新闻上载后，你完全没有收敛，反而更越发嚣张。
mt: After the news that I called the police was uploaded, you did not restrain yourself at all, but became more and more arrogant.
ref: After the news of me calling the police was published, you did not restrain yourself at all, but became more arrogant.

src: 我不理你是什么政治背景，也不管你是什么身份地位，在我们的社会，是需要两性尊重的。
mt: I don't care what political background you are, or what status you are. In our society, there is a need for gender respect.
ref: I don’t care about your political background or your identity or position; in our society, the two genders shall respect each other.

src: 是的，你们可以继续这种具调侃性、隐晦、羞辱、辱骂的言论，你也可以继续说你只是关爱和关注我，你可以继续认为这并不是骚扰、你甚至可以继续否认那不是你制的图或者继续发表一切攻击性言论。
mt: Yes, you can continue this ridiculous, obscure, humiliating, insulting remark, you can also continue to say that you just care and follow me, you can continue to think that this is not harassment, you can even continue to deny that it is not your picture or continue to make all offensive remarks.
ref: Yes, you can continue with your ridicule, obscure, humiliating and abusive remarks; you can continue to say that you just care about and pay attention to me; you can continue to think that this is not harassment; you can even continue to deny that you made the pictures or continue to make all the offensive remarks.

src: 没错，我不能，也没有能力阻止你们。
mt: Yeah, I can't, and I can't stop you.
ref: Yes, I can’t and won’t stop you.

src: 我既不认识你，也不想认识你，我的样貌和身材更不需要你评头论足。
mt: I don't know you, I don't want to know you, I don't need you to comment on my appearance and figure.
ref: I don’t know you and I don’t want to know you, and my appearance and body don’t need you judgement.

src: 我甚至不认为会有哪一位女生愿意让别人如此地羞辱自己来换来出名。
mt: I don't even think there's a girl who's willing to let others humiliate herself so much to become famous.
ref: I don’t even think any girl would want to be famous by being humiliated like this.

src: 朋友问我，还好吗？
mt: My friend asked me if I was okay.
ref: My friends asked me if I was okay.

src: 我说好，你也不会信。
mt: I said yes, and you wouldn't believe it.
ref: You won’t believe it if I say yes.

src: 我觉得不会有任何一位女生被如此霸凌后还可以说自己还好。
mt: I don't think any girl can say she's okay after being bullied like this.
ref: I don’t think any girl could say they are okay after being bullied like this.

src: 无论在工作、社会、政坛或商界，只有那些连基本品德都没有的人，才会选择用这种方式来伤害任何一位女性。
mt: Whether in work, society, politics or business, only those who have no basic moral character will choose to hurt any woman in this way.
ref: No matter it’s in the workplace, society, politics or the business world, only those without basic moral character will harm a woman in this way.

src: 我相信，公道自在人心。
mt: I believe that justice naturally inhabits man's heart
ref: I believe justice is in everyone’s heart.

src: 我截了部分留言给大家评理
mt: I give you some screenshots that you can comment
ref: I took screenshots of part of the comments and you can make your judgement.

src: 你自己发的贴应该没有人可以冒充你了吧
mt: Your own posting should not be able to be impersonated
ref: You posted it yourself, and no one will pretend to be you, right?

src: 我只能说你是文明的公敌
mt: I can only say that you are a civilized public enemy
ref: I can only say you’re the enemy of civilization.

src: 会心一笑
mt: A smile from the heart
ref: Smile

src: 美三航母集结中国周边 最强大武器罕见访问关岛 2022-01-17 多维 亲中共媒体多维报道：中美关系最新消息：最新卫星图像显示，美国三艘航母正在中国周边集结；美媒还披露，美国海军武器库中最强大的武器之一罕见访问关岛，对印太地区美国的盟友与敌手释放重要信号。
mt: U.S. Three Aircraft Carriers Rally Around China  Most Powerful Weapons Make Rare Visit to Guam 2022-01-17  Multidimensional Pro-CCP Media Multidimensional Report:China-U.S. Relations Update: The latest satellite image shows that three United States aircraft carriers are gathering around China. The U.S. media also disclosed that one of the most powerful weapons in the United States naval arsenal rarely visited Guam, sending important signals to allies and adversaries of the United States in the Indo-Pacific region.
ref: Three US aircraft carriers assemble around China; the most powerful weapons visit Guam in rare situation 2022-01-17 multidimensional Pro Communist media multidimensionally reports: latest news on China US Relation: the latest satellite image showed that three US aircraft carriers are assembling around China; US media also disclosed that one of the most powerful weapons in the US Navy’s arsenal in a rare case visited Guam, and sent an important signal to US allies and enemies in the Indo-Pacific region.

src: 据中国智库“南海战略态势感知平台”消息，1月9日，卫星在巴拉巴克海峡附近发现了美军“卡尔·文森”号（USS Carl Vinson）航母。
mt: According to the South China Sea Strategic Situational Awareness Platform, a think tank in China, satellites spotted the USS Carl Vinson near the Barabak Strait on January 9.
ref: According to Chinese think-tank “South China Sea Strategic Situation Detection Platform”, on January 9, the satellite found the USS Carl Vinson aircraft carrier from the US army near the Balabac Strait.

src: 巴拉巴克海峡连通南海和苏禄海，是西太平洋第一岛链上的战略要地。
mt: The Balabac Strait, which connects the South China Sea and the Sulu Sea,is a strategic location on the first island chain in the Western Pacific.
ref: Connecting the South China Sea and Sulu Sea, the Balabac Strait is a strategic place on the first island chain in the Western Pacific.

src: 该平台预计，“卡尔·文森”号将前往南海部署。
mt: The platform expects Carl Vinson to be deployed in the South China Sea.
ref: The platform predicts that Carl Vinson will do deployment at the South China Sea.

src: 这是“卡尔·文森”号航母首次搭载F-35C战斗机和CMV-22“鱼鹰”舰载运输机进行部署。
mt: This is the first deployment of the USS Carl Vinson with F-35C fighters and CMV-22 Ospreys.
ref: This will be the first time that Carl Vinson carries F-35C fighter and CMV-22 Osprey carrier transport aircraft to do the deployment.

src: 现在正在太平洋上游弋的美军航母，除了“卡尔·文森”号外，还有1月3日从美国出发的“亚伯拉罕·林肯”号（USS Abraham Lincoln）航母。
mt: In addition to the Carl Vinson, the USS Abraham Lincoln, which departed from the United States on 3 January, is now on the Pacific Ocean.
ref: In addition to Carl Vinson, the US aircraft carriers cruising in the Pacific Ocean now also include the USS Abraham Lincoln, which departed from the United States on January 3.

src: “林肯”号也首次搭载了F-35C舰载机中队，该中队隶属美国海军陆战队的第314战斗机攻击中队。
mt: For the first time, the USS Lincoln also carries a squadron of F-35Cs, which is part of the U.S. Marine Corps' 314th Fighter Attack Squadron.
ref: USS Abraham Lincoln also carried the F-35C carrier based aircraft squadron for the first time, which belongs to the 314th Fighter Attack Squadron of the US Marine Corps.

src: 除了上述两艘航母外，目前美国海军部署在亚太地区的还有停靠在日本横须贺的“里根”号（USS Ronald Reagan）航母。
mt: In addition to the above two carriers, the United States Navy is currently deployed in the Asia-Pacific region on the USS Ronald Reagan docked in Yokosuka, Japan.
ref: Apart from the above two aircraft carriers, the US Navy currently also deploys the USS Ronald Reagan aircraft carrier, which is docked in Yokosuka, Japan, in the Asia Pacific region.

src: 航母战斗群中还包括“尚普兰湖”号导弹巡洋舰、“斯托克达尔”号导弹驱逐舰等。
mt: The carrier strike group also includes the guided-missile cruiser USS Lake Champlain and the guided missile destroyer USS Stokdal.
ref: The aircraft carrier battle group also includes the missile cruiser “Champlain Lake” and guided missile destroyer “Stockdale”.

src: 美三航母集结中国周边 最强大武器罕见访问关岛 2022年1月17日，“南海战略态势感知平台”公布最新卫星图片，显示美军三艘航母正在中国周边集结。
mt: U.S. Three Aircraft Carriers Rally Around China  Most Powerful Weapons Make Rare Visit to Guam 2022-01-17  the "South China Sea Strategic Situational Awareness Platform" released the latest satellite image, showing that three U.S. aircraft carriers are gathering around China.
ref: Three US aircraft carriers are assembling around China; the most powerful weapon paid a visit to Guam in a rare case; on January 17, 2022, the “South China Sea Strategic Situation Detection Platform” released the latest satellite images, showing that three US aircraft carriers are assembling around China.

src: （微博@南海战略态势感知） 美三航母集结中国周边 最强大武器罕见访问关岛 2022年1月17日，美军舰载运输机CMV-22B飞行路线。
mt: (Weibo @South China Sea Strategic Situational Awareness) Three U.S. Aircraft Carrier Assembling Around China Most Powerful Weapons Rarely Visit Guam On January 17, 2022, the CMV-22B Flight Route of U.S. Carrier-based Transport Aircraft.
ref: (Weibo @SouthChinaSeaStrategicSituationDetection) three US aircraft carriers assembled around China; the most powerful weapon paid a visit to Guam in a rare case; on January 17, 2022, the flight route of the US carrier-borne transport aircraft CMV-22B.

src: （微博@南海战略态势感知） 另据美国有线电视新闻网（CNN）1月17日报道，美国海军武器库中最强大的武器之一上周末罕见地访问了关岛。
mt: (Weibo@South China Sea Strategic Situational Awareness) According to a January 17 report from the United States Cable News Network (CNN), one of the most powerful weapons in the United States Navy's arsenal visited Guam last weekend in a rare way.
ref: (Weibo @SouthChinaSeaStrategicSituationDetection) According to report of CNN on January 17, one of the most powerful weapons in the US Navy arsenal paid a visit to Guam in a rare case.

src: 载有20枚三叉戟（Trident）弹道导弹和数十枚核弹头的俄亥俄级核潜艇“内华达号”（USS Nevada）上周六（1月15日）驶入美国关岛海军基地。
mt: The Ohio-class nuclear submarine USS Nevada, carrying 20 Trident ballistic missiles and dozens of nuclear warheads, entered the United States naval base in Guam on Saturday, January 15.
ref: The Ohio class nuclear submarine USS Nevada, which carries 20 Trident ballistic missiles and dozens of nuclear warheads, entered the US naval base in Guam last Saturday (January 15).

src: 美三航母集结中国周边 最强大武器罕见访问关岛 分析称，这是向印度-太平洋地区日益紧张的局势中的盟友和敌人发出了一个信号。
mt: Three U.S. Aircraft Carriers Gathering the Most Powerful Weapons Around China the Most Powerful Weapons Around China Visit Guam Rarely  Analysts says it is a signal to allies and foes in the increasingly tense Indo-Pacific region.
ref: Three US aircraft carriers are assembling around China; the most powerful weapon paid a visit to Guam in a rare case; according to analysis, this is a signal to allies and enemies in the increasingly tense situation in the Indo-Pacific region.

src: 这是美国弹道导弹潜艇自2016年以来首次访问关岛，也是自20世纪80年代以来第二次公开访问关岛。
mt: This is the first visit to Guam by a United States ballistic missile submarine since 2016 and the second public visit to Guam since the 1980s.
ref: This is the first visit to Guam by a US ballistic missile submarine since 2016 and the second public visit to Guam since the 1980s.

src: 美三航母集结中国周边 最强大武器罕见访问关岛 中国近年来在南沙群岛修建大批军事设施。
mt: Three U.S. Aircraft Carriers Gather Around China Most Powerful Weapons Make Rare Visit to Guam China has built a large number of military facilities in the Spratly Islands in recent years.
ref: Three US aircraft carriers are assembling around China; the most powerful weapon paid a visit to Guam in a rare case; China has built a large number of military facilities in the Nansha Islands in recent years.

src: 图为中国在南沙群岛的永暑岛。
mt: The picture shows China's Yongshu Island in the Spratly Islands.
ref: The picture shows China’s Yongshu Island in the Nansha Islands.

src: （南海研究论坛） 美国海军在声明中称，俄亥俄级核潜艇“内华达号”此次对关岛的访问加强了美国和该地区盟友之间的合作，展示了美国的能力、灵活性、战备状态，以及对印太地区安全与稳定的持续承诺。
mt: (South China Sea Research Forum) The United States Navy said in a statement that the visit to Guam by the Ohio-class nuclear submarine USS Nevada strengthened cooperation between the United States and allies in the region, demonstrating the United States' ability, flexibility, readiness, and continued commitment to security and stability in the Indo-Pacific region.
ref: (South China Sea Research Forum) the U.S. Navy said in a statement that the visit of the Ohio class nuclear submarine “Nevada” to Guam strengthened the cooperation between the US and its allies in the region, demonstrated the ability, flexibility, combat readiness of the US, as well as its continued commitment to security and stability in the Indo-Pacific region.

src: 弹道导弹潜艇通常被称为“雷鸣潜艇”（Boomer submarine）。
mt: Ballistic missile submarines are often referred to as "Boomer submarines".
ref: Ballistic missile submarines are often called “Boomer submarines”.

src: 美国海军舰队中14艘“雷鸣潜艇”的行踪通常是被严格保密的。
mt: The whereabouts of the 14 "thunder submarines" in the United States naval fleet are generally kept strictly confidential.
ref: The whereabouts of the 14 “Boomer Submarines” in the US Navy fleet are usually strictly confidential.

src: 围绕着弹道导弹潜艇的秘密使“雷鸣潜艇”成为“核三位一体中最重要的生存武器”，这一体系还包括位于美国本土的发射井弹道导弹，以及B-2和B-52等可携带核弹头的轰炸机。
mt: The secrets surrounding ballistic missile submarines make the Thunder Submarine the "most important survivable weapon in the nuclear triad", a system that also includes silo-based ballistic missiles located in the continental United States and nuclear-capable bombers such as the B-2 and B-52.
ref: The secret surrounding ballistic missile submarines makes “Boomer Submarine" the “most important survival weapon in the Nuclear Trinity”; this system also includes launching silo ballistic missile located in the US, as well as bombers such as B-2 and B-52 that can carry nuclear warheads.

src: 跟朋友聊起最近Meta大跌 26%，市值蒸发 2510 亿美元，扎克伯格回应「面临前所未有的竞争」，原因为何？
mt: I was talking to a friend about Meta's recent 26% plunge and $251 billion market value evaporation.  Zuckerberg responded to why [facing unprecedented competition].
ref: I talked to my friend about the recent 26% plunge in Meta and its loss of US $251 billion in market value; Zuckerberg responded that he was “facing unprecedented competition”; why?

src: Meta（原 Facebook）实质是一家广告公司，收入主要来自于广告，今时今日赚钱的广告公司，自己是有流量渠道的。
mt: Meta (formerly Facebook) is essentially an advertising company whose revenue mainly comes from advertising. Today's profitable advertising company has its own traffic channels.
ref: Meta (formerly Facebook) is essentially an advertising company, whose revenue mainly comes from advertising; the advertising company that makes money today has its own channel for traffic.

src: Facebook，Instagram，Whatsapp 等等，无论什么样的功能定位，都是 Meta 的流量渠道。
mt: Facebook, Instagram, Whatsapp, etc., whatever the functional orientation, are the traffic channels of Meta.
ref: Regardless of its function positioning, Facebook, Instagram, Whatsapp, etc. are all channels of traffic for Meta.

src: 不仅如此，Meta 还是最大的”广告联盟”,很多 App 外接 Meta 的广告，通过 Meta 的广告平台是实现变现。
mt: Moreover, Meta is also the largest "advertising alliance". Many apps connect to Meta's advertising, and realizable value can be attained through Meta's advertising platform.
ref: Not only that, Meta is also the biggest “advertisement alliance”; Many apps are externally connected to Meta’s advertising, and they achieve realization through Meta’s advertising platform.

src: 但是，时代变了。
mt: But times have changed.
ref: But, the time has changed.

src: 第一，因为苹果隐私政策的调整，Meta 很难再拿到用户的数据信息，影响了广告投放的效率。
mt: First, due to the adjustment of Apple's privacy policy, it is difficult for Meta to obtain user data, which affects the efficiency of advertising.
ref: First, due to the adjustment of Apple’s privacy policy, it is difficult for Meta to get users’ data information now, which affects the efficiency of advertising.

src: 苹果现在的隐私政策对用户很友好，会很明显的提示用户是否允许 App 获取自己的信息，大多数人的正常反应肯定是不允许。
mt: Apple's current privacy policy is very user-friendly, and will clearly prompt users whether to allow Apps to obtain their own information. Most people's normal reactions are definitely not allowed.
ref: Apple’s current privacy policy is very user-friendly; it will use explicit prompt to ask users whether they allow apps to access their own information; most people’s normal reaction is definitely not to allow it.

src: 接下来如果 Google 再捅一刀，对 Meta 的收入影响还会更大。
mt: Next, if Google makes another move, it would have a greater impact on Meta's revenue.
ref: If Google stabs again next, it will have a greater impact on Meta’s revenue.

src: 第二，以前 Meta 的收入增长里的中国因素也弱化了（这个因素的比重不确定有多高，但确实存在）。
mt: Second, the China factor in Meta's previous revenue growth has also weakened (the proportion of this factor is uncertain, but it does exist).
ref: Second, the Chinese factor in Meta’s revenue growth has also been weakened (the proportion of this factor is uncertain, but it does exist).

src: 大家平时都知道 Meta 在中国是没有业务的，但是这个理解并不准确。
mt: As we all know, Meta has no business in China, but this understanding is not accurate.
ref: We all know that Meta doesn’t have business in China, but this understanding is not accurate.

src: 每年 Meta 至少10%的收入都来自中国，主要是中国做出海业务的公司贡献的。
mt: Every year, at least 10% of Meta's revenue comes from China, mainly contributed by companies engaged in overseas business in China.
ref: At least 10% of Meta’s revenue comes from China every year, mainly contributed by Chinese companies engaged in offshore business.

src: Meta 在香港的办公室大概几百人，在大陆还有几大代理商。
mt: Meta has around a few hundred people in its offices in Hong Kong and several agents in the mainland.
ref: There are around hundreds of staff at its Hong Kong office and several major agents in the mainland.

src: 中国公司想要拓展海外市场，Meta 都是绕不过的广告渠道，烧的钱大多都给了 Meta。
mt: Chinese companies want to expand overseas markets, Meta is an inescapable advertising channel, and most of the money they invested is given to Meta.
ref: When Chinese companies want to expand overseas market, Meta is an advertising channel that cannot be bypassed, and so most of the money is given to Meta.

src: 有意思的是，现在字节的 TT 是 Meta 主要的竞争对手之一，但是前两年 Meta 从字节身上可赚到不少钱。
mt: Interestingly, ByteDance's TT is now one of Meta's main competitors, but Meta made a lot of money from ByteDance two years ago.
ref: Interestingly, the TT of ByteDance now is one of Meta’s main competitors, but Meta made a lot of money from ByteDance in the past two years.

src: 国内各个代理都在帮字节去 Meta 那里投广告，Meta 大中华区的业绩也很不错。
mt: Domestic agencies are helping ByteDance advertise on Meta, and Meta Greater China also performs well.
ref: All domestic agents are helping ByteDance to do advertising at Meta, and Meta’s performance in Greater China is also very good.

src: 最近我没有专门去了解，但是肯定不会比之前好。
mt: I don't know much about it recently, but it's definitely not as good as before.
ref: I haven’t specifically learned about it recently, but it’s definitely not better than before.

src: 中国公司在海外大规模烧钱的阶段已经过去了。
mt: The stage of massive cash-burning overseas by Chinese companies has passed.
ref: The stage when Chinese companies were burning money overseas on a large scale has passed.

src: 第三，新的流量渠道拓展不顺利。
mt: Third, the expansion of new traffic channels is not smooth.
ref: Third, the expansion of new traffic channels is not smooth.

src: Facebook 越来越老了，新的包括 TT 在内的平台，都不在 Meta 手中。
mt: Facebook is getting older and new platforms, including TT, are not in the hands of Meta.
ref: Facebook is getting older, and new platforms including TT is not in the hands of Meta.

src: 最大的问题不仅仅是收入下滑，而是缺乏增长预期。
mt: The biggest problem is not just a decline in income, but a lack of growth expectations.
ref: The biggest problem is not the decline of revenue but lack of growth expectation.

src: 资本市场不仅仅看中收入，更重要的是看未来的预期怎么样。
mt: The capital market is not just about income, but more importantly about future expectations.
ref: The capital market not only focuses on income; more importantly, it depends on future expectations.

src: 很显然，Meta 的预期是不够的。
mt: Obviously, Meta's expectations are insufficient.
ref: Obviously, the expectation for Meta is not enough.

src: 为了给市场讲出新的故事，扎克伯格讲了 “元宇宙”.
mt: To tell the market a new story, Zuckerberg said, "The metaverse."
ref: In order to tell new stories to the market, Zuckerberg told the story about “Meta-universe”.

src: 元宇宙确实应该是未来的方向之一，但是元宇宙的实现周期比较长，这个故事在这两三年应该不足以支撑起 Meta 的市值。
mt: The metaverse should indeed be one of the future directions, but the realization cycle of the metaverse is relatively long, and this story should not be enough to support the market value of meta in the past two to three years.
ref: Meta-universe indeed should be one of the future directions, but the period of the realization of Meta-universe is long, and this story is not sufficient to support the market value of Meta.

src: 所以未来这两年，应该是 Meta 比较艰难的时期。
mt: Therefore, in the next two years, Meta will have a tough time.
ref: Therefore, the next two years should be a difficult time for Meta.

src: 别看脸书现在非常的风光，每年也有1,000亿到2,000亿美元的收入，实际上脸书现在危机感非常强，跟其他的互联网企业和高科技公司相比，没有什么好的安全的护城河。
mt: Although Facebook enjoys reputation now and has a huge  revenue of USD 100bn-200bn every year, it has a strong sense of crisis. Compared with other internet companies and high-tech companies, Facebook has no good security barrier.
ref: Although Facebook is very popular now with an annual income of US $100 billion to $200 billion; in fact, Facebook has a strong sense of crisis; compared with other Internet companies and high-tech companies, there is not any good security moat.

src: 虽然他的几款社交软件现在的日活比较高，也是主流的社交软件，比如Facebook，WhatsApp等等，但是面对tiktok的快速发展，脸书也没有什么信心，颠覆之间也就是眨眼的功夫。
mt: Although some of its social apps, such as Facebook and WhatsApp, have high DAUs, Facebook has little confidence in the rapid development of tiktok. Subversion can happen between the blink of an eye.
ref: Although the DAU of several of his social software is relatively high, and they are mainstream social software such as Facebook, WhatsApp; however, in the face of the rapid development of TikTok, Facebook has little confidence, and subversion could happen in the blink of an eye.

src: 而搞元宇宙这个可望而不可及的概念，短时间之内完全没有成功的希望，因此脸书非常的危险，这也是为什么扎克伯格又是换公司的名字，又是不停的寻找新的赛道的根本原因，但是我觉得他的赛道选择是错的，是一条不归路 以上是我的一些思考，供参考。
mt: The metaverse is an unreachable concept, and there is no hope of success in a short period of time. Therefore, Facebook is very dangerous. This is why Zuckerberg changed the name of the company and kept looking for new tracks. However, I think his track selection is wrong and it is a non-return path. The above is my thoughts for reference.
ref: The unattainable concept of meta universe has no hope of success in a short time, so Facebook is in danger; this is also the fundamental reason why Zuckerberg changed the name of the company and kept looking for new tracks, but I think his choice is wrong and there is no way back; the above is some of my thoughts for reference.

src: 第十七条 国家对注册消防工程师资格实行注册执业管理制度。
mt: Article 17 The State shall implement a registered practice management system for the qualification of registered fire engineers.
ref: Article 17 The state implements the registration and practice management system for the qualification of certified Fire Engineers.

src: 取得一级、二级注册消防工程师资格证书的人员，经注册方可以相应级别注册消防工程师名义执业。
mt: Personnel who have obtained the qualification certificates of Class I and Class II registered fire protection engineers can practice in the name of registered fire protection engineers of the corresponding level after registration.
ref: People who obtained the Level 1 and Level 2 qualification certificates of registered Fire Engineers can practice in the name of registered Fire Engineers of corresponding level.

src: 第十八条 公安部消防局是一级注册消防工程师资格的注册审批部门。
mt: Article 18 The Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security is a registered examination and approval department with the qualification of a first-class registered fire engineer.
ref: Article 18 The Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security is the registration and approval department of the qualification of Level 1 registered Fire Engineer.

src: 省、自治区、直辖市公安机关消防机构为二级注册消防工程师资格的注册审批部门，并负责一级注册消防工程师资格注册的初步审查工作。
mt: The fire department of the public security organs of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government is the registered examination and approval department for the qualification of Class II registered fire engineer, and is responsible for the preliminary examination of the registration of Class I registered fire engineer.
ref: The fire departments of the public security organs of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government are the registration and approval departments for the qualification of Level 2 registered Fire Engineers, and are responsible for the preliminary review of the qualification of registration of Level 1 registered Fire Engineers.

src: 第十九条 取得一级、二级注册消防工程师资格证书并申请注册的人员，应当受聘于一个经批准的消防技术服务机构或者消防安全重点单位，并通过聘用单位向本单位所在地(聘用单位属企业的，通过本企业向工商注册所在地)的公安机关消防机构提交注册申请材料。
mt: Article 19 Personnel who have obtained the qualification certificates of Class I and Class II registered fire protection engineers and apply for registration shall be employed by an approved fire protection technical service institution or key unit of fire safety, and submit registration application materials to the fire protection institution of the public security organ where the employer is located (if the employer is an enterprise, the enterprise shall submit registration application materials to the fire protection institution of the public security organ where the industrial and commercial registration is located).
ref: Article 19 A person who has obtained the qualification certificate of Level 1 and Level 2 registered Fire Engineer and applies for registration shall be employed by an approved fire protection technical service institution or key fire safety unit, and the employer shall submit registration application materials to the fire protection institution of the public security organ in the place where the employer is located (if the employer is an enterprise, it shall be submitted to the place where the industrial and commercial registration is located).

src: 第二十条 省、自治区、直辖市公安机关消防机构在收到申请人的注册申请材料后，对申请材料不齐全或者不符合法定形式的，应当当场或者在5个工作日内，一次 性告知申请人需要补正的全部内容，逾期不告知的，自收到申请材料之日起即为受理。
mt: Article 20 After receiving the registration application materials from the applicant, the fire department of the public security organ of the province, autonomous region or municipality directly under the Central Government shall inform the applicant of all the contents to be supplemented and corrected on the spot or within 5 working days if the application materials are incomplete or do not conform to the legal form. If the applicant fails to notify within the time limit, it shall be deemed as accepted from the date of receiving the application materials.
ref: Article 20 After receiving the registration application materials of the applicant, the fire protection institutions of the public security organs of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the central government shall inform the applicant of all the contents that need to be supplemented and corrected all at once on the spot or within 5 working days if the application materials are incomplete or do not conform to the legal form; if they fail to inform within the time limit, they will be accepted from the date of receiving the application materials.

src: 对受理或者不予受理的注册申请，均应当出具加盖本级公安机关消防机构专用印章和注明日期的书面凭证。
mt: The registration application accepted or rejected shall be provided with a written certificate stamped with the special seal of the fire department of the public security organ at the corresponding level and dated.
ref: For the registration applications that are accepted or rejected, a written certificate stamped with the special seal of the fire protection institution of the public security organ at the same level and date shall be issued.

src: 第二十一条 省、自治区、直辖市公安机关消防机构自受理注册申请之日起20个工作日内，按规定条件和程序完成一级注册消防工程师资格注册申请材料的初步审查工作和二级注册消防工程师资格的注册审批工作，并将一级注册消防工程师资格注册申请材料和初步审查意见报公安部消防局审批。
mt: Article 21 The fire departments of the public security organs of the provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the Central Government shall, within 20 working days from the date of accepting the registration application, complete the preliminary examination of the application materials for the registration of the first-class registered fire engineer and the registration and approval of the second-class registered fire engineer according to the prescribed conditions and procedures, and submit the application materials for the registration of the first-class registered fire engineer and the preliminary examination opinions to the fire department of the Ministry of Public Security for approval.
ref: Article 21 The fire protection institutions of the public security organs of provinces, autonomous regions and municipalities directly under the central government shall, within 20 working days after the date of accepting the registration application, complete the preliminary review of the application materials for the registration of the Level 1 registered Fire Engineer qualification and the registration and approval of the Level 2 registered Fire Engineer qualification according to the specified conditions and procedures, and submit the application materials for the registration of the Level 1 registered Fire Engineer qualification and the preliminary review opinions to the Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security for approval.

src: 公安部消防局应当自收到省级公安机关消防机构报送的申请材料和初步审查意见之日起，20个工作日内作出是否批准的决定。
mt: The fire department of the Ministry of Public Security shall make a decision on whether to approve or not within 20 working days from the date of receiving the application materials and preliminary review opinions submitted by the fire department of the provincial public security organ.
ref: The Fire Department of the Ministry of Public Security shall make a decision on whether to approve or not within 20 working days from the date of receiving the application materials and preliminary review opinions submitted by the Fire Department of the provincial public security organ.

src: 在规定的期限内不能作出批准决定的，应当将延长的期限和理由告知申请人。
mt: If the approval decision cannot be made within the specified period, the applicant shall be informed of the extended period and reasons.
ref: If the approval decision cannot be made within the prescribed time limit, the applicant shall be informed of the extended time limit and the reason.

src: 对作出不予批准决定的，应当书面说明理由，并告知申请人享有依法申请行政复议或者提起行政诉讼的权利。
mt: Where a decision on disapproval is made, the reasons shall be given in writing and the applicant shall be informed of the right to apply for administrative reconsideration or file an administrative lawsuit according to law.
ref: If the decision of disapproval is made, the reasons shall be explained in writing, and the applicant shall be informed of the right to apply for administrative reconsideration or file an administrative lawsuit according to law.

src: 第二十二条 注册审批部门应当自作出批准决定之日起10个工作日内，颁发、送达相应级别的注册证。
mt: Article 22 The registration approval department shall, within 10 working days from the date of making the approval decision, issue and deliver the registration certificate of the corresponding level.
ref: Article 22 The registration review and approval department shall issue and deliver the registration certificate of the corresponding level within 10 working days from the date of making the approval decision.

src: 第二十三条 注册证的每一注册有效期为3年。
mt: Article 23 Each registration certificate shall be valid for 3 years.
ref: Article 23 The period of validity is 3 years for each registration period of the registration certificate.

src: 注册证在有效期内是相应级别注册消防工程师的执业凭证，由注册消防工程师本人保管、使用。
mt: The registration certificate is the practicing certificate of the registered fire protection engineer of the corresponding level within the validity period, which shall be kept and used by the registered fire protection engineer himself.
ref: The registration certificate is the practicing certificate of the registered Fire Engineer of the corresponding level within the period of validity, which is kept and used by the registered Fire Engineer themselves.

src: 第二十四条 申请初始注册的，应当自取得一级、二级注册消防工程师资格证书之日起1年内提出申请。
mt: Article 24 To apply for initial registration, an application shall be made within one year from the date of obtaining the qualification certificates of Class I and Class II registered fire engineers.
ref: Article 24 Initial registration shall be applied within 1 year from the date of obtaining the qualification certificate of Level 1 and Level 2 registered Fire Engineer.

src: 逾期申请初始注册时，须符合本规定继续教育要求。
mt: Late applications for initial registration must meet the continuing education requirements of the Regulations.
ref: When applying for initial registration beyond the time limit, it must meet the requirements on continuing education in this Regulation.

src: 初始注册、延续注册、变更注册、注销注册和不予注册等注册管理的具体办法，由公安部另行规定。
mt: Specific measures for the administration of initial registration, renewal of registration, change of registration, cancellation of registration and denying registration shall be separately stipulated by the Ministry of Public Security.
ref: The specific measures for registration administration of initial registration, continuation of registration, change of registration, cancellation of registration and not-approved registration shall be separately formulated by the Ministry of Public Security.

src: 第二十五条 继续教育是注册消防工程师延续注册、重新注册和逾期初始注册的必备条件。
mt: Article 25 Continuing education is a necessary condition for the renewal, re-registration and overdue initial registration of registered fire protection engineers.
ref: Article 25 Continuation of Education is a necessary condition for the continuation of registration, re-registration and overdue initial registration of registered Fire Engineers.

src: 在每个注册有效期内，各级别注册消防工程师应当按照规定完成相应的继续教育。
mt: Within the validity period of each registration, registered fire engineers at all levels shall complete corresponding continuing education as required.
ref: Within the period of validity of each registration, registered Fire Engineer of different levels shall complete the corresponding continuation of education according to the regulations.

src: 第二十六条 注册审批部门应当及时向社会公告注册消防工程师注册有关情况，建立注册消防工程师诚信档案，对其执业活动实行信用管理。
mt: Article 26 The registration and approval department shall promptly announce to the public the relevant information on the registration of registered fire protection engineers, establish integrity files of registered fire protection engineers, and implement credit management for their practicing activities.
ref: Article 26 The registration review and approval department shall timely announce the registration of registered Fire Engineers to the public, establish the integrity archives of registered Fire Engineers, and implement credit management on their practices.

src: 第二十七条 各级注册消防工程师资格的注册管理部门，应当严格执行《中华人民共和国行政许可法》有关规定。
mt: Article 27 The administrative departments for registration of registered fire engineers at all levels shall strictly implement the relevant provisions of the Administrative License Law of the People's Republic of China.
ref: Article 27 The registration administration departments for the qualification of registered Fire Engineers at all levels shall strictly implement the relevant provisions of the Administrative License Law of the people’s Republic of China.

src: 今日的考试资讯分享到此为止，希望能给大家一些帮助。
mt: That's all for today's sharing of exam information，I hope I can help you.
ref: This is the end of the sharing of today’s examination information; I hope this will be helpful to you.

src: 大家一定要努力备考，争取早日通过消防工程师考试！
mt: Everyone must try their best to prepare for the examination and strive to pass the fire engineer examination as soon as possible!
ref: Everyone, please work hard on this and hopefully you will pass the Fire Engineer examination soon!

src: 实时分享金融/财会/建筑最新考试资讯。
mt: Share the latest financial/accounting/construction examination information in real time.
ref: Real time sharing of the latest examination information of Finance/ Accounting/Architecture.

src: 先说结论，我个人认为《四海》是一部全方位的烂片，从各种意义上来说都是。
mt: To conclude, I personally think the Four Seas is a full-length shit, in all respects.
ref: I will say my conclusion first; I think Only Fools Rush In is utterly a terrible film in any sense.

src: 但你要说这部电影是不是一个亮点也没有，那倒也不是至少配乐选的挺好。
mt: But if you say that this film is not a highlight, it is not at least a good choice.
ref: But it is not without any highlight; at least the music is good.

src: 烂片分很多种，让你能在电影院里酣然入睡的算一种，让你看完后义愤填膺的也算一种，《四海》对观众来说就像是峨眉山上的猴子，它能用无数种方式来点燃你的怒火。
mt: A lot of kinds of shit, you can fall asleep in the movie theater is one, you can see the aftermath of anger is also one, the Four Seas for the audience is like a monkey on the ears, it can in countless ways to light up your anger.
ref: There are many types of terrible films; some make you sleep soundly in the cinema, some make you angry after watching it; Only Fools Rush In is like monkeys on Mount Emei; it can ignite your anger in countless ways.

src: 在侮辱观众这点上，韩寒真的是天赋绝伦。
mt: In this point of insulting the audience, Korean is truly talented.
ref: Han Han is super talented in insulting the audience.

src: 这部片子最让人感到痛苦的就是它仿佛是克系小说里的造物，难以名状，漏洞多的就像是小马哥身上的风衣。
mt: The most painful thing about this film is that it seems to be a creature in the novel, difficult to name, and there are many flaws like the shirt on the body of the little Mago.
ref: The most painful part of the film is that it is hard to describe like a monster in Cthulhu novels, and has as many loopholes as the holes on the trench coat on Javier Mascherano.

src: 甚至看完后你会怀疑这里面是否有导演暗含的隐喻，但当你仔细思考之后发现它其实就是一坨屎。
mt: Even after viewing it, you’ll doubt if there’s a metaphor of the director’s implication, but when you think about it carefully, you find it’s actually shit.
ref: After watching it, you may even wonder if there is metaphors the director planted in it; but you will find that it is only a piece of shit after close examination.

src: 先简单的说下我很难理解的一些情节。
mt: First, let me explain a few things that I find difficult to understand.
ref: I’ll first briefly talk about some plots that are hard to understand.

src: 男主居住地应该是偏南方的某个小岛上，和他的奶奶相依为命。
mt: The man's home should be on a small island in the south, with his grandmother.
ref: The male leading role lives with his grandma on some island in the south.

src: 她奶奶有个愿望是想看下雪，然后剧情就安排邻里中的一个大爷开着小面包车送她去东北看雪。
mt: Her grandmother had a desire to see the snow, and then the story arranged a gentleman in the neighborhood to drive her to the northeast to see the snow.
ref: His grandma has a wish, watching the snow, and the a old male neighbor drove a minibus to take her to watch the snow in the Northeast.

src: 高龄老人坐着面包车从南方到东北看雪？？
mt: Old man sitting in the car from the south to the northeast to see the snow?
ref: An elderly goes to watch the snow in the northeast from the south in a minibus? ?

src: 他和他爹对此还非常放心。
mt: He and his father are very reassured.
ref: He and his father were okay with it.

src: 然后这位老人就没下文了。
mt: The old man is not below.
ref: And then there is no follow-up on this old lady.

src: 在废弃轮船上开酒店，女主他哥怎么拿到营业执照的？
mt: Opening a hotel on an abandoned boat, how did the owner get a business license?
ref: Opening a hotel on an abandoned ship; how does the brother of the female leading role get the license?

src: 岛上飞车党小混混为什么能轻轻松松就把一段山路做到封路？？
mt: Why can the island's flying car party small mess easily block a mountain road?
ref: How do the racing bike gang on the island easily block a mountain road? ?

src: 然后路中间送钢筋的卡车就停在路边，四周连卡车司机都找不到。
mt: Then the truck that sent the steel pipe in the middle of the road stopped on the side of the road, not even the truck driver could be found.
ref: Then the truck delivering steel bars in the middle of the road just stopped at the roadside, and the truck driver was nowhere to be found.

src: 这道具感也太明显了吧。
mt: This feeling is too obvious.
ref: They are obviously props.

src: 一个征信不行的且有违法嫌疑的小混混飞车党为什么会成为一名辅警？
mt: Why would a small blunder car party suspected of violating the law become an auxiliary policeman?
ref: Why could a little gangster biker with poor credit and who was suspected of breaking the law become an auxiliary policeman?

src: 面对高利贷为啥不报警，电影里警察还特地问了是否有难处？
mt: In the face of Goliath loan, why not call the police, the police in the movie also asked specifically whether there were difficulties?
ref: Why didn’t he call the police when there was usury involved, and the police specifically asked if there was any problem.

src: 一个成年人懂得用智能手机，却不知道在旅馆如何用房卡开门，然后强行安排找不到旅馆老板，坐在房间门外睡一宿？
mt: An adult who knows how to use a smartphone, but does not know how to open the door in a hotel with a room card, then forcefully arrange not to find the hotel owner, sitting outside the room door to sleep?
ref: An adult who knows how to use smart phone doesn’t know how to use the card to open the door at the hotel, and it was forcefully arranged for him not being able to find the owner of the hotel and so he slept outside the hotel for the night?

src: 这种莫名其妙的情节充斥在整个影片里，由于情节过于离谱以至于我回忆它们时都会令我感到痛苦。
mt: This bizarre plot is filled with the whole film, and it’s so unspectical that it hurts me when I recall them.
ref: Such ridiculous plots were everywhere in the film; the plots are so ridiculous that I feel painful when I remember them.

src: 除了情节外，更糟糕的是电影的主旨，或者说这电影根本没有主旨，就是一个面目可憎的缝合怪。
mt: In addition to the plot, what is worse is the main purpose of the film, or that the film has no subject at all, is a look disgusting seamless.
ref: In addition to the plots, the theme of the film is even more terrible, or you can say there is no theme in the film; it’s just a horrible monster that is stitched together.

src: 影片开头你会以为他想拍个喜剧片，20多分钟后你猜它也许是个励志片，看一半时你觉得它可能是个想体现小镇青年生存不易的剧情片，看完后你就压根也不知道自己究竟看了个啥，随之而来的是对自己深深的怀疑，大过年的为什么要跑到电影院去欣赏大便。
mt: At the beginning of the film you will think he wants to shoot a comedy, more than 20 minutes later you guess it may be an incentive film, half of the time you think it may be a drama that wants to reflect the survival of small town youth, after watching you do not know exactly what you watched, followed by deep doubts about yourself, why over the years to run to the cinema to admire sputum.
ref: In the beginning of the film, you may think he wants to make a comedy; after twenty minutes, you may guess it’s an inspiration film; after a half of it, you may think it’s a drama showcasing the hardship of a small town boy; after you watch all of it, you don’t even know what you have watched; what follows is deep doubt in yourself; why would you go to the cinema to watch a piece of shit during the Spring Festival?

src: 对于大部分人来说其实也都非常熟悉各类电影的套路了，比如你要想拍摩托车手，那就励志＋喜剧然后告诉观众一个有天赋的菜鸟是如何一步步走向成功的。
mt: For most people, they are actually very familiar with all kinds of movies, such as if you want to shoot a motorcycle driver, then encourage + comedy and tell the audience how a talented cookbird is step by step towards success.
ref: Most people are familiar with the routines of various films; for example, if you want to make a film about a biker, then make it an inspiration + comedy to tell the audience how a talented rookie achieves success step by step.

src: 第十八届“世界饮料创新奖”（World Beverage Innovation Awards）是FoodBev Media与德国纽伦堡国际啤酒、酿酒及饮料工业展览会（Brau Beviale）联合举办的奖项。
mt: The eighteenth World Beverage Innovation Awards is a joint award organised by FoodBev Media and the Brau Beviale International Beer, Wine and Beverage Industry Exhibition in Nuremberg, Germany.
ref: The 18th “World Beverage Innovation Awards” is an award jointly held by FoodBev Media and Brau Beviale.

src: 吸引了来自25个国家、22个不同品类的279个作品参赛。
mt: The competition attracted 279 works from 25 countries and 22 different categories.
ref: It attracted 279 works from 25 countries and 22 categories to participate in the competition.

src: 10月15日，决赛入围者名单公布，最终获奖者名单将于11月11日（英国夏令时）线上公布。
mt: The finalists will be announced on October 15 and the final winners will be announced online on November 11 (Summer Time).
ref: On October 15th, the list of the finalists was published, and the final list of winners will be published online on November 11 (BST).

src: 我们看到，元气森林的LP28无糖酸奶入围最佳乳饮料奖，伊利安慕希的“GOGO武汉”营销入围最佳营销活动，百事可乐和人民日报新媒体合作的包装还入围最佳包装设计/标签奖。
mt: We see that the LP28 sugar-free yogurt of Yongji Forest is included in the best dairy beverage award, the "GOGO Wuhan" marketing of Illian Muchi is included in the best marketing campaign, and the packaging of PepsiCo and People's Daily New Media collaboration is also included in the best packaging design / label award.
ref: We have seen that Genki Forest’s LP28 sugar-free yoghurt was shortlisted for the Award of Best Milk Drink; the marketing of “GOGO Wuhan” of Yili AMBROSIAL was shortlisted for the Award of Best Marketing Activity; the packaging jointly designed by Pepsi and the new media of People’s Daily was shortlisted for the Award of Best Packaging Design/Label.

src: FoodBev Media高级市场营销总监Laura Nettle表示：我们很高兴与Brau Beviale一起庆祝年度世界饮料创新奖的第18年。
mt: Laura Nettle, Senior Marketing Director at FoodBev Media, said: “We are delighted to celebrate the 18th year of the World Beverage Innovation Award with Brau Beviale.
ref: Laura Nettle, senior marketing director of Foodbev Media, said, “we are pleased to celebrate the 18th year of the annual world beverage innovation award with Brau beviale”.

src: 从新口味、新概念和新功能到品牌、包装和制造，随着行业不断以更可持续的方式进行创新，我们看到了饮料行业的趋势。
mt: From new tastes, new concepts and new features to branding, packaging and manufacturing, we see trends in the beverage industry as the industry continues to innovate in a more sustainable way.
ref: From new tastes, new concepts, new functions to brands, packaging and manufacturing, as the industry continues to innovate in a more sustainable way, we have seen the trends of the beverage industry.

src: 世界饮料创新奖表彰了全球饮料行业新老品牌今年最具雄心的新产品和新发展。
mt: The World Beverage Innovation Award recognizes the new and old brands in the global beverage industry for the most ambitious new products and new developments this year.
ref: The world beverage innovation award recognizes the most ambitious new products and developments of new and old brands in the global beverage industry this year.

src: 以下是每个类别的决赛入围者的完整榜单。
mt: Below is a complete list of finalists for each category.

src: 2021年什么最火？

src: 无疑是东京奥运会。
mt: The Tokyo Olympics.
ref: It was none other than the Tokyo Olympics.

src: 您以为只有奥运健儿才能拿奖吗？
mt: Do you think only the Olympics can win the prize?
ref: Do you think only Olympic athletes can win awards?

src: 前段时间有篇《快看！项目经理可冲击金牌的奥运项目》文章很火，里面提到项目经理们在很多项目上，绝对是可以一马当先，无人能匹： 搬砖、出差、熬夜是项目经理的日常，救火、背锅、道歉更是不在话下。
mt: The previous period of time there was an article "Have a look! project manager can hit gold medal Olympic project" article is very fiery, in which the project managers in many projects, absolutely can be a horse in advance, no one can match: moving bricks, traveling, staying overnight is the project manager's daily, fire rescue, bacon, apology is not in the words.
ref: Recently, there is an article titled Look! An article titled Olympic Disciplines in Which Project Managers Can Win Gold Medals was viral, and it mentioned that project managers can be the foremost and unmatched in many disciplines, such as working arduously, going on business trips, and staying up late, the everyday work of project manager, and handling emergency, taking the blame and apologizing are nothing difficult at all.

src: 看似玩笑调侃的一篇文章，却也道出了项目经理们的日常辛酸，背后代表的是对当前项目管理工作的力不从心。
mt: A seemingly joking article, but also outlines the daily bitterness of project managers, behind which is the lack of attention to the current project management work.
ref: A seemingly joking article also tells the bitterness of their daily work, and the hidden message is their insufficient energy to handle the current project management work.

src: 而从事项目管理工作的人员，也渐渐选择通过一些行动来让自己摆脱工作中的困境。
mt: And people engaged in project management work, also gradually choose to get rid of the difficulty in the work through some actions.
ref: People engaged in project management also gradually choose to get rid of the predicament in work by taking certain actions.

src: 从每年攀升的PMP（国际认证的项目管理专业人士资格）报名人数来看，越来越多的项目管理从业人员通过学习来提升自己的项目管理能力。
mt: From the year-on-year rise in PMP (International Accredited Project Management Professional Qualification) enrollment, more and more project management practitioners improve their project management skills through learning.
ref: Judging from the increasing number of PMP (internationally certified project management professional qualification) applicants each year, increasing project management practitioners improve their project management ability through learning.

src: 据《中国项目管理二十年发展报告(1999-2019)》称：截止到2019年9月，全国累计PMP®报考人数近60万人次，通过PMP®认证人数约42万人，有效持证人数约30万人, 占全球PMP®持证总量的31.2%。
mt: According to the "China Project Management Twenty-Year Development Report (1999-2019)": As of September 2019, the national cumulative PMP® application number was 600,000, the PMP® certification number was approximately 420,000, and the effective holding number was about 300,000, accounting for 31.2% of the global PMP® holding total.
ref: According to the 20-year Development Report on China’s Project Management (1999-2019), as of September 2019, the national PMP ® applicants totals 600,000, with 420,000 passed the PMP ® certification, and the number of valid certificate holders are about 300,000, accounting for 31.2% of the total number of certificates of PMP ® in the world.

src: 近10年PMP持证人数逐年递增，这说明越来越多的项目管理者意识到：靠简单照搬以往“老经验”来做事已不可取，瞬息万变的工作环境让我们知道一个要学会，站在科学巨人的肩膀上去探索前行的道路。
mt: In the past 10 years, the number of PMP certificates has increased year by year, which shows that more and more project managers realize that it is no longer desirable to do things by simply taking pictures of past "old experiences", and the rapidly changing working environment let us know one to learn, stand on the shoulders of science giants to explore the way forward.
ref: In the past ten years, the number of people holding PMP certificates keeps increasing, which indicates that more and more project managers realize it is no longer advisable to do things by simply copying “past experience”; the rapidly changing working environment tells us that we should learn to stand on the shoulders of scientific giants and explore the way forward.

src: 然而，考了PMP就能保证项目管理工作畅通无阻了吗？
mt: However, can PMP ensure that project management works smoothly?
ref: However, can you ensure the smooth proceeding of project management work after passing the PMP test?

src: 很多项目管理初学者表示，通过学习PMP/IPMP等相关课程，可以系统性地掌握项目管理的十大领域和五大过程组等相关知识点，但真正进行项目管理工作的时候却还是一头雾水。
mt: Many project management beginners say that by studying related courses such as PMP / IPMP, you can systematically master the top ten areas of project management and five major process groups, but when you really do project management work, it is still a fog.
ref: Many beginners of project management say that by learning courses of PMP/IPMP, they can systematically master knowledge points such as the ten fields and five major process groups of project management, but they are still confused when they are actually engaged in project management work.

src: 很多项目经理常常反馈以下问题： 项目管理认知不到位，单纯依靠个人经验，空有项目管理理论，不知如何实践； 缺乏系统的项目管理流程制度支撑，工作中无法落地，项目预估不准，把控度灵敏度差，项目一拖再拖； 成员分工不明确、团队中的“老油条”不知如何应对 跨部门协助沟通不顺畅，项目难以推进 ……
mt: Many project managers often feedback on the following questions: project management awareness is not in place, simply relying on personal experience, empty project management theory, not knowing how to practice; lack of system of project management process system support, work cannot land, project forecast is not permitted, the control sensitivity is poor, the project is delayed and delayed; members' division of work is not clear, the "old oil line" in the team does not know how to respond to cross-departmental assistance communication is not smooth, the project is difficult to advance.
ref: Many project managers often reflect the following problems: project management awareness is not sufficient, relying solely on personal experience, and there is only project management theories and no ideas about how to practice them; lack of support of systematic project management process and system, unable to actually implement the work, inaccurate project estimation, poor sensitivity of control, and project being delayed again and again; the members’ division of labor is not clear, there’s no way to handle the “sophisticated ones” in the team, communication is not smooth between departments, and it is difficult to push the project forward...

src: 因此，专注产品创新与研发管理领域十余载，已帮助众多优秀的企业培养了大批的产品经理、项目经理等研发关键人才，并获得了 “中国企业研发管理人才培训示范基地”等荣誉称号的中天华夏咨询带着《研发项目经理特训营》线上课程来了。
mt: Therefore, focusing on product innovation and R & D management in the field of more than ten loads, has helped numerous excellent enterprises to train a large number of product managers, project managers and other key research and development talents, and obtained the honorary title of "Chinese enterprises R & D and management talents training demonstration base" and other "R&D project manager special training camp" online course.
ref: Therefore, ZTCHINA, which has been focusing on the field of product innovation and R&D of management for more than ten years and helped many excellent enterprises cultivate a large number of key R&D talents such as product managers and project managers, and won the honorary title of “China Enterprise R&D and Management Talents Training Demonstration Base”, presents the online course R&D Project Manager Special Training Camp.

src: 《研发项目经理特训营》线上课程 这是一种线上碎片化学习的方式，结合了众多研发型企业的实战案例、工具和方法，帮助您掌握项目经理必备知识及标准动作，走上自身项目管理的进阶之路。
mt: This is an online method of fragmented learning, combining practical cases, tools and methods of many R&D-based enterprises, to help you master the necessary knowledge and standard actions of project managers and take the path of project management.
ref: The online course R&D Project Manager Special Training Camp is an online fragmented learning method, which combines the practical cases, tools and methods of many research and development type enterprises to help you master the necessary knowledge and standard actions of project managers, and embark on the advancing journey of project management on your own.

src: 这也是一次让企业用更低的成本和更少的投入，促进项目经理的培养进程，为企业带来高效运作结果的机会。
mt: It is also an opportunity for enterprises to facilitate the training process of project managers with lower costs and less investment, and bring efficient operating results to the enterprise.
