mt: The decision not to approve shall be justified in writing and the applicant shall be informed of the right to apply for administrative reconsideration or to initiate administrative proceedings in accordance with the law.
ref: If the decision of disapproval is made, the reasons shall be explained in writing, and the applicant shall be informed of the right to apply for administrative reconsideration or file an administrative lawsuit according to law.

src: 第二十二条 注册审批部门应当自作出批准决定之日起10个工作日内，颁发、送达相应级别的注册证。
mt: Article 22 The registration and approval department shall, within 10 working days from the date of the approval decision, issue and deliver a registration certificate of the corresponding level.
ref: Article 22 The registration review and approval department shall issue and deliver the registration certificate of the corresponding level within 10 working days from the date of making the approval decision.

src: 第二十三条 注册证的每一注册有效期为3年。
mt: Article 23 Each registration of a registration certificate shall be valid for three years.
ref: Article 23 The period of validity is 3 years for each registration period of the registration certificate.

src: 注册证在有效期内是相应级别注册消防工程师的执业凭证，由注册消防工程师本人保管、使用。
mt: The registration certificate is a practice certificate of the corresponding level of registered fire engineer and is kept and used by the registered fire engineer himself.
ref: The registration certificate is the practicing certificate of the registered Fire Engineer of the corresponding level within the period of validity, which is kept and used by the registered Fire Engineer themselves.

src: 第二十四条 申请初始注册的，应当自取得一级、二级注册消防工程师资格证书之日起1年内提出申请。
mt: Article 24 An application for initial registration shall be submitted within one year from the date of obtaining the certificate of fire engineer qualification at the first and second level.
ref: Article 24 Initial registration shall be applied within 1 year from the date of obtaining the qualification certificate of Level 1 and Level 2 registered Fire Engineer.

src: 逾期申请初始注册时，须符合本规定继续教育要求。
mt: When applying for late initial registration, the requirements for continuing education must be met in accordance with these provisions.
ref: When applying for initial registration beyond the time limit, it must meet the requirements on continuing education in this Regulation.

src: 初始注册、延续注册、变更注册、注销注册和不予注册等注册管理的具体办法，由公安部另行规定。
mt: Specific measures for registration management such as initial registration, continued registration, change of registration, cancellation of registration and non-registration shall be specified separately by the Ministry of Public Security.
ref: The specific measures for registration administration of initial registration, continuation of registration, change of registration, cancellation of registration and not-approved registration shall be separately formulated by the Ministry of Public Security.

src: 第二十五条 继续教育是注册消防工程师延续注册、重新注册和逾期初始注册的必备条件。
mt: Article 25 Continuing education is a necessary condition for registered fire engineers to continue registration, re-registration and late initial registration.
ref: Article 25 Continuation of Education is a necessary condition for the continuation of registration, re-registration and overdue initial registration of registered Fire Engineers.

src: 在每个注册有效期内，各级别注册消防工程师应当按照规定完成相应的继续教育。
mt: Within the period of validity of each registration, the registered fire engineers of all levels shall complete the corresponding continuing education in accordance with the regulations.
ref: Within the period of validity of each registration, registered Fire Engineer of different levels shall complete the corresponding continuation of education according to the regulations.

src: 第二十六条 注册审批部门应当及时向社会公告注册消防工程师注册有关情况，建立注册消防工程师诚信档案，对其执业活动实行信用管理。
mt: Article 26 The department for registration and approval shall promptly register fire engineers with the public announcement, establish a registered fire engineer's integrity file, and carry out credit management on their activities.
ref: Article 26 The registration review and approval department shall timely announce the registration of registered Fire Engineers to the public, establish the integrity archives of registered Fire Engineers, and implement credit management on their practices.

src: 第二十七条 各级注册消防工程师资格的注册管理部门，应当严格执行《中华人民共和国行政许可法》有关规定。
mt: Article 27 The registration and management departments of fire engineers at all levels shall strictly implement the relevant provisions of the Administrative Licensing Law of the People's Republic of China.
ref: Article 27 The registration administration departments for the qualification of registered Fire Engineers at all levels shall strictly implement the relevant provisions of the Administrative License Law of the people’s Republic of China.

src: 今日的考试资讯分享到此为止，希望能给大家一些帮助。
mt: Today's exam information has been shared here, hopefully it will help you.
ref: This is the end of the sharing of today’s examination information; I hope this will be helpful to you.

src: 大家一定要努力备考，争取早日通过消防工程师考试！
mt: Everyone must try to prepare for the fire engineer exam early!
ref: Everyone, please work hard on this and hopefully you will pass the Fire Engineer examination soon!

src: 实时分享金融/财会/建筑最新考试资讯。
mt: Share the latest financial/financial/building exam information in real time.
ref: Real time sharing of the latest examination information of Finance/ Accounting/Architecture.

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that I find very meaningful...first aid certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skills certificates that I find important besides the driver’s license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Let’s popularize it: first aid measures actually means emergency rescue in the event of an emergency, that is, the rescue before an ambulance arrives.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is actually still a period of time before the ambulance arrives after an accident, and it is this period of time that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is the time when emergency help is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I do have a heart attack, a brain haemorrhage, or a respiratory arrest, then our window of life will only be four minutes, the golden four minutes!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So people around you know how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls, we can rescue him with our professional knowledge, instead of just standing there motionless and doing nothing. This feeling of helplessness is so terrifying.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: “In China, we have official statistics claiming that three million people die each year accidently, the most dangerous of which is called cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, on average 15% of people will be rescued.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In Las Vegas casino hotels, 70 to 80 percent can be rescued, while in Shanghai and Beijing it is less than 1 percent."
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, founder of First Response, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If an individual has cardiac arrest, with no breathing or heartbeat, pinchling the person will be of no use.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: In order to save the person, artificial respiration and chest compressions are required.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I find that few of us currently have the awareness to learn first aid, but when something happens it is too late, which is why I appeal to everyone to learn this skill in order to have a timely response when faced with emergencies.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: Maybe it might even save someone’s life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: You can register your first aid certificate in your local Red Cross Society training center. I registered at the Red Cross Society Training Center in Zhuhai; there are also discounts for students.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is to record the goals that I have to accomplish before I turn 25 years old. It was also a few months ago that I added the first aid certificate to the goal list, but it has indeed been completed!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Then, I will be going to take other certification test; I plan to test a diving certificate. I saw there is also a diving first aid certificate in Xiaohongshu. I seem to need a first aid certificate before I can go for the test, so the first aid certificate is actually quite helpful!
ref: Next, I will apply for other certificates; I plan to get Diving Certificate; I saw on Red earlier that there is a Diving First Aid Certificate, which requires a Certificate of First Aid first, so getting a Certificate of First Aid is useful!

src: 1.本店合作快递公司，
mt: 1. Our store cooperates with courier companies:
ref: 1. Cooperating delivery companies of our store,

src: 1）合作快递以旺旺签名为准！
mt: 1) The cooperative express delivery is subject to WANT’s signature!
ref: 1) Refer to our Ali Want slogan for our cooperating delivery companies!

src: 2）顺丰快递
mt: 2) SF Express
ref: 2) SF-express

src: 2.买家急需产品或有时效限制，建议选择顺风快递，建议到付，顺丰相对有所保证，修改运费后再付款。
mt: 2. The buyer is in urgent need of the product or has a time limit. We suggest you choose Shunfeng Express delivery. It is recommended to pay on delivery as Shunfeng Express is relatively guaranteed. You can pay after modifying the shipping fee.
ref: 2. It is recommended to choose SF-express delivery with payment upon arrival for buyers who need the products urgently or need to receive it within a time range; SF is relatively secure and you may pay after the shipping fee is edited.

src: 3.买家对本店的运费收取有疑问，可选运费到付。
mt: 3. Buyers have questions about our store's freight charges and can choose to pay the freight on delivery.
ref: 3. If you have doubts about the shipping fee of our store, you may choose payment upon arrival.

src: 4.重物产品一般发物流，另行联系。
mt: 4. Heavy products will generally be delivered through logistics. Please contact us separately.
ref: 4. Heavy products are sent by express companies; please contact us separately.

src: 1.本店支持7天退换货服务，由于产品质量及发错数量问题，本店承担运费。
mt: 1. Our shop supports 7-day return and exchange service. Due to product quality and wrong quantity, our shop will bear the shipping costs.
ref: 1. Our store supports seven-day return and exchange service; our store will bear the freight if there is a problem of product quality or if the quantity of products is wrong.

src: 2.非产品本身质量问题，由于买家选错型号及其他因素需要退换货，在不影响产品本身功能没有问题及不影响二次销售的，本店支持除运费外的免费退换货服务，来回运费运费需要买件承担。
mt: 2. If it is not the quality problem of the product itself, the buyer needs to return or exchange the product due to the buyer selecting the wrong model and other factors. If the product's own functions are not affected or will not affect the secondary sales, our store supports free return and exchange services except the freight charges. The shipping cost needs to be borne by the purchasers.
ref: 2. If you need to exchange or return the products due to reasons other than the quality of the product itself, such as the buyer choosing the wrong model or other factors, our store supports free exchange and return services under the condition that the function of the products or a second sale is not affected, and the shipping fee back and forth shall be borne by the buyer.

src: 3.本店不支持以快递延误而造成需要退货，且需要卖家承担运费诉求。
mt: 3. Our store does not support returns due to delivery delays, and the seller is required to bear the freight charges.
ref: 3. Our store does not support return of product and the appeal for the seller to bear the shipping fee due to delay of express delivery.

src: 4.定制产品非质量问题不予退换货。
mt: 4. Customized products will not be returned or exchanged if they have non-quality problems.
ref: 4. Exchange or return of customized products is not supported unless there is quality issue.

src: 1.本品是原装正品？
mt: 1. Is this product original?
ref: 1. Is this product original and authentic?

src: 答：未注明原厂品牌的一律国产替代产品。
mt: Answer: All products that do not specify the original brand are domestic replacement products.
ref: Answer: Those with no specified original brand are all domestic-made substitute products.

src: 2.本店有仿品吗？
mt: 2. Are there any imitation products in our store?
ref: 2. Is there counterfeit in this store?

src: 答：很抱歉，本店不出售高仿产品，所谓高仿产品，具有原厂的LOGO与包装。
mt: Answer: Sorry, our store does not sell high imitation products. The so called high imitation products have the original LOGO and packaging.
ref: Answer: Sorry, our store doesn’t sell high-level counterfeit products, which have the LOGO and package of the original factory.

src: 3.国产xxx，是原厂在中国生产的吗？
mt: 3. Is the domestic xxx originally manufactured in China?
ref: 3. Is domestic made xxx made in an original factory in China?

src: 答：国产的是替代产品，非原厂在中国生产的产品，只是国内都沿用该说法。
mt: Answer: Domestically produced products are substitute products. Products that are not made by original factories in China are only used domestically.
ref: Answer: The domestic-made ones are substitute products, not products made in the original factory in China; it’s just that it is described as that in our country.

src: 专业提供三菱，安川，台达，松下，欧姆龙，西门子等国产伺服、PLC的连接电缆、接头等周边配件，主要包括伺服编码器、电源电缆、控制接头、电源航空插头、端子台及电缆、锂电池、PLC程序下载线、连接线等，刹车电阻 ，现场总线，电线电缆，所有配件均严格按照三菱标准，专业工程师定做。
mt: Specializing in supplying domestic servo and PLC connection cables and connectors from Mitsubishi, Yaskawa, Delta, Panasonic, Omron, Siemens, etc., the accessories mainly include servo encoders, power cables, control connectors, power aviation plugs, terminal blocks and cables, lithium batteries, PLC program download lines, and connection lines, etc., braking resistors, field buses, wires and cables. All accessories are in strict compliance with Mitsubishi’s standards and are customized by professional engineers.
ref: We specialize in providing connecting cables, connectors and other accessories of Mitsubishi, Yaskawa, Delta, Panasonic, Omron, Siemens and other domestic servo and PLC, mainly including servo coder, power cable, control connector, power aviation plug, terminal block and cable, lithium battery, PLC program download cable, connecting cable, brake resistance, fieldbus, wires and cables, and all accessories are customized by professional engineers strictly in accordance with Mitsubishi standards.

src: 并采用伺服与PLC实际测试把关，以确保为客户提供优质耐用的产品。
mt: And adopt the actual testing of servo and PLC to ensure that we provide customers with high-quality and durable products.
ref: And servo and PLC are adopted to conduct actual tests so as to provide the customers with durable products with high-quality.

mt: Welcome to inquiries!
ref: You are welcome to enquire about the price!

ref: Zhengzhou Yixin is a specialized manufacturer of concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, inspection shaft building block machinery and shaft wall module equipment, with semi-automatic and automatic production lines.

src: 通过多年的实践和开发，现具备了质量过硬，主要生产液压式、移动式、全自动化检查井系列设备及配套装置。

ref: Based on practice and development of many years, it is engaged in production of high quality hydraulic type, mobile type and automatic inspection shaft series of equipment and supporting devices.

src: 检查井混凝土模块生产加工设备 郑州井壁砖模块设备的特点及优势:
mt: Inspection well concrete module production and processing equipment Zhengzhou well wall brick module equipment features and advantages:
ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the characteristics and advantages of Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment

src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。
mt: Yixin inspection well block brick making machine equipment is widely used in new masonry materials for municipal underground structures such as coal, heat, water, electricity, and gas.
ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: various inspection wells for drainage and water storage facilities, rainwater inlets, square ditches, septic tanks, small structures, bridge wing walls, etc.
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper, lower, left and right sides of the modules are all concave-convex groove structure, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shear resistance of shaft walls is far superior to that of flat friction masonry.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure. After the combined masonry work is done, the vertical holes and the horizontal holes are connected. After the hole core is being poured, it forms a cast-in-place concrete network structure which plays the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproofing.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The modules are provided with grooves for inserting reinforcement bars vertically and horizontally, the horizontal and longitudinal reinforcement bars increase the overall strength of the structure accordingly.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, the inspection wells and drainage wells constructed using concrete inspection well modules are not prone to collapse, subsidence, water leakage, etc. The well wall modules have stable mechanical properties, easy operation, and standardized forming dimensions.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备智能控制配备数据输入、输出装置一键通触摸式液晶显示监控机械操作全部过程，实现理想的人机对话、自动分析比料、密度运转、安全逻辑控制及故障诊断系统。
mt: The intelligent control of the concrete inspection well module block machine equipment is equipped with data input and output devices, one-touch touch-type LCD display, and monitors the entire process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis of material ratio, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械液压系统采用单缸液压、输送，双缸液压、输送。
mt: The mechanical hydraulic system of the well wall module adopts single-cylinder hydraulic and transporting, and double-cylinder hydraulic and transporting.
ref: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.

src: 独立的液压集成站，避免了由于主机振动对液压系统的影响，从而保证液压系统工作的可靠性。
mt: The independent hydraulic integration station avoids the influence of the host vibration on the hydraulic system, thus ensuring the reliability of the hydraulic system.
ref: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备布料箱行进模箱脱模上升，储料箱门关闭，自动输送托板，全部由液压系统独立完成，从而达到减少机械的磨损和维修。
mt: The concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment, distributing box moves, and the mold box is released and lifted, the storage box door is closed, and the pallet is automatically conveyed, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system, thus reducing the mechanical wear and maintenance.
ref: In the concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, the fabric box proceeding box de-molds and lifts, the storage box door closes, and the supporting plate is transported automatically, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system so as to reduce mechanical abrasion and times of repair.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备采用进口电脑、电器，密封件液压件，准保设备综合性能稳定可靠。
mt: The concrete inspection well modular block making equipment adopts imported computers, electrical appliances and hydraulic sealing parts to ensure the stability and reliability of the overall performance of the equipment.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment is composed by imported computer and appliances, as well as sealing elements and hydraulic element to ensure stable and reliable comprehensive performance.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振平台采用整体板钢，台面线切割合模无焊接点，使填料箱自由摆动导向，充分减少机械磨损。
mt: The mechanical vibration platform for well wall modules adopts integral plate steel, and the table top is cut CNC and clamped without welding points, allowing the stuffing box to freely swing and guide, and fully reduce mechanical wear.
ref: The integral steel plate is adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical vibration platform, with no welding points of wire-electrode cutting mold closing of mesa, so that the stuffing box can swing and orient freely to greatly reduce mechanical abrasion.

src: 使模具负荷减少、填料并二合一加密振幅，采用一体化、全同步，台振、模振，确保达到振实效果。
mt: The mold load is reduced, the filler and integration are combined to enhance the amplitude, and the integrated, fully-synchronized, table vibration and mold vibration are used to ensure the vibrating effect.
ref: It reduces loads of molds and reinforces vibration; integrated and full synchronization are adopted for vibration of the platform and the molds to ensure the vibration effect.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振机械、电脑自动控制振幅根据原料性价比调节振幅，无磨损制动，从而延长使用寿命，降低成本。
mt: The mechanical vibration excitation machinery of the wall module and the computer automatically control the vibration amplitude according to the cost-effectiveness of the raw materials. The amplitude is adjusted without wear or brake, thus extending the service life and reducing the costs.
ref: The shaft wall module mechanical excitation machinery and the computer automatically control the vibration range according to the cost performance of raw materials, leading to no abrasion brake; in this way, it extends the service life and reduces the cost.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械自动控制和手动控制双重功能。
mt: The well wall module has dual functions of mechanical automatic control and manual control.
ref: The shaft wall module machinery is equipped with dual functions, i.e., automatic control and manual control.

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association classifies olive oil into two major types: Virgin Olive Oil and Refined Olive Oil (Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil), with five grades.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is the oil obtained directly from fresh olive fruits by mechanical cold pressing and filtering to remove foreign matter.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: Depending on the acidity there are three levels:
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra virgin olive oil (Extra Virgin): is the highest grade, highest quality olive oil and is a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: Excellent taste, with light and pleasant botanical aromas and acidity not exceeding 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: Fine Virgin Olive Oil: The acidity is slightly higher but not more than 2% and the taste is pure and aromatic.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary Virgin Olive Oil: The taste and flavor are acceptable and the acidity does not exceed 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil obtained by refining virgin olive oil with an acidity exceeding 3.3% or called “secondary oil”.
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two grades :
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Ordinary Olive Oil: Refined olive oil is mixed with a certain percentage of virgin olive oil to harmonize the flavor and colour. Its acidity is below 1.5%, and it is a transparent light golden yellow colour.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined olive oil or olive pomace oil (Refined Olive-Pomace Oil): is an olive oil that is extracted from oil residue through the dissolution method and refined.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you've read the classifications, you may have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You must know that olives are like the grapes used to make wine. Olives from different producing regions and various olive varieties will produce different standards of olive oil.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: Best Growing Places for Olive Oil:
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable climate conditions such as soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity and precipitation for olive growth.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Except the Mediterranean coast, other regions can only have sporadic planting in suitable areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main producing areas (Mediterranean):
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc. have similar climates, as are Argentina, Peru, South Africa and so on in the far southern latitudes.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Picking months for olives:
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: From March to June each year, olive trees bloom and produce fruits. From July to October, the fruits begin to develop and mature, and the fruits transition from green to red, purple, and finally black.

src: 其实对于身体微胖的女孩子穿衣搭配的讲究很多。
mt: In fact, there are many things to pay attention to in dressing for girls with a slightly fat body.
ref: Actually, there are many tricks for slightly overweight girls to match their clothes.

src: 身体胖的女孩穿的裙子不能太短或太长，长度差不多在膝盖，刚好能盖住大腿胖的地方即可。
mt: The skirts worn by fat girls should not be too short or too long. The length of the skirts should be approximately within the knees, just enough to cover the fat thighs.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall wear skirts not too long or too short; they shall be of the length at around the knees, just covering the fat part of the thighs.

src: 裙子过短就会把腿上的肥胖显露出来。
mt: A skirt that is too short will reveal the fat on the legs.
ref: The fat thighs will be shown if the skirt is too short.

src: 过长就会给人矮而胖的感觉。
mt: If it is too long, it will make you feel short and fat.
ref: Skirts that are too long will make you look short and fat.

src: 如果穿出分出上中下三段来，就显得你自然增高了，就是上身、裙和长筒袜用不同的颜色，看上去就会产生一种修长的感觉 。
mt: If you wear it in three sections: the upper, middle and lower parts, it will appear that you are naturally taller. Even if the upper body, skirt and socks are in different colors, it will seem to create a slender feel.
ref: If you are dressed in three sections, upper, middle and lower, you will naturally look taller; that is, use different colors for upper body, skirt and stockings, and you will look taller and slimmer.

src: 其实很多深色系的衣服是微胖女孩子们的标配（这一点作者深有体会），深颜色也是掩盖你身体胖的好方法，高贵典雅的黑色短裙也是微胖女孩的首选。
mt: In fact, many dark clothes are the standard items for fat girls (the author has a deep understanding of this). Dark colors are also a good way to conceal your body fat, and elegant black skirts are also the first option for fat girls.
ref: In fact, a lot of darker color clothes are what slightly overweight girls all have, which the author deeply agrees; dark colors are good methods to cover fatness of your bodies; in addition, noble and elegant black short shirts are best choices for slightly overweight girls.

src: 穿上深颜色的衣服，特别是黑色的短裙，会让人觉得你瘦一些。
mt: Wearing dark colored clothes, especially short black skirts, can make you look thinner.
ref: You will look slimmer in dark clothes, especially black short skirts.

src: 如果小腿很胖，你的袜子和鞋不要穿得太让人注意。
mt: If you have fat calves, keep your socks and shoes from being too noticeable.
ref: Wear stockings and low-key shoes if your calves are fat.

src: 越大众化越好，颜色也不要太鲜艳了。
mt: The more popular the better, and the colors should not be too bright.
ref: The more common the better; the color shouldn’t be too bright.

src: 以免人们对你的腿部和脚部注意时，让人得到肥胖的感觉。
mt: To prevent people from giving the impression of being fat when they gaze at your legs and feet.
ref: In case people will notice your legs and feet and think you’re fat.

src: 对于微微稍胖的女孩子一定要讲就好穿衣搭配的诀窍。
mt: For girls who are a little bit fat, some tips about dressing well must be shared.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall master the tricks for clothing matching.

src: 微胖女孩千万不要穿紧身的短裙，另外上衣不要过短或者塞在裙子里，会让人看了很不舒服，如果腿粗的话，要穿黑色的长筒袜或者网格袜(细格子的那种哦)，选择质地柔软的印花喇叭裙，搭配一件荡领的上衣，可以很好的掩盖胖女孩的不足。
mt: Fat girls should never wear tight-fitting short skirts. Also the tops should not be too short or tucked into the skirts, it will make people uncomfortable to look at. If your legs are thick, wear black stockings or mesh socks (the kind with fine lattices). Choose a printed flared skirt with soft texture, and a top with a swinging collar to hide the shortcomings of fat girls.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall never wear close-fitting short skirts and the upper outer garment shall not be too short or tucked inside the skirt, which seem strange; slightly overweight girls with thicker legs shall wear black stockings or mesh stockings (thin meshes), a flare skirt with print pattern and soft texture, and a loose-collar upper outer garment to cover the defects of the body.

src: 当然了，微胖的女孩儿在穿短裙上也是有讲究的。
mt: Of course, fat girls are also particular about wearing short skirts.
ref: Of course, there are some skills for slightly overweight girls to wear short skirts.

src: 胖女孩穿短裙，应该选择与短裙的颜色一致的上衣，这样会使你胖胖的身材有增加高度的效果。
mt: Fat girls who wear short skirts, should choose a top that is in the same color as the skirt, which will increase the height of your fat figure.
ref: When slightly overweight girls wear short skirts, they shall choose upper outer garment with the same color as the short skirt, so as to make them look taller.

src: 短裙搭配高跟鞋，可以让你的双腿显得更为修长，这可是夏季最IN的搭配喔!

src: 全新原装，性价比超高的一款游戏笔记本电脑，设计风格很不错已经安装了windows11和office2019
mt: Brand new, cost-effective gaming laptop with great design style. Both Windows 11 and Office 2019 are installed.
ref: Brand new in original packaging, highly cost-effective game laptop; design style is good and windows 11 and office 2019 have already been installed.

src: 显示效果：买了小孩做3D渲染用的,软件己装,小孩说可以使用没问题,这款电脑做3D设计工作性能可以.
mt: Display effect: I bought a kid's computer for 3D rendering, the software has been installed, the kid said that it can be used without any problem, and the performance of this computer is good for 3D design work.
ref: Display effect: I bought it for my child to do 3D rendering; the software has been installed and my child said it worked fine; this laptop works OK for 3D design.

src: 买给儿子的，他说很好。
mt: Bought it for my son and he said it was fine.
ref: I bought it for my son, and he said it’s pretty good.

src: 电脑挺好的，尤其是客服态度很好，不懂的问就好，推荐购买
mt: The computer is very good, especially the customer service attitude is very good. If you don’t understand, just ask, and it is recommended to buy it
ref: The laptop is good; the customer service staff is really nice; just ask them if you have any question; recommended.

src: 还不错，玩游戏的画质是真的香
mt: It's fine. The picture quality of the game is really nice.
ref: Not bad, the image quality for playing games is really nice.

src: 全视觉婚纱摄影基地(河北店) 暂时还没有分店
mt: Full Vision Wedding Photography Base (Hebei branch) has no branches yet
ref: Full Vision Wedding Photography Base (Hebei Store) has no branch store yet

src: 婚纱时尚前卫，化妆师也是首屈一指的，拍摄技术和角度那叫一个专业，拍摄效果很好。
mt: The wedding attire is fashionable and avant-garde, and the makeup artist is second to none. The shooting technique and angle are a professional affair, and the shooting effect is very good.
ref: The wedding dresses are fashionable and trendy, the makeup artists are among the best, the photography skills and perspectives are professional, and the final results are good.

src: 非常有信誉的卖家，服务态度也很好。
mt: Very reputable seller with great service attitude.
ref: Very trustable seller with nice service and attitude.

src: 妆容很精致，团队服务也很好，这次旅行很开心，很专业的团队，卖家服务态度很好，会介绍给朋友的，很满意。
mt: The makeup is quite exquisite, and the team service is also very good. I am very pleased with this trip. The team is very professional and the seller has a good service attitude. I will introduce it to my friends. I am very satisfied.
ref: The makeup was delicate, the team offered good service, and I had a nice trip with this professional team; the seller was nice; I was satisfied and would recommend it to friends.

src: 感谢摄影师与化妆师，让我拥有了独一无二的婚纱照。
mt: Thanks to the photographer and makeup artist for providing me with a unique wedding photo.
ref: Thanks to the photographer and makeup artist for giving me the unique wedding dress photos.

src: 感谢今天拍婚纱照的所有工作人员，期待成片的出炉。
mt: Thank you to all the staff who took wedding photos today, and we are looking forward to the release of the finished film.
ref: Thank you to every staff at the wedding dress photoshoot, and I look forward to the final photos.

src: 拍摄婚纱照简直是一项体力活，尤其是摄影师，又跑又跳的。
mt: Taking wedding photos is indeed a physically demanding job, especially for photographers, running and jumping all the time.
ref: Shooting wedding dress photos is basically physical work, especially the photographer, who has to run up and down.

src: 化妆师很贴心的帮我设计了一种适合我脸型的妆面，摄影大哥拍摄的时候幽默风趣，值得好评。
mt: The makeup artist was very considerate in helping me design a makeup that suited my face shape. The photographer was humorous when taking pictures, which was worthy of praise.
ref: The makeup artist considerably designed a makeup that’s suitable for me, and the photographer guy was funny at the shoot, recommended.

src: 感谢我的摄影师和化妆师，有生之年还能看到自己可以这么美。
mt: Thanks to my photographer and my makeup artist, I can still see myself this beautiful throughout my life.
ref: Thanks to my photographer and markup artist, I was able to see me being so beautiful in my life.

src: 夸女方，眼睛漂亮，长相大方得体，一看就是贤妻良母，以后勤俭持家。
mt: Praising the woman, her eyes are beautiful and her appearance is generous and decent. At first glance, she is a good wife and good mother. She will be diligent and thrifty in her future.
ref: They complimented the woman for having pretty eyes and a presentable look, and said she looked like a nice mother and wife who would handle the household matters well at first glance.

src: 新郎算是赚到了，一生幸福，和和美美的。
mt: The groom is considered to have earned it, and he will be happy and beautiful throughout his life.
ref: The groom is winning and will have a happy life.

src: 婚纱照质量真的不错，就像网上说的一样，我和爱人拍的很帅和漂亮，我们很满意。
mt: The quality of wedding photos is really good, just like what is said in the Internet, the photos my wife and I took are very handsome and beautiful, and we are very satisfied.
ref: The quality of the wedding dress photos are nice as what others say in the reviews; they made me and my wife very handsome and beautiful and we are satisfied.

src: 卖家服务态度也很热情。
mt: The seller's service attitude is also very盎.
ref: The seller has a nice attitude and is enthusiastic.

src: 这次旅拍，不仅欣赏了美景，还拍了美美的婚纱照，还认识了摄影师这位好友。
mt: During this trip, I not only enjoyed the beautiful scenery, but also took beautiful wedding photos, and I even met the photographer as a friend.
ref: This shooting trip gave me the chance to enjoy the great views, get the wedding dress photoshoot done, and get acquainted with the photographer as a friend.

src: 婚纱照太好看了，吹爆摄影师和化妆师，你们真的超级超级专业。
mt: The wedding photos are so beautiful, the photographer and makeup artist are blown away, you are really super professional.
ref: The wedding dress photos are so great; I want to give the photographer and makeup artist the best comment ever because you are super professional.

src: 非常感谢穆姐耐心陪伴和悉心教导，拍出来的照片我很喜欢~
mt: Thank you very much to Sister Mu for her patience and her careful teaching. I really like the photos I took~
ref: I would like to thank Ms. Mu for patiently accompanying and guiding us, and I really like the photos~

src: 看到婚纱照的那一刻，我竟一时没有认出自己来。
mt: The moment I saw the wedding photos, I didn’t recognize myself for a moment.
ref: I didn’t recognize myself the moment I saw the wedding dress photos.

src: 只要摄影师选的好，你也可以拥有可以媲美明星的婚纱照。
mt: As long as the photographer is well chosen, you can have wedding photos rivaling that of famous stars.
ref: As long as you choose the right photographer, you can have wedding dress photos that are on par with those of the celebrities.

src: 拍摄婚纱照较重要的是摄影师跟化妆师都审美在线，幸好我遇到了。
mt: What's more importantly when it comes to taking wedding photos is that both photographers and makeup artists are both online and fortunately I met them.
ref: What is important in shooting wedding dress photos is the aesthetics of photographer and makeup artist, and luckily I met such people.

src: 看到我的婚纱照之后，我发现原来我也是“照骗”。
mt: After seeing my wedding pictures, I found out that I too was a “photo cheat”.
ref: After seeing my wedding dress photos, I found that I could also have flattering photos.

src: 日昌餐馆(五道口店)
mt: Richang Restaurant (Wudaokou Branch)
ref: Richang Restaurant (Wudaokou)

src: [薄荷]环境： 中规中矩 [服务铃]服务： 上菜很快 「古法马拉糕」我的必点菜 马拉糕太香太软太好吃了😋喜欢甜品的小伙伴一定要试试「东江墨鱼滑酿豆腐煲」汤非常鲜美 豆腐很嫩 墨...
mt: [Mint] Environment: Moderate [Serving Bell] Service: the food comes out very fast. “Ancient Malala Cake” was my staple order. The mala cake is too fragrant, soft, and tasty 😋 Friends who like desserts must try the “Dongjiang Cuttlefish Smooth and Stuffed Bean Curd Pot”. The soup is delicious and the tofu is tender.    …
ref: Emoji mint, environment is average, emoji service Bell, as for service, the dishes were served fast, “traditional Cantonese sponge cake” is one I must order, the cake is so soft, sweet and delicious😋; you must try it if you like dessert, and “Dongjiang tofu casserole with cuttlefish balls” has nice soup, tender tofu and...

src: 味道赞 肉类好 服务热情
mt: Great taste, good meat, nice service
ref: Nice taste, great meat, enthusiastic service

src: 好久没来日昌了，水果捞还是那么好喝&真材实料足，第一次点叉烧包，就是我爱的松软面粉的南方口感！
mt: It's been a long time since I came to Richang. The fruit scramble is still tasty and full of real ingredients. It is my first time to order barbecued pork buns, which I like with the southern taste of soft flour!
ref: I haven’t been to Richang for a long time, and the Fruit Mix is still delicious and has a lot of real stuff in it, it was the first time for me to order Cha Siu Bao, and it has the Southern taste with fluffy flour which I enjoyed!

src: 煲仔饭干湿成程度正好，份量非常足，招牌锡纸鸡翅一如既往赞，例汤也不错，芥兰处理得也比较...
mt: The claypot rice is well-dry and moist, the portion is very generous, the signature tinfoil chicken wings are outstanding as always, the soup is also good, the kale is also well handled...
ref: The wetness of the clay pot rice was just right, and the portion was generous, the special tinfoil chicken wings were great as always, the soup was nice as well, the cabbage mustard was also...

src: 味道赞 服务热情 肉类好
mt: Great taste, good service, good meat
ref: Nice taste, enthusiastic service, great meat

src: 日昌老店 好多年前也是网红的存在吧，东单小楼，木地板。
mt: The old store in Richang was also an internet celebrity many years ago. It’s a small building in Dongdan and has wooden floors.
ref: Original Richang restaurant was also popular many years ago, Dongdan little building, wooden floor.

src: 门口总是要等很久才能吃上的煲仔饭，煲仔饭的砂锅都开裂了…
mt: You always have to wait for a long time to get the claypot rice. The claypot of claypot rice is cracked....
ref: You have to wait a long time at the door to have the clay pot rice, and the clay pot cracked...

src: 好几年没去吃日昌了，各种小店粤菜的崛起分散了客流。
mt: I haven't gone to Richang for several years, and the rise of Cantonese cuisine in various small restaurants has dispersed the flow of customers.
ref: I haven’t been to Richang for a few years as emerging little Cantonese restaurants scattered the customers.

src: 难得一见的到店就有座位啊，菜品质量没的说，一如既往的好。
mt: It is rare to see a seat as you arrive in the establishment. The quality of the dishes is as good as ever.
ref: It was rare to have seats available as soon as I arrived, and the dishes were great as always.

src: 味道赞 肉类好 主食赞
mt: Great taste, good meat, good main food
ref: Nice taste, great meat, great principal food

src: 日昌外卖。
mt: Richang takeaway.
ref: Richang takeout.

src: [米饭]餐食：这次的菜稍微有一点点失望了。
mt: [Rice] Meal: This time’s dishes were a little bit disappointing.
ref: [rice] Meal: the dishes this time were a little disappointing.

src: 三杯鸡：配菜有点多，鸡肉稍微有点少。
mt: Three Cup Chicken: A little more side dishes and a little less chicken.
ref: Three Cup Chicken: there were too many vegetables and too little chicken.

src: 主要调的这个味道有点偏差，底味的咸不够，就凸显了甜味了，大家可以脑补一下甜+各种香料配菜...
mt: The main taste is a little off, the bottom taste is not salty enough, which highlights the sweetness, we can make up for that with sweetness + various spices on the side dishes...
ref: It was mainly because the flavor was a little off, the base was not salty enough and the sweetness was exaggerated, you can imagine sweetness + various spice and garnish...

src: 红牌威士忌喝法是什么？
mt: How to drink red label whiskey?
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。
mt: Everyone's hobbies are different, some people like collecting, some people like food, and some people like wine tasting. The Red Label whisky is now one of the best-selling Scotch whiskies in various countries. Moreover, the Red Label whisky has won the gold medal in the international wine competition.
ref: Different people have different preferences; some like to collect, some like food, and certainly some like wine tasting; Johnnie Walker Red Label is one of the fastest selling Scottish whiskies in the world and has won the gold prize of International Wine Competition.

src: 每一瓶红牌威士忌都有独特的味道，不过如果不知道如何品味它，岂不是糟蹋了它的醇香。
mt: Every bottle of Red Label whisky has a unique taste, but if you don’t know how to taste it you're just ruining the flavour.
ref: Each bottle of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky has its own unique flavor, but if you don’t know how to taste it, it would be such a waste of its mellow fragrance.

src: 那么红牌威士忌怎么喝呢？
mt: So what about red label whiskey?
ref: Then how do we drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 小编为大家简单介绍下。
mt: Let me give you a brief introduction.
ref: I’ll introduce for you now.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法：
mt: How to drink red label whiskey :
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky:

src: 尊尼获加红牌威士忌由约35种苏格兰威士忌调配而成，具有浓郁芳香及传统苏格兰威士忌的特质，浓郁芳香中带有甘甜及烟熏香味。
mt: Johnnie Walker Red Label whiskey is blended from around 35 Scotch whiskies, has a strong aromatic and traditional Scotch whisky characteristics, a rich aroma with sweet and smoky character.
ref: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended with around 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, possesses rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

src: 入口浓醇清新，略带香草及浓烈的烟熏麦芽味道。
mt: The entry is full-bodied and refreshing, with hints of vanilla and a strong smoky malt flavour.
ref: It is mellow and fresh in the mouth, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.

src: 该酒可以直接加冰饮用，或者与最喜爱的饮品混合饮用。
mt: This wine can be enjoyed straight on ice or mixed with your favorite drink.
ref: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: Red brand whiskey has been introduced into China. In order to meet the taste of the Chinese people, sparkling drinks such as red brand whiskey + Cola, Sprite or Sunkist have become an enduring fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: These sweet drinks, in addition to neutralizing sour taste, can visually bring pleasure to people. When added to drinks, they have the effect of diluting the taste of alcohol and changing the taste.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Red brand whiskey + sliced lemon + sugar cube (granulated sugar is also available), is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.
ref: Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.

src: 正宗的红方威味道有些酸涩,加入糖可以中和其中的酸味,柠檬则会给酒带来清新的香味,当然,甜酸度可根据个人的口味爱好调配。
mt: The authentic Hongfangwei tastes a bit sour. Adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, and lemon will bring fresh aroma to the wine. Of course, the sweetness and acidity can be adjusted according to personal taste preferences.
ref: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour; adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, lemon will bring fresh fragrance to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and sourness can be adjusted according to personal tastes.

src: 以上三种都是红牌威士忌的最好喝法，大家可以作为参考尝试下，希望小编的介绍可以帮助到大家。
mt: The above three are the best ways to drink red brand whiskey. You can try it out as a reference. I hope my introduction can be helpful to everyone.
ref: The above are the best drinking methods of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky for your refence, and I hope my introduction can help you.

src: 金夫人婚纱摄影(南街店) 暂时还没有分店
mt: Mrs. Jin Wedding Photography (South Street Branch) has no branches yet
ref: Mrs. Gold Wedding Dress Photography (Nanjie Store) has no branch store yet.

src: 拍照之前因为我们时间没安排好，更换了两次时间，顾问兰兰很耐心地帮我们安排了时间。
mt: Before taking the pictures, we changed the time twice because we had not arranged the time correctly. Consultant Lan Lan patiently helped us arrange the time.
ref: Because I didn’t arrange my time well before the shoot, I rescheduled twice and consultant Lanlan patiently arranged time for us.

src: 后来选择了一个天气好的周末拍的。
mt: I chose to shoot it on a weekend with nice weather.
ref: Later we chose a weekend with nice weather to shoot it.

src: 金夫人的工作人员，无论是顾问，化妆师还是摄影师都超赞的。
mt: Mrs. Kim's staff, be it consultants, makeup artists or photographers were amazing.
ref: The staff at Mrs. Gold, no matter it’s consultant or makeup artist, are fantastic.

src: 那是我生平第一次正式地化妆，哇～简直不敢相信，我有一天也会变得那么好看，哈哈。
mt: It was the first time in my life that I had to officially wear makeup, and wow~ I can't believe I would be so good-looking one day lol.
ref: That was the first time that I had officially put on makeup and wow, I couldn’t even believe that I could be so pretty one day, haha.

src: 晓洁和另一个妹子（抱歉我记不得名字了）化妆超级有耐心，化妆也很自然。
mt: Xiaojie and another girl (sorry I can't remember her name) are super patient with makeup and the make-up is very natural.
ref: Xiaojie and the other girl (sorry, I forgot her name) were super patient while doing my makeup and the makeup was natural.

src: 外景在江湾城拍的，幸亏那天天气很好，没有觉得很冷，拍照的时候，化妆师时不时地留意我们的衣服，头饰，稍微有一点不好了就马上帮我们整理。
mt: The outside scene was shot in Jiangwan City. Fortunately, the weather was great that day and I didn't feel it was too cold. During the photo shoot, the makeup artist paid attention to our clothes and headwear from time to time, and if there was a little problem, she immediately helped us clean it up.
ref: We shot the outdoor scene at Jiangwancheng, and fortunately the weather was nice that day, we didn’t feel cold; during the shoot, makeup artist was paying attention to our clothes, headwear, and made adjustment immediately once there was a problem.

src: 摄影师也非常幽默，拍照一天下来都觉得很开心。
mt: The photographer is also very humorous and had a good time taking pictures all day long.
ref: The photographer was funny, and we were happy throughout the day.

src: 在选照片的时候，因为在网上看到很多案例，不愿意让客人删太多照片，但是我们选照片的时候，真的，一点没有让我们加照片的意思，直接套餐里的24张，一张都没有加（听说和我差不多时间拍婚纱照的表妹，七千多的套餐还加了一万多的照片，当时我就惊呆了，心里也很怕自己会选太多）
mt: When choosing photos, because I saw lots of cases on the Internet I was not willing to let customers delete too many pictures. But when we chose photos, we didn’t really want to add photos at all, so he didn’t add a single out of the 24 photos in the package. (I heard that my cousin, who had taken wedding photos around the same time as I, added more than 10,000 photos to the package of over 7,000. I was shocked at that time. I was also afraid that I would choose too many pictures.)
ref: When choosing the photos, I saw many cases online where they wouldn’t let the customers delete too many photos, but they didn’t ask us to add photos at all, just the 24 photos in the set and nothing more (I heard that my cousin who was also taking wedding dress photos added photos worth over 10,000 in addition to the 7,000 yuan set, and I was stunned and feared I might choose too many).

src: 今天照片修好了，兰兰发给我，我看了有两张觉得不太好，他们立刻就帮我重新修了。
mt: I repaired the pictures today and Lanlan sent them to me. I looked at two pictures and felt they were not very nice so they immediately repaired them for me.
ref: The editing was finished today and Lanlan sent it to me; I felt two were not good enough and they immediately re-edited them for me.

src: 把妹妹以前拍的照片翻出来对比，我觉得我们的照片我真的太满意了，简约清新，就是我想要的风格。
mt: After comparing the pictures my sister took before, I feel that I am really satisfied with our pictures. They are simple and fresh, just the style I want.
ref: I found the old photos of my sister to make comparison, and I felt that our photos were really satisfying, simple and fresh, exactly what I wanted.

src: 真心推荐大家去宣汉金夫人拍婚纱照！
mt: I sincerely recommend everyone to take wedding photos with Mrs. Xuan Han Jin!
ref: I sincerely recommend choosing Xuanhan Mrs. Gold to take your wedding dress photoshoot!

src: 套系价格：3999 元
mt: Set price: 3999 yuan.
ref: Set price: 3,999 yuan

src: 金夫人感恩有你们真心祝愿你们幸福美满，前程似锦！
mt: Mrs. Jin would like to thank you all and sincerely wish you happiness and a bright future!
ref: Mrs. Gold is grateful for you and sincerely wishes you a happy life and a promising future!

src: 这一套多少钱啊
mt: How much is this set?
ref: How much is this set?

src: 小编为大家带来欧米茄机械对表哪款好？
mt: Let me introduce to you which Omega mechanical watch is better?
ref: Which pair of OMEGA mechanical watches shall I introduce to you?

src: 欧米茄机械对表怎么样好用吗？
mt: How does the OMEGA mechanical pair of watches work?
ref: How are the OMEGA mechanical pair watches?

src: 1、瑞士欧米茄OMEGA碟飞系列情侣对表，自动机械男表，石英女表
mt: 1. Swiss Omega OMEGA De Ville series couple watches, automatic mechanical men’s watches, quartz women’s watches
ref: 1. OMEGA Switzerland De Ville couples watches, automatic mechanical male’s watch and quartz female’s watch

src: 推荐理由:传承瑞士，时间艺术尽在腕间，欧米茄端庄优雅、朴素简单，不招摇但却很迷人，通勤和正式场合都可佩戴。

ref: Mr. Li told reporter that he recently bought a feet bath basin for his father as a birthday present, but his father felt that the bottom of his feet were numb when using it.

src: 李先生一开始以为是足浴盆的振动功能引起的，没想到关了振动功能，父亲还是感觉到脚底麻麻的。
mt: At first, Mr. Li thought it was caused by the vibration function of the foot bath tub. Unexpectedly, after turning off the vibration function, his father still felt numbness in the soles of the feet.
ref: Mr. Li first thought it was caused by the vibration function of the feet bath basin, and it was unexpected that his father still felt his feet were numb after turning off the vibration function.

src: 李先生用电笔一试，电笔居然亮了，李先生惊讶地发现足浴盆的水里居然带电。

ref: Mr. Li used a tester and the light on it was on; it was to Mr. Li’s surprise that the water in the feet bath basin was electrified.

src: 后来他联络了商家，商家的态度还不错，尽管退掉了足浴盆，李先生依然感到不快。

src: 但是一般情况下足浴盆是不会有带电问题的，但也不排除少数产品在出厂时没有严格把关。

src: 因此在在购买的时候选择分体式的足浴盆。

src: 大美360集成家装
mt: Dayey 360 Integrated Home Improvement
ref: Damei 360 Integrated Home Decoration

src: 地 址：环城南路156号幸福家园12楼
mt: Address: 12th Floor, Happy Home, No. 156 South Huancheng Road
ref: Address: Happy Home Building 12, South Ring Road 156

src: 一开始是朋友介绍的因为信任，所以选择来看一下起初我的预算是7万做个基本装修。
mt: At first, it was introduced by a friend because of trust, so I chose to take a look at it. My budget at first was 70,000 to do basic decoration.
ref: I trusted it because my friend made the recommendation, so I chose to check it out, and originally my budget for a basic decoration was 70,000.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。
mt: Upon arrival at the store, a series of deceptive tricks began.
ref: A series of scam began as soon as I came into the store.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: It was the first time that I went to the store but I just showed them my floor plan. They didn’t inspect the house on the spot and yet, they actually gave me a quotation saying that my 135 house could cost 70,000 yuan. I took a look at the materials and didn’t know what brand they were.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second set of tricks is that as soon as you go to the store, they will drag you to pay the deposit (and once the money has been paid, you will never get it back unless you have enough experience to argue with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: When I was hesitating about whether to pay a deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell you how much discount we can give you as long as you pay the deposit today.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。
mt: This is a huge pit. I am a living example of being deceived. When I was in a hurry, I paid a deposit of more than 10,000.
ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: The quote he gave me had many problems. The price of 70,000 does not include electricity and water renovations, nor includes any doors, cabinets, bathrooms, and these three are the bulk of the cost of the base installation.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。
mt: Apart from these, their service points charges are also higher than those of other companies.
ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

src: 我对这个公司失去了信任，一开始什么都没有讲清楚就让我签合同。
mt: I lost trust in this company and asked me to sign a contract without stating anything clearly at first.
ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

src: 当我去找他们退钱的时候他们表现出很有经验的样子，有专门的小团队来对付你。
mt: When I went to them to get your money refunded, they appeared experienced and had a small team dedicated to dealing with you.
ref: When I went to ask for a refund, they acted rather experienced and sent a small team to deal with me.

src: 无论如何都会一口咬死是客户的问题他们全然无责。
mt: In any event, getting bitten is the customer's fault and they are completely not to blame.
ref: Anyway, they just said it was the client’s problem and they had absolutely no responsibility for it.

src: 各种推卸责任，还有很多细节，不想一一说了都是泪，总之不要选择他们，因为我朋友找他们装修的房子也是质量不好，后期给你算各种费用。
mt: There are all kinds of shirking of responsibility, and there are many details. If you do not want to mention them all, you will be in tears. In short, don’t choose them because the houses my friends asked them to renovate are of poor quality, and you will pay various expenses later.
ref: They just shrunk their responsibility in any way possible, and there were a lot more details that I don’t want to mention now; all in all, do not choose them because my friend had them renovate her apartment, and the quality was poor and they would charge you all kinds of other costs in the later stage.

src: 坑爹，他们就是原来骗人的龙头装饰，现在改成大美，好像又倒闭了又改成其他的。
mt: Fool, they are the original deceptive tap decoration, and now they have changed to be Damei, they seem to have closed down and changed into something else.
ref: Swindle; they used to be the swindler company Longtou Renovation, then it’s changed to Damei, and now it seems they have closed down and changed into something else.

src: 所以大家别选择这样坑爹的装修公司。
mt: So please don’t choose such a crap decoration company.
ref: So please don’t choose such a swindler company.

src: 以后大家在选择的时候多百度看看这些查一下这些咨询因为装修不是小钱。
mt: In the future, when you are making choices, you will take a look at these on Baidu and check these consultations because decoration is not a small sum.
ref: When you choose renovation companies in the future, please search them on Baidu because renovation cost is not a small amount.

src: 想要向商家提问，请先登录或注册
mt: To ask questions to a merchant, please log in or register first
ref: If you want to ask the merchant a question, please log in or register first.

src: 严禁发布各种形式的商家点评，详细请见商户收录声明
mt: Posting merchant reviews in various forms is strictly prohibited. Please refer to Merchant Acceptance Statement for details.
ref: It is strictly prohibited to publish any type of merchant review, and please refer to the Merchant Inclusion Statement for details.

src: 大众点评昆明装修设计频道为您提供大美360集成家装地址，电话，营业时间等最新商户信息，找装修公司装修公司，就上大众点评
mt: Dianping’s Kunming Decoration Design Channel provides you with the latest business information such as Damei 360 integrated home improvement address, telephone number, opening hours and other business information. When looking for a decoration company, you can go to Dianping
ref: Dianping Kunming Renovation and Design Channel will provide you with the address, phone number, operation time and other information of Damei 360 Integrated Home Renovation, and please come to Dianping if you are looking for a renovation company.

src: 文摄视觉美学摄影馆优选品质店 暂时还没有分店
mt: Wenshe's Visual Aesthetics Photography Gallery's Best Quality Store has no branch yet
ref: Wenshe Visual Aesthetics Photography Studio Premium Store has no branch store yet

src: 加了微信预约日期，小姐姐就把可选择的时间安排发给我，回复信息比较及时~
mt: After adding the appointment date in WeChat, the lady will send me the selected time arrangement so that the reply information is more timely~
ref: I added their WeChat to make an appointment, then they sent me the available dates; their reply was speedy~

src: 去之前看了店里的拍摄作品，更多的是户外婚纱，拍的很漂亮，涉及到的拍摄风格也很多。
mt: Before going there, I watched the shoots in the store, and most of them were outdoor wedding dresses. They were beautifully photographed, and there were many shooting styles involved.
ref: I went to the store to see the photography works, and there were more beautiful outdoor wedding dress photos and a lot of different styles.

src: 当天到了之后和小姐姐简单交流了自己的想法，非常耐心地帮我试了两套我纠结的风格衣服，最终敲定开始化妆造型~摄影师拍摄之前会摆一些道具，会指导动作，对各个细节也比较精益求精。
mt: After the day arrived, I briefly shared my thoughts with my Miss Sister, patiently helped me to try on two styles of clothes that I was struggling with, and finally decided to do my makeup. Before shooting, the photographer will set some props, guide actions, and keep improving on each detail.
ref: After I arrived that day, I communicated my own ideas with the young lady and she patiently helped me try on two outfits I was having trouble deciding and I made the final decision before starting styling and makeup~ the photographer would place some props and guide me to pose before the shoot, and was very attentive to the details.

src: 但是可能因为没和我交流具体的拍摄想法，所以拍出来的不是我想要的风格，但是应该是好看的🙊🙊
mt: But maybe because I didn't communicate the specific shooting ideas with me, what I shot was not the style I wanted, but it should be beautiful🙊🙊
ref: However, the photos taken were not in the style I wanted, perhaps it was because they didn’t communicate with me about the specific shooting ideas, but the photos should look nice🙊🙊

src: 拍好之后摄影师会帮忙挑选照片，交流后期风格，感觉挺细心的叭。
mt: After the shots are taken, the photographer will help select photos and communicate post-production style, so I feel very attentive.
ref: After the shoot, the photographer would help pick the photos, communicate about post-editing style, and I think it was very thoughtful.

src: 修好的片大约要半个月，坐等效果~
mt: The repaired version will take about half a month, wait for the effect~
ref: It will take about half a month to edit all the photos and I look forward to seeing them~

src: 第二次中了写真类的霸王餐活动～全场大部分的衣服能够选择一件拍摄。
mt: This is my second time winning the buffet dinner event which is a photo category. Most of outfits in the audience can choose one piece for the photo shoot.
ref: This is the second time that I have won the chance to experience a photoshoot for free~ you may choose one from most of the available outfits to do the photoshoot.

src: 最后选择了一件黑色的纱裙，体验下不同的风格。
mt: Finally, I chose a black gauze skirt to experience different style.
ref: Eventually, I chose a black veil skirt so as to experience a different style.

src: 整个拍摄过程要2个小时左右，化妆+拍摄，负责拍摄的摄影师是95后的弟弟呢，感觉稍微还是有点青涩，希望在顾客拍摄动作指导方面以后能给更多的建议呀～挺健谈的，拍摄过程比较愉快。
mt: The whole shooting process takes about 2 hours. Makeup + shooting. The photographer responsible for shooting is a young brother from the post-95 generation. I still feel a little bit young and I hope I can give more advice on the customer’s shooting action guide in the future~ I am very talkative and the shooting process was quite pleasant.
ref: The entire photoshoot took about 2 hours including the makeup and shoot; the photographer was a young guy born after 1995, who seemed to be a little shy; I hope he could give more advice to clients in terms of poses~ he was talkative and the shoot was pleasant.

src: 文摄视觉美学摄影馆优选品质店 回复
mt: Wenshe visual aesthetics photography studio preferred quality store
ref: Wenshe Visual Aesthetics Photography Studio Premium Store reply

src: 上首页了，也来看看Queenie吧~

src: 到店先填了姓名电话然后选服装，婚纱都可以选，换了三四套服装还蛮耐心的，选好后化妆化了很久，服务态度也好，后面拍摄会教你怎么摆造型，就是拍出来的感觉脸好大，精修说是要半个月，三四天就发来了，感觉好像跟原片没啥差别
mt: When I arrived at the store, I listed my name and phone number, then chose clothes, such as wedding dresses. After changing three or four suits, I was quite patient. After choosing, I would put on makeup for a long time. The service attitude was good. Later, the photographer would teach you how to pose. However, the pictures were so large that they said the repairs took half a month, and sent them within three to four days, which felt like the same as the original.
ref: After I arrived at the store, I filled in my name and chose the outfits; all the wedding dresses were available to be chosen; I tried on three or four outfits and they were quite patient; after I decided on the dress, they were doing my makeup for a long time and they were also nice during this time; later in the shoot, they would teach you how to pose; I felt my face was too big on the photo; they said detailed editing would take a month, but they sent them to me after three to four days, and they seemed not that different from the original photos.

src: 【环境】整体还好。

ref: [Environment] It was not bad overall.

src: 可选衣服很多。

ref: There are a lot of outfits to choose from.

src: 化妆位置差不多有三个，里边是摄影棚。

ref: There are about three seats for doing makeup and the studio is inside.

src: 【服务】很热情，也很细心。
mt: 【Service】 Very friendly and attentive.
ref: [Service] Very enthusiastic and attentive to details.

src: 造型师挺有耐心的。
mt: The stylist is very patient.
ref: The stylist was patient.

src: 摄影师也会很认真教你动作。
mt: The photographer will also teach you motions very carefully.
ref: Photographer would patiently teach you to pose.

src: 不满意，摄影师也会主动提出补拍。
mt: If you are not satisfied, the photographer will also offer to take additional shots.
ref: If you are not satisfied, the photographer would propose to take it again.

mt: [Experience] Maybe the shape is a little off, as the original double eyelid was pasted over with a third eyelid.
ref: [Experience] Maybe the style was a little too much, double eyelids turned into triple eyelids.

src: 眉尾也被剃了，对于日常不画眉的有点尴尬。
mt: The ends of the eyebrows have also been shaved, which is a bit embarrassing for those who don't draw eyebrows everyday.
ref: The tail of my eyebrow got shaved, and it was a little awkward for those who don’t wear makeup normally.

src: 照片十来天给了，但是P图效果不怎么满意，感觉双眼皮贴那些还是很明显。
mt: I have given the photos around ten days ago, but the results of the P image are not very satisfying, it seems the double eyelid stickers are still obviously visible.
ref: The photos were sent to me after about ten days, but I was not very satisfied with the photoshop effect, and I feel that the double eyelids tapes are still obvious.

src: 因为不太清楚要什么风格 试了两套 结果挑来挑去 还是选了黑色礼服 小姐姐说这套是比较赫本复古风
mt: Because I am not sure what style I want, I tried two sets and I still chose the black dress. The lady said that this set is more Hepburn retro style.
ref: I tried on two outfits because I didn’t know what style to choose, and I ended up choosing the black suit after trying hesitating; the young lady said it was a vintage Audrey Hepburn style.

src: 选好衣服后就开始弄妆发啦 发型师和化妆师小姐姐都超级耐心在帮我弄 弄出来的效果非常满意
mt: After choosing my clothes, I started doing makeup and hair. The hairstylist and makeup artist were super patient and helped me get the results. I am very pleased with the results.
ref: After choosing the outfit, we began with the hair and makeup; the hair stylist and makeup artist were super patient and I was really satisfied.

src: 弄好妆发后就开始拍照了 摄影师全程都有指挥我摆姿势 过程很轻松和谐
mt: After I got the makeup and hair done, I began to take photos. The photographer had instructed me to pose throughout the whole process. The process was very relaxing and harmonious.
ref: The photoshoot started after finishing makeup and hair, and the photographer guided me to pose the whole time; the process was relaxed and harmonious.

src: 拍完后认真选了四张最喜欢的当精修 小哥哥说15内成片 结局非常心满意足～
mt: After finishing filming, I carefully selected four of my favorites as the finishing touches. My brother said that the film will be completed in fifteen and he was very satisfied with its ending~
ref: After the photoshoot, I chose my four favorite ones to be retouched, and the guy said the photos would be completed within 15 days and I was really satisfied with the results~

src: 推荐理由:经过多年窖藏，就为更浓，更透澈，是内蒙古大草原游牧民族爱喝的酒，浓香形秉承了传统酿造工艺，陶醉了华夏质朴亲切，适合各类宴席或者居家使用的一款白酒。
mt: Recommendation reason: After years of storage, it becomes stronger and clearer, it is a favorite liquor of nomadic people in the prairie of Inner Mongolia. The strong fragrance adheres to traditional brewing craftsmanship and is enchanted by the simplicity of China. It is suitable for all kinds of feasts or home use.
ref: Recommendation: After beings stored in the cellar for many years, it is richer and clearer; it is what nomadic people in Inner Mongolia prairie like to drink; the rich flavor inherits the traditional brewing process, and is intoxicated with the simplicity and friendliness of the Chinese people; it is suitable for all kinds of banquets or drinking at home.

ref: Recommendation: This baijiu uses carefully selected sorghum and has balanced aroma; with fermentation in the cellar, baijiu will be aged and the taste of it will be richer.

src: 来自内蒙古高原的白酒，口感更为经典，浓香四溢的味道滑过宾客们的唇齿，让他们喝的尽兴。

ref: Baijiu from Inner Mongolia Plateau tastes more classic; the rich flavor touches guests’ lips and tongues, giving them a pleasant time.

src: 推荐理由:精选高粱，通过独特技艺的加工，让你在宴请欢聚，家庭小酌的时候，都能够开怀畅饮。

ref: Recommendation: carefully selected sorghum and the unique processing methods will give you a happy time together at the banquet or a pleasant drink at home.
