src: 这儿家居家电比较齐全，品牌众多，知名品牌全。
mt: Here the home appliances are relatively complete, with numerous brands and all the well-known ones.
ref: Home appliances in this store are quite complete, with many brands including almost all well-known brands.

src: 双十二那阵，到“汉斯顿”净水器店，看净水器，店内正在做活动，价格比较优惠。
mt: During Double Twelve, we went to the “Hanston” water purifier store and saw the water purifiers. Activities were going on in the store, and the prices were relatively favorable.
ref: During the Double 12 Sale, I went to the "Hunsdon" water purifier store to see the water purifiers, and there were sale activities in the store with favorable prices.

src: 居然之家一共11层，负二层到9层，负一负二都是停车的地方，而且白天停车免费!
mt: The house has 11 floors in total, from the negative 2nd floor to the 9th floor, and the negative 1 and negative 2 are all parking spaces, and the parking is free during the day!
ref: There are 11 floors in Easyhome, from B2 to 9th floor, in which B2 and B2 are for parking and parking is free during the day!

src: 周围是真不怎样，饭店五金店寥寥无几，而且饭店味道一般般。
mt: The surrounding is not so good. There are few hardware stores at the hotel, and the restaurant tastes just average.
ref: The surroundings are really not nice, with few restaurants and hardware store, and the food there tasted average.

src: 这个电梯也是很无语，跟有那大病一样，负二到负一，来回折腾，不停我按的这一层，从安全通道下去到一楼，也是很无语，直接通到一个家具店，家具店关门，安全通道出不去!
mt: This elevator is also speechless. Just like that serious illness, it has to go back and forth from negative two to negative one. It keeps hitting the floor I pressed down and I go down to the first floor from the safety passage. It is also very speechless. It leads directly to a furniture store, which is closed and I cannot get out through the safe passage!
ref: This elevator really makes people speechless; it went back and forth from B2 to B1 and did not stop on my floor, and it was ridiculous that when I went to the 1st floor from fire escape, it led to a furniture store which was closed, so I couldn’t get out from the fire escape, either!

src: 居然之家还是需要提升，有很多地方都没有开发。
mt: Actually, the home still needs improvement, and there are many areas that have not been developed.
ref: Easyhome still needs to be improved with a lot of spaces to be developed.

src: 地址：沙依巴克区高铁北一路555号，交通方便，停车场很大，白天还是免费的。
mt: Address: No.555 of High Speed Rail North 1st Road, Shayibhak District. It has convenient transportation and a large parking lot. It is free during the day.
ref: Address: HSR North One Road, Bayishake District, convenient transportation, big parking lot free during the day.

src: 环境：说实话店里面积大，有8～9层，家里想买的家具、家用电器、各种小东西……，都能买到，好多名牌商家都入驻在店里，慕思、欧派、华帝、老板、峰创之家、汉斯顿、雅克、友邦、丝涟、富品居、万家乐、大自然、中联、美的、雅丹……，品牌真的是太多了，我只能记得这么多了，是购买产品的好去处，逛累了可以坐在沙发上休息休息哦。
mt: Environment: Honestly speaking, the store is big, with 8 ~ 9 floors, you can buy any furniture, household appliances, small things etc. that you want to buy, as well as lots of famous brands, including Mousse, OPPEIN, Vatican, Boss, Fengchuangzhijia, Hanston, Jacques, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, Macro, Nature, Zhonglian, Midea, Yadan…, there are really too many brands, I can only remember so many, it is a good place for buying products, if you are tired you can sit on the sofa and rest.
ref: Environment: Honestly, the store is large with 8-9 floors, where you can buy all the furniture, household appliances and small things your home needs, and many famous brands have settled in the store, such as DeRUCCI, OPPEIN, VATTI, Robam, Fengchuang Home, Hunsdon, Yake, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, GUANGDONG MACRO, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, and so many other brands, I can only remember so many; it is a good place to buy products, and you can sit on the couch and have a rest if you get tired.

src: 最近想买一套舒适的沙发，朋友说这里有好多沙发可以选，看了顾家家居、美克美家的，感觉还可以，就是价格略贵，所以还在纠结中
mt: I wanted to buy a set of comfortable sofas recently. My friends said, there are many sofas to choose from there, and I looked at the ones from Gujia Home Furnishings and Meakemeijia, and I think they are okay, but the price is slightly more expensive, so I'm still in a tangle.
ref: I recently want to buy a couch and my friend said there was a lot of couch to choose from here; I looked at Kuka Home and Markor Furnishings, and I felt they were okay but a little expensive, so I am still struggling to decide.

src: 大众点评乌鲁木齐家居卖场频道为您提供高铁居然之家地址，电话，营业时间等最新商户信息，找装修公司，就上大众点评
mt: Dianping, Urumqi Home Furnishing Store channel will provide you the latest business information such as location of High Speed Railway, telephone number and business hours, etc. If you find decoration companies, you can go to Dianping.com
ref: Dianping Urumqi Renovation and Design Channel will provide you with the address, phone number, operation time and other information of HSR Easyhome, and please come to Dianping if you are looking for a renovation company.

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that I think is very meaningful - first aid certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skills certificates that I think is important besides a driver's license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Popularize it: first aid measures are actually emergency rescue in the event of an emergency, that is, the rescue before the ambulance arrives.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is still a period of time before the ambulance arrives after an accident, and it is this time that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I do have a heart attack, a cerebral hemorrhage, or a respiratory arrest, then our window of life is only four minutes, golden four minutes!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So people around you know how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls down, we can rescue him through professional knowledge, instead of standing there dumbfounded and unable to do anything. This feeling of helplessness is so frightening.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: "In China, we have official data that 3 million people die accidentally every year, the most dangerous one is called cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, an average of 15% can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In the casino hotels in Las Vegas, 70 to 80 percent can be saved, and less than 1 percent in Shanghai and Beijing.”
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, founder of First Response, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has a sudden cardiac arrest, there is no breathing, no heartbeat, you have no effect on pinching the person.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: You must do artificial respiration and chest compressions to save the person.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I find that few of us have this awareness to learn first aid, but it is too late when something happens, so I still call on everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond in time when faced with emergencies.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: It might even save a life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: The first aid certificate can be registered at your local Red Cross training center. I registered at the Red Cross training center in Zhuhai, and there are discounts for students.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is to record the goals to be completed before the age of 25. Adding the first aid certificate to the list of goals was a few months ago, but it is indeed completed!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Now I'm going to take another test for other certificates. I plan to take a diving certificate. I saw in Xiaohongshu before I have a diving first aid certificate. It seems that I have to have a first aid certificate to take the test, so the first aid certificate is actually very useful!
ref: Next, I will apply for other certificates; I plan to get Diving Certificate; I saw on Red earlier that there is a Diving First Aid Certificate, which requires a Certificate of First Aid first, so getting a Certificate of First Aid is useful!

ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the characteristics and advantages of Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment

src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。
mt: Yixin inspection well block brick machine equipment is widely used in new masonry materials for municipal underground structures such as coal, heat, water, electricity, and gas.
ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: various inspection wells for drainage and water storage facilities, storm drains, square ditches, septic tanks and small structures, bridge wing walls, etc.
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper, lower, left and right sides of the modules are all concave-convex groove structure, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shear resistance of the shaft wall is much better than that of the flat friction masonry.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure. After the combined masonry is connected, the longitudinal holes are connected, and the horizontal holes are connected. After the hole core is poured, a cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed, which plays a role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The modules are provided with grooves for inserting reinforcements vertically and horizontally, and the horizontal and longitudinal reinforcement should improve the overall strength of the structure.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, the inspection wells and drainage wells built with concrete inspection well modules are not prone to collapse, subsidence, water leakage, etc., and the well wall module has stable mechanical performance, simple operation and standard forming size.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备智能控制配备数据输入、输出装置一键通触摸式液晶显示监控机械操作全部过程，实现理想的人机对话、自动分析比料、密度运转、安全逻辑控制及故障诊断系统。
mt: The intelligent control of the concrete inspection well module block machine equipment is equipped with data input and output devices, one-touch touch-type LCD display, and monitors the entire process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis of material ratio, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械液压系统采用单缸液压、输送，双缸液压、输送。
mt: The mechanical hydraulic system of the well wall module adopts single cylinder hydraulic and conveying, and double-cylinder hydraulic and conveying.
ref: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.

src: 独立的液压集成站，避免了由于主机振动对液压系统的影响，从而保证液压系统工作的可靠性。
mt: The independent hydraulic integration station avoids the influence of the host vibration on the hydraulic system, thus ensuring the reliability of the hydraulic system.
ref: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.

mt: Concrete inspection well module block machine equipment distributing box goes up to release the mold box, the storage box door is closed, and the pallet is automatically transported, all independently completed by the hydraulic system, thus reducing the mechanical wear and tear and maintenance.
ref: In the concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, the fabric box proceeding box de-molds and lifts, the storage box door closes, and the supporting plate is transported automatically, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system so as to reduce mechanical abrasion and times of repair.

mt: The mechanical vibration excitation platform of the well wall module adopts the integral plate steel, and the table has no welding point for line cutting and clamping, so that the stuffing box can be swing and guided freely and fully reduce the mechanical wear.
ref: The integral steel plate is adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical vibration platform, with no welding points of wire-electrode cutting mold closing of mesa, so that the stuffing box can swing and orient freely to greatly reduce mechanical abrasion.

src: 使模具负荷减少、填料并二合一加密振幅，采用一体化、全同步，台振、模振，确保达到振实效果。
mt: The mold load is reduced, the filling is combined into one to encrypt the amplitude, and the integrated, full synchronization, table vibration and mold vibration are adopted to ensure the vibration effect.
ref: It reduces loads of molds and reinforces vibration; integrated and full synchronization are adopted for vibration of the platform and the molds to ensure the vibration effect.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振机械、电脑自动控制振幅根据原料性价比调节振幅，无磨损制动，从而延长使用寿命，降低成本。
mt: The shaft wall module mechanical vibration excitation mechanism and computer automatically control the amplitude to adjust the amplitude according to the cost performance of raw materials, and there is no wear and breakage, thus extending the service life and reducing costs.
ref: The shaft wall module mechanical excitation machinery and the computer automatically control the vibration range according to the cost performance of raw materials, leading to no abrasion brake; in this way, it extends the service life and reduces the cost.

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories: Virgin Olive Oil and Refined Olive Oil (Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil), with five levels.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is the oil obtained directly from fresh olive fruits by mechanical cold pressing and filtering to remove foreign matter.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: There are three levels according to the acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra virgin olive oil (Extra Virgin): It is the highest grade, highest quality olive oil and a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary Virgin Olive Oil: The taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil obtained by refining virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or "secondary oil".
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have seen the classification, you should have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You must know that olives are just like grapes that make wine. Olives from different producing areas and different varieties of olives will produce different standards of olive oil.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable soil and temperature, sunshine, air humidity and precipitation for the growth of olive oil.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Except for the Mediterranean coast, other regions can only be grown sporadically in suitable areas.

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and similar climates are also Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc. in the southern latitudes.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Picking months for olives:
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: Each year from March to June, olive trees bloom and bear fruit. From July to October, the fruit begins to develop and mature, and the fruit transitions from green to red, purple, and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, as well as vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered to be the most suitable oil for human nutrition of the oils found so far.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法是什么？
mt: What is the red label whisky?
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。
mt: Everyone has different hobbies. Some people like collecting, some like food, and of course some people like wine tasting. The red brand whisky is one of the best-selling Scotch whisky in various countries, and the red brand whisky has won the gold medal of the International Wine Competition.
ref: Different people have different preferences; some like to collect, some like food, and certainly some like wine tasting; Johnnie Walker Red Label is one of the fastest selling Scottish whiskies in the world and has won the gold prize of International Wine Competition.

src: 每一瓶红牌威士忌都有独特的味道，不过如果不知道如何品味它，岂不是糟蹋了它的醇香。
mt: Every bottle of Red Label whisky has a unique taste, but if you don't know how to taste it, you are dousing it.
ref: Each bottle of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky has its own unique flavor, but if you don’t know how to taste it, it would be such a waste of its mellow fragrance.

src: 那么红牌威士忌怎么喝呢？
mt: So how do you drink red label whisky?
ref: Then how do we drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 小编为大家简单介绍下。
mt: Let me briefly introduce it to you.
ref: I’ll introduce for you now.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法：
mt: How to drink red label whisky:
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky:

src: 尊尼获加红牌威士忌由约35种苏格兰威士忌调配而成，具有浓郁芳香及传统苏格兰威士忌的特质，浓郁芳香中带有甘甜及烟熏香味。
mt: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended from about 35 Scotch whiskies, with a rich aroma and characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with sweet and smoky aroma in the rich aroma.
ref: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended with around 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, possesses rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

src: 入口浓醇清新，略带香草及浓烈的烟熏麦芽味道。
mt: The entry is rich and fresh, with hints of vanilla and a strong smoky malt flavor.
ref: It is mellow and fresh in the mouth, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.

src: 该酒可以直接加冰饮用，或者与最喜爱的饮品混合饮用。
mt: The wine can be enjoyed straight over ice or mixed with your favorite beverage.
ref: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: Red label whiskey enters China, in order to adapt to the taste of Chinese people, red brand whiskey + sparkling drinks such as Coke or Sprite or Sunkist have become an enduring fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: These sweet drinks, in addition to neutralizing the sour taste, can bring visual pleasure to people, and adding drinks to dilute the taste and change the taste.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Red brand whiskey + sliced lemon + sugar cube (granulated sugar can also), is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.
ref: Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.

src: 正宗的红方威味道有些酸涩,加入糖可以中和其中的酸味,柠檬则会给酒带来清新的香味,当然,甜酸度可根据个人的口味爱好调配。
mt: Authentic Hong Fangwei tastes a little sour. Adding sugar can neutralize the acidity, and lemon will bring a fresh aroma to the wine. Of course, the sweetness and acidity can be adjusted according to personal taste.
ref: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour; adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, lemon will bring fresh fragrance to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and sourness can be adjusted according to personal tastes.

src: 以上三种都是红牌威士忌的最好喝法，大家可以作为参考尝试下，希望小编的介绍可以帮助到大家。
mt: The above three are the best ways to drink red brand whisky. You can try it as a reference. I hope my introduction can help you.
ref: The above are the best drinking methods of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky for your refence, and I hope my introduction can help you.

src: 金夫人婚纱摄影(南街店) 暂时还没有分店
mt: Mrs. Jin Wedding Photography (South Street) has no branch yet
ref: Mrs. Gold Wedding Dress Photography (Nanjie Store) has no branch store yet.

mt: Before taking the pictures, because our time was not arranged well, we changed the time twice, and consultant Lan Lan patiently helped us arrange the time.
ref: Because I didn’t arrange my time well before the shoot, I rescheduled twice and consultant Lanlan patiently arranged time for us.

src: 后来选择了一个天气好的周末拍的。
mt: I chose to shoot on a weekend with good weather.

src: 金夫人的工作人员，无论是顾问，化妆师还是摄影师都超赞的。

src: 那是我生平第一次正式地化妆，哇～简直不敢相信，我有一天也会变得那么好看，哈哈。
mt: It was the first time in my life to actually wear makeup, wow~ I can't believe I will be so pretty one day lol.
ref: That was the first time that I had officially put on makeup and wow, I couldn’t even believe that I could be so pretty one day, haha.

src: 晓洁和另一个妹子（抱歉我记不得名字了）化妆超级有耐心，化妆也很自然。
mt: Xiaojie and another girl (sorry I can't remember the name) are super patient in their makeup and natural.
ref: Xiaojie and the other girl (sorry, I forgot her name) were super patient while doing my makeup and the makeup was natural.

src: 外景在江湾城拍的，幸亏那天天气很好，没有觉得很冷，拍照的时候，化妆师时不时地留意我们的衣服，头饰，稍微有一点不好了就马上帮我们整理。
mt: The exterior location was shot in Jiangwan City. Fortunately, the weather was good that day, and I didn’t feel cold. When taking pictures, the makeup artist paid attention to our clothes and headwear from time to time, and would immediately help us to organize anything in case of a little bit of trouble.
ref: We shot the outdoor scene at Jiangwancheng, and fortunately the weather was nice that day, we didn’t feel cold; during the shoot, makeup artist was paying attention to our clothes, headwear, and made adjustment immediately once there was a problem.

src: 摄影师也非常幽默，拍照一天下来都觉得很开心。
mt: The photographer is also very humorous, and I feel very happy after taking pictures all day.
ref: The photographer was funny, and we were happy throughout the day.

src: 在选照片的时候，因为在网上看到很多案例，不愿意让客人删太多照片，但是我们选照片的时候，真的，一点没有让我们加照片的意思，直接套餐里的24张，一张都没有加（听说和我差不多时间拍婚纱照的表妹，七千多的套餐还加了一万多的照片，当时我就惊呆了，心里也很怕自己会选太多）
mt: When choosing photos, because we saw a lot of cases on the Internet, I did not want to let the customers delete too many photos, but when we chose photos, we really didn’t want to let us add photos at all. Of the 24 photos in the package, not a single photo was added. (I heard that my cousin who took wedding photos at about the same time as me, added more than 10,000 photos to the seven thousand获胜 package. So I was shrill, and I was afraid that I would choose too much)
ref: When choosing the photos, I saw many cases online where they wouldn’t let the customers delete too many photos, but they didn’t ask us to add photos at all, just the 24 photos in the set and nothing more (I heard that my cousin who was also taking wedding dress photos added photos worth over 10,000 in addition to the 7,000 yuan set, and I was stunned and feared I might choose too many).

src: 今天照片修好了，兰兰发给我，我看了有两张觉得不太好，他们立刻就帮我重新修了。
mt: I have completed photos today and Lan Lan sent them to me. I saw two of them that were not very good, so they immediately fixed them for me.

src: 玻璃基底的芯片在发货前均在800mbar（100um沟道）进样压力下通过纯水测试，您在使用玻璃基底芯片过程中请注意不要与尖锐物体碰撞，否则会损坏基底。

mt: Damei 360 integrated home improvement
ref: Damei 360 Integrated Home Decoration

mt: Address: 12th Floor, Happy Home, No. 156 South Huancheng Road

src: 一开始是朋友介绍的因为信任，所以选择来看一下起初我的预算是7万做个基本装修。
mt: At the beginning, it was introduced by a friend because of trust, so I chose to take a look at it. At first my budget was 70,000 to do a basic decoration.
ref: I trusted it because my friend made the recommendation, so I chose to check it out, and originally my budget for a basic decoration was 70,000.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。
mt: Coming to the store, a series of tricks began.
ref: A series of scam began as soon as I came into the store.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: It was the first time I went to the store and I just showed them my layout. They didn’t go to measure the house on site, but they can actually quote me that my 135 house is less than 70,000 yuan. They probably showed me their materials and I didn’t know what brand they were.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second trick is that as long as you come to the store, they will drag you to pay the deposit (and once the money is paid, you will never get it back unless you have enough experience to argue with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: When I was hesitating to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell you how much discount we can give you as long as you pay the deposit today.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。
mt: This is a big pit. I am a living example of being cheated. When I was impulsive, I paid a deposit of more than 10,000.
ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: There were a lot of problems in his quote he gave me 70,000 does not include plumbing and utilities, not including any doors and cabinets, bathroom, and these three are the bulk of the cost of decompression.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。
mt: Apart from these, their service point charges are also higher than other companies.
ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

src: 我对这个公司失去了信任，一开始什么都没有讲清楚就让我签合同。
mt: I lost trust in this company and asked me to sign the contract without making it clear at the beginning.
ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

src: 当我去找他们退钱的时候他们表现出很有经验的样子，有专门的小团队来对付你。
mt: When I went to them to refund the money they seemed experienced and have a small team to deal with you.
ref: When I went to ask for a refund, they acted rather experienced and sent a small team to deal with me.

src: 无论如何都会一口咬死是客户的问题他们全然无责。
mt: Anyhow, the bite to death is the client's problem and they are totally not responsible.
ref: Anyway, they just said it was the client’s problem and they had absolutely no responsibility for it.

src: 各种推卸责任，还有很多细节，不想一一说了都是泪，总之不要选择他们，因为我朋友找他们装修的房子也是质量不好，后期给你算各种费用。
mt: All kinds of shirking the responsibilities, and there are many details. I do not want to talk about them all. I will be in tears. In short, don’t choose them, because the house my friends find them to decorate is of poor quality, and I will give you all kinds of expenses later.
ref: They just shrunk their responsibility in any way possible, and there were a lot more details that I don’t want to mention now; all in all, do not choose them because my friend had them renovate her apartment, and the quality was poor and they would charge you all kinds of other costs in the later stage.

src: 坑爹，他们就是原来骗人的龙头装饰，现在改成大美，好像又倒闭了又改成其他的。
mt: Darn, they are the original deceiving leading decoration, and now they are changed to Damei, it seems that it has closed down and changed to something else.

src: 所以大家别选择这样坑爹的装修公司。

src: 以后大家在选择的时候多百度看看这些查一下这些咨询因为装修不是小钱。

src: 环境：说实话店里面积大，有8～9层，家里想买的家具、家用电器、各种小东西……，都能买到，好多名牌商家都入驻在店里，慕思、欧派、华帝、老板、峰创之家、汉斯顿、雅克、友邦、丝涟、富品居、万家乐、大自然、中联、美的、雅丹……，品牌真的是太多了，我只能记得这么多了，是购买产品的好去处，逛累了可以坐在沙发上休息休息哦。

Many famous brand merchants have settled in the store, such as Mousse, Oppe, Vantage, boss, Feng Chuang home, Hanston, Jacques, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, Macro, Nature, Zhonglian, Midea, Yadan... There are so many brands, I can only remember so many, and it is a good place to buy products, you can sit on the sofa rest and relax when you are tired.
ref: Environment: Honestly, the store is large with 8-9 floors, where you can buy all the furniture, household appliances and small things your home needs, and many famous brands have settled in the store, such as DeRUCCI, OPPEIN, VATTI, Robam, Fengchuang Home, Hunsdon, Yake, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, GUANGDONG MACRO, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, and so many other brands, I can only remember so many; it is a good place to buy products, and you can sit on the couch and have a rest if you get tired.

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that I think is very meaningful - a first aid certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skills certificates I think is important in addition to a driver's license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Popularize it: First aid measures are actually emergency rescue in the event of an emergency, that is, rescue before the ambulance arrives.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is actually a period of time left for the ambulance to arrive after the accident, and it is this period that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is the time when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I actually had a heart attack, a cerebral hemorrhage, or respiratory arrest, then the window of our lives would only be four minutes, golden four minutes!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: That's why people around you understand how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls down, we can rescue him through our expertise instead of standing there motionless and unable to do anything. This feeling of helplessness is so scary.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: “In China, our official data shows that 3 million people die unexpectedly every year. The most dangerous is cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the US, an average of 15% can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In casino hotels in Las Vegas, 780 percent can be saved, and less than 1% in Shanghai and Beijing.”
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, founder of First Response, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has a cardiac arrest, no breathing, and no heartbeat, there is no effect on you choking people.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: Artificial respiration and chest compression are necessary to save people.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I found that few of us now have this kind of awareness to learn first aid, but when things happen, it's too late, so I urge everyone to learn this skill so that we can respond in a timely manner when faced with an emergency.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: Maybe it can also save a person's life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: You can register for a first aid certificate at your local Red Cross training center. I signed up at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai. Students still have discounts.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is a record of the goals I have to complete before I'm 25 years old. Adding the first aid certificate to the goal list was a few months ago, but it was done!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Next, I'm going to take the other certificates I want to take. I'm planning to take a diving certificate. I saw in Xiaohongshu before that there was also a diving first aid certificate. It seems like you still have to have a first aid certificate to take the exam, so in fact, a first aid certificate is still very useful!
ref: Next, I will apply for other certificates; I plan to get Diving Certificate; I saw on Red earlier that there is a Diving First Aid Certificate, which requires a Certificate of First Aid first, so getting a Certificate of First Aid is useful!

mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the top, bottom, left and right sides of the module are concave and convex grooves, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: After the core is poured, a cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed, which plays the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproofing.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。

ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil obtained by refining extra virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or “secondary oil”.
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two levels:
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Olive Oil (Olive Oil): Refined olive oil is mixed with a percentage of extra virgin olive oil to balance the taste and color. It has an acidity of less than 1.5% and is transparent, light golden yellow.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined olive impurity oil or olive pomace oil (Refined Olive Pomace Oil): Olive oil extracted from oil residue by dissolution and refined.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have read the grade classification, you should have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You need to know that olive fruits are just like grapes that make wine. Olive fruits from different regions and varieties of olive fruits produce olive oil of different standards.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: The best places to grow oleocanthal:
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable soil and climate conditions for oleocanthal growth, such as temperature, sunshine, air humidity, and precipitation.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Other than the Mediterranean coast, other regions can only be cultivated sporadically in suitable habitats.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main regions of origin (Mediterranean):
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc. Similar climates are Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc. far south latitude.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: The month in which oleocanthal is harvested:
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: Every year, March to June is the time when the oleocanthal tree blooms and sets fruit. From July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the fruit transitions from green to red, purple, and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: November to February is the fruit picking season (the freshness of the olive oil is very important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: The nutritional content of olive oil:
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered one of the most nutritious oils found to date.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.

src: 其实对于身体微胖的女孩子穿衣搭配的讲究很多。
mt: In fact, a lot of attention is paid to how girls with slightly fat bodies dress and match.
ref: Actually, there are many tricks for slightly overweight girls to match their clothes.

src: 身体胖的女孩穿的裙子不能太短或太长，长度差不多在膝盖，刚好能盖住大腿胖的地方即可。
mt: Girls with fat bodies can't wear skirts that are too short or too long. The length is about the knee, just enough to cover the fat thighs.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall wear skirts not too long or too short; they shall be of the length at around the knees, just covering the fat part of the thighs.

src: 裙子过短就会把腿上的肥胖显露出来。
mt: If the skirt is too short, it will reveal the obesity on the legs.
ref: The fat thighs will be shown if the skirt is too short.

src: 过长就会给人矮而胖的感觉。
mt: Being too long gives people the feeling of being short and fat.
ref: Skirts that are too long will make you look short and fat.

src: 如果穿出分出上中下三段来，就显得你自然增高了，就是上身、裙和长筒袜用不同的颜色，看上去就会产生一种修长的感觉 。
mt: If you wear it in three sections, the top, middle, and bottom, it will appear that you are naturally taller. That is, the upper body, skirt, and stockings are used in different colors, and you will look slender.
ref: If you are dressed in three sections, upper, middle and lower, you will naturally look taller; that is, use different colors for upper body, skirt and stockings, and you will look taller and slimmer.

src: 其实很多深色系的衣服是微胖女孩子们的标配（这一点作者深有体会），深颜色也是掩盖你身体胖的好方法，高贵典雅的黑色短裙也是微胖女孩的首选。
mt: In fact, many dark clothes are standard for chubby girls (the author deeply appreciates this). Dark colors are also a good way to hide your body weight. Noble and elegant black skirts are also the first choice for chubby girls.
ref: In fact, a lot of darker color clothes are what slightly overweight girls all have, which the author deeply agrees; dark colors are good methods to cover fatness of your bodies; in addition, noble and elegant black short shirts are best choices for slightly overweight girls.

src: 穿上深颜色的衣服，特别是黑色的短裙，会让人觉得你瘦一些。
mt: Wearing dark clothes, especially short black skirts, can make people think you're thinner.
ref: You will look slimmer in dark clothes, especially black short skirts.

src: 如果小腿很胖，你的袜子和鞋不要穿得太让人注意。
mt: If your calves are fat, don't wear socks and shoes that are too noticeable.
ref: Wear stockings and low-key shoes if your calves are fat.

src: 越大众化越好，颜色也不要太鲜艳了。
mt: The more popular it is, the better, and the colors should not be too bright.
ref: The more common the better; the color shouldn’t be too bright.

src: 以免人们对你的腿部和脚部注意时，让人得到肥胖的感觉。
mt: So as not to make people feel obese when they pay attention to your legs and feet.
ref: In case people will notice your legs and feet and think you’re fat.

src: 对于微微稍胖的女孩子一定要讲就好穿衣搭配的诀窍。
mt: For girls who are slightly fat, be sure to tell you tips on how to dress and match well.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall master the tricks for clothing matching.

src: 微胖女孩千万不要穿紧身的短裙，另外上衣不要过短或者塞在裙子里，会让人看了很不舒服，如果腿粗的话，要穿黑色的长筒袜或者网格袜(细格子的那种哦)，选择质地柔软的印花喇叭裙，搭配一件荡领的上衣，可以很好的掩盖胖女孩的不足。
mt: Chubby girls should never wear tight skirts, and the top should not be too short or tucked into the skirt, which makes people look very uncomfortable. If the legs are thick, wear black stockings or mesh socks (the kind of fine plaid oh), choose a printed flared skirt with a soft texture, with a swinging top, can cover up the shortcomings of fat girls well.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall never wear close-fitting short skirts and the upper outer garment shall not be too short or tucked inside the skirt, which seem strange; slightly overweight girls with thicker legs shall wear black stockings or mesh stockings (thin meshes), a flare skirt with print pattern and soft texture, and a loose-collar upper outer garment to cover the defects of the body.

src: 当然了，微胖的女孩儿在穿短裙上也是有讲究的。
mt: Of course, chubby girls also pay attention to wearing short skirts.
ref: Of course, there are some skills for slightly overweight girls to wear short skirts.

mt: When fat girls wear short skirts, they should choose a top that matches the color of the short skirt, so that your fat figure will have the effect of increasing height.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法是什么？
mt: What is the way to drink red brand whiskey?
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。
mt: Everyone has different hobbies. Some people like to collect, some like food, and of course others like wine tasting. Red Brand whiskey is currently one of the best-selling Scotch whiskies in various countries, and the Red Brand whiskey has won a gold medal in the International Wine Competition.
ref: Different people have different preferences; some like to collect, some like food, and certainly some like wine tasting; Johnnie Walker Red Label is one of the fastest selling Scottish whiskies in the world and has won the gold prize of International Wine Competition.

src: 每一瓶红牌威士忌都有独特的味道，不过如果不知道如何品味它，岂不是糟蹋了它的醇香。
mt: Every bottle of red brand whiskey has a unique taste, but if you don't know how to taste it, wouldn't it ruin its mellow aroma.
ref: Each bottle of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky has its own unique flavor, but if you don’t know how to taste it, it would be such a waste of its mellow fragrance.

src: 那么红牌威士忌怎么喝呢？
mt: So how do you drink red brand whiskey?
ref: Then how do we drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 小编为大家简单介绍下。
mt: Xiaobian will give you a brief introduction.
ref: I’ll introduce for you now.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法：
mt: How to drink red brand whiskey:
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky:

src: 尊尼获加红牌威士忌由约35种苏格兰威士忌调配而成，具有浓郁芳香及传统苏格兰威士忌的特质，浓郁芳香中带有甘甜及烟熏香味。
mt: Johnnie Walker Red Whisky is a blend of about 35 Scotch whiskies. It has a rich aroma and the characteristics of traditional scotch whiskies, with sweet and smoky aromas in the rich aroma.
ref: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended with around 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, possesses rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

src: 入口浓醇清新，略带香草及浓烈的烟熏麦芽味道。
mt: The mouth is rich and fresh, with hints of vanilla and strong smoky malt.
ref: It is mellow and fresh in the mouth, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.

src: 该酒可以直接加冰饮用，或者与最喜爱的饮品混合饮用。
mt: You can drink it directly with ice, or mix it with your favorite drink.
ref: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: Red whiskey has entered the country. In order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, sparkling drinks such as red brand whiskey+cola or Sprite or Novice have become an enduring fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: In addition to neutralizing the sour taste, these sweet drinks are visually pleasing. Adding them to the drink has the effect of diluting the taste and changing the taste.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Red whiskey+sliced lemon+sugar cube (sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional way to drink.
ref: Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.

src: 正宗的红方威味道有些酸涩,加入糖可以中和其中的酸味,柠檬则会给酒带来清新的香味,当然,甜酸度可根据个人的口味爱好调配。
mt: Authentic Red Fang Wei has a slightly sour taste. Adding sugar neutralizes the sour taste, while lemon brings a fresh aroma to the wine. Of course, the sweet acidity can be adjusted according to personal tastes and tastes.
ref: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour; adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, lemon will bring fresh fragrance to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and sourness can be adjusted according to personal tastes.

src: 以上三种都是红牌威士忌的最好喝法，大家可以作为参考尝试下，希望小编的介绍可以帮助到大家。
mt: The above three are the best ways to drink red whiskey. You can try them as a reference. I hope Xiaobian's introduction can help you.
ref: The above are the best drinking methods of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky for your refence, and I hope my introduction can help you.

src: 外景在江湾城拍的，幸亏那天天气很好，没有觉得很冷，拍照的时候，化妆师时不时地留意我们的衣服，头饰，稍微有一点不好了就马上帮我们整理。
mt: The location was taken in Jiangwan City. Fortunately, the weather was very good that day, and I didn't feel very cold. When we took pictures, the makeup artist paid attention to our clothes and headwear from time to time, and helped us sort it out right away if it was a little bad.
ref: We shot the outdoor scene at Jiangwancheng, and fortunately the weather was nice that day, we didn’t feel cold; during the shoot, makeup artist was paying attention to our clothes, headwear, and made adjustment immediately once there was a problem.

src: 摄影师也非常幽默，拍照一天下来都觉得很开心。
mt: The photographer was also very humorous, and I felt very happy taking pictures all day.
ref: The photographer was funny, and we were happy throughout the day.

src: 在选照片的时候，因为在网上看到很多案例，不愿意让客人删太多照片，但是我们选照片的时候，真的，一点没有让我们加照片的意思，直接套餐里的24张，一张都没有加（听说和我差不多时间拍婚纱照的表妹，七千多的套餐还加了一万多的照片，当时我就惊呆了，心里也很怕自己会选太多）
mt: When selecting photos, because I saw many cases on the Internet, I didn't want guests to delete too many photos, but when we chose photos, really, it didn't mean that we added photos at all. None of the 24 photos in the direct package were added (I heard that my cousin who took wedding photos about the same time as me, added more than 10,000 photos to the 7,000 package. At the time, I was stunned, and I was afraid I would choose too many)
ref: When choosing the photos, I saw many cases online where they wouldn’t let the customers delete too many photos, but they didn’t ask us to add photos at all, just the 24 photos in the set and nothing more (I heard that my cousin who was also taking wedding dress photos added photos worth over 10,000 in addition to the 7,000 yuan set, and I was stunned and feared I might choose too many).

src: 今天照片修好了，兰兰发给我，我看了有两张觉得不太好，他们立刻就帮我重新修了。
mt: Today's photo was fixed. Lan Lan sent it to me. I saw two of them that I didn't think were very good, and they immediately helped me fix them again.
ref: The editing was finished today and Lanlan sent it to me; I felt two were not good enough and they immediately re-edited them for me.

src: 把妹妹以前拍的照片翻出来对比，我觉得我们的照片我真的太满意了，简约清新，就是我想要的风格。
mt: Comparing the photos my sister took before, I think I'm really satisfied with our photos. They are simple and fresh, just the style I want.
ref: I found the old photos of my sister to make comparison, and I felt that our photos were really satisfying, simple and fresh, exactly what I wanted.

ref: Mr. Li told reporter that he recently bought a feet bath basin for his father as a birthday present, but his father felt that the bottom of his feet were numb when using it.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: The first time I arrived at the store, I only showed them my apartment map. They didn't go to the site to measure the house. They could actually quote me that 70,000 of my 135 house could be done. I probably showed me their materials and I didn't know what brand they were.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second trick is that you will drag you to pay the deposit as soon as you arrive at the store (and once this money is paid, you will never be able to withdraw it, unless you have enough experience to fight a theoretical battle with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: When I'm hesitant about paying a deposit, they invite their so-called manager to tell you how much discount we can give you if you pay the deposit today.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。

ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: There were a lot of questions about the offer he gave me 70,000, which did not include water and electricity transformations, did not include any doors and cabinets in the bathroom, and these three were the bulk of the cost of the base installation.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。

ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

If you're tired of shopping, you can sit on the sofa and rest.

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that feels very meaningful - first aid certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skills certificates that I think is important in addition to the driver's license!!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Popularize it: First aid measures are actually emergency rescue in the event of an emergency, that is, rescue before the ambulance arrives.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is still a period of time in the process of the ambulance coming after the accident, and it is this period that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is the time when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I do have a heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage, or respiratory arrest, then our window of life is only four minutes, four golden minutes!!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So the people around you know how important first aid is!!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone falls down around us, we can use our professional knowledge to rescue him, instead of standing there motionless and unable to do anything, the feeling of helplessness is so terrible.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: "In China, our official figures show that three million people die accidentally every year, the most dangerous being cardiac arrest."
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, an average of 15% can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In the casino hotels in Las Vegas, 70% and 80% can be saved, while in Shanghai and Beijing, less than 1% can be saved.
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, the founder of First Response, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has cardiac arrest, no breathing, no heartbeat, there is no effect in your pinching.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: It is necessary to do artificial respiration and chest compressions to save people.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I find that few of us have this awareness to learn first aid, but when things happen, it is too late, so I call on everyone to learn this skill so that we can respond in time when facing emergencies.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: Maybe it can save a person's life!!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: The first aid card can be registered at your local Red Cross training center. I signed up at the Red Cross training center in Zhuhai.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is a record of the goals to be completed before the age of 25. It was also a few months ago that the first aid card was added to the list of goals, but it was indeed completed!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Then I have to take the other certificates I want to take, and I plan to take a diving certificate. I saw a diving first aid certificate in Xiaohongshu before, and it seems that I have to have a first aid certificate to take the test, so in fact, the first aid certificate is still very useful!

mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper, lower, left and right sides of the modules are concave and convex grooves, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure, and after the combined masonry, the longitudinal holes are connected, and the transverse holes are connected. After the core is poured, a cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed, which plays a role of secondary reinforcement and waterproofing.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

ref: Nice perception, good color rendition performance and high quality!

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, with five levels.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is the oil obtained directly from fresh olive fruit after mechanical cold pressing and filtering to remove foreign matter.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: There are three levels according to the acidity:
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra Virgin Olive Oil: The highest grade and highest quality olive oil, it is a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: The taste is excellent, with a light and pleasant botanical aroma, and the acidity is not more than 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: Fine Virgin Olive Oil: Slightly higher acidity, but not more than 2%, pure and aromatic.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary Virgin Olive Oil: The taste and flavor are fair, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or as "secondary oil."
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two grades:
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Ordinary Olive Oil: Refined olive oil is mixed with a certain proportion of virgin olive oil to blend flavor and color. Its acidity is below 1.5%, and it is a transparent pale golden yellow.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined Olive - Pomace Oil: Olive oil is extracted from oil residue by dissolution and refined.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have looked at the classification, you should have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You should know that olive fruit is just like the grapes used to make wine. Olive fruit from different regions and varieties of olive fruit will produce different standards of olive oil.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: The best place to grow olives:.
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable soil and climate conditions for the growth of olives, such as temperature, sunshine, air humidity and precipitation.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Except for the Mediterranean coast, other areas can only be sporadically planted in suitable areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main producing areas (Mediterranean):.
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and similar climates include Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far south latitudes.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Olive picking month:.
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: From March to June of each year, the olive tree blossoms and bears fruit. From July to October, the fruit begins to develop and mature, and the fruit transitions from green to red, purple, and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: November to February is the picking season (the freshness of olive oil is very important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: Nutritional content of olive oil:.
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, as well as vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered to be the most suitable oil for human nutrition among the oils found so far.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.

src: 其实对于身体微胖的女孩子穿衣搭配的讲究很多。
mt: In fact, there is a lot of emphasis on dressing and matching for girls who are slightly fat.
ref: Actually, there are many tricks for slightly overweight girls to match their clothes.

src: 身体胖的女孩穿的裙子不能太短或太长，长度差不多在膝盖，刚好能盖住大腿胖的地方即可。
mt: The skirt worn by a fat girl should not be too short or too long, and the length is almost at the knee, just enough to cover the fat part of the thigh.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall wear skirts not too long or too short; they shall be of the length at around the knees, just covering the fat part of the thighs.

src: 裙子过短就会把腿上的肥胖显露出来。
mt: If the skirt is too short, it will show the fat on the legs.
ref: The fat thighs will be shown if the skirt is too short.

src: 过长就会给人矮而胖的感觉。
mt: Too long will give a person the feeling of short and fat.
ref: Skirts that are too long will make you look short and fat.

src: 如果穿出分出上中下三段来，就显得你自然增高了，就是上身、裙和长筒袜用不同的颜色，看上去就会产生一种修长的感觉 。
mt: If you wear the upper, middle and lower sections, it will appear that you will naturally increase in height, that is, the upper body, skirt and stockings with different colors, it will look like a slender feeling.
ref: If you are dressed in three sections, upper, middle and lower, you will naturally look taller; that is, use different colors for upper body, skirt and stockings, and you will look taller and slimmer.

src: 其实很多深色系的衣服是微胖女孩子们的标配（这一点作者深有体会），深颜色也是掩盖你身体胖的好方法，高贵典雅的黑色短裙也是微胖女孩的首选。
mt: In fact, many dark colors are standard for fat girls (which the author has a deep understanding of), dark colors are also a good way to cover up your body fat, and elegant black skirts are also the first choice for fat girls.
ref: In fact, a lot of darker color clothes are what slightly overweight girls all have, which the author deeply agrees; dark colors are good methods to cover fatness of your bodies; in addition, noble and elegant black short shirts are best choices for slightly overweight girls.

src: 穿上深颜色的衣服，特别是黑色的短裙，会让人觉得你瘦一些。
mt: Wearing dark clothes, especially short black skirts, will make people think you are thinner.
ref: You will look slimmer in dark clothes, especially black short skirts.

src: 如果小腿很胖，你的袜子和鞋不要穿得太让人注意。
mt: If your calves are fat, don't wear your socks and shoes too noticeably.
ref: Wear stockings and low-key shoes if your calves are fat.

src: 越大众化越好，颜色也不要太鲜艳了。
mt: The more popular the better, and the colors should not be too bright.
ref: The more common the better; the color shouldn’t be too bright.

src: 以免人们对你的腿部和脚部注意时，让人得到肥胖的感觉。
mt: Lest people pay attention to your legs and feet, so that people get the feeling of obesity.
ref: In case people will notice your legs and feet and think you’re fat.

src: 对于微微稍胖的女孩子一定要讲就好穿衣搭配的诀窍。
mt: For girls who are slightly fat, we must tell you the tricks of how to dress and match.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall master the tricks for clothing matching.

src: 微胖女孩千万不要穿紧身的短裙，另外上衣不要过短或者塞在裙子里，会让人看了很不舒服，如果腿粗的话，要穿黑色的长筒袜或者网格袜(细格子的那种哦)，选择质地柔软的印花喇叭裙，搭配一件荡领的上衣，可以很好的掩盖胖女孩的不足。
mt: Weak fat girls should never wear tight skirts, and the top should not be too short or tucked into the skirt, which will make people look uncomfortable. If the legs are thick, wear black stockings or mesh socks (the kind of thin plaid), choose a soft printed flared skirt, and match it with a top with a swinging collar, which can cover up the shortcomings of fat girls.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall never wear close-fitting short skirts and the upper outer garment shall not be too short or tucked inside the skirt, which seem strange; slightly overweight girls with thicker legs shall wear black stockings or mesh stockings (thin meshes), a flare skirt with print pattern and soft texture, and a loose-collar upper outer garment to cover the defects of the body.

src: 当然了，微胖的女孩儿在穿短裙上也是有讲究的。
mt: Of course, fat girls are also fastidious in wearing short skirts.
ref: Of course, there are some skills for slightly overweight girls to wear short skirts.

src: 胖女孩穿短裙，应该选择与短裙的颜色一致的上衣，这样会使你胖胖的身材有增加高度的效果。
mt: When fat girls wear short skirts, they should choose a top that is the same color as the short skirt, which will increase the height of your fat body.
ref: When slightly overweight girls wear short skirts, they shall choose upper outer garment with the same color as the short skirt, so as to make them look taller.

src: 短裙搭配高跟鞋，可以让你的双腿显得更为修长，这可是夏季最IN的搭配喔!
mt: A short skirt with high heels can make your legs look more slender, which is the most IN match in summer!
ref: Wearing skirt with a pair of high heels will make your legs seem slimmer and longer, which is the most fashionable outfit in summer!

src: 如果你是上身胖，但腿很瘦的MM，推荐选择华丽感的连衣短裙。
mt: If you are MM with fat upper body but thin legs, it is recommended to choose a short dress with a gorgeous feeling.
ref: Girls with fat upper body and slim legs shall choose short dress of luxurious style.

src: 不但能遮住大肚皮，更能展现你的优点。
mt: Not only can you cover your big belly, but you can also show your good points.
