src: 红牌威士忌喝法是什么？
mt: What is the drinking method of red brand whisky?
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。
mt: Everyone has different hobbies. Some people like to collect, some people like food, and of course some people like wine tasting. Red brand whisky is one of the best-selling Scotch whiskies in various countries, and Red brand whisky has won the gold medal in the International Wine Competition.
ref: Different people have different preferences; some like to collect, some like food, and certainly some like wine tasting; Johnnie Walker Red Label is one of the fastest selling Scottish whiskies in the world and has won the gold prize of International Wine Competition.

src: 每一瓶红牌威士忌都有独特的味道，不过如果不知道如何品味它，岂不是糟蹋了它的醇香。
mt: Every bottle of red brand whisky has a unique taste, but if you don't know how to taste it, it spoils its mellow flavor.
ref: Each bottle of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky has its own unique flavor, but if you don’t know how to taste it, it would be such a waste of its mellow fragrance.

src: 那么红牌威士忌怎么喝呢？
mt: So how do you drink red whisky?!
ref: Then how do we drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 小编为大家简单介绍下。
mt: Xiao Bian will give you a brief introduction.
ref: I’ll introduce for you now.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法：
mt: Red brand whisky drinking method:.
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky:

src: 尊尼获加红牌威士忌由约35种苏格兰威士忌调配而成，具有浓郁芳香及传统苏格兰威士忌的特质，浓郁芳香中带有甘甜及烟熏香味。
mt: Johnny Walker Red Brand Whisky is made from about 35 kinds of Scotch whiskies. It has a rich aroma and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky. It has a rich aroma with sweet and smoky aromas.
ref: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended with around 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, possesses rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

src: 入口浓醇清新，略带香草及浓烈的烟熏麦芽味道。
mt: The entrance is rich and fresh, with a hint of vanilla and strong smoked malt flavor.
ref: It is mellow and fresh in the mouth, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.

src: 该酒可以直接加冰饮用，或者与最喜爱的饮品混合饮用。
mt: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drink.
ref: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: Red brand whisky has entered the country, and in order to adapt to the tastes of the people, red brand whisky + Coke or Sprite or Sinkis and other sparkling drinks have become a long-lasting fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: These sweet beverages, in addition to neutralizing the sour taste, can bring visual pleasure, and add beverages to dilute the taste and change the taste.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Red brand whisky + sliced lemon + sugar cube (also sugar) is the most authentic and traditional drink.
ref: Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.

src: 正宗的红方威味道有些酸涩,加入糖可以中和其中的酸味,柠檬则会给酒带来清新的香味,当然,甜酸度可根据个人的口味爱好调配。
mt: The authentic Red Fangwei taste is a bit sour and astringent, and adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, while lemon will bring a fresh aroma to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and acidity can be blended according to your taste preferences.
ref: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour; adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, lemon will bring fresh fragrance to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and sourness can be adjusted according to personal tastes.

src: 以上三种都是红牌威士忌的最好喝法，大家可以作为参考尝试下，希望小编的介绍可以帮助到大家。
mt: The above three are the best way to drink red brand whisky, you can try it as a reference, I hope the introduction of Xiaobian can help you.

src: 李先生告诉记者，近日，他买了一个足浴盆送给父亲做生日礼物，可是父亲泡脚时却感觉脚底发麻。

ref: Mr. Li told reporter that he recently bought a feet bath basin for his father as a birthday present, but his father felt that the bottom of his feet were numb when using it.

src: 李先生一开始以为是足浴盆的振动功能引起的，没想到关了振动功能，父亲还是感觉到脚底麻麻的。
mt: At first, Mr. Li thought it was caused by the vibration function of the foot bath, but he did not expect to turn off the vibration function, and his father still felt numb on the soles of his feet.

src: 李先生用电笔一试，电笔居然亮了，李先生惊讶地发现足浴盆的水里居然带电。

src: 后来他联络了商家，商家的态度还不错，尽管退掉了足浴盆，李先生依然感到不快。

mt: The microfluidic chips of ordinary substrates pass the pure water test at 500mbar (100um channel depth) or 300mbar (50um channel depth) injection pressure before delivery.

src: 玻璃基底的芯片在发货前均在800mbar（100um沟道）进样压力下通过纯水测试，您在使用玻璃基底芯片过程中请注意不要与尖锐物体碰撞，否则会损坏基底。

src: 普通基底的微流控微芯片在注射泵使用纯水进样的条件下，我们给您的建议流速设置在150ul/min以下，油相流速建议设置在50ul/min以下。

src: 一开始是朋友介绍的因为信任，所以选择来看一下起初我的预算是7万做个基本装修。
mt: At the beginning, it was introduced by a friend because of trust, so I chose to take a look at the initial budget of 70,000 to do a basic decoration.
ref: I trusted it because my friend made the recommendation, so I chose to check it out, and originally my budget for a basic decoration was 70,000.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。
mt: Come to the store and start a series of tricks.
ref: A series of scam began as soon as I came into the store.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: This is the first time I went to the store just showed them my hut map, they didn't go to the field to measure the house, they could actually give me a quote saying that my house of 135 and 70,000 can be handled, and I probably showed them their materials and I didn't know what brand they were.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second trick is that as soon as you get to the store, you will drag you to pay the deposit (and once you pay the money, you will never be able to return it unless you have enough experience to fight a theoretical battle with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: When I hesitate to pay the deposit, they will invite their so-called manager to tell you how much discount we can give you if you pay the deposit today.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。
mt: This is a big pit, and I am a living example of being cheated. When I was impulsive, I paid a deposit of more than 10,000 yuan.
ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: The offer he gave me had a lot of problems 70,000 does not include water and electricity renovation, does not include any doors and cabinets bathroom, and these three are the bulk of the cost of the basic installation.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。
mt: Apart from these, their service point fees are also higher than those of other companies.
ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

src: 我对这个公司失去了信任，一开始什么都没有讲清楚就让我签合同。

ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

ref: They just shrunk their responsibility in any way possible, and there were a lot more details that I don’t want to mention now; all in all, do not choose them because my friend had them renovate her apartment, and the quality was poor and they would charge you all kinds of other costs in the later stage.

src: 这个电梯也是很无语，跟有那大病一样，负二到负一，来回折腾，不停我按的这一层，从安全通道下去到一楼，也是很无语，直接通到一个家具店，家具店关门，安全通道出不去!
mt: This elevator is also very speechless, just like the serious illness, negative two to negative one, toss back and forth, I keep pressing this floor, from the safe passage down to the first floor, it is also very speechless, directly to a furniture store, the furniture store is closed, the safe passage can not get out!
ref: This elevator really makes people speechless; it went back and forth from B2 to B1 and did not stop on my floor, and it was ridiculous that when I went to the 1st floor from fire escape, it led to a furniture store which was closed, so I couldn’t get out from the fire escape, either!

src: 居然之家还是需要提升，有很多地方都没有开发。

src: 环境：说实话店里面积大，有8～9层，家里想买的家具、家用电器、各种小东西……，都能买到，好多名牌商家都入驻在店里，慕思、欧派、华帝、老板、峰创之家、汉斯顿、雅克、友邦、丝涟、富品居、万家乐、大自然、中联、美的、雅丹……，品牌真的是太多了，我只能记得这么多了，是购买产品的好去处，逛累了可以坐在沙发上休息休息哦。
mt: Environment: To tell the truth, the store has a large area, 8 to 9 floors, furniture, household appliances, all kinds of small things that you want to buy at home..., you can buy, many famous brands are located in the store, Mousse, Oupai, Vantage, Boss, Fengchuang Home, Hunston, Jacques, AIA, Silian, Fu Pin Ju, Wanjia Le, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan..., the brand is really too many, I can only remember so much, it is a good place to buy products, I can sit on the sofa and rest when I am tired.
ref: Environment: Honestly, the store is large with 8-9 floors, where you can buy all the furniture, household appliances and small things your home needs, and many famous brands have settled in the store, such as DeRUCCI, OPPEIN, VATTI, Robam, Fengchuang Home, Hunsdon, Yake, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, GUANGDONG MACRO, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, and so many other brands, I can only remember so many; it is a good place to buy products, and you can sit on the couch and have a rest if you get tired.

src: 最近想买一套舒适的沙发，朋友说这里有好多沙发可以选，看了顾家家居、美克美家的，感觉还可以，就是价格略贵，所以还在纠结中

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that I find very meaningful - First Aid Certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skills that I feel is important in addition to my driver's license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: To popularize: first aid measures are actually to do emergency rescue when an emergency occurs, i.e. resuscitation before the ambulance comes.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is actually a period of time during the process of the ambulance coming after the accident, and it is this time that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is the time when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I really have a heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage, respiratory arrest, then we only have a window of four minutes to live, the golden four minutes!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: That's why it's so important to have people around you who know first aid!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us collapses, we can use our professional knowledge to resuscitate him, instead of standing there stupidly motionless and unable to do anything, this helpless feeling is too frightening.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: "In China, we have official data of three million accidental deaths each year, the most dangerous called cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States nationwide is an average of 15 percent can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In casino hotels in Las Vegas, seventy to eighty percent can be saved, and less than one percent in Shanghai and Beijing."
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: That's according to Lu Le, founder of First Response.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has a cardiac arrest, breathing is gone, the heartbeat is gone, you pinch the person is of no use.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: You have to do artificial respiration and chest compressions to save the person.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I found that few of us would have the awareness to learn first aid, but when something happens it's too late, so I urge everyone to learn this skill, so that we can react in time when faced with an emergency situation.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: It may even save a life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: First aid certificate can be registered in your local Red Cross training center, I was registered in the Red Cross training center in Zhuhai, students still have a discount it.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！

mt: Sensory good, good color reproduction, quality can!

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories and five grades: Virgin Olive Oil and Refined Olive Oil (Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil).
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin Olive Oil or Natural Olive Oil is the oil obtained directly from the fresh olive fruit by mechanical cold pressing and filtering to remove foreign substances.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: It can be divided into three grades according to the acidity.
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra Virgin: it is the highest grade, the highest quality olive oil and is a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: It has an excellent taste, a light and pleasant vegetal aroma and an acidity of not more than 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: Fine Virgin: slightly higher acidity, but not more than 2%, with a pure and aromatic taste.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary Virgin: fair taste and flavor, with an acidity of not more than 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil is the olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with acidity over 3.3%, or "secondary oil".
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two grades.
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Olive Oil: Refined olive oil is mixed with a certain percentage of virgin olive oil to harmonize the flavor and color, with an acidity of 1.5% or less and a transparent light golden color.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined Olive Impurity Oil or Olive-Pomace Oil (Refined Olive-Pomace Oil): is the olive oil extracted from the pomace by the dissolution method and refined.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have read the classification of grades, you should have noticed that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You should know that olives are like grapes for wine making, olives from different production areas and different varieties of olives will produce different standards of olive oil.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: The best places to grow olive oil.
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable soil and climatic conditions in terms of temperature, sunlight, air humidity and precipitation for the growth of olive oil.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Except for the Mediterranean coast, it can only be grown sporadically in the suitable areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main producing areas of origin (Mediterranean).
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc. Similar climates are found in Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc. in the southern latitudes.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Months of harvesting olive.
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: From March to June, the oil olive trees flower and bear fruit. From July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, transitioning from green to red, purple and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: From November to February is the harvesting season (the freshness of olive oil is very important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: Nutritional composition of olive oil.
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid and linoleic and linolenic acids, as well as vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered to be the most suitable oil for human nutrition among the fats found so far.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.

src: 小编为大家带来洁面乳霜哪款好？
mt: I bring you which is the best cleansing cream?
ref: Which cleaning cream shall I bring for you?

src: 洁面乳霜怎么样好用吗？

src: 其实对于身体微胖的女孩子穿衣搭配的讲究很多。
mt: In fact, there are a lot of instructions for girls with a slight body fat to wear with their clothes.
ref: Actually, there are many tricks for slightly overweight girls to match their clothes.

src: 身体胖的女孩穿的裙子不能太短或太长，长度差不多在膝盖，刚好能盖住大腿胖的地方即可。
mt: Body fat girls wear skirts can not be too short or too long, the length of almost in the knee, just enough to cover the fat thighs.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall wear skirts not too long or too short; they shall be of the length at around the knees, just covering the fat part of the thighs.

src: 裙子过短就会把腿上的肥胖显露出来。
mt: The skirt is too short will show the fat on the legs.
ref: The fat thighs will be shown if the skirt is too short.

src: 过长就会给人矮而胖的感觉。
mt: Too long will give people a short and fat feeling.
ref: Skirts that are too long will make you look short and fat.

src: 如果穿出分出上中下三段来，就显得你自然增高了，就是上身、裙和长筒袜用不同的颜色，看上去就会产生一种修长的感觉 。
mt: If you wear a division out of the upper middle and lower three sections to look like you are naturally taller, is the upper body, skirt and stockings with different colors, looks like it will produce a slender feeling .
ref: If you are dressed in three sections, upper, middle and lower, you will naturally look taller; that is, use different colors for upper body, skirt and stockings, and you will look taller and slimmer.

src: 其实很多深色系的衣服是微胖女孩子们的标配（这一点作者深有体会），深颜色也是掩盖你身体胖的好方法，高贵典雅的黑色短裙也是微胖女孩的首选。
mt: In fact, many dark-colored clothes are the standard for slightly fat girls (which the author knows well), dark colors are also a good way to cover your body fat, noble and elegant black skirt is also the first choice for slightly fat girls.
ref: In fact, a lot of darker color clothes are what slightly overweight girls all have, which the author deeply agrees; dark colors are good methods to cover fatness of your bodies; in addition, noble and elegant black short shirts are best choices for slightly overweight girls.

src: 穿上深颜色的衣服，特别是黑色的短裙，会让人觉得你瘦一些。
mt: Wearing dark-colored clothes, especially black short skirts, will make people think you are thin some.
ref: You will look slimmer in dark clothes, especially black short skirts.

src: 如果小腿很胖，你的袜子和鞋不要穿得太让人注意。
mt: If your calves are fat, your socks and shoes should not be worn too much for people to notice.
ref: Wear stockings and low-key shoes if your calves are fat.

src: 越大众化越好，颜色也不要太鲜艳了。
mt: The more popular the better, and the colors should not be too bright.
ref: The more common the better; the color shouldn’t be too bright.

src: 以免人们对你的腿部和脚部注意时，让人得到肥胖的感觉。
mt: So as not to let people get the feeling of obesity when people pay attention to your legs and feet.
ref: In case people will notice your legs and feet and think you’re fat.

src: 对于微微稍胖的女孩子一定要讲就好穿衣搭配的诀窍。
mt: For slightly fat girls must speak on the knack of dressing well with.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall master the tricks for clothing matching.

src: 微胖女孩千万不要穿紧身的短裙，另外上衣不要过短或者塞在裙子里，会让人看了很不舒服，如果腿粗的话，要穿黑色的长筒袜或者网格袜(细格子的那种哦)，选择质地柔软的印花喇叭裙，搭配一件荡领的上衣，可以很好的掩盖胖女孩的不足。
mt: Slightly fat girls should never wear tight short skirts, in addition to tops not too short or stuffed in the skirt, will make people look very uncomfortable, if the legs are thick, to wear black stockings or grid socks (fine plaid kind oh), choose a soft texture of the print flare skirt, with a swing collar top, can be a good cover up the fat girl's shortcomings.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall never wear close-fitting short skirts and the upper outer garment shall not be too short or tucked inside the skirt, which seem strange; slightly overweight girls with thicker legs shall wear black stockings or mesh stockings (thin meshes), a flare skirt with print pattern and soft texture, and a loose-collar upper outer garment to cover the defects of the body.

src: 当然了，微胖的女孩儿在穿短裙上也是有讲究的。
mt: Of course, the slightly fat girl in wearing a short skirt is also delicate.
ref: Of course, there are some skills for slightly overweight girls to wear short skirts.

src: 胖女孩穿短裙，应该选择与短裙的颜色一致的上衣，这样会使你胖胖的身材有增加高度的效果。
mt: Fat girls wearing short skirts should choose a top that is the same color as the short skirt, which will give your chubby body the effect of adding height.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法是什么？

ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。
mt: Everyone has different hobbies, some people like to collect, some people like food, of course, some people like to taste wine, Red Label Whisky is currently one of the best-selling Scotch whisky in various countries, and Red Label Whisky has won the gold medal in the International Foreign Wine Competition.
ref: Different people have different preferences; some like to collect, some like food, and certainly some like wine tasting; Johnnie Walker Red Label is one of the fastest selling Scottish whiskies in the world and has won the gold prize of International Wine Competition.

src: 每一瓶红牌威士忌都有独特的味道，不过如果不知道如何品味它，岂不是糟蹋了它的醇香。
mt: Each bottle of Red Label Whisky has a unique flavor, but if you do not know how to taste it, it is not a waste of its mellow flavor.
ref: Each bottle of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky has its own unique flavor, but if you don’t know how to taste it, it would be such a waste of its mellow fragrance.

src: 那么红牌威士忌怎么喝呢？
mt: So how to drink red whiskey?
ref: Then how do we drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 小编为大家简单介绍下。
mt: I briefly introduce for you.
ref: I’ll introduce for you now.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法：
mt: Red Label whisky drinking method.
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky:

src: 尊尼获加红牌威士忌由约35种苏格兰威士忌调配而成，具有浓郁芳香及传统苏格兰威士忌的特质，浓郁芳香中带有甘甜及烟熏香味。
mt: Johnnie Walker Red Label Whisky is blended from about 35 kinds of Scotch whisky, has a rich aroma and traditional Scotch whisky characteristics, rich aroma with sweet and smoky flavor.
ref: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended with around 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, possesses rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

src: 入口浓醇清新，略带香草及浓烈的烟熏麦芽味道。
mt: In the mouth, it is rich and fresh, with a slight vanilla and strong smoky malt flavor.
ref: It is mellow and fresh in the mouth, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.

src: 该酒可以直接加冰饮用，或者与最喜爱的饮品混合饮用。
mt: The spirit can be served directly on the rocks or mixed with your favorite beverage.
ref: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: Red Label whisky into the country, in order to adapt to the taste of the Chinese, Red Label whisky + Coke or Sprite or Sunkist and other fizzy drinks become an enduring fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: These sweet drinks, in addition to neutralizing the sour taste, visually can bring pleasure to people, adding drinks, play a diluted taste of alcohol to change the effect of taste.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Red Label Whiskey + lemon slices + sugar (sugar can also be), is the most authentic, the most traditional way to drink.

src: 一开始是朋友介绍的因为信任，所以选择来看一下起初我的预算是7万做个基本装修。

ref: I trusted it because my friend made the recommendation, so I chose to check it out, and originally my budget for a basic decoration was 70,000.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。
mt: When I came to the store, I started a series of deception.
ref: A series of scam began as soon as I came into the store.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: I was the first time to the store just to show them my floor plan, they did not go to the field to measure the house, they can actually give me a quote that my 135 house 70,000 can be done, probably showed me their materials and do not know what brand of materials they are.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second scam is that you will be dragged to pay the deposit as soon as you arrive at the store (and once the money is paid you can never get it back, unless you have enough experience to fight a theoretical battle with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: I hesitate to pay the deposit, they will invite their so-called manager to tell you, you just pay the deposit today we can give you how much discount.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。
mt: This is a big hole, I am a living example of being cheated, in the impulse of the mind, paid a deposit of more than 10,000.
ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: He gave me a quote with a lot of questions 70,000 does not include plumbing and electrical remodeling, does not include any doors and cabinets bathrooms, and these three are the bulk of the cost of the base installation.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。
mt: In addition to these their service point fees were higher than other companies.
ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

ref: When I went to ask for a refund, they acted rather experienced and sent a small team to deal with me.

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that I find very meaningful – a first aid certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skills certificates that I feel are important in addition to my driver's license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Popularize it: first aid measures are actually emergency rescue in the event of an emergency, that is, rescue before the ambulance comes.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is actually a period of time in the process of ambulance coming after the accident, and it is this time that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I do have a heart attack, a cerebral hemorrhage, a respiratory arrest, then the window of our life is only four minutes, four minutes of gold!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So the people around you understand how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls, we can rescue him through professional knowledge, rather than standing there stupidly and doing nothing, this feeling of helplessness is too frightening.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: "In China, our official data counts three million accidental deaths each year, the most dangerous of which is called cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, an average of 15% can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In las Vegas casino hotels, 70% or 80% can be saved, shanghai, Beijing less than 1%. ”
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, the founder of First Reaction, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has a cardiac arrest, the breathing is gone, the heartbeat is gone, there is no effect on you pinching the person.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: Artificial respiration and chest compressions must be done to save people.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I find that few of us have this awareness to learn first aid now, but it is too late when things happen, so I still call on everyone to learn this skill so that we can respond in time when facing unexpected situations.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: Maybe it can save a person's life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: First aid certificates can be registered at your local Red Cross training center, I registered at the Red Cross training center in Zhuhai, and there are discounts for students.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。

ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: drainage, water storage facilities of various types of inspection wells, rainwater inlets, square ditches, septic tanks and small structures, bridge wing walls, etc.
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper and lower left and right sides of the module are surrounded by concave and convex groove structures, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shear resistance of the well wall wall is far superior to the masonry form of flat friction masonry.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure, after the combination of masonry, the longitudinal holes are connected, the transverse holes are connected, and the hole core is poured to form a cast-in-place concrete mesh structure, which plays a role in secondary reinforcement and waterproofing.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The module is equipped with rib grooves in both vertical and horizontal lines, and the horizontal ribs and longitudinal ribs correspondingly improve the overall strength of the structure.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, the use of concrete inspection well module masonry out of the inspection well, drainage well is not easy to collapse, sink, leakage and other phenomena, the well wall wall module mechanical properties are stable, simple operation, forming size standards.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two broad categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Refined Olive Oil, with five levels.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is an oil obtained directly from fresh olive fruit by mechanical cold pressing, filtering and other treatments to remove foreign matter.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: According to the different acidity, it can be divided into three levels:
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra Virgin: The highest grade and highest quality olive oil, it is a natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: The taste is excellent, with a light and pleasant plant aroma, and the acidity does not exceed 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: Fine Virgin: Slightly more acidic, but not more than 2%, with a pure, aromatic taste.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary Virgin: The taste and flavor are acceptable, and the acidity does not exceed 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil obtained after refining virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or becomes a "secondary oil".
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two levels:
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Ordinary Olive Oil: Refined olive oil is mixed with a certain proportion of virgin olive oil to reconcile taste and color, and its acidity is below 1.5%, and it is a transparent pale golden yellow.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil: Olive oil obtained by dissolving and refining the oil residue.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have seen the classification of grades, you should have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You know, olive fruit is like a grape that makes wine, olive fruit from different appellations, different olive fruit varieties, will produce different standards of olive oil.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: Best places to grow olive oil:
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable climatic conditions such as soil and temperature, sunshine, air humidity and precipitation required for olive oil growth.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Except for the Mediterranean coast, other areas can only be cultivated sporadically in suitable areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main regions of origin (Mediterranean):
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and its climate is similar to argentina, Peru, South Africa and so on in the southern latitudes.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Olive harvest months:
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: From March to June of each year, it is the time for the olive tree to flower and set fruit, and from July to October the fruit begins to develop and mature, and the fruit transitions from green to red, purple and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: From November to February, the fruit is picked (the freshness of olive oil is very important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: Nutritional facts of olive oil:
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid and linoleic acid, linolenic acid, as well as vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered to be the most suitable oil for human nutrition among the oils and fats found so far.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.

src: 其实对于身体微胖的女孩子穿衣搭配的讲究很多。
mt: In fact, for girls with slightly fat bodies, there is a lot of attention to dressing.
ref: Actually, there are many tricks for slightly overweight girls to match their clothes.

src: 身体胖的女孩穿的裙子不能太短或太长，长度差不多在膝盖，刚好能盖住大腿胖的地方即可。
mt: Fat girls wear skirts that are not too short or too long, and are almost knee-length, just enough to cover the fat thighs.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall wear skirts not too long or too short; they shall be of the length at around the knees, just covering the fat part of the thighs.

src: 裙子过短就会把腿上的肥胖显露出来。
mt: Skirts that are too short will reveal the fat on the legs.
ref: The fat thighs will be shown if the skirt is too short.

src: 过长就会给人矮而胖的感觉。
mt: Too long will give people a feeling of short and fat.
ref: Skirts that are too long will make you look short and fat.

src: 如果穿出分出上中下三段来，就显得你自然增高了，就是上身、裙和长筒袜用不同的颜色，看上去就会产生一种修长的感觉 。
mt: If you wear out the upper, middle and lower three paragraphs, it will appear that you naturally increase your height, that is, the upper body, skirt and stockings use different colors, which will look like a slender feeling.
ref: If you are dressed in three sections, upper, middle and lower, you will naturally look taller; that is, use different colors for upper body, skirt and stockings, and you will look taller and slimmer.

src: 其实很多深色系的衣服是微胖女孩子们的标配（这一点作者深有体会），深颜色也是掩盖你身体胖的好方法，高贵典雅的黑色短裙也是微胖女孩的首选。
mt: In fact, many dark colored clothes are the standard for slightly fat girls (this point the author has a deep understanding), dark colors are also a good way to cover up your body fat, noble and elegant black short skirts are also the first choice for slightly fat girls.
ref: In fact, a lot of darker color clothes are what slightly overweight girls all have, which the author deeply agrees; dark colors are good methods to cover fatness of your bodies; in addition, noble and elegant black short shirts are best choices for slightly overweight girls.

src: 穿上深颜色的衣服，特别是黑色的短裙，会让人觉得你瘦一些。
mt: Wearing dark-colored clothes, especially short black skirts, will make people think that you are thinner.
ref: You will look slimmer in dark clothes, especially black short skirts.

src: 如果小腿很胖，你的袜子和鞋不要穿得太让人注意。
mt: If your calves are fat, don't wear your socks and shoes too noticeably.
ref: Wear stockings and low-key shoes if your calves are fat.

src: 越大众化越好，颜色也不要太鲜艳了。
mt: The more popular the better, and the colors should not be too bright.
ref: The more common the better; the color shouldn’t be too bright.

src: 以免人们对你的腿部和脚部注意时，让人得到肥胖的感觉。
mt: Lest people pay attention to your legs and feet, people will feel fat.
ref: In case people will notice your legs and feet and think you’re fat.

src: 对于微微稍胖的女孩子一定要讲就好穿衣搭配的诀窍。
mt: For girls who are slightly fat, they must talk about the tricks of good dressing.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall master the tricks for clothing matching.

src: 微胖女孩千万不要穿紧身的短裙，另外上衣不要过短或者塞在裙子里，会让人看了很不舒服，如果腿粗的话，要穿黑色的长筒袜或者网格袜(细格子的那种哦)，选择质地柔软的印花喇叭裙，搭配一件荡领的上衣，可以很好的掩盖胖女孩的不足。
mt: Slightly fat girls must not wear tight short skirts, in addition, the top should not be too short or tucked in the skirt, it will make people look very uncomfortable, if the legs are thick, you must wear black stockings or grid socks (fine plaid kind of Oh), choose a soft texture printed flared skirt, with a collared top, can cover up the fat girl's deficiencies very well.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall never wear close-fitting short skirts and the upper outer garment shall not be too short or tucked inside the skirt, which seem strange; slightly overweight girls with thicker legs shall wear black stockings or mesh stockings (thin meshes), a flare skirt with print pattern and soft texture, and a loose-collar upper outer garment to cover the defects of the body.

src: 当然了，微胖的女孩儿在穿短裙上也是有讲究的。

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。

src: 随着人们保健意识的增强，足浴盆越来越受到消费者的喜爱，在市场上也涌现出一大批档次不同的产品，从一百多元到上千元的足浴盆琳琅满目，给了消费者很大的选择空间。

ref: According to related statistics, compared with traditional home appliances, the sales of healthcare products such as feet bath basin was hot, but there is no specialized industry standard for feet bath basin and so there is potential safety risk.

src: “在带电的水里泡脚，实在太危险了吧!”

src: 李先生告诉记者，近日，他买了一个足浴盆送给父亲做生日礼物，可是父亲泡脚时却感觉脚底发麻。
mt: Mr. Li told reporters that recently, he bought a foot bath for his father to make a birthday gift, but his father felt numbness in the soles of his feet when he soaked his feet.
ref: Mr. Li told reporter that he recently bought a feet bath basin for his father as a birthday present, but his father felt that the bottom of his feet were numb when using it.

src: 李先生一开始以为是足浴盆的振动功能引起的，没想到关了振动功能，父亲还是感觉到脚底麻麻的。
mt: At first, Mr. Li thought that it was caused by the vibration function of the foot bath, but he did not expect that the vibration function was turned off, and his father still felt numbness in the soles of his feet.
ref: Mr. Li first thought it was caused by the vibration function of the feet bath basin, and it was unexpected that his father still felt his feet were numb after turning off the vibration function.

src: 李先生用电笔一试，电笔居然亮了，李先生惊讶地发现足浴盆的水里居然带电。
mt: Mr. Li tried with an electric pen, the pen actually lit up, and Mr. Li was surprised to find that the water in the foot bath was actually charged.
ref: Mr. Li used a tester and the light on it was on; it was to Mr. Li’s surprise that the water in the feet bath basin was electrified.

src: 后来他联络了商家，商家的态度还不错，尽管退掉了足浴盆，李先生依然感到不快。
mt: Later, he contacted the merchant, and the merchant's attitude was not bad, and although he returned the foot bath, Mr. Li still felt unhappy.
ref: Then he contacted the seller, whose attitude was nice, but Mr. Li still felt upset although he had returned it.

src: 因为他发现这个已经流行已久的足浴盆如今在最高温度的设定、适用于何种人群、何种材料保证无害等方面都没有一个明确详细的行业规定。
mt: Because he found that this foot bath, which has been popular for a long time, now has no clear and detailed industry regulations in terms of the setting of the maximum temperature, what kind of people are suitable, and what kind of materials are guaranteed to be harmless.
ref: Because he found that feet bath basin, which has been popular for a long time, still has no explicit and detailed industry regulations on the setting of the maximum temperature, suitable crowd, what materials are safe to use, etc.

src: 但是一般情况下足浴盆是不会有带电问题的，但也不排除少数产品在出厂时没有严格把关。

ref: But normally feet bath basin shouldn’t be electrified, however we can’t rule out the fact that a few products might not have been strictly checked before leaving the factory.

src: 因此在在购买的时候选择分体式的足浴盆。

src: 一开始是朋友介绍的因为信任，所以选择来看一下起初我的预算是7万做个基本装修。
mt: At first, it was introduced by a friend because of trust, so I chose to take a look at it At first, my budget was 70,000 to do a basic renovation.
ref: I trusted it because my friend made the recommendation, so I chose to check it out, and originally my budget for a basic decoration was 70,000.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。
mt: When you come to the store, you start a series of tricks.
ref: A series of scam began as soon as I came into the store.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: I was the first time to the store just showed them my floor plan, they did not go to the field to measure the house, they can actually give me an offer to say that my 135 house 70,000 can be done, probably show me their materials and do not know what brand of materials they are.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second trick is that you will drag you to pay the deposit as soon as you arrive at the store (and once you pay the money, you will never be able to return it, unless you have enough experience to fight with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: When I hesitate to pay the deposit, they will invite their so-called manager to tell you how much of a discount we can give you as long as you pay the deposit today.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。
mt: This is a big pit, I am a living example of being deceived, when the mind is impulsive, paid more than 10,000 deposits.
ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: The offer he gave me had a lot of problems 70,000 excluding hydroelectric retrofits, not including any doors and cabinets in the bathroom, and these three were the majority of the cost of the base.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。
mt: In addition to these, their point-of-service fees are also higher than those charged by other companies.
ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

src: 我对这个公司失去了信任，一开始什么都没有讲清楚就让我签合同。
mt: I lost trust in the company and asked me to sign the contract without making anything clear at first.
ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

src: 当我去找他们退钱的时候他们表现出很有经验的样子，有专门的小团队来对付你。
mt: When I go to them for a refund, they show a very experienced look, with a dedicated small team to deal with you.
ref: When I went to ask for a refund, they acted rather experienced and sent a small team to deal with me.

src: 无论如何都会一口咬死是客户的问题他们全然无责。
mt: In any case, it is the customer's problem that they are completely irresponsible for.
ref: Anyway, they just said it was the client’s problem and they had absolutely no responsibility for it.

src: 各种推卸责任，还有很多细节，不想一一说了都是泪，总之不要选择他们，因为我朋友找他们装修的房子也是质量不好，后期给你算各种费用。
mt: All kinds of shirking responsibilities, there are many details, do not want to say one by one are tears, in short, do not choose them, because my friends look for them to decorate the house is also of poor quality, the later for you to calculate various costs.
ref: They just shrunk their responsibility in any way possible, and there were a lot more details that I don’t want to mention now; all in all, do not choose them because my friend had them renovate her apartment, and the quality was poor and they would charge you all kinds of other costs in the later stage.

ref: Swindle; they used to be the swindler company Longtou Renovation, then it’s changed to Damei, and now it seems they have closed down and changed into something else.

src: 所以大家别选择这样坑爹的装修公司。

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of important skill certificates except for driving license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Popularization: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., the first aid conducted before the coming of the ambulance.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As everyone knows, there is certain period before the coming of the ambulance after the happening of the accident, which is the critical time for rescue.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This period is the most important time for first aid.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If we suffer from heart disease, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, there are four minutes as the window for our life, the golden four minutes!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So it is very important to know first aid!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, but not doing nothing by only standing there; this helpless feeling really makes people afraid.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as sudden cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: 15% of people of sudden cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the America.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In the Casino hotels in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: Pinching of philtrum takes no effect at all if a person suffers from sudden cardiac arrest, with no breath or heartbeat.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: In my opinion, very few people have this awareness to study first aid knowledge, which is very important once accident happens; therefore, we should learn this skill, so that we can give timely reaction when facing with emergency situations.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！

src: 检查井混凝土模块生产加工设备 郑州井壁砖模块设备介绍：
mt: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, Introduction to shaft wall brick module equipment of Zhengzhou:
ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, introduction to Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment:

src: 郑州宜欣是国内混凝土检查井模块砖机设备，检查井砌块机械，井壁墙体模块机械专业的生产厂家，从半自动到全自动化生产线。
mt: Zhengzhou Yixin is a specialized manufacturer of concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, inspection shaft building block machinery, shaft wall module equipment, with semi-automatic and automatic production lines.
ref: Zhengzhou Yixin is a specialized manufacturer of concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, inspection shaft building block machinery and shaft wall module equipment, with semi-automatic and automatic production lines.

src: 通过多年的实践和开发，现具备了质量过硬，主要生产液压式、移动式、全自动化检查井系列设备及配套装置。
mt: Based on practice and development of many years, it is engaged in production of hydraulic type, mobile type and automatic inspection shaft series of equipment and supporting devices with high quality.
ref: Based on practice and development of many years, it is engaged in production of high quality hydraulic type, mobile type and automatic inspection shaft series of equipment and supporting devices.

src: 检查井混凝土模块生产加工设备 郑州井壁砖模块设备组装现场：
mt: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the assembly field for shaft wall brick module equipment of Zhengzhou”
ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the assembly site for Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment

src: 检查井混凝土模块生产加工设备 郑州井壁砖模块设备的特点及优势:
mt: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the characteristics and advantages of the shaft wall brick module equipment of Zhengzhou”
ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the characteristics and advantages of Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment

src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。
mt: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied to new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.
ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities,
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of building inspection shafts by using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is much better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, there is no phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备智能控制配备数据输入、输出装置一键通触摸式液晶显示监控机械操作全部过程，实现理想的人机对话、自动分析比料、密度运转、安全逻辑控制及故障诊断系统。
mt: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation, to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械液压系统采用单缸液压、输送，双缸液压、输送。
mt: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.
ref: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.

src: 独立的液压集成站，避免了由于主机振动对液压系统的影响，从而保证液压系统工作的可靠性。
mt: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized, to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master, so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.
ref: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备布料箱行进模箱脱模上升，储料箱门关闭，自动输送托板，全部由液压系统独立完成，从而达到减少机械的磨损和维修。
mt: In the concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, the fabric box proceeding box demolds and lifts, and the storage box door closes, and the  supporting plate is transported automatically, all which are independently completed by the hydraulic system, so as to reduce mechanical abrasion and repair.
ref: In the concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, the fabric box proceeding box de-molds and lifts, the storage box door closes, and the supporting plate is transported automatically, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system so as to reduce mechanical abrasion and times of repair.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备采用进口电脑、电器，密封件液压件，准保设备综合性能稳定可靠。
mt: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment is composed by imported computer and appliances, as well as sealing elements and hydraulic element, to ensure stable and reliable comprehensive performance.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment is composed by imported computer and appliances, as well as sealing elements and hydraulic element to ensure stable and reliable comprehensive performance.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振平台采用整体板钢，台面线切割合模无焊接点，使填料箱自由摆动导向，充分减少机械磨损。
mt: The integral steel plate is adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical vibration platform, with no welding points, so that the stuffing box can swing and orient freely, to greatly reduce mechanical abrasion.
ref: The integral steel plate is adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical vibration platform, with no welding points of wire-electrode cutting mold closing of mesa, so that the stuffing box can swing and orient freely to greatly reduce mechanical abrasion.

src: 使模具负荷减少、填料并二合一加密振幅，采用一体化、全同步，台振、模振，确保达到振实效果。
mt: It reduces loads of moulds and reinforces vibration; integrated and full synchronization is adopted for vibration of the platform and the moulds, to ensure the vibration effect.
ref: It reduces loads of molds and reinforces vibration; integrated and full synchronization are adopted for vibration of the platform and the molds to ensure the vibration effect.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振机械、电脑自动控制振幅根据原料性价比调节振幅，无磨损制动，从而延长使用寿命，降低成本。
mt: The shaft wall module mechanical exciting machinery and the computer automatically control the vibration range according to the cost performance of raw materials, leading to no abrasion brake; in this way, it extends the service life and reduces the cost.

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: Olive oil is divided into five levels of two categories, i.e., the virgin olive oil and the lampante olive oil or refined olive oil, by International Olive OIl Council.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil is also known as the natural olive oil, which is the grease acquired by cold pressing from fresh olive fruits and removing of foreign things by means of filtration.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: Virgin olive oil can be divided into three levels according to acidity:
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra virgin: is the olive oil of the highest level and the best quality, a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: With excellent taste and elegant and pleasant plant flavor, it has the acidity of no more than 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: Fine virgin: with a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, it has pure and aromatic taste.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary virgin: with acceptable taste and flavor, it has the acidity of no more than 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil acquired from the refined virgin olive oil with acidity of more than 3.3%, and is also known as the “secondary oil”.
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two levels:
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Olive Oil: the refined olive oil and the virgin olive oil with certain proportion are mixed, to blend taste and color, with the acidity less than 1.5%, showing transparent light golden color.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil: it is the olive oil acquired by refining the oil extracted from oil residues with the dissolution method.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: After reading the classification by levels, you may find that acidity is a very important index.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: We know that olive fruits are just like the grapes used for brewing wine, and olive fruits of different types from different producing areas will produce olive oil of different standards.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: The best growing areas for olives:
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the best climatic conditions needed for growing of olives such as soil, temperature, sunlight, air humidity and precipitation.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: The major production areas (the Mediterranean):
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude with similar climatic conditions.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Picking time of olives:
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit; July to October each year is the time for olive fruits to grow and mature, and the fruits change from green, red, purple and then dark.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: November to February of the next year is the picking season of the fruits (the freshness of olives is especially important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: Nutritional ingredients of olive oil:
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, i.e., oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is regarded as the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.
