src: 其实对于身体微胖的女孩子穿衣搭配的讲究很多。
mt: In fact, there are many rules of clothing matching for slightly fat girls.
ref: Actually, there are many tricks for slightly overweight girls to match their clothes.

src: 身体胖的女孩穿的裙子不能太短或太长，长度差不多在膝盖，刚好能盖住大腿胖的地方即可。
mt: Slightly fat girls shall wear skirts not too long or too short; they shall be of the length at around the knee, just covering the fat part of thighs.
ref: Slightly overweight girls shall wear skirts not too long or too short; they shall be of the length at around the knees, just covering the fat part of the thighs.

src: 裙子过短就会把腿上的肥胖显露出来。
mt: The fat thighs will be shown with much too short skirts.
ref: The fat thighs will be shown if the skirt is too short.

src: 过长就会给人矮而胖的感觉。
mt: Very long shirts give a feeling of short and fat.
ref: Skirts that are too long will make you look short and fat.

src: 如果穿出分出上中下三段来，就显得你自然增高了，就是上身、裙和长筒袜用不同的颜色，看上去就会产生一种修长的感觉 。
mt: Girls dressed with three parts, i.e., upper outer garment, skirt and stockings, give a feeling of slim.
ref: If you are dressed in three sections, upper, middle and lower, you will naturally look taller; that is, use different colors for upper body, skirt and stockings, and you will look taller and slimmer.

src: 其实很多深色系的衣服是微胖女孩子们的标配（这一点作者深有体会），深颜色也是掩盖你身体胖的好方法，高贵典雅的黑色短裙也是微胖女孩的首选。
mt: In fact, lots of dark color clothes are standard configuration of slightly fat girls (which the author deeply agrees on), and dark colors are good methods to cover fatness; in addition, noble and elegant black short shirts are best choices for slightly fat girls.
ref: In fact, a lot of darker color clothes are what slightly overweight girls all have, which the author deeply agrees; dark colors are good methods to cover fatness of your bodies; in addition, noble and elegant black short shirts are best choices for slightly overweight girls.

src: 穿上深颜色的衣服，特别是黑色的短裙，会让人觉得你瘦一些。
mt: You seem slimmer with dark clothes, especially black short skirts.
ref: You will look slimmer in dark clothes, especially black short skirts.

src: 如果小腿很胖，你的袜子和鞋不要穿得太让人注意。
mt: Wear stockings and shoes under the notice if your calves are fat.
ref: Wear stockings and low-key shoes if your calves are fat.

src: 越大众化越好，颜色也不要太鲜艳了。
mt: In a commonly seen and not bright-colored style.
ref: The more common the better; the color shouldn’t be too bright.

src: 以免人们对你的腿部和脚部注意时，让人得到肥胖的感觉。
mt: So that people will not fee you fat when they notice your legs and feet.
ref: In case people will notice your legs and feet and think you’re fat.

src: 对于微微稍胖的女孩子一定要讲就好穿衣搭配的诀窍。

mt: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is mixed with about 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, with rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

mt: The wine can be drunk directly with ice, or can be mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble drinks such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: These sweet drinks can not only neutralize the sour taste but also bring joys in visual sense; the addition of drinks can dilute the taste of wine and change the flavor.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.
ref: Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.

src: 正宗的红方威味道有些酸涩,加入糖可以中和其中的酸味,柠檬则会给酒带来清新的香味,当然,甜酸度可根据个人的口味爱好调配。
mt: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour and acrid, and the addition of sugar can neutralize the sour taste, and lemon can bring fresh taste to the wine; of course, the sweet and sour degree can be adjusted as per personal taste.
ref: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour; adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, lemon will bring fresh fragrance to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and sourness can be adjusted according to personal tastes.

src: 以上三种都是红牌威士忌的最好喝法，大家可以作为参考尝试下，希望小编的介绍可以帮助到大家。
mt: The above three are the best method for drinking of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky, which can be taken as references; I wish that my introduction can provide you with some help.
ref: The above are the best drinking methods of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky for your refence, and I hope my introduction can help you.

mt: We had saw some cases that many wedding photography stores tried their best to make customers keep as more photos as possible during choosing photos; however, the staffs there did not show any intention to make up add more photos except for the 24 ones in the package (I heard that many girls who shot wedding dress photos chose additional photos of more than 10 thousand yuan in addition to the package of more than 7 thousand yuan; I was astonished then, and afraid that I would choose too many).
ref: When choosing the photos, I saw many cases online where they wouldn’t let the customers delete too many photos, but they didn’t ask us to add photos at all, just the 24 photos in the set and nothing more (I heard that my cousin who was also taking wedding dress photos added photos worth over 10,000 in addition to the 7,000 yuan set, and I was stunned and feared I might choose too many).

src: 随着人们保健意识的增强，足浴盆越来越受到消费者的喜爱，在市场上也涌现出一大批档次不同的产品，从一百多元到上千元的足浴盆琳琅满目，给了消费者很大的选择空间。

src: 在相关的数据表面，与传统家电相比，足浴盆等保健类家电销售火爆，但足浴盆并没有专门行业标准，因此存在一定的安全隐患。
mt: According to related data, when compared with traditional home appliances, healthcare appliances such as foot tubs are getting increasingly popular; however, there has been no specialized industry standard for foot tubs, with certain security hazards.
ref: According to related statistics, compared with traditional home appliances, the sales of healthcare products such as feet bath basin was hot, but there is no specialized industry standard for feet bath basin and so there is potential safety risk.

src: “在带电的水里泡脚，实在太危险了吧!”
mt: “It’s really dangerous when soaking feet in water with electricity!”
ref: “Having a feet bath in the water with electricity is too dangerous!”

src: 李先生告诉记者，近日，他买了一个足浴盆送给父亲做生日礼物，可是父亲泡脚时却感觉脚底发麻。
mt: Mr. Li told the author that he bought a foot tub for his father as a birthday present recently, but his father felt numb when he soaking his feet in the foot tub.
ref: Mr. Li told reporter that he recently bought a feet bath basin for his father as a birthday present, but his father felt that the bottom of his feet were numb when using it.

src: 李先生一开始以为是足浴盆的振动功能引起的，没想到关了振动功能，父亲还是感觉到脚底麻麻的。
mt: At first, Mr. Li thought it was caused by the vibration function of the foot tub; however, his father still felt numb after turning off the vibration function.
ref: Mr. Li first thought it was caused by the vibration function of the feet bath basin, and it was unexpected that his father still felt his feet were numb after turning off the vibration function.

src: 李先生用电笔一试，电笔居然亮了，李先生惊讶地发现足浴盆的水里居然带电。
mt: Mr. Li checked with an electroprobe, and it lit; he was astonished that the water in the foot tub was charged.
ref: Mr. Li used a tester and the light on it was on; it was to Mr. Li’s surprise that the water in the feet bath basin was electrified.

src: 后来他联络了商家，商家的态度还不错，尽管退掉了足浴盆，李先生依然感到不快。
mt: Then he contacted the merchant, whose attitude was good; the foot tub was returned, but Mr. Li was still unhappy.
ref: Then he contacted the seller, whose attitude was nice, but Mr. Li still felt upset although he had returned it.

src: 因为他发现这个已经流行已久的足浴盆如今在最高温度的设定、适用于何种人群、何种材料保证无害等方面都没有一个明确详细的行业规定。
mt: Because he found that there had been no definite and detailed industry regulation on setting of the maximum temperature, applicable groups and materials adopted to ensure harmless in the foot tub field which had been popular for long.
ref: Because he found that feet bath basin, which has been popular for a long time, still has no explicit and detailed industry regulations on the setting of the maximum temperature, suitable crowd, what materials are safe to use, etc.

src: 但是一般情况下足浴盆是不会有带电问题的，但也不排除少数产品在出厂时没有严格把关。
mt: In general conditions, there was no problem of charged foot tub; however, a few products may not be strictly controlled before leaving factory.
ref: But normally feet bath basin shouldn’t be electrified, however we can’t rule out the fact that a few products might not have been strictly checked before leaving the factory.

src: 因此在在购买的时候选择分体式的足浴盆。
mt: For this reason, split type foot tub is a better choice.
ref: Therefore, choose split type feet bath basin.

src: 水电分离，没有任何安全隐患。
mt: There is no safety risk because of separated water and electricity.
ref: There is no safety risk when water and electricity are separated.

src: 同时你可以随便拿电笔测。
mt: In addition, you can check with an elecroprobe at any time.
ref: Meanwhile, you can use a tester to test it.

src: 羊行屮（chè），本名姜波，生于羊年羊月，羊行草上，适得其所，是为羊行屮，人称“羊叔”。
mt: Yang Xingche, with the real name of Jiang Bo, was born in the month of the sheep and the year of the sheep; the name Yang Xingche means the sheep feel most comfortable when they are on grass; people call him Uncle Yang (Sheep in Chinese).
ref: Yang Xingche, real name Jiang Bo, was born in the month of the sheep in the year of the sheep; the name Yang Xingche means the sheep feel most comfortable when they are on grass; people call him Uncle Yang (Sheep in Chinese).

src: 因出版“异域密码”系列的《泰国异闻录》《印度异闻录》《日本异闻录》《韩国异闻录》等作品，在业内有“悬疑怪才”之称，自称“擅长一本正经地胡说八道”
mt: He is called as a “maverick genius” in the industry because of his “foreign lands password” series of works including Odd Stories in Thailand, Odd Stories in India, Odd Stories in Japan and Odd Stories in South Korea, and he describes himself as “good at telling stuff and nonsense stockily”.
ref: He is called “thriller genius” in the industry due to the publication of his “Foreign Password” series including Strange Stories in Thailand, Strange Stories in India, Strange Stories in Japan and Strange Stories in Korea, and he said that he’s “good at talking serious nonsense”

src: 《灯下黑》，又名《中国异闻录》，“悬疑怪才”羊行屮用全新作品《灯下黑》带你深入领略中国民俗的骨髓，那些流传至今的传说，背后有怎样凄美、动人的爱恨绝唱？

src: 请勿使用手推注射器直接对芯片进行进样，否则容易发生漏液。

src: 普通基底的微流控芯片发货前均在500mbar（100um沟道深度）或300mbar（50um沟道深度）进样压力下通过纯水测试。
mt: The micro-fluid chips of ordinary base have passed the pure water test with the sample injection pressure of 500mbar (100um channel depth) or 300mbar (50um channel depth) before delivery.
ref: The micro-fluid chips with ordinary base have passed the pure water test with the sample injection pressure of 500mbar (100um channel depth) or 300mbar (50um channel depth) before delivery.

src: 玻璃基底的芯片在发货前均在800mbar（100um沟道）进样压力下通过纯水测试，您在使用玻璃基底芯片过程中请注意不要与尖锐物体碰撞，否则会损坏基底。
mt: The micro-fluid chips of glass base have passed the pure water test with the sample injection pressure of 800mbar (100um channel) before delivery; please avoid collision with sharp articles when using glass-base chips, which may lead to damage to the base.
ref: The micro-fluid chips of glass base have passed the pure water test with the sample injection pressure of 800mbar (100um channel) before delivery; please avoid collision with sharp articles when using glass-base chips, which may lead to damage to the base.

src: 使用过程中请结合溶液粘稠度考虑并勿超出此范围，否则会引起漏液。

ref: Please take the viscosity of the solution into consideration during usage and do not exceed the range, or it will lead to liquid leakage.

src: 普通基底的微流控微芯片在注射泵使用纯水进样的条件下，我们给您的建议流速设置在150ul/min以下，油相流速建议设置在50ul/min以下。
mt: In condition of sample injection with pure water for micro-fluid chips of ordinary base, you are recommended to set the flow velocity under 150ul/min and set the flow velocity of oil phase under 50ul/min.
ref: In condition of sample injection with pure water for micro-fluid chips of ordinary base, you are recommended to set the flow velocity as under 150ul/min and set the flow velocity of oil phase as under 50ul/min.

src: 请根据实际进样液体的粘稠度综合考虑，由慢到快增加您的流速参数值。

ref: Please take the viscosity of sample injection liquid into consideration, and increase your parameters of flow velocity from slowly to rapidly.

src: 通用芯片在实验完成后，请及时将内部沟道清洗干净，否则容易造成堵塞。

src: 如果您需要可承受更大压力或者流速的微流控芯片，可联系客服定制。

src: 尊敬的顾客您好！
mt: Hello, dear customers!
ref: Hello, deal customer!

src: 感谢您能够选择支雲餐厅用餐，您吃的开心快乐一直是我们的使命，为您和您的家人提供更可口放心的菜肴，更优质的服务，您的满意跟好评一直是我们前进的动力！
mt: Thank you for choosing Zhi Yun Restaurant to have your dinner, and it’s our mission to make you have a happy dinner here; we work hard to provide you and your family members with delicious and safe dishes and high-quality services, and your satisfaction and good reputation are power to drive us to change better!
ref: Thank you for choosing Zhi Yun Restaurant, and offering you a pleasant meal has been our mission; we are committed to providing you and your family with delicious food, quality service, and your satisfaction and good review will always be our momentum to move forward!

src: 感谢亲的五星好评哦，爱你么么哒！
mt: Thank you for your 5-star review, love and kiss!
ref: Thank you for your 5-star review, lots of love!

src: 感谢您能够选择支雲餐厅用餐，由此给您带来困扰，非常抱歉！
mt: Thank you for choosing Zhi Yuan Restaurant to have your dinner, and we’re very sorry to bring you troubles!
ref: Thank you for choosing Zhi Yuan Restaurant, and we are deeply sorry for the trouble brought to you!

src: 同时非常感谢您给予真实体验评价，让我们及时发现不足的地方，我们一定采取有效的措施进行改善，严格把控菜品的质量及分量，我是支雲餐厅“小雲”我们的电话是18912251735微信同步，期待与再此你相遇
mt: At the same time, thank you very much to give your comments on your true experience, so that we can find our shortcomings and adopt measures to improve them, and we will control the quality and the quantity of the dishes; I’m “Xiaoyun” from Zhi Yun Restaurant, with mobile phone number and WeChat account of 18912251735; look forward to meeting you again.
ref: At the same time, we are grateful for your review of your real experience so that we can timely find our shortcomings, and we will definitely take effective measures to make improvement, strictly control the quality and amount of dishes; we are “Xiao Yun” of Zhi Yun Restaurant and our phone number and WeChat account is 18912251735; we look forward to meeting you again.

src: 尊敬的顾客您好，感谢您能够选择支雲餐厅用餐，因为菜品的问题给您带来不愉快的用餐体验我们深感歉意，我们已与厨房对接沟通对菜品进行严格把控，同事感谢您对我们的理解与支持，我是支雲餐厅小雲，期待与您再此相遇！
mt: Hello, dear customer, thank you for choosing Zhi Yun Restaurant to have your dinner; we’re really sorry about your unfavorable meal experience due to problems about dishes; we’ve communicated with staffs in the kitchen to control our dishes strictly, and thank you very much for your understanding and support; I’m “Xiaoxue” from Zhi Yun Restaurant, and look forward to meeting you again.
ref: Hello, dear customer, thank you for choosing Zhi Yun Restaurant, and we are deeply sorry for your unpleasant dining experience due to the issues of the dishes; we have communicated with the kitchen to strictly control the quality of dishes, and we would like to thank you for your understanding and support for us at the same time; we are Xiao Yun of Zhi Yun Restaurant, and we look forward to meeting you again!

src: 赴宴来支雲，留下好心情！
mt: Come to Zhi Yun and enjoy a pleasant meal!
ref: Come to Zhi Yun and enjoy a pleasant meal!

src: 亲爱的顾客，感谢您对我们“小雲”的评价与支持，当我们用心烹饪的菜品得到您的肯定时，是我们最开心的时刻！
mt: Dear customers, thank you for your evaluation and support to “Xiaoyun”; we are very happy when our dishes cooked deligently are affirmed by you!
ref: Dear customer, thank you for you comment and support for “Xiao Yun”, and it is our happiest moment to win your affirmation for the food we carefully cooked!

src: 期待与再此你相遇
mt: Look forward to meeting you again.
ref: We look forward to meeting you again.

src: 亲爱的小主，首先非常感谢您的认可和评价，支雲会努力越做越好!
mt: Dear customers, firstly, thank you very much for your confirmation and evaluation, and Zhi Yun will try it best to do better!
ref: Dear customer, we would like to first thank you for your affirmation and comment, and Zhi Yun will work hard and get better and better!

src: 其次也特别感谢您在百忙之中的支持和点赞，祝您用餐愉快天天好心情!
mt: In addition, thank you very much for your support and like, and wish you a happy dinner!
ref: We would also love to thank you for your support and likes out of your busy schedule, and we wish you a happy meal time and good mood every day!

src: 大美360集成家装
mt: Damei 360 integrated home decoration
ref: Damei 360 Integrated Home Decoration

src: 地 址：环城南路156号幸福家园12楼
mt: Address: Floor 12, Happy Home, No. 156 of South Ring Road
ref: Address: Happy Home Building 12, South Ring Road 156

src: 一开始是朋友介绍的因为信任，所以选择来看一下起初我的预算是7万做个基本装修。
mt: I went there because of recommendation by one of my friends, and I planned to make a basic decoration with the budget of 70 thousand yuan.
ref: I trusted it because my friend made the recommendation, so I chose to check it out, and originally my budget for a basic decoration was 70,000.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。
mt: I suffered a series of tricks as soon as I went there.
ref: A series of scam began as soon as I came into the store.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: It was my first visit to the shop, and I just showed them my floor plan; unexpectedly, they gave me the offer of 70 thousand yuan for decoration of my house of 135m2 before they had field measurement; they showed me something about their materials of brands that I did not know.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second trick was to push you to pay the deposit as soon as you arrived at their shop (the money that they will never refund unless you have enough energy to argue with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: When I was hesitated about the deposit, they invited their “manager” to tell me that I could be provided with considerable discounts as long as I paid the deposit on that day.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。
mt: This was really a big trick, and I was cheated to pay the deposit of more than 10 thousand yuan on impulse.
ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: However, there were many problems in their offer: the budget of 70 thousand yuan did not include water and electricity transformation, any door, cabinet or bathroom, which were actually the major part in basic decoration.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。
mt: In addition, they charged service fee higher than other similar companies.
ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

src: 我对这个公司失去了信任，一开始什么都没有讲清楚就让我签合同。
mt: I don’t trust the company now, and they pushed me to sign the contract as soon as I arrived there before making anything clear.
ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

src: 当我去找他们退钱的时候他们表现出很有经验的样子，有专门的小团队来对付你。
mt: When I returned there to ask them make refund, their specialized team argued with me in a very experienced way.
ref: When I went to ask for a refund, they acted rather experienced and sent a small team to deal with me.

src: 无论如何都会一口咬死是客户的问题他们全然无责。
mt: They blamed all responsibilities on customers.
ref: Anyway, they just said it was the client’s problem and they had absolutely no responsibility for it.

src: 各种推卸责任，还有很多细节，不想一一说了都是泪，总之不要选择他们，因为我朋友找他们装修的房子也是质量不好，后期给你算各种费用。
mt: They tried their best to shift the blame to other shoulders, with really many details which I don’t want to tell one by one; in a word, don’t choose them, and the home of one of my friends, a decoration work undertaken by them, too, had really poor decoration quality; in addition, they added various expenses during later stage.
ref: They just shrunk their responsibility in any way possible, and there were a lot more details that I don’t want to mention now; all in all, do not choose them because my friend had them renovate her apartment, and the quality was poor and they would charge you all kinds of other costs in the later stage.

src: 坑爹，他们就是原来骗人的龙头装饰，现在改成大美，好像又倒闭了又改成其他的。
mt: Cheaters, their company is the Longtou Decoration originally, wahich was renamed as Damei later, and it seems that Damei has closed down and is renamed as another name.
ref: Swindle; they used to be the swindler company Longtou Renovation, then it’s changed to Damei, and now it seems they have closed down and changed into something else.

src: 所以大家别选择这样坑爹的装修公司。
mt: So please don’t choose a cheating decoration company like this.
ref: So please don’t choose such a swindler company.

src: 以后大家在选择的时候多百度看看这些查一下这些咨询因为装修不是小钱。
mt: Please check decoration companies in Baidu when you want to choose one, because what we spend in decoration is a lot of money.
ref: When you choose renovation companies in the future, please search them on Baidu because renovation cost is not a small amount.

src: 想要向商家提问，请先登录或注册
mt: Please log in or register if you want to ask questions to merchants.
ref: If you want to ask the merchant a question, please log in or register first.

src: 严禁发布各种形式的商家点评，详细请见商户收录声明
mt: It is strictly prohibited to publish comments on merchants of various types, and please refer to statement on commercial tenants for details.
ref: It is strictly prohibited to publish any type of merchant review, and please refer to the Merchant Inclusion Statement for details.

src: 大众点评昆明装修设计频道为您提供大美360集成家装地址，电话，营业时间等最新商户信息，找装修公司装修公司，就上大众点评
mt: Kunming Decoration Design Channel of Dianping.com provides you with latest information of Damei 360 integrated home decoration such as address, telephone number and business hours; come to Dianping.com to find decoration companies.
ref: Dianping Kunming Renovation and Design Channel will provide you with the address, phone number, operation time and other information of Damei 360 Integrated Home Renovation, and please come to Dianping if you are looking for a renovation company.

src: 文摄视觉美学摄影馆优选品质店 暂时还没有分店
mt: Wenshe Visual Aesthetics Photography Studio Premium Store has no branch store yet
ref: Wenshe Visual Aesthetics Photography Studio Premium Store has no branch store yet

src: 加了微信预约日期，小姐姐就把可选择的时间安排发给我，回复信息比较及时~
mt: We added WeChat friends and make an appointment, and then the female staff sent me the time schedule for selection, who replied in time.
ref: I added their WeChat to make an appointment, then they sent me the available dates; their reply was speedy~

src: 去之前看了店里的拍摄作品，更多的是户外婚纱，拍的很漂亮，涉及到的拍摄风格也很多。
mt: I went to the store to see the photography works before, and there were lots of beautiful outdoor wedding dress photos, involving in various photography styles.
ref: I went to the store to see the photography works, and there were more beautiful outdoor wedding dress photos and a lot of different styles.

src: 当天到了之后和小姐姐简单交流了自己的想法，非常耐心地帮我试了两套我纠结的风格衣服，最终敲定开始化妆造型~摄影师拍摄之前会摆一些道具，会指导动作，对各个细节也比较精益求精。
mt: I and the female staff exchanged our ideas briefly after I got there on that day, and the female staff assisted me in trying two sets of clothes with patience and I finally chose one before start of makeup; the photographer laid some props before photographing and guided for my actions, and pursued for perfection in various details.
ref: After I arrived that day, I communicated my own ideas with the young lady and she patiently helped me try on two outfits I was having trouble deciding and I made the final decision before starting styling and makeup~ the photographer would place some props and guide me to pose before the shoot, and was very attentive to the details.

src: 但是可能因为没和我交流具体的拍摄想法，所以拍出来的不是我想要的风格，但是应该是好看的🙊🙊
mt: However, we did not exchange specific ideas about photography, and the photos were not of my ideal ones; however, in fact, these photos were beautiful🙊🙊
ref: However, the photos taken were not in the style I wanted, perhaps it was because they didn’t communicate with me about the specific shooting ideas, but the photos should look nice🙊🙊

src: 拍好之后摄影师会帮忙挑选照片，交流后期风格，感觉挺细心的叭。
mt: After shooting, the photographer assisted in selecting photos and exchanged ideas about post-editing styles in a thoughtful way.
ref: After the shoot, the photographer would help pick the photos, communicate about post-editing style, and I think it was very thoughtful.

src: 修好的片大约要半个月，坐等效果~
mt: It will take me about half a month to get the final photos, and I’m looking forward to them.
ref: It will take about half a month to edit all the photos and I look forward to seeing them~

src: 第二次中了写真类的霸王餐活动～全场大部分的衣服能够选择一件拍摄。
mt: It was the second time for me to win a prize in the lottery of free photo album, and I can choose a set of clothes for most clothes in the studio.
ref: This is the second time that I have won the chance to experience a photoshoot for free~ you may choose one from most of the available outfits to do the photoshoot.

src: 最后选择了一件黑色的纱裙，体验下不同的风格。
mt: Finally, I chose a black gauzy skirt, to experience a different style.
ref: Eventually, I chose a black veil skirt so as to experience a different style.

src: 整个拍摄过程要2个小时左右，化妆+拍摄，负责拍摄的摄影师是95后的弟弟呢，感觉稍微还是有点青涩，希望在顾客拍摄动作指导方面以后能给更多的建议呀～挺健谈的，拍摄过程比较愉快。
mt: It took about 2 hours during the photographing period, including makeup and shooting; the photographer of the generation after 95s was young, who was expected to give more advices in action guidance in the future; he was conversational, and I was happy during the whole shooting period.
ref: The entire photoshoot took about 2 hours including the makeup and shoot; the photographer was a young guy born after 1995, who seemed to be a little shy; I hope he could give more advice to clients in terms of poses~ he was talkative and the shoot was pleasant.

src: 文摄视觉美学摄影馆优选品质店 回复
mt: Reply from Wenshe Visual Aesthetics Photography Studio Premium Store
ref: Wenshe Visual Aesthetics Photography Studio Premium Store reply

src: 上首页了，也来看看Queenie吧~
mt: It is on the front page, and come and see Queenie~
ref: It is on the front page, come and see Queenie~

src: 到店先填了姓名电话然后选服装，婚纱都可以选，换了三四套服装还蛮耐心的，选好后化妆化了很久，服务态度也好，后面拍摄会教你怎么摆造型，就是拍出来的感觉脸好大，精修说是要半个月，三四天就发来了，感觉好像跟原片没啥差别
mt: After I arrived at the store, I firstly filled in the name and the mobile phone number, and then chose clothes or wedding dresses; I tried three or four sets of clothes, and the staffs were patient; after that, it took me a lot of time for makeup, with good service attitude; the staffs taught me how to make pose, but my face seemed big; I was told that it would take me half a month for fine editing of the photos; however, they sent me the photos in three or four days, and I didn’t feel too many differences with the original photos.
ref: After I arrived at the store, I filled in my name and chose the outfits; all the wedding dresses were available to be chosen; I tried on three or four outfits and they were quite patient; after I decided on the dress, they were doing my makeup for a long time and they were also nice during this time; later in the shoot, they would teach you how to pose; I felt my face was too big on the photo; they said detailed editing would take a month, but they sent them to me after three to four days, and they seemed not that different from the original photos.

src: 【环境】整体还好。
mt: [Environment] It was not bad on the whole.
ref: [Environment] It was not bad overall.

src: 可选衣服很多。
mt: There were a lot of clothes to choose.
ref: There are a lot of outfits to choose from.

src: 化妆位置差不多有三个，里边是摄影棚。
mt: There were three seats for makeup, and there was a photostudio.
ref: There are about three seats for doing makeup and the studio is inside.

src: 【服务】很热情，也很细心。
mt: [Service] Very enthusiastic and thoughtful.
ref: [Service] Very enthusiastic and attentive to details.

src: 造型师挺有耐心的。
mt: The stylist was patient.
ref: The stylist was patient.

src: 摄影师也会很认真教你动作。
mt: The photographer taught me something about actions seriously.
ref: Photographer would patiently teach you to pose.

src: 不满意，摄影师也会主动提出补拍。
mt: If you are not satisfied, the photographer will actively propose to reshot.
ref: If you are not satisfied, the photographer would propose to take it again.

src: 【体验】可能造型有点过了，原本双眼皮被贴出了三眼皮。
mt: [Experience] The style was a little exaggerated, and my double-fold eyelids were changed into triple-fold ones.
ref: [Experience] Maybe the style was a little too much, double eyelids turned into triple eyelids.

src: 眉尾也被剃了，对于日常不画眉的有点尴尬。
mt: The tail of my eyebrow was also shaved, which was a little bit awkward to me who do not draw my eyebrows.
ref: The tail of my eyebrow got shaved, and it was a little awkward for those who don’t wear makeup normally.

src: 照片十来天给了，但是P图效果不怎么满意，感觉双眼皮贴那些还是很明显。
mt: I got the photos in about ten days, but I was not satisfied with the editing effect, for the double-eyelid stickers were very obvious.
ref: The photos were sent to me after about ten days, but I was not very satisfied with the photoshop effect, and I feel that the double eyelids tapes are still obvious.

src: 因为不太清楚要什么风格 试了两套 结果挑来挑去 还是选了黑色礼服 小姐姐说这套是比较赫本复古风
mt: Since I was not clear about the style, I tried two sets, and finally chose the black dress, and the female staff told me that this set was of the Herben ancient style.
ref: I tried on two outfits because I didn’t know what style to choose, and I ended up choosing the black suit after trying hesitating; the young lady said it was a vintage Audrey Hepburn style.

src: 选好衣服后就开始弄妆发啦 发型师和化妆师小姐姐都超级耐心在帮我弄 弄出来的效果非常满意
mt: After choosing the clothes, the hairstylist and the dresser dressed me patiently, with very satisfying effect.
ref: After choosing the outfit, we began with the hair and makeup; the hair stylist and makeup artist were super patient and I was really satisfied.

src: 弄好妆发后就开始拍照了 摄影师全程都有指挥我摆姿势 过程很轻松和谐
mt: The photographer started working after dressing and makeup, who commanded me to make pose, making the whole course easy and harmonious.
ref: The photoshoot started after finishing makeup and hair, and the photographer guided me to pose the whole time; the process was relaxed and harmonious.

src: 拍完后认真选了四张最喜欢的当精修 小哥哥说15内成片 结局非常心满意足～
mt: After shooting, I selected four photos that I preferred for fine editing, and the staff told me that I would get the final photos within 15 days, and the final photos were really satisfying.
ref: After the photoshoot, I chose my four favorite ones to be retouched, and the guy said the photos would be completed within 15 days and I was really satisfied with the results~

src: 高铁居然之家
mt: Easyhome, High-speed rail station
ref: HSR Easyhome

src: 地 址：高铁北一路555号 查看地图
mt: Address: No. 555 of North First Road, High-speed rail station, check the map
ref: Address: HSR North One Road 555 View Map

src: 这儿家居家电比较齐全，品牌众多，知名品牌全。
mt: There are complete household items and home appliances, with multiple brands, including famous ones.
ref: Home appliances in this store are quite complete, with many brands including almost all well-known brands.

src: 双十二那阵，到“汉斯顿”净水器店，看净水器，店内正在做活动，价格比较优惠。
mt: I went to Hunsdon water purifier shop to buy a water purifier during the Double Twelve Festival, and there was sales promotion in the shop, with favorable price.
ref: During the Double 12 Sale, I went to the "Hunsdon" water purifier store to see the water purifiers, and there were sale activities in the store with favorable prices.

src: 居然之家一共11层，负二层到9层，负一负二都是停车的地方，而且白天停车免费!
mt: Easyhome has totally 11 floors from B2 to Floor 9, in which B1 and B2 are parking lots, and people can park there for free during daytime!
ref: There are 11 floors in Easyhome, from B2 to 9th floor, in which B2 and B2 are for parking and parking is free during the day!

src: 周围是真不怎样，饭店五金店寥寥无几，而且饭店味道一般般。
mt: However, there were only several restaurants and hardware stores nearby, and the dishes in these restaurants are just so so.
ref: The surroundings are really not nice, with few restaurants and hardware store, and the food there tasted average.

src: 这个电梯也是很无语，跟有那大病一样，负二到负一，来回折腾，不停我按的这一层，从安全通道下去到一楼，也是很无语，直接通到一个家具店，家具店关门，安全通道出不去!
mt: The elevator is also disappointing, which runs repeatedly from B2 to B1, and did not stop on the floor I wanted to get off, and I had to go to Floor 1 from the exit passageway, which led to a furniture store, and the store was closed and I could not get out from the exit passageway!
ref: This elevator really makes people speechless; it went back and forth from B2 to B1 and did not stop on my floor, and it was ridiculous that when I went to the 1st floor from fire escape, it led to a furniture store which was closed, so I couldn’t get out from the fire escape, either!

src: 居然之家还是需要提升，有很多地方都没有开发。
mt: Easyhome shall be further improved, and lots of spaces in it are not developed.
ref: Easyhome still needs to be improved with a lot of spaces to be developed.

src: 地址：沙依巴克区高铁北一路555号，交通方便，停车场很大，白天还是免费的。
mt: Address: No. 555 of North First Road, High-speed rail station, Saybagh District, with convenient traffic, large parking lot, free for daytime.
ref: Address: HSR North One Road, Bayishake District, convenient transportation, big parking lot free during the day.

src: 环境：说实话店里面积大，有8～9层，家里想买的家具、家用电器、各种小东西……，都能买到，好多名牌商家都入驻在店里，慕思、欧派、华帝、老板、峰创之家、汉斯顿、雅克、友邦、丝涟、富品居、万家乐、大自然、中联、美的、雅丹……，品牌真的是太多了，我只能记得这么多了，是购买产品的好去处，逛累了可以坐在沙发上休息休息哦。
mt: Environment: The shop is really large, with 8 or 9 floors, and people can buy furniture, home appliances and various little things there, with lots of famous brands such as Mousse, OPPEIN, VATTI, Robam, Fengchuang Home, Hunsdon, Yake, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, GUANGDONG MACRO, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, and so many other brands, I can only remember these ones; it is a good place to buy products, and people can sit on couches and have a rest if they are tired.
ref: Environment: Honestly, the store is large with 8-9 floors, where you can buy all the furniture, household appliances and small things your home needs, and many famous brands have settled in the store, such as DeRUCCI, OPPEIN, VATTI, Robam, Fengchuang Home, Hunsdon, Yake, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, GUANGDONG MACRO, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, and so many other brands, I can only remember so many; it is a good place to buy products, and you can sit on the couch and have a rest if you get tired.

src: 最近想买一套舒适的沙发，朋友说这里有好多沙发可以选，看了顾家家居、美克美家的，感觉还可以，就是价格略贵，所以还在纠结中
mt: I want to buy a set of comfortable sofa recently, and I went there due to recommendation by one of my friends; I shopped stores of KUKA and Markor Furnishings, the sofa there was good, but with relatively high price, and I’m still considering which to buy.
ref: I recently want to buy a couch and my friend said there was a lot of couch to choose from here; I looked at Kuka Home and Markor Furnishings, and I felt they were okay but a little expensive, so I am still struggling to decide.

src: 大众点评乌鲁木齐家居卖场频道为您提供高铁居然之家地址，电话，营业时间等最新商户信息，找装修公司，就上大众点评
mt: Urumchi Home Store Channel of Dianping.com provides you with latest information of Easyhome, High-speed rail station such as address, telephone number and business hours; come to Dianping.com to find decoration companies.
ref: Dianping Urumqi Renovation and Design Channel will provide you with the address, phone number, operation time and other information of HSR Easyhome, and please come to Dianping if you are looking for a renovation company.

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that I think is very meaningful - first aid certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skill certificates that I think is important besides the driver's license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Popularize it: first aid measures are actually emergency rescue in the event of an emergency, that is, the rescue before the ambulance arrives.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is actually a period of time before the ambulance arrives after an accident, and it is this period of time that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I do have a heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage, or respiratory arrest, then our window of life is only four minutes, golden four minutes!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So people around you know how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls down, we can use our professional knowledge to rescue him, instead of just standing there motionless and unable to do anything. This feeling of helplessness is so terrifying.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: "In China, we have official figures of three million accidental deaths a year, the most dangerous being called cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, an average of 15% can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In Las Vegas casinos and hotels, 70% to 80% can be saved, and less than 1% in Shanghai and Beijing. "
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, founder of First Response, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person suffers cardiac arrest, there is no breathing, and there is no heartbeat, you will have no effect by pinching the person.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: You must do artificial respiration and chest compressions to save someone.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I found that few of us have this awareness to learn first aid, but when something happens, it is too late, so I still call on everyone to learn this skill, so that we can be timely in the face of emergencies react.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: It might even save someone's life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: The first aid certificate can be registered at your local Red Cross training center. I registered at the Red Cross training center in Zhuhai, and there are discounts for students.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is to record the goal to be completed before the age of 25. It was also a few months ago that the first aid certificate was added to the goal list, but it was indeed completed!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Then I'm going to take the other certifications I want to take. I plan to take a diving certificate. I saw a diving first aid certificate in Xiaohongshu before. Still very useful!
ref: Next, I will apply for other certificates; I plan to get Diving Certificate; I saw on Red earlier that there is a Diving First Aid Certificate, which requires a Certificate of First Aid first, so getting a Certificate of First Aid is useful!

ref: Zhengzhou Yixin is a specialized manufacturer of concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, inspection shaft building block machinery and shaft wall module equipment, with semi-automatic and automatic production lines.

ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the characteristics and advantages of Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment

src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。
mt: Yixin inspection well block brick machine equipment is widely used in new masonry materials for municipal underground structures such as coal, heat, water, electricity and gas.
ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: various inspection wells of drainage and water storage facilities, rainwater inlets, square ditches, septic tanks and small structures, bridge wing walls, etc.
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper, lower, left, and right sides of the modules are concave-convex groove structures, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shear resistance of the shaft wall is much better than that of the flat friction masonry.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure. After combined masonry, the longitudinal holes are connected, and the horizontal holes are connected. After the hole core is poured, a cast-in-place concrete network structure is formed, which plays a secondary reinforcement and waterproofing role.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The modules are provided with grooves for inserting bars vertically and horizontally, and the horizontal and vertical reinforcing bars increase the overall strength of the structure accordingly.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, the inspection wells and drainage wells built with concrete inspection well modules are not prone to collapse, subsidence, water leakage, etc. The well wall module has stable mechanical properties, simple operation, and standard forming dimensions.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备智能控制配备数据输入、输出装置一键通触摸式液晶显示监控机械操作全部过程，实现理想的人机对话、自动分析比料、密度运转、安全逻辑控制及故障诊断系统。
mt: The intelligent control of the concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment is equipped with data input and output devices, one-touch LCD display to monitor the entire process of mechanical operation, to achieve ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis of material ratio, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system .
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械液压系统采用单缸液压、输送，双缸液压、输送。
mt: The mechanical hydraulic system of the well wall module adopts single-cylinder hydraulic and conveying, and double-cylinder hydraulic and conveying.
ref: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.

src: 独立的液压集成站，避免了由于主机振动对液压系统的影响，从而保证液压系统工作的可靠性。
mt: The independent hydraulic integration station avoids the influence of the host vibration on the hydraulic system, thus ensuring the reliability of the hydraulic system.
ref: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备布料箱行进模箱脱模上升，储料箱门关闭，自动输送托板，全部由液压系统独立完成，从而达到减少机械的磨损和维修。
mt: Concrete inspection well module block making machine equipment distributing box travels and lifts the mold box, the storage box door is closed, and the pallet is automatically conveyed, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system, thereby reducing mechanical wear and tear and maintenance.
ref: In the concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, the fabric box proceeding box de-molds and lifts, the storage box door closes, and the supporting plate is transported automatically, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system so as to reduce mechanical abrasion and times of repair.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备采用进口电脑、电器，密封件液压件，准保设备综合性能稳定可靠。
mt: The concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment adopts imported computers, electrical appliances, and hydraulic seals to ensure stable and reliable comprehensive performance of the equipment.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment is composed by imported computer and appliances, as well as sealing elements and hydraulic element to ensure stable and reliable comprehensive performance.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振平台采用整体板钢，台面线切割合模无焊接点，使填料箱自由摆动导向，充分减少机械磨损。
mt: The mechanical vibration excitation platform of the wall module of the well wall is made of integral plate steel, and there is no welding point for the line cutting and clamping of the table surface, so that the stuffing box can be freely swayed and guided, and the mechanical wear and tear can be fully reduced.
ref: The integral steel plate is adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical vibration platform, with no welding points of wire-electrode cutting mold closing of mesa, so that the stuffing box can swing and orient freely to greatly reduce mechanical abrasion.

src: 使模具负荷减少、填料并二合一加密振幅，采用一体化、全同步，台振、模振，确保达到振实效果。
mt: The mold load is reduced, the packing is combined with two-in-one to encrypt the amplitude, and the integrated, full synchronization, table vibration and mold vibration are adopted to ensure the vibration effect.
ref: It reduces loads of molds and reinforces vibration; integrated and full synchronization are adopted for vibration of the platform and the molds to ensure the vibration effect.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振机械、电脑自动控制振幅根据原料性价比调节振幅，无磨损制动，从而延长使用寿命，降低成本。
mt: The shaft wall module mechanical vibration excitation machine and computer automatically control the amplitude to adjust the amplitude according to the cost-effectiveness of the raw materials, and brake without wear, thereby prolonging the service life and reducing the cost.
ref: The shaft wall module mechanical excitation machinery and the computer automatically control the vibration range according to the cost performance of raw materials, leading to no abrasion brake; in this way, it extends the service life and reduces the cost.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械自动控制和手动控制双重功能。
mt: The well wall module has dual functions of mechanical automatic control and manual control.
ref: The shaft wall module machinery is equipped with dual functions, i.e., automatic control and manual control.

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories: virgin olive oil (Virgin Olive Oil) and refined olive oil (Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil), with five levels.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is the oil obtained directly from the fresh olive fruit after mechanical cold pressing and filtering to remove foreign matter.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: There are three levels of acidity:
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra virgin olive oil (Extra Virgin): It is the highest grade and highest quality olive oil, and it is a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: Excellent taste, with light and pleasant botanical aromas and an acidity of no more than 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: Fine Virgin Olive Oil: Slightly higher acidity, but no more than 2%, pure and aromatic.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary Virgin Olive Oil: The taste and flavor are acceptable, and the acidity does not exceed 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to olive oil obtained by refining virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or "secondary oil".
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: There are two grades of refined olive oil:
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Ordinary olive oil (Olive Oil): Refined olive oil is mixed with a certain proportion of virgin olive oil to harmonize taste and color, its acidity is below 1.5%, and it is transparent and light golden yellow.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined olive oil or olive pomace oil (Refined Olive-Pomace Oil): It is an olive oil obtained by the dissolution method extracted from the oil residue and refined.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have seen the classification, you should have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You know, olives are like grapes that make wine. Olives from different producing areas and varieties of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: The best places to grow olives:
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable soil and temperature, sunshine, air humidity and precipitation for the growth of olive oil.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Except for the Mediterranean coast, other areas can only be grown sporadically in suitable areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main producing areas (Mediterranean):
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., have similar climates to Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Picking months for olives:
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: From March to June each year, the olive tree blooms and bears fruit. From July to October, the fruit begins to develop and mature, and the fruit transitions from green to red, purple, and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: The fruit picking season is from November to February of the following year (the freshness of the olive oil is very important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: Nutritional content of olive oil:
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, as well as vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered to be the most suitable oil for human nutrition among the oils found so far.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.

src: 其实对于身体微胖的女孩子穿衣搭配的讲究很多。

src: 身体胖的女孩穿的裙子不能太短或太长，长度差不多在膝盖，刚好能盖住大腿胖的地方即可。
mt: The skirts worn by fat girls should not be too short or too long. The length is almost at the knees, just enough to cover the fat thighs.

src: 裙子过短就会把腿上的肥胖显露出来。

ref: The fat thighs will be shown if the skirt is too short.

src: 过长就会给人矮而胖的感觉。
mt: Too long will give the impression of short and fat.
ref: Skirts that are too long will make you look short and fat.

src: 如果穿出分出上中下三段来，就显得你自然增高了，就是上身、裙和长筒袜用不同的颜色，看上去就会产生一种修长的感觉 。
mt: If you wear it into three sections, upper, middle and lower, it will appear that you will naturally increase in height. Even if the upper body, skirt and stockings are used in different colors, it will look like a slender feeling.
ref: If you are dressed in three sections, upper, middle and lower, you will naturally look taller; that is, use different colors for upper body, skirt and stockings, and you will look taller and slimmer.

src: 其实很多深色系的衣服是微胖女孩子们的标配（这一点作者深有体会），深颜色也是掩盖你身体胖的好方法，高贵典雅的黑色短裙也是微胖女孩的首选。
mt: In fact, many dark clothes are standard for fat girls (the author has a deep understanding of this), dark colors are also a good way to cover up your body fat, and elegant black skirts are also the first choice for fat girls.

src: 李先生一开始以为是足浴盆的振动功能引起的，没想到关了振动功能，父亲还是感觉到脚底麻麻的。
mt: At first, Mr. Li thought it was caused by the vibration function of the foot bath tub, but he did not expect to turn off the vibration function, and his father still felt numbness on the soles of his feet.
ref: Mr. Li first thought it was caused by the vibration function of the feet bath basin, and it was unexpected that his father still felt his feet were numb after turning off the vibration function.

src: 李先生用电笔一试，电笔居然亮了，李先生惊讶地发现足浴盆的水里居然带电。
mt: Mr. Li tried the electric pen, and the electric pen actually turned on. Mr. Li was surprised to find that the water in the foot bath was actually charged.
ref: Mr. Li used a tester and the light on it was on; it was to Mr. Li’s surprise that the water in the feet bath basin was electrified.

src: 后来他联络了商家，商家的态度还不错，尽管退掉了足浴盆，李先生依然感到不快。
mt: Later, he contacted the merchant, and the merchant's attitude was not bad. Although he returned the foot tub, Mr. Li was still unhappy.
ref: Then he contacted the seller, whose attitude was nice, but Mr. Li still felt upset although he had returned it.

src: 因为他发现这个已经流行已久的足浴盆如今在最高温度的设定、适用于何种人群、何种材料保证无害等方面都没有一个明确详细的行业规定。
mt: Because he found that this long-established footbath does not have a clear and detailed industry regulation in terms of the maximum temperature setting, what kind of people it is suitable for, and what kind of materials are guaranteed to be harmless.
ref: Because he found that feet bath basin, which has been popular for a long time, still has no explicit and detailed industry regulations on the setting of the maximum temperature, suitable crowd, what materials are safe to use, etc.

src: 但是一般情况下足浴盆是不会有带电问题的，但也不排除少数产品在出厂时没有严格把关。
mt: However, under normal circumstances, the foot bath tub will not have the problem of electrification, but it does not rule out that a few products are not strictly checked when they leave the factory.
ref: But normally feet bath basin shouldn’t be electrified, however we can’t rule out the fact that a few products might not have been strictly checked before leaving the factory.

src: 因此在在购买的时候选择分体式的足浴盆。
mt: Therefore, choose a split foot bath when purchasing.
ref: Therefore, choose split type feet bath basin.

src: 水电分离，没有任何安全隐患。
mt: Separation of water and electricity, there is no safety hazard.
ref: There is no safety risk when water and electricity are separated.

src: 同时你可以随便拿电笔测。
mt: At the same time, you can take a pencil test at will.
ref: Meanwhile, you can use a tester to test it.

src: 羊行屮（chè），本名姜波，生于羊年羊月，羊行草上，适得其所，是为羊行屮，人称“羊叔”。
mt: Sheep Xingxi (chè), whose real name is Jiang Bo, was born in the year of the sheep, the month of the sheep, on the grass of the sheep.
ref: Yang Xingche, real name Jiang Bo, was born in the month of the sheep in the year of the sheep; the name Yang Xingche means the sheep feel most comfortable when they are on grass; people call him Uncle Yang (Sheep in Chinese).

src: 因出版“异域密码”系列的《泰国异闻录》《印度异闻录》《日本异闻录》《韩国异闻录》等作品，在业内有“悬疑怪才”之称，自称“擅长一本正经地胡说八道”
mt: He is known as a "suspenseful geek" in the industry due to the publication of the "Exotic Code" series of "Thailand Variations", "India Variations", "Japan Variations", "Korea Variations" and other works. nonsense"
ref: He is called “thriller genius” in the industry due to the publication of his “Foreign Password” series including Strange Stories in Thailand, Strange Stories in India, Strange Stories in Japan and Strange Stories in Korea, and he said that he’s “good at talking serious nonsense”

src: 《灯下黑》，又名《中国异闻录》，“悬疑怪才”羊行屮用全新作品《灯下黑》带你深入领略中国民俗的骨髓，那些流传至今的传说，背后有怎样凄美、动人的爱恨绝唱？
mt: "Black Under the Lamp", also known as "Chinese Stories", "suspenseful geek" Yang Xingxi uses the new work "Black Under the Lamp" to take you in-depth understanding of the marrow of Chinese folklore, and the poignant and beautiful behind the legends that have been passed down to this day , moving love-hate swan song?
ref: Darkness under the Light, also known as Strange Stories in China, a brand new work from the “thriller genius”, allows you to experience the essence of Chinese folk customs; what are the sad, beautiful and moving stories behind the legends passed down until now?

src: “异途行者”南晓楼、月无华再次开启作死的探秘之旅，他们的身世即将揭晓。
mt: "Strangers" Nan Xiaolou and Yue Wuhua once again embarked on a quest for death, and their life experiences are about to be revealed.
ref: Nan Xiaolou and Yue Wuhua, the “travelers of a different journey”, start the risky travel of secrets exploration, and their life stories will be revealed soon.

src: “悬疑怪才”羊行屮熬白了头发，累积百万册畅销书奉献！
mt: "Suspense geek" Yang Xingxi has whitened his hair and accumulated millions of bestsellers!
ref: Yang Xingche, the “thriller genius”, worked until his hair turned gray to contribute a million bestselling books!

src: 正版《中国异闻录》，“异域密码”之后的全新作品，同样的作者，同样的主角，延续《泰国异闻录》《印度异闻录》未完的故事！
mt: Genuine "China Variations", a brand new work after "Exotic Code", the same author, the same protagonist, continuing the unfinished story of "Thailand Variations" and "India Variations"!
ref: The authentic Strange Stories in China, a brand new work after the “Foreign Password” series, has the same author and the same leading actors; it extends the unfinished stories of Strange Stories in Thailand and Strange Stories in India!

src: 非常感谢您选择我们的产品，在您使用我们芯片前，请花5分钟认真阅读以下内容：
mt: Thank you very much for choosing our products. Before you use our chips, please take 5 minutes to read the following carefully:
ref: Thank you very much for choosing our product, and please take 5 minutes to carefully read the following contents before using our chip:

src: 开箱后请检查货物是否齐全。
mt: Please check whether the goods are complete after unpacking.
ref: Please check if the product is complete after opening the box.

src: 如有缺失，请及时与客服联系。
mt: If there is any missing, please contact customer service in time.
ref: Please contact the customer service staff immediately if any part is missing.

src: 微流控芯片上盖板为PC材质，请勿通入与PC发生化学反应的溶剂。
mt: The upper cover of the microfluidic chip is made of PC material. Do not pass solvents that chemically react with PC.
ref: The upper cover plate of the micro-fluid chip is made from PC material, and please do not add any solvent which could have chemical reaction with PC.

src: 请勿使用手推注射器直接对芯片进行进样，否则容易发生漏液。
mt: Do not use a hand-push syringe to directly inject samples into the chip, otherwise liquid leakage may occur.
ref: Don’t inject sample into the chip directly with the hand syringe, or there may be liquid leakage.

src: 普通基底的微流控芯片发货前均在500mbar（100um沟道深度）或300mbar（50um沟道深度）进样压力下通过纯水测试。
mt: The microfluidic chips of common substrates pass the pure water test under the injection pressure of 500mbar (100um channel depth) or 300mbar (50um channel depth) before delivery.
ref: The micro-fluid chips with ordinary base have passed the pure water test with the sample injection pressure of 500mbar (100um channel depth) or 300mbar (50um channel depth) before delivery.

src: 玻璃基底的芯片在发货前均在800mbar（100um沟道）进样压力下通过纯水测试，您在使用玻璃基底芯片过程中请注意不要与尖锐物体碰撞，否则会损坏基底。
mt: Chips with glass substrates pass the pure water test under 800mbar (100um channel) injection pressure before delivery. Please be careful not to collide with sharp objects when using glass substrate chips, otherwise the substrate will be damaged.
ref: The micro-fluid chips of glass base have passed the pure water test with the sample injection pressure of 800mbar (100um channel) before delivery; please avoid collision with sharp articles when using glass-base chips, which may lead to damage to the base.

src: 使用过程中请结合溶液粘稠度考虑并勿超出此范围，否则会引起漏液。
mt: During use, please consider the viscosity of the solution and do not exceed this range, otherwise it will cause liquid leakage.
ref: Please take the viscosity of the solution into consideration during usage and do not exceed the range, or it will lead to liquid leakage.

src: 普通基底的微流控微芯片在注射泵使用纯水进样的条件下，我们给您的建议流速设置在150ul/min以下，油相流速建议设置在50ul/min以下。
mt: For microfluidic microchips with ordinary substrates, under the condition that the syringe pump uses pure water to inject samples, we recommend that the flow rate be set below 150ul/min, and the oil phase flow rate is recommended to be set below 50ul/min.
ref: In condition of sample injection with pure water for micro-fluid chips of ordinary base, you are recommended to set the flow velocity as under 150ul/min and set the flow velocity of oil phase as under 50ul/min.

src: 请根据实际进样液体的粘稠度综合考虑，由慢到快增加您的流速参数值。
mt: Please increase your flow parameter value from slow to fast according to the viscosity of the actual injection liquid.
ref: Please take the viscosity of sample injection liquid into consideration, and increase your parameters of flow velocity from slowly to rapidly.

src: 通用芯片在实验完成后，请及时将内部沟道清洗干净，否则容易造成堵塞。
mt: After the experiment of the general chip is completed, please clean the internal channel in time, otherwise it will easily cause blockage.
ref: After completing the experiment, please clean the internal channel of the chips in time, or it may lead to blocking.

src: 微流控芯片属于易耗品，不能长期重复使用。
mt: Microfluidic chips are consumables and cannot be reused for a long time.
ref: As consumables, micro-fluid chips cannot be used repeatedly for long.

src: 如果由于长期使用或者不正当操作造成芯片的损坏不予退换。
mt: If the chip is damaged due to long-term use or improper operation, it will not be returned.
ref: The chips with damages caused by long-term usage or improper operation will not be exchanged or refunded.

src: 如果您需要可承受更大压力或者流速的微流控芯片，可联系客服定制。
mt: If you need a microfluidic chip that can withstand higher pressure or flow rate, you can contact customer service for customization.
ref: Please contact the customer service staff for customization if you need micro-fluid chips that can bear larger pressure or with bigger flow velocity.

src: 芯片正常发货周期为1周以内，库存有现货部分拍下后24小时可以发货，请下单前与客服咨询。
mt: The normal delivery cycle of chips is within 1 week, and the parts in stock can be shipped within 24 hours after being photographed. Please consult with customer service before placing an order.
ref: In general conditions, the chips will be dispatched within 1 week, and the ones in stock can be dispatched within 24 hours, and please consult to the customer service staff before placing an order.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: It was the first time I went to the store and I just showed them my floor plan. They didn't go to the house to measure the house. They could actually give me a quote saying that my house of 135 can be dealt with at 70,000 yuan. I looked at their material and didn't know what brand of material they were.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second trick is that as long as you go to the store, they will drag you to pay the deposit (and once the money is paid, you will never be able to get it back, unless you have enough experience to argue with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。

ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。

mt: There are many problems with the quote he gave me. 70,000 does not include water and electricity renovations, and does not include any doors and cabinet bathrooms, and these three are the bulk of the cost of the basic installation.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

mt: So people around you know how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls, we can rescue him through professional knowledge, instead of standing there motionless and doing nothing. This feeling of helplessness is terrible.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: "In China, according to our official data, three million people die accidentally every year, and the most dangerous one is cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, an average of 15% can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In casino hotels in Las Vegas, 70 to 80% can be saved, while Shanghai and Beijing are less than 1%."
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, founder of First Reaction, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has a cardiac arrest, his breathing is gone, and his heartbeat is gone, there is no effect in pinching people.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: Artificial respiration and chest compressions are necessary to save people.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I found that few of us have this awareness to learn first aid, but it is too late when things happen, so I still call on everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond in time in the face of emergencies.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: Maybe it can save a person's life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: The first aid certificate can be registered at your local Red Cross training center. I signed up at the Red Cross training center in Zhuhai. There is still a discount for students.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is a record of the goals to be completed before the age of 25. It was a few months ago that the first aid certificate was added to the goal list, but it was indeed completed!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Then I have to take other certificates I want to take. I plan to take a diving certificate. I saw a diving first aid certificate in Xiaohongshu before. It seems that I have to have a first aid certificate to take the test, so in fact, the first aid certificate is still very useful!
ref: Next, I will apply for other certificates; I plan to get Diving Certificate; I saw on Red earlier that there is a Diving First Aid Certificate, which requires a Certificate of First Aid first, so getting a Certificate of First Aid is useful!

ref: Zhengzhou Yixin is a specialized manufacturer of concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, inspection shaft building block machinery and shaft wall module equipment, with semi-automatic and automatic production lines.
