src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。
mt: Yixin inspection well block brick machine equipment is widely used in new masonry materials for municipal underground structures such as coal, heat, water, electricity and gas.
ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: all kinds of inspection wells for drainage and water storage facilities, rainwater inlets, square ditches, septic tanks and small structures, bridge wing walls, etc.
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper, lower, left and right sides of the module are concave and convex groove structures, and the combined masonry forms a chain.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shear resistance of shaft wall is much better than that of flat friction masonry.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure. After the combined masonry, the longitudinal holes are connected, and the transverse holes are intersected. After the hole core is poured, the cast-in-place concrete network structure is formed, which plays a secondary reinforcement and waterproof role.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The module is provided with reinforcement grooves vertically and horizontally, and the horizontal and longitudinal reinforcement correspondingly improve the overall strength of the structure.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, the inspection wells and drainage wells built with concrete inspection well modules are not prone to collapse, sinking, water leakage and other phenomena. The shaft wall module has stable mechanical properties, simple operation and standard forming size.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备智能控制配备数据输入、输出装置一键通触摸式液晶显示监控机械操作全部过程，实现理想的人机对话、自动分析比料、密度运转、安全逻辑控制及故障诊断系统。
mt: The intelligent control of concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment is equipped with data input and output devices, and the one-touch touch LCD display monitors the whole process of mechanical operation, realizing ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis and material ratio, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械液压系统采用单缸液压、输送，双缸液压、输送。
mt: The mechanical hydraulic system of shaft wall module adopts single cylinder hydraulic and conveying, and double cylinder hydraulic and conveying.
ref: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.

src: 独立的液压集成站，避免了由于主机振动对液压系统的影响，从而保证液压系统工作的可靠性。
mt: The independent hydraulic integrated station avoids the influence of the vibration of the main engine on the hydraulic system, thus ensuring the reliability of the hydraulic system.
ref: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备布料箱行进模箱脱模上升，储料箱门关闭，自动输送托板，全部由液压系统独立完成，从而达到减少机械的磨损和维修。
mt: The concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment distribution box goes up and down the mold box, the storage box door is closed, and the automatic conveying support plate is all completed independently by the hydraulic system, so as to reduce mechanical wear and maintenance.
ref: In the concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, the fabric box proceeding box de-molds and lifts, the storage box door closes, and the supporting plate is transported automatically, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system so as to reduce mechanical abrasion and times of repair.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备采用进口电脑、电器，密封件液压件，准保设备综合性能稳定可靠。
mt: The concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment adopts imported computers, electrical appliances, and hydraulic seals to ensure the comprehensive performance of the equipment is stable and reliable.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment is composed by imported computer and appliances, as well as sealing elements and hydraulic element to ensure stable and reliable comprehensive performance.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振平台采用整体板钢，台面线切割合模无焊接点，使填料箱自由摆动导向，充分减少机械磨损。
mt: The mechanical excitation platform of shaft wall module adopts integral plate steel, and the table surface is wire-cut and molded without welding points, so that the stuffing box can swing freely and guide, and fully reduce mechanical wear.
ref: The integral steel plate is adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical vibration platform, with no welding points of wire-electrode cutting mold closing of mesa, so that the stuffing box can swing and orient freely to greatly reduce mechanical abrasion.

src: 使模具负荷减少、填料并二合一加密振幅，采用一体化、全同步，台振、模振，确保达到振实效果。
mt: The mold load is reduced, the filler is combined with the two-in-one encryption amplitude, and the integration, full synchronization, platform vibration and mold vibration are adopted to ensure the vibration effect.
ref: It reduces loads of molds and reinforces vibration; integrated and full synchronization are adopted for vibration of the platform and the molds to ensure the vibration effect.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振机械、电脑自动控制振幅根据原料性价比调节振幅，无磨损制动，从而延长使用寿命，降低成本。
mt: Shaft wall module mechanical excitation machinery, computer automatic control amplitude according to the cost performance of raw materials to adjust the amplitude, no wear braking, so as to prolong the service life and reduce costs.
ref: The shaft wall module mechanical excitation machinery and the computer automatically control the vibration range according to the cost performance of raw materials, leading to no abrasion brake; in this way, it extends the service life and reduces the cost.

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories: virgin olive oil (Virgin OliveOil) and refined olive oil (Virgam OliveOil or Refined OliveOil), with five grades.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is an oil obtained directly from fresh olive fruits by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: It can be divided into three levels according to the acidity:
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra Virgin olive oil: It is the highest grade and highest quality olive oil, and it is a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: The taste is excellent, with light and pleasant plant aroma and acidity of no more than 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: Quality virgin olive oil (FineVirgin): slightly higher acidity, but no more than 2%, pure and aromatic.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary virgin olive oil (OrdinaryVirgin): The taste and flavor are acceptable, and the acidity does not exceed 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to olive oil obtained from refined virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or become "secondary oil".
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two grades:
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Olive Oil: Refined olive oil is mixed with a certain proportion of virgin olive oil to reconcile taste and color, its acidity is less than 1.5%, and it is transparent light golden yellow.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined olive impurity oil or olive fruit residue oil (RefinedOlive-PomaceOil): olive oil extracted from oil residue by dissolution method and refined.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have seen the classification, you should have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You know, olive fruits are like grapes that make wine. Olive fruits from different producing areas and different olive fruit varieties will produce different standards of olive oil.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: The best place to grow olives:
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable soil and climatic conditions such as temperature, sunshine, air humidity and precipitation for olive growth.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: With the exception of the Mediterranean coast, other areas can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main producing areas (Mediterranean):
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon and so on. Similar to its climate are Argentina, Peru, South Africa and so on as far away as the southern latitude.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Olive picking month:
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: From March to June every year, it is the time for olive trees to blossom and set fruit. From July to October, the fruits begin to develop and mature, and the fruits transition from green to red, purple, and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: November to February is the fruit picking season (the freshness of olive oil is very important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: Nutrients of olive oil:
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, as well as vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered to be the most suitable oil for human nutrition among the oils found so far.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.

mt: Johnnie Walker Red Card whisky is a blend of about 35 kinds of Scotch whisky. It has the characteristics of strong aroma and traditional Scotch whisky, with sweet and smoky aroma in the rich aroma.

mt: Red card whisky has entered China. In order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, red card whisky+cola or Sprite or Sunkis and other sparkling drinks have become an enduring fashion.

mt: These sweet drinks can not only neutralize the sour taste, but also bring pleasure to people visually. Adding drinks can dilute the taste of wine and change the taste.

src: 在相关的数据表面，与传统家电相比，足浴盆等保健类家电销售火爆，但足浴盆并没有专门行业标准，因此存在一定的安全隐患。
mt: On the surface of relevant data, compared with traditional home appliances, health care appliances such as foot baths are selling well, but there is no special industry standard for foot baths, so there are certain potential safety hazards.
ref: According to related statistics, compared with traditional home appliances, the sales of healthcare products such as feet bath basin was hot, but there is no specialized industry standard for feet bath basin and so there is potential safety risk.

src: “在带电的水里泡脚，实在太危险了吧!”
mt: "It's too dangerous to soak your feet in electrified water!"
ref: “Having a feet bath in the water with electricity is too dangerous!”

src: 李先生告诉记者，近日，他买了一个足浴盆送给父亲做生日礼物，可是父亲泡脚时却感觉脚底发麻。
mt: Mr. Li told reporters that recently, he bought a foot bath for his father as a birthday present, but when his father soaked his feet, he felt numb on the soles of his feet.
ref: Mr. Li told reporter that he recently bought a feet bath basin for his father as a birthday present, but his father felt that the bottom of his feet were numb when using it.

src: 李先生一开始以为是足浴盆的振动功能引起的，没想到关了振动功能，父亲还是感觉到脚底麻麻的。
mt: At first, Mr. Li thought it was caused by the vibration function of the foot bath, but when the vibration function was turned off, his father still felt the soles of his feet numb.
ref: Mr. Li first thought it was caused by the vibration function of the feet bath basin, and it was unexpected that his father still felt his feet were numb after turning off the vibration function.

src: 李先生用电笔一试，电笔居然亮了，李先生惊讶地发现足浴盆的水里居然带电。
mt: Mr. Li tried the electric pen, and the electric pen turned on. Mr. Li was surprised to find that the water in the foot bath was actually charged.
ref: Mr. Li used a tester and the light on it was on; it was to Mr. Li’s surprise that the water in the feet bath basin was electrified.

src: 后来他联络了商家，商家的态度还不错，尽管退掉了足浴盆，李先生依然感到不快。
mt: Later, he contacted the merchant, and the attitude of the merchant was not bad. Although he returned the foot bath, Mr. Li still felt unhappy.
ref: Then he contacted the seller, whose attitude was nice, but Mr. Li still felt upset although he had returned it.

src: 因为他发现这个已经流行已久的足浴盆如今在最高温度的设定、适用于何种人群、何种材料保证无害等方面都没有一个明确详细的行业规定。
mt: Because he found that the foot bath, which has been popular for a long time, now has no clear and detailed industry regulations on the setting of the maximum temperature, what kind of people it is suitable for, and what materials are guaranteed to be harmless.
ref: Because he found that feet bath basin, which has been popular for a long time, still has no explicit and detailed industry regulations on the setting of the maximum temperature, suitable crowd, what materials are safe to use, etc.

src: 但是一般情况下足浴盆是不会有带电问题的，但也不排除少数产品在出厂时没有严格把关。
mt: However, under normal circumstances, there will be no electrification problem in the foot bath, but it does not rule out that a few products are not strictly checked when they leave the factory.
ref: But normally feet bath basin shouldn’t be electrified, however we can’t rule out the fact that a few products might not have been strictly checked before leaving the factory.

src: 因此在在购买的时候选择分体式的足浴盆。
mt: Therefore, choose a split foot bath when buying.
ref: Therefore, choose split type feet bath basin.

src: 水电分离，没有任何安全隐患。
mt: Water and electricity are separated without any potential safety hazards.
ref: There is no safety risk when water and electricity are separated.

src: 同时你可以随便拿电笔测。

ref: Meanwhile, you can use a tester to test it.

ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。

mt: When you go to the store, fill in your name and phone number and then choose your clothes. You can choose your wedding dress. It is quite patient to change three or four sets of clothes. After choosing, you have made up for a long time, and your service attitude is good. The later shooting will teach you how to pose, that is, the face is so big. It takes half a month to refine and it will be sent in three or four days. It feels like it is no different from the original film.
ref: After I arrived at the store, I filled in my name and chose the outfits; all the wedding dresses were available to be chosen; I tried on three or four outfits and they were quite patient; after I decided on the dress, they were doing my makeup for a long time and they were also nice during this time; later in the shoot, they would teach you how to pose; I felt my face was too big on the photo; they said detailed editing would take a month, but they sent them to me after three to four days, and they seemed not that different from the original photos.

mt: [Experience] Maybe the shape is a little too much. The original double eyelids were pasted with three eyelids.
ref: [Experience] Maybe the style was a little too much, double eyelids turned into triple eyelids.

mt: The tail of the eyebrow has also been shaved, which is a little embarrassing for those who do not thrush.
ref: The tail of my eyebrow got shaved, and it was a little awkward for those who don’t wear makeup normally.

src: 照片十来天给了，但是P图效果不怎么满意，感觉双眼皮贴那些还是很明显。
mt: The photos have been given for more than ten days, but the effect of the P picture is not very satisfactory. I feel that the double eyelids are still very obvious.
ref: The photos were sent to me after about ten days, but I was not very satisfied with the photoshop effect, and I feel that the double eyelids tapes are still obvious.

ref: I tried on two outfits because I didn’t know what style to choose, and I ended up choosing the black suit after trying hesitating; the young lady said it was a vintage Audrey Hepburn style.

src: 弄好妆发后就开始拍照了 摄影师全程都有指挥我摆姿势 过程很轻松和谐

src: 拍完后认真选了四张最喜欢的当精修 小哥哥说15内成片 结局非常心满意足～
mt: After shooting, I carefully selected four of my favorite pictures when the finishing brother said that the ending of the film within 15 years was very satisfied ~
ref: After the photoshoot, I chose my four favorite ones to be retouched, and the guy said the photos would be completed within 15 days and I was really satisfied with the results~

src: 这个电梯也是很无语，跟有那大病一样，负二到负一，来回折腾，不停我按的这一层，从安全通道下去到一楼，也是很无语，直接通到一个家具店，家具店关门，安全通道出不去!
mt: This elevator is also very speechless, just like the serious illness, negative two to negative one, tossing back and forth, I keep pressing this floor, going down from the safe passage to the first floor, it is also very speechless, directly leading to a furniture store, the furniture store is closed, the safe passage can't get out!
ref: This elevator really makes people speechless; it went back and forth from B2 to B1 and did not stop on my floor, and it was ridiculous that when I went to the 1st floor from fire escape, it led to a furniture store which was closed, so I couldn’t get out from the fire escape, either!

src: 环境：说实话店里面积大，有8～9层，家里想买的家具、家用电器、各种小东西……，都能买到，好多名牌商家都入驻在店里，慕思、欧派、华帝、老板、峰创之家、汉斯顿、雅克、友邦、丝涟、富品居、万家乐、大自然、中联、美的、雅丹……，品牌真的是太多了，我只能记得这么多了，是购买产品的好去处，逛累了可以坐在沙发上休息休息哦。

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。

ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This time is when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I really have a heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage, or respiratory arrest, then the window of our lives is only four minutes, four minutes of gold!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So the people around you know how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls down, we can use professional knowledge to rescue him, rather than standing there stupidly motionless and unable to do anything. This feeling of helplessness is too terrifying.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: “In China, our official data shows that three million people die unexpectedly every year. The most dangerous is cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, an average of 15% can be rescued.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In Las Vegas casinos and hotels, 70 or 80% can be rescued, while Shanghai and Beijing are less than 1%. ”
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, the founder of the first reaction, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has a cardiac arrest, his breathing is gone, and his heartbeat is gone, it is useless for you to pinch him.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: Artificial breathing and chest compressions must be performed to save people.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I found that few of us still have the awareness to learn first aid, but when something happens, it's too late, so I still call on everyone to learn this skill so that we can respond in time when facing emergencies.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: Maybe it can save a person's life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: The first aid certificate can be registered at your local Red Cross Training center. I registered at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai. There are discounts for students.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is to record the goals I want to complete before the age of 25. Adding the first aid certificate to the goal list was also a few months ago, but it was indeed completed!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Then I'm going to take other certificates I want to take. I plan to take a diving certificate. I saw in Xiaohongshu that there is also a diving first aid certificate. It seems that you have to have a first aid certificate to take the test, so in fact, the first aid certificate is still very useful!
ref: Next, I will apply for other certificates; I plan to get Diving Certificate; I saw on Red earlier that there is a Diving First Aid Certificate, which requires a Certificate of First Aid first, so getting a Certificate of First Aid is useful!

src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。
mt: Yixin inspection well block brick machine equipment is widely used in new masonry materials for municipal underground structures such as coal, heat, water, electricity, and gas.
ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: various inspection wells, rainwater outlets, square ditches, septic tanks and small structures for drainage and water storage facilities, bridge wing walls, etc.
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper, lower, left and right sides of the modules are all concave-convex groove structures, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shear resistance of the well wall is far better than that of the masonry form of flat friction masonry.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure. After the combination of masonry, the longitudinal holes are interlinked and the transverse holes intersect. After the hole core is poured, a cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed, which plays a secondary reinforcing and waterproof role.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The module is equipped with ribs in both vertical and horizontal directions, and the horizontal and vertical ribs increase the overall strength of the structure accordingly.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, inspection wells and drainage wells built with concrete inspection well modules are not easy to collapse, sink, and leak. The mechanical properties of the well wall modules are stable, the operation is simple, and the forming size is standard.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备智能控制配备数据输入、输出装置一键通触摸式液晶显示监控机械操作全部过程，实现理想的人机对话、自动分析比料、密度运转、安全逻辑控制及故障诊断系统。
mt: The intelligent control of the concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment is equipped with data input and output devices, one-button touch-type LCD display to monitor the entire process of mechanical operation, and realize the ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis and material ratio, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械液压系统采用单缸液压、输送，双缸液压、输送。
mt: The mechanical hydraulic system of the well wall module adopts single-cylinder hydraulic and conveying, and double-cylinder hydraulic and conveying.
ref: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.

src: 独立的液压集成站，避免了由于主机振动对液压系统的影响，从而保证液压系统工作的可靠性。
mt: The independent hydraulic integration station avoids the impact of the vibration of the host on the hydraulic system, thereby ensuring the reliability of the hydraulic system.
ref: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备布料箱行进模箱脱模上升，储料箱门关闭，自动输送托板，全部由液压系统独立完成，从而达到减少机械的磨损和维修。
mt: The concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment cloth box, the mold box, the mold release box rises, the storage box door is closed, and the pallet is automatically transported, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system, so as to reduce mechanical wear and maintenance.
ref: In the concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, the fabric box proceeding box de-molds and lifts, the storage box door closes, and the supporting plate is transported automatically, all of which are independently completed by the hydraulic system so as to reduce mechanical abrasion and times of repair.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备采用进口电脑、电器，密封件液压件，准保设备综合性能稳定可靠。
mt: The concrete inspection well module brick machine equipment adopts imported computers, electrical appliances, seals and hydraulic parts to ensure that the overall performance of the equipment is stable and reliable.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment is composed by imported computer and appliances, as well as sealing elements and hydraulic element to ensure stable and reliable comprehensive performance.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振平台采用整体板钢，台面线切割合模无焊接点，使填料箱自由摆动导向，充分减少机械磨损。
mt: The mechanical excitation platform of the well wall module adopts integral plate steel, and the countertop wire cutting and clamping has no welding points, so that the packing box can swing freely and guide, fully reducing mechanical wear.
ref: The integral steel plate is adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical vibration platform, with no welding points of wire-electrode cutting mold closing of mesa, so that the stuffing box can swing and orient freely to greatly reduce mechanical abrasion.

src: 使模具负荷减少、填料并二合一加密振幅，采用一体化、全同步，台振、模振，确保达到振实效果。
mt: The mold load is reduced, the packing is combined with the two-in-one encrypted amplitude, and the integrated, fully synchronous, taiwan vibration and mold vibration are used to ensure that the vibration effect is achieved.
ref: It reduces loads of molds and reinforces vibration; integrated and full synchronization are adopted for vibration of the platform and the molds to ensure the vibration effect.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械激振机械、电脑自动控制振幅根据原料性价比调节振幅，无磨损制动，从而延长使用寿命，降低成本。
mt: The mechanical excitation machinery and computer automatic control of the well wall module automatically adjust the amplitude according to the cost performance of the raw material, and brake without wear, thereby extending the service life and reducing costs.

src: 国际橄榄油协会将橄榄油分为初榨橄榄油（Virgin Olive Oil）和精炼橄榄油（Lampante Olive Oil或Refined Olive Oil）两大类，五个级别。
mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil (Virgin Olive Oil) and Refined Olive Oil (Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil), with five levels.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is the oil obtained directly from fresh olive fruits by mechanical cold pressing, filtering and other treatments to remove foreign objects.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：
mt: According to the different acidity, it can be divided into three levels：
ref: There are three levels according to acidity:

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra Virgin olive oil (Extra Virgin): It is the highest grade and highest quality olive oil, and it is a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。
mt: The taste is excellent, with an elegant and pleasant plant fragrance, and the acidity does not exceed 1%.
ref: It has premium taste, a slight and pleasant plant fragrance and a acidity of less than 1%.

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。
mt: High-quality virgin olive oil (Fine Virgin): the acidity is slightly higher, but not more than 2%, and the taste is pure and aromatic.
ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。
mt: Ordinary Virgin olive oil (Ordinary Virgin): The taste and flavor are acceptable, and the acidity does not exceed 3.3%.
ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil obtained after refining virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or it becomes a “secondary oil”.
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：
mt: Refined olive oil can be divided into two levels：
ref: Refined Olive Oil can be divided into two categories:

src: 普通橄榄油（Olive Oil）：精炼橄榄油与一定比例的初榨橄榄油混合，以调和味道与颜色，其酸度在1.5%以下，呈透明的淡金黄色。
mt: Ordinary olive oil (Olive Oil): Refined olive oil is mixed with a certain proportion of virgin olive oil to reconcile the taste and color. Its acidity is below 1.5% and it is transparent and light golden yellow.
ref: Olive Oil: is refined olive oil mixed with virgin olive oil in a certain proportion to adjust the taste and color, has an acidity of under 1.5% and a transparent light gold color.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。
mt: Refined olive impurity oil or Olive Pomace Oil (Refined Olive-Pomace Oil): It is olive oil extracted from the oil residue by dissolution method and refined.
ref: Refined Olive-Pomace Oil is olive oil obtained and refined from pomace with dissolution method.

src: 看过等级分类的你应该已经发现，橄榄油的酸度是一个非常重要的指标。
mt: If you have read the grade classification, you should have found that the acidity of olive oil is a very important indicator.
ref: After reading the classification, you may find the acidity of olive oil is an important index.

src: 要知道，橄榄果就好像酿制葡萄酒的葡萄一样，来自不同的产区、不同橄榄果品种的橄榄果，就会出产不同标准的橄榄油。
mt: You know, olive fruits are just like grapes for making wine. Olive fruits from different regions and different olive fruit varieties will produce different standards of olive oil.
ref: You should know that olives are just like grapes that make wine, olives from different producing areas and different types of olives will produce olive oil of different standards.

src: 油橄榄的最佳生长地：
mt: The best place to grow olives：
ref: The best growing area of olives:

src: 地中海沿岸具有油橄榄生长所需的最适宜的土壤和气温、日照、空气湿度以及降水量等气候条件。
mt: The Mediterranean coast has the most suitable soil and climatic conditions such as temperature, sunshine, air humidity, and precipitation required for olive growth.
ref: The Mediterranean coastal area has the most suitable soil, temperature, sunshine, air humidity, precipitation and other weather conditions for olive growth.

src: 除地中海沿岸外，其它地区只能在适生区零星种植。
mt: Except for the Mediterranean coast, other areas can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas.
ref: Aside from the Mediterranean costal area, olives can only be planted sporadically in suitable areas in other areas.

src: 主要产区产地（地中海）：
mt: Main production area (Mediterranean Sea)：
ref: Main producing areas (the Mediterranean):

src: 意大利、西班牙、希腊、土耳其、葡萄牙、摩洛哥、叙利亚、以色列、突尼斯、阿尔及利亚、埃及、巴基斯坦、黎巴嫩等等，与其气候类似的也有远在南纬度的阿根廷、秘鲁、南非等等。
mt: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and similar climates are Argentina, Peru, South Africa and so on at far southern latitudes.
ref: Italy, Spain, Greece, Turkey, Portugal, Morocco, Syria, Israel, Tunisia, Algeria, Egypt, Pakistan, Lebanon, etc., and Argentina, Peru, South Africa, etc., which are far away in the southern latitude and have similar climate.

src: 油橄榄的采摘月份：
mt: Olive picking month：
ref: Picking time of olives:

src: 每年的3至6月，是油橄榄树开花坐果的时间，7至10月果实开始发育并且成熟，果实从绿色过渡到红色，紫色，最后变黑。
mt: Every year from March to June, it is the time for olive trees to bloom and bear fruit. From July to October, the fruits begin to develop and mature, and the fruits transition from green to red, purple, and finally black.
ref: March to June each year is the time for olive trees to blossom and bear fruit, and from July to October, the fruit begins to develop and ripen, and the color of fruit will transition from green to red, purple and finally black.

src: 11月至次年2月是果实的采摘季节（橄榄油的新鲜度可是很重要的哦）。
mt: November to February of the following year is the fruit picking season (the freshness of olive oil is very important).
ref: November to February of next year is the picking time of fruit (the freshness of olive oil is very important).

src: 橄榄油的营养成分：
mt: Nutrients of olive oil：
ref: Nutrients of olive oil:

src: 橄榄油富含丰富的单不饱和脂肪酸，即油酸及亚油酸、亚麻酸，还有维生素A、维生素B、维生素D、维生素E、维生素K及抗氧化物等。
mt: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, as well as vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.
ref: Olive oil is rich in monounsaturated fatty acids, namely oleic acid, linoleic acid, linolenic acid, vitamin A, vitamin B, vitamin D, vitamin E, vitamin K and antioxidants.

src: 橄榄油被认为是迄今所发现的油脂中最适合人体营养的油。
mt: Olive oil is considered to be the most suitable oil for human nutrition among the oils found so far.
ref: Olive oil is deemed the most suitable oil for human nutrition among all the oils found so far.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法是什么？

ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。
mt: Everyone has different hobbies. Some people like to collect, some people like food, and of course some people like wine tasting. Red brand whiskey is currently one of the best-selling Scotch whiskies in various countries, and red brand whiskey has won the gold medal in the International Wine Competition.
ref: Different people have different preferences; some like to collect, some like food, and certainly some like wine tasting; Johnnie Walker Red Label is one of the fastest selling Scottish whiskies in the world and has won the gold prize of International Wine Competition.

src: 每一瓶红牌威士忌都有独特的味道，不过如果不知道如何品味它，岂不是糟蹋了它的醇香。
mt: Every bottle of red brand whiskey has a unique taste, but if you don't know how to taste it, wouldn't it ruin its mellow fragrance?
ref: Each bottle of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky has its own unique flavor, but if you don’t know how to taste it, it would be such a waste of its mellow fragrance.

src: 那么红牌威士忌怎么喝呢？
mt: So how do you drink red brand whiskey?
ref: Then how do we drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 小编为大家简单介绍下。
mt: Xiaobian will give you a brief introduction.
ref: I’ll introduce for you now.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法：
mt: How to drink red brand whiskey：
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky:

src: 尊尼获加红牌威士忌由约35种苏格兰威士忌调配而成，具有浓郁芳香及传统苏格兰威士忌的特质，浓郁芳香中带有甘甜及烟熏香味。
mt: Johnnie Walker Red Brand Whiskey is blended from about 35 kinds of Scotch whiskies. It has a rich aroma and the characteristics of traditional Scotch Whiskies. The rich aroma has sweet and smoky aromas.
ref: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended with around 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, possesses rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

src: 入口浓醇清新，略带香草及浓烈的烟熏麦芽味道。
mt: The entrance is mellow and fresh, with a slight vanilla and strong smoky malt flavor.
ref: It is mellow and fresh in the mouth, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.

src: 该酒可以直接加冰饮用，或者与最喜爱的饮品混合饮用。
mt: The wine can be drunk directly with ice, or mixed with your favorite drink.
ref: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: Red-brand whiskey has entered the country. In order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, sparkling drinks such as red-brand whiskey + Coke or Sprite or Sunkist have become an enduring fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: In addition to neutralizing the sour taste, these sweet drinks can visually bring pleasure to people. Adding drinks can dilute the taste of the wine and change the taste.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Red brand whiskey + sliced lemon + sugar cube (granulated sugar is also available) is the most authentic and traditional way to drink.
ref: Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.

src: 正宗的红方威味道有些酸涩,加入糖可以中和其中的酸味,柠檬则会给酒带来清新的香味,当然,甜酸度可根据个人的口味爱好调配。
mt: The authentic Hongfangwei taste is a bit sour. Adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, while lemon will bring a fresh fragrance to the wine. Of course, the sweetness and acidity can be adjusted according to personal tastes and hobbies.
ref: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour; adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, lemon will bring fresh fragrance to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and sourness can be adjusted according to personal tastes.

src: 以上三种都是红牌威士忌的最好喝法，大家可以作为参考尝试下，希望小编的介绍可以帮助到大家。
mt: The above three are the best ways to drink red brand whiskey. You can try it as a reference. I hope Xiaobian's introduction can help you.
ref: The above are the best drinking methods of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky for your refence, and I hope my introduction can help you.

src: “在带电的水里泡脚，实在太危险了吧!”

src: 李先生告诉记者，近日，他买了一个足浴盆送给父亲做生日礼物，可是父亲泡脚时却感觉脚底发麻。
mt: Mr. Li told reporters that recently, he bought a foot bath for his father as a birthday gift, but when his father soaked his feet, he felt numb on the soles of his feet.
ref: Mr. Li told reporter that he recently bought a feet bath basin for his father as a birthday present, but his father felt that the bottom of his feet were numb when using it.

src: 李先生一开始以为是足浴盆的振动功能引起的，没想到关了振动功能，父亲还是感觉到脚底麻麻的。
mt: Mr. Li thought it was caused by the vibration function of the foot bath at first, but he didn't expect that when the vibration function was turned off, his father still felt numb on the soles of his feet.
ref: Mr. Li first thought it was caused by the vibration function of the feet bath basin, and it was unexpected that his father still felt his feet were numb after turning off the vibration function.

src: 李先生用电笔一试，电笔居然亮了，李先生惊讶地发现足浴盆的水里居然带电。
mt: Mr. Li tried it with an electric pen, and the electric pen turned on. Mr. Li was surprised to find that the water in the foot bath was actually charged.
ref: Mr. Li used a tester and the light on it was on; it was to Mr. Li’s surprise that the water in the feet bath basin was electrified.

src: 后来他联络了商家，商家的态度还不错，尽管退掉了足浴盆，李先生依然感到不快。
mt: Later, he contacted the merchant, and the merchant's attitude was not bad. Although he returned the foot bath, Mr. Li still felt unhappy.
ref: Then he contacted the seller, whose attitude was nice, but Mr. Li still felt upset although he had returned it.

src: 因为他发现这个已经流行已久的足浴盆如今在最高温度的设定、适用于何种人群、何种材料保证无害等方面都没有一个明确详细的行业规定。
mt: Because he found that this foot bath, which has been popular for a long time, now does not have a clear and detailed industry regulation on the setting of the highest temperature, what kind of people it is suitable for, and what materials are guaranteed to be harmless.
ref: Because he found that feet bath basin, which has been popular for a long time, still has no explicit and detailed industry regulations on the setting of the maximum temperature, suitable crowd, what materials are safe to use, etc.

src: 但是一般情况下足浴盆是不会有带电问题的，但也不排除少数产品在出厂时没有严格把关。

ref: Address: HSR North One Road, Bayishake District, convenient transportation, big parking lot free during the day.

src: 环境：说实话店里面积大，有8～9层，家里想买的家具、家用电器、各种小东西……，都能买到，好多名牌商家都入驻在店里，慕思、欧派、华帝、老板、峰创之家、汉斯顿、雅克、友邦、丝涟、富品居、万家乐、大自然、中联、美的、雅丹……，品牌真的是太多了，我只能记得这么多了，是购买产品的好去处，逛累了可以坐在沙发上休息休息哦。
mt: Environment: To be honest, the store has a large area, with 8 to 9 floors. You can buy furniture, household appliances, all kinds of small things you want to buy at home... Many famous brand merchants have settled in the store, Mousse, Opai, Vantage, Boss, Fengchuang's House, Hanston, Jacques, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, Wanshu, Nature, Zhonglian, Midea, Yadan..., There are really too many brands, I can only remember so many, it is a good place to buy products, you can sit on the sofa when you are tired of shopping. Take a break.
ref: Environment: Honestly, the store is large with 8-9 floors, where you can buy all the furniture, household appliances and small things your home needs, and many famous brands have settled in the store, such as DeRUCCI, OPPEIN, VATTI, Robam, Fengchuang Home, Hunsdon, Yake, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, GUANGDONG MACRO, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, and so many other brands, I can only remember so many; it is a good place to buy products, and you can sit on the couch and have a rest if you get tired.

src: 最近想买一套舒适的沙发，朋友说这里有好多沙发可以选，看了顾家家居、美克美家的，感觉还可以，就是价格略贵，所以还在纠结中
mt: Recently, I wanted to buy a comfortable sofa. My friend said that there are many sofas to choose from. After looking at Gujia Home Furnishing and Meike Meijia, I feel it's okay, but the price is slightly expensive, so I'm still struggling.
ref: I recently want to buy a couch and my friend said there was a lot of couch to choose from here; I looked at Kuka Home and Markor Furnishings, and I felt they were okay but a little expensive, so I am still struggling to decide.

src: 大众点评乌鲁木齐家居卖场频道为您提供高铁居然之家地址，电话，营业时间等最新商户信息，找装修公司，就上大众点评
mt: Volkswagen Dianping Urumqi Home Furnishing Channel provides you with the latest merchant information such as the address, telephone number, and business hours of the high-speed rail home. If you find a decoration company, you can go to Volkswagen Dianping.
ref: Dianping Urumqi Renovation and Design Channel will provide you with the address, phone number, operation time and other information of HSR Easyhome, and please come to Dianping if you are looking for a renovation company.

src: 觉得很有意义的一本证书——急救证
mt: A certificate that I think is very meaningful - first aid certificate
ref: A certificate I deem meaningful, Certificate of First Aid

src: 这是我除了驾驶证之外一本觉得重要的技能证书之一！
mt: This is one of the skill certificates that I think are important in addition to my driver's license!
ref: I think this is one of the most important skill type certificate except for driving license!

src: 普及一下：急救措施其实是做发生突发事件时候的应急救援，即在救护车来之前的抢救。
mt: Popularize it: first aid measures are actually emergency rescue in case of emergencies, that is, rescue before the ambulance arrives.
ref: For your information: first aid measures refer to emergency rescue in emergencies, i.e., emergency treatment conducted before the coming of the ambulance.

src: 众所周知，在事故发生后救护车来的过程中其实是还有一段时间的，而正是这段时间才是最关键的。
mt: As we all know, there is still a period of time before the ambulance arrives after the accident, and it is this period of time that is the most critical.
ref: As everyone knows, there is a period before the coming of the ambulance after the accident happens, which is most critical.

src: 这个时候便是需要急救的时候。
mt: This is when first aid is needed.
ref: This period is the most important time for first aid.

src: 如果我真的发生了心脏病、脑溢血、呼吸骤停，那么我们生命的窗口只有四分钟，黄金四分钟！
mt: If I really have heart disease, cerebral hemorrhage, respiratory arrest, then the window of our life is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!
ref: If we suffer from heart attack, cerebral hemorrhage or respiratory arrest, our life window is only four minutes, the golden four minutes!

src: 所以身边的人懂得急救是多么重要呀！
mt: So the people around you know how important first aid is!
ref: So it is very important for those around us to know first aid!

src: 当我们身边有人倒下的时候，我们可以通过专业的知识去对他进行抢救，而不是傻傻地站在那里一动不动什么也做不了，这种无助的感觉太让人感到可怕了。
mt: When someone around us falls, we can rescue him through professional knowledge, instead of standing there and doing nothing. This feeling of helplessness is terrible.
ref: When somebody falls down, we can conduct first aid with our professional knowledge, instead of doing nothing and only standing there; this helpless feeling is really frightening.

src: “在中国，我们官方数据每年有三百万人意外死亡，最危险的叫心脏骤停。
mt: "In China, according to our official data, three million people die unexpectedly every year, and the most dangerous one is cardiac arrest.
ref: “In China, 3 million people die from accidents every year according to official data, and the most dangerous one is known as cardiac arrest.

src: 在美国全国是平均15%能救过来。
mt: In the United States, an average of 15% can be saved.
ref: 15% of people of cardiac arrest can be brought back to life in the United States.

src: 在拉斯维加斯的赌场酒店，百分之七八十能救过来，上海、北京低于1%。”
mt: In Las Vegas casino hotels, 70% or 80% can be saved, and less than 1% in Shanghai and Beijing. "
ref: In the Casino Hotel in Las Vegas, 70% or 80% of them can be brought back to life, and the proportion in Shanghai and Beijing is lower than 1%. ”

src: 这是第一反应创始人陆乐说的。
mt: This is what Lu Le, the founder of first reaction, said.
ref: Said Lu Le, the founder of the First Reaction.

src: 如果一个人发生了心脏骤停，呼吸没有了，心跳没有了，你掐人中是没有任何作用的。
mt: If a person has a sudden cardiac arrest, his breathing and heartbeat are gone, there is no effect in pinching him.
ref: Pinching philtrum has no effect at all if a person suffers from cardiac arrest and there is no sign of breathing or heartbeat.

src: 必须做人工呼吸、胸外按压才有可能把人救过来。
mt: Artificial respiration and chest compression are necessary to save people.
ref: Artificial respiration and external chest compression are required to bring them back to life.

src: 我发现我们现在还很少人会有这种意识去学习急救，但是当事情发生的时候就来不及了，所以还是呼吁大家都去学习一下这个技能，让我们在面对突发状况的时候能够及时作出反应。
mt: I found that few of us have this awareness to learn first aid now, but it's too late when things happen, so I still call on everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond in time in the face of emergencies.
ref: I found that very few people have the awareness to study first aid knowledge, but it will be too late once accident happens; therefore, I appeal to everyone to learn this skill, so that we can respond timely when faced with emergency situations.

src: 说不定还能挽救一个人的生命！
mt: Maybe it can save a person's life!
ref: We may bring somebody back to life with this skill!

src: 急救证可以在你们当地的红十字会培训中心报名，我是在珠海的红十字会培训中心报名的，学生还有优惠呢。
mt: The first aid certificate can be registered at your local Red Cross training center. I signed up at the Red Cross training center in Zhuhai. Students still have discounts.
ref: People can apply for the certificate of first aid at your local Red Cross Training Center, and I applied for my certificate at the Red Cross Training Center in Zhuhai; students are offered with a discount.

src: PS：最后一张图是记录自己25岁前要完成的目标的，把急救证加入目标清单也是几个月前的事情，但是确实是完成了呀！
mt: PS: The last picture is to record the goals to be completed before the age of 25. It was a few months ago to add the first aid certificate to the goal list, but it was really completed!
ref: PS: The last picture is the goals I aim to achieve before 25 years old; I added the Certificate of First Aid a couple months ago, but I did achieve it!

src: 接着要去考其他想考的证书了，打算去考个潜水证，之前在小红书看到还有个潜水急救证，考这个证好像还得有急救证才可以去考，所以其实急救证还是很有用的！
mt: Then I'm going to take an examination of other certificates I want to take an examination of. I plan to take an examination of a diving certificate. I saw a diving first aid certificate in Xiaohongshu before. It seems that I have to have a first aid certificate to take an examination of this certificate, so in fact, the first aid certificate is still very useful!
ref: Next, I will apply for other certificates; I plan to get Diving Certificate; I saw on Red earlier that there is a Diving First Aid Certificate, which requires a Certificate of First Aid first, so getting a Certificate of First Aid is useful!

src: 检查井混凝土模块生产加工设备 郑州井壁砖模块设备介绍：
mt: Inspection well concrete module production and processing equipment Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment introduction:
ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, introduction to Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment:

src: 郑州宜欣是国内混凝土检查井模块砖机设备，检查井砌块机械，井壁墙体模块机械专业的生产厂家，从半自动到全自动化生产线。
mt: Zhengzhou Yixin is a professional manufacturer of concrete manhole module brick machine equipment, manhole block machinery and shaft wall module machinery in China, from semi-automatic to fully automated production lines.
ref: Zhengzhou Yixin is a specialized manufacturer of concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment, inspection shaft building block machinery and shaft wall module equipment, with semi-automatic and automatic production lines.

src: 通过多年的实践和开发，现具备了质量过硬，主要生产液压式、移动式、全自动化检查井系列设备及配套装置。
mt: Through years of practice and development, we now have excellent quality, mainly producing hydraulic, mobile and fully automated inspection well series equipment and supporting devices.
ref: Based on practice and development of many years, it is engaged in production of high quality hydraulic type, mobile type and automatic inspection shaft series of equipment and supporting devices.

src: 检查井混凝土模块生产加工设备 郑州井壁砖模块设备组装现场：
mt: Inspection well concrete module production and processing equipment Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment assembly site:
ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the assembly site for Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment

src: 检查井混凝土模块生产加工设备 郑州井壁砖模块设备的特点及优势:
mt: Inspection well concrete module production and processing equipment characteristics and advantages of Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment:
ref: Inspection shaft concrete module production and processing equipment, the characteristics and advantages of Zhengzhou shaft wall brick module equipment

src: 宜欣检查井砌块砖机设备广泛适用于煤、热、水、电、气等市政地下构筑物的新型砌筑材料。
mt: Yixin manhole block brick machine equipment is widely used as new masonry materials for municipal underground structures such as coal, heat, water, electricity, gas, etc.
ref: Yixin inspection shaft module brick equipment is widely applied in new-type masonry materials for municipal underground structures for coal, heating, electricity and gas.

src: 如：排水、储水设施的各类检查井、雨水口、方沟、化粪池及小型构筑物、桥梁翼墙等。
mt: Such as: various inspection wells, rainwater inlets, square ditches, septic tanks, small structures, bridge wing walls, etc. of drainage and water storage facilities.
ref: Foe example: various types of inspection shafts, gutter inlets, box drains, septic tanks, small-sized structures and wing walls of bridges for drainage and water storage facilities.

src: 使用混凝土模块筑建检查井的优势在于模块的上下左右四周均为凹凸槽结构，组合砌筑形成链锁。
mt: The advantage of using concrete modules to build inspection wells is that the upper, lower, left and right sides of the modules are concave convex groove structures, and the combined masonry forms a chain lock.
ref: The advantage of building inspection shafts using concrete modules is that the four sides of the modules are of concave groove structures, which are built to form chain locks.

src: 井壁墙体抗剪力远优于平摩擦砌体的砌筑形式。
mt: The shear resistance of shaft wall is much better than that of flat friction masonry.
ref: The shearing resistance of the shaft wall is far better than the masonry form of the flat friction of the brickwork.

src: 模块为中空结构，组合砌筑后纵向孔孔相通，横向孔孔相贯，孔芯浇注后，形成现浇混凝土网状结构，起到了二次补强和防水作用。
mt: The module is a hollow structure. After the combined masonry, the longitudinal holes are connected, and the horizontal holes are connected. After the hole core is poured, the cast-in-place concrete network structure is formed, which plays a role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.
ref: The modules are of hollow structure, with connected holes vertically and interpenetrated horizontally; the cast-in-place concrete mesh structure is formed after pouring of the cores of holes, playing the role of secondary reinforcement and waterproof.

src: 模块纵横均设有插筋槽，横向卧筋、纵向插筋相应提高结构整体强度。
mt: The module is provided with joint bar slots vertically and horizontally, and the horizontal and longitudinal joint bars correspondingly improve the overall strength of the structure.
ref: The joint bar grooves are equipped for modules vertically and horizontally; the horizontal and vertical joint bars can improve the overall strength of the structure.

src: 另外使用混凝土检查井模块砌筑出来的检查井、排水井不容易出现坍塌，下沉，漏水等现象，井壁墙体模块机械性能稳定，操作简单，成形尺寸标准。
mt: In addition, the inspection well and drainage well built with concrete inspection well module are not easy to collapse, sink, leak and other phenomena. The shaft wall module has stable mechanical performance, simple operation and standard forming size.
ref: In addition, phenomena such as collapse, sink or water leakage are rare in the inspection shafts and pumping shafts laid with concrete inspection shaft modules, with stable mechanical performance in shaft wall modules, easy operation and standard forming size.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备智能控制配备数据输入、输出装置一键通触摸式液晶显示监控机械操作全部过程，实现理想的人机对话、自动分析比料、密度运转、安全逻辑控制及故障诊断系统。
mt: The intelligent control of brick machine equipment of concrete manhole module is equipped with data input and output devices. One touch LCD monitors the whole process of mechanical operation, realizing the ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis and comparison, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.
ref: The concrete inspection shaft module brick equipment can automatically control the input and output of the configured data, and the one-key contact crystal display can monitor all the process of mechanical operation to realize ideal man-machine dialogue, automatic analysis on materials, density operation, safety logic control and fault diagnosis system.

src: 井壁墙体模块机械液压系统采用单缸液压、输送，双缸液压、输送。
mt: The mechanical hydraulic system of shaft wall module adopts single cylinder hydraulic pressure and transmission, and double cylinder hydraulic pressure and transmission.
ref: Single-cylinder and double-cylinder hydraulic pressure and transportation are adopted for the shaft wall module mechanical and hydraulic system.

src: 独立的液压集成站，避免了由于主机振动对液压系统的影响，从而保证液压系统工作的可靠性。
mt: The independent hydraulic integrated station avoids the influence of the main engine vibration on the hydraulic system, so as to ensure the reliability of the hydraulic system.
ref: The independent hydraulic integration station is utilized to avoid the influences on the hydraulic system caused by vibration of the master so as to ensure reliability of the operation of the hydraulic system.

src: 混凝土检查井模块砖机设备布料箱行进模箱脱模上升，储料箱门关闭，自动输送托板，全部由液压系统独立完成，从而达到减少机械的磨损和维修。

mt: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories: virgin olive oil and refined olive oil, with five levels.
ref: The International Olive Oil Association divides olive oil into two categories, Virgin Olive Oil and Lampante Olive Oil or Refined Olive Oil, and five levels.

src: 初榨橄榄油或称为天然橄榄油，是直接从新鲜的橄榄果实中采取机械冷榨、经过过滤等处理除去异物后得到的油脂。
mt: Virgin olive oil, or natural olive oil, is the oil obtained directly from fresh olive fruits by mechanical cold pressing and filtering to remove foreign matters.
ref: Virgin olive oil, also known as natural olive oil, is oil obtained from fresh olive fruit after removing foreign matters by mechanical cold pressing and filtering.

src: 根据酸度的不同可分为三个级别：

src: 特级初榨橄榄油（Extra Virgin）：是最高级别、质量最高的橄榄油，是纯天然产品。
mt: Extra virgin olive oil: it is the highest grade and highest quality olive oil, and it is a pure natural product.
ref: Extra Virgin: is the highest level, best quality olive oil, a pure natural product.

src: 口味绝佳，有淡雅怡人的植物芬芳，酸度不超过1%。

src: 优质初榨橄榄油（Fine Virgin）：酸度稍高，但不超过2%，味道纯正、芳香。

ref: Fine Virgin: has a slightly higher acidity of less than 2%, tastes pure and aromatic.

src: 普通初榨橄榄油（Ordinary Virgin）：口味与风味尚可，酸度不超过3.3%。

ref: Ordinary Virgin: taste and flavor are acceptable, with an acidity of no more than 3.3%.

src: 精炼橄榄油是指酸度超过3.3%的初榨橄榄油精炼后所得到的橄榄油，或成为“二次油”。
mt: Refined olive oil refers to the olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of more than 3.3%, or become "secondary oil."
ref: Refined Olive Oil refers to olive oil obtained from the refining of virgin olive oil with an acidity of over 3.3%, also called as “secondary oil”.

src: 精炼橄榄油可分为两个级别：

mt: Olive oil: refined olive oil is mixed with a certain proportion of virgin olive oil to reconcile taste and color. Its acidity is less than 1.5%, showing a transparent light golden yellow.

src: 精炼橄榄杂质油或橄榄果渣油（Refined Olive-Pomace Oil）：是通过溶解法从油渣中提取并经过精炼而得到的橄榄油。

src: 红牌威士忌喝法是什么？
mt: What is the drinking method of red brand whisky?
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 每个人的爱好不同，有人喜欢收藏，有人喜欢美食，当然也有人喜欢品酒，红牌威士忌是目前各个国家最畅销的苏格兰威士忌之一，而且红牌威士忌曾获国际洋酒大赛金奖。
mt: Everyone has different hobbies. Some people like collection, some people like food, and of course, some people like wine tasting. Red brand whisky is one of the best-selling Scotch whiskies in various countries at present, and red brand whisky has won the gold medal in the international wine competition.
ref: Different people have different preferences; some like to collect, some like food, and certainly some like wine tasting; Johnnie Walker Red Label is one of the fastest selling Scottish whiskies in the world and has won the gold prize of International Wine Competition.

src: 每一瓶红牌威士忌都有独特的味道，不过如果不知道如何品味它，岂不是糟蹋了它的醇香。
mt: Every bottle of red brand whisky has a unique taste, but if you don't know how to taste it, you will spoil its mellowness.
ref: Each bottle of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky has its own unique flavor, but if you don’t know how to taste it, it would be such a waste of its mellow fragrance.

src: 那么红牌威士忌怎么喝呢？
mt: So how to drink red brand whisky?
ref: Then how do we drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky?

src: 小编为大家简单介绍下。
mt: Xiaobian will give you a brief introduction.
ref: I’ll introduce for you now.

src: 红牌威士忌喝法：
mt: Red label whisky drinking method:
ref: How to drink Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky:

src: 尊尼获加红牌威士忌由约35种苏格兰威士忌调配而成，具有浓郁芳香及传统苏格兰威士忌的特质，浓郁芳香中带有甘甜及烟熏香味。
mt: Johnnie Walker red whisky is blended from about 35 kinds of Scotch whisky. It has the characteristics of rich aroma and traditional Scotch whisky, with sweet and smoked flavor in the rich aroma.
ref: Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky is blended with around 35 kinds of Scotch Whiskies, possesses rich fragrance and the characteristics of traditional Scotch whisky, with both sweetness and smoked smell in its rich fragrance.

src: 入口浓醇清新，略带香草及浓烈的烟熏麦芽味道。
mt: It tastes mellow and fresh, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.
ref: It is mellow and fresh in the mouth, with a slight taste of vanilla and strong smoked malt.

src: 该酒可以直接加冰饮用，或者与最喜爱的饮品混合饮用。
mt: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with favorite drinks.
ref: The wine can be drunk directly with ice or mixed with your favorite drinks.

src: 红牌威士忌进入国内,为了适应国人的口味,红牌威士忌+可乐或雪碧或新奇士等气泡饮料成为一种经久不衰的时尚。
mt: Red brand whisky has entered China. In order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, red brand whisky + cola or Sprite or Sunkist and other bubble drinks have become an enduring fashion.
ref: After Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky entered China, in order to adapt to the tastes of Chinese people, drinking Red Label whisky with bubble beverage such as Cola, Sprite or Sunkist has become an enduring fashion.

src: 这些甜味的饮料，除了可以中和酸味,在视觉上能给人带来愉悦，加入饮料,起到冲淡酒味改变口感的效果。
mt: In addition to neutralizing the sour taste, these sweet drinks can bring pleasure to people visually. Adding drinks can dilute the wine taste and change the taste.
ref: These sweet drinks not only can neutralize the sour taste, bring pleasure to people visually, but also can dilute the taste of wine and change the overall taste.

src: 红牌威士忌+切片柠檬+方糖(砂糖亦可),是最正宗、最传统的喝法.
mt: Red whisky + sliced lemon + sugar (sugar can also be used), is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.
ref: Red Label whisky + sliced lemon + cube sugar (granulated sugar is also acceptable) is the most authentic and traditional drinking method.

src: 正宗的红方威味道有些酸涩,加入糖可以中和其中的酸味,柠檬则会给酒带来清新的香味,当然,甜酸度可根据个人的口味爱好调配。
mt: The authentic Hongfangwei tastes a little sour. Adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, and lemon will bring fresh flavor to the wine. Of course, the sweetness and acidity can be mixed according to personal taste preferences.
ref: Authentic Red Label whisky tastes a little sour; adding sugar can neutralize the sour taste, lemon will bring fresh fragrance to the wine, and of course, the sweetness and sourness can be adjusted according to personal tastes.

src: 以上三种都是红牌威士忌的最好喝法，大家可以作为参考尝试下，希望小编的介绍可以帮助到大家。
mt: The above three kinds of whisky are the best way to drink red brand whisky. You can try them as a reference. I hope the introduction of Xiaobian can help you.
ref: The above are the best drinking methods of Johnnie Walker Red Label whisky for your refence, and I hope my introduction can help you.

src: 金夫人婚纱摄影(南街店) 暂时还没有分店
mt: Mrs. Kim wedding photography (South Street store) has no branch for the time being

mt: Before taking photos, because we didn't arrange the time well, we changed the time twice. The consultant Lan Lan patiently arranged the time for us.
ref: Because I didn’t arrange my time well before the shoot, I rescheduled twice and consultant Lanlan patiently arranged time for us.

src: 后来选择了一个天气好的周末拍的。

mt: The location was taken in Jiangwan City. Fortunately, the weather was very good that day, and I didn't feel very cold. When taking photos, the makeup artist paid attention to our clothes and headwear from time to time, and immediately helped us tidy up if there was a little bad.
ref: We shot the outdoor scene at Jiangwancheng, and fortunately the weather was nice that day, we didn’t feel cold; during the shoot, makeup artist was paying attention to our clothes, headwear, and made adjustment immediately once there was a problem.

src: 在选照片的时候，因为在网上看到很多案例，不愿意让客人删太多照片，但是我们选照片的时候，真的，一点没有让我们加照片的意思，直接套餐里的24张，一张都没有加（听说和我差不多时间拍婚纱照的表妹，七千多的套餐还加了一万多的照片，当时我就惊呆了，心里也很怕自己会选太多）
mt: When choosing photos, because I saw many cases on the Internet, I didn't want to let guests delete too many photos, but when we chose photos, we really didn't mean to add photos at all. We directly added 24 photos in the set meal, and didn't add any (I heard that my cousin, who took wedding photos in the same time as me, added more than 10000 photos to more than 7000 set meals. At that time, I was stunned and afraid that I would choose too many)
ref: When choosing the photos, I saw many cases online where they wouldn’t let the customers delete too many photos, but they didn’t ask us to add photos at all, just the 24 photos in the set and nothing more (I heard that my cousin who was also taking wedding dress photos added photos worth over 10,000 in addition to the 7,000 yuan set, and I was stunned and feared I might choose too many).

src: 今天照片修好了，兰兰发给我，我看了有两张觉得不太好，他们立刻就帮我重新修了。
mt: Today, the photos were repaired, and LAN LAN sent them to me. I saw two of them and didn't feel very good. They immediately repaired them for me.

src: 大美360集成家装
mt: Da Mei 360 integrated home decoration
ref: Damei 360 Integrated Home Decoration

src: 地 址：环城南路156号幸福家园12楼
mt: Address: 12th floor, happy home, No. 156 Huancheng South Road
ref: Address: Happy Home Building 12, South Ring Road 156

src: 一开始是朋友介绍的因为信任，所以选择来看一下起初我的预算是7万做个基本装修。
mt: At first, it was introduced by a friend. Because of trust, I chose to have a look. At first, my budget was 70000 for basic decoration.
ref: I trusted it because my friend made the recommendation, so I chose to check it out, and originally my budget for a basic decoration was 70,000.

src: 来到店里就开始一系列的骗术。
mt: When I came to the store, I began a series of tricks.
ref: A series of scam began as soon as I came into the store.

src: 我是第一次到店只是给他们看了我的户型图，他们并没有去实地量过房子，他们居然就能给我报价说我的135的房子7万是可以搞定的，大概的给我看了一下他们的材料也并不知道他们是什么品牌的材料。
mt: This is the first time I went to the store. I just showed them my house type map. They didn't go to measure the house on the spot. Unexpectedly, they could quote me that 70000 yuan of my 135 house can be done. They probably showed me their materials and didn't know what brand they were.
ref: When I first came to the store, I showed them my floor plan; although they didn’t really go to my apartment to take the measurement, they said they could do it within 70,000 for my 135 square meters apartment, and they showed me their materials whose brand was unclear.

src: 他们的第二套骗术就是你只要到店就会拖着你把定金交了（而这个钱一旦交了你是永远退不出来，除非你有足够的经历和他们打理论战）。
mt: Their second trick is that as long as you arrive at the store, you will drag you to pay the deposit (and once the money is paid, you will never return it unless you have enough experience to fight with them).
ref: The second scam was forcing you to pay the deposit, which cannot be refunded once paid, unless you have enough experience to reason with them.

src: 我在犹豫要不要交定金的时候，他们就会邀请他们所谓的经理来告诉你，你今天只要把定金交了我们就能给你多少的优惠。
mt: When I hesitate to pay the deposit, they will invite their so-called manager to tell you how much discount we can give you as long as you pay the deposit today.
ref: As I hesitated about whether to pay the deposit, they would invite their so-called manager to tell me that once I paid the deposit on that day, they could give me certain discount.

src: 这个就是一个大坑，我就是活生生被骗的例子，在头脑冲动的时候，交了一万多的定金。
mt: This is a big hole. I am a living example of being cheated. When my mind was impulsive, I paid more than 10000 deposits.
ref: This is a big swindle, and I was a victim who paid a deposit of more than 10,000 when I didn’t really think it through.

src: 他给我的报价有很多问题7万不包括水电改造，不包括任何门和橱柜 浴室，而这三个就是基装的费用大头。
mt: There are many problems in the quotation he gave me. 70000 does not include water and electricity transformation, nor does it include any doors and cabinets. The bathroom, and these three are the bulk of the cost of basic installation.
ref: Their quoted price had a lot of problems; for instance, the 70,000 didn’t include water and electricity renovation, doors, cabinets or bathrooms, and these three take up a large proportion of the cost of basic installation.

src: 除去这些他们的服务点费收的也比其他家公司的高。
mt: Apart from these, their service point fees are also higher than those of other companies.
ref: Apart from these, their service point fee is also higher than that of other companies.

src: 我对这个公司失去了信任，一开始什么都没有讲清楚就让我签合同。
mt: I lost trust in this company and let me sign the contract without making it clear at the beginning.
ref: I’ve lost trust in this company, because they asked me to sign the contract when they didn’t explain anything clearly.

src: 当我去找他们退钱的时候他们表现出很有经验的样子，有专门的小团队来对付你。
mt: When I went to them to refund money, they showed a very experienced appearance, and there was a special small team to deal with you.
ref: When I went to ask for a refund, they acted rather experienced and sent a small team to deal with me.

src: 无论如何都会一口咬死是客户的问题他们全然无责。
mt: It's the customer's problem that they will bite to death in one bite anyway. They are completely irresponsible.
ref: Anyway, they just said it was the client’s problem and they had absolutely no responsibility for it.

src: 各种推卸责任，还有很多细节，不想一一说了都是泪，总之不要选择他们，因为我朋友找他们装修的房子也是质量不好，后期给你算各种费用。

mt: Unexpectedly, the house has a total of 11 floors, from the second floor to the ninth floor. Negative one and negative two are parking places, and parking during the day is free!
ref: There are 11 floors in Easyhome, from B2 to 9th floor, in which B2 and B2 are for parking and parking is free during the day!

src: 周围是真不怎样，饭店五金店寥寥无几，而且饭店味道一般般。
mt: It's really not so good around. There are few hotel hardware stores, and the restaurant tastes so-so.
ref: The surroundings are really not nice, with few restaurants and hardware store, and the food there tasted average.

src: 这个电梯也是很无语，跟有那大病一样，负二到负一，来回折腾，不停我按的这一层，从安全通道下去到一楼，也是很无语，直接通到一个家具店，家具店关门，安全通道出不去!
mt: This elevator is also very speechless. Like the serious illness, it tosses back and forth from minus two to minus one. I keep pressing this floor, and it is also very speechless to go down from the safe passage to the first floor. It directly leads to a furniture store. The furniture store is closed, and the safe passage can't get out!
ref: This elevator really makes people speechless; it went back and forth from B2 to B1 and did not stop on my floor, and it was ridiculous that when I went to the 1st floor from fire escape, it led to a furniture store which was closed, so I couldn’t get out from the fire escape, either!

src: 居然之家还是需要提升，有很多地方都没有开发。
mt: Unexpectedly, the home still needs to be improved, and there are many places that have not been developed.
ref: Easyhome still needs to be improved with a lot of spaces to be developed.

src: 地址：沙依巴克区高铁北一路555号，交通方便，停车场很大，白天还是免费的。
mt: Address: No. 555, North 1st Road, high-speed railway, Saybak District, with convenient transportation and large parking lot, it is free during the day.
ref: Address: HSR North One Road, Bayishake District, convenient transportation, big parking lot free during the day.

src: 环境：说实话店里面积大，有8～9层，家里想买的家具、家用电器、各种小东西……，都能买到，好多名牌商家都入驻在店里，慕思、欧派、华帝、老板、峰创之家、汉斯顿、雅克、友邦、丝涟、富品居、万家乐、大自然、中联、美的、雅丹……，品牌真的是太多了，我只能记得这么多了，是购买产品的好去处，逛累了可以坐在沙发上休息休息哦。
mt: Environment: to be honest, the store has a large area, with 8-9 floors. You can buy furniture, household appliances, and all kinds of small things that you want to buy at home. Many famous brands have settled in the store, such as Muse, OuPai, Vatti, Boss, Fengchuang Home, Hanston, Jacques, AIA, Silian, Fupinju, Wanjiale, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, etc. There are really too many brands. I can only remember so many. It is a good place to buy products. If you are tired of shopping, you can sit on the sofa and have a rest.
ref: Environment: Honestly, the store is large with 8-9 floors, where you can buy all the furniture, household appliances and small things your home needs, and many famous brands have settled in the store, such as DeRUCCI, OPPEIN, VATTI, Robam, Fengchuang Home, Hunsdon, Yake, AIA, Sealy, Fupinju, GUANGDONG MACRO, Nature, Zoomlion, Midea, Yadan, and so many other brands, I can only remember so many; it is a good place to buy products, and you can sit on the couch and have a rest if you get tired.

src: 最近想买一套舒适的沙发，朋友说这里有好多沙发可以选，看了顾家家居、美克美家的，感觉还可以，就是价格略贵，所以还在纠结中
mt: Recently, I want to buy a set of comfortable sofas. My friend said that there are many sofas to choose from. After reading Gujiaju and Meikemeijia, I feel that they are OK, but the price is slightly expensive, so I'm still struggling
ref: I recently want to buy a couch and my friend said there was a lot of couch to choose from here; I looked at Kuka Home and Markor Furnishings, and I felt they were okay but a little expensive, so I am still struggling to decide.

src: 大众点评乌鲁木齐家居卖场频道为您提供高铁居然之家地址，电话，营业时间等最新商户信息，找装修公司，就上大众点评
